||
atha śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyumāsaṃhitā prārabhyate ||
--- Page 6 ---
śrīgaṇeśāya namaḥ ||
śrīgaurīśaṅkarābhyāṃ namaḥ ||
atha pañcamumāsaṃhitā prārabhyate ||
yo gante suvananī satta guṇavānṣṭhā rajasstasrāśreyassaṃhartāṃ taṃ sāṃvitō guṇavartī māyāmatītya sthitaḥ ||
satyānandamanantabodhamayalaṃ brahmādiśaṃjñālpadaṃ nityaṃ sarvvasamanvayādikagatāṃ pūrṇaṃ śivaṃ bhīmahi || 1 ||
ṛṣaya ūcuḥ ||
sūtasūta mahāprājña vyāsaśiṣya namostu te ||
caturthī koṭikrudākṣyā śrāditā saṃhitā tvayā || 2 ||
athomāsaṃhitāntaṃ svanāryānasaminvitaṣu ||
śṛhi śaṃbhoścaritraṃ ve sāmbhasya paramātmanaḥ || 3 ||
sūta uvāca ||
aharṣayastuonakābhāḥ śṛṇuta prematāḥ śubham ||
śāṅkaraṃ caritaṃ divyaṃ muktimuktipradaṃ param || 4 ||
itīdṛśaṃ puṇyapraśnaṃ pṛṣṭavānmunisat tamaḥ ||
vyāsassanat kumāraṃ vai śaivaṃ saṃcaritaṃ jagau || 5 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
vāsudevāya yatproktatupmanuyumahiṣīṇā ||
tatucyate mayā vyāsa caritaṃ hi maheśithuḥ || 6 ||
purā putrārthayagavṛtakailāsaṃ śaṃkarālayam ||
vasudev śrutaḥ kṛṣṇastapastaptum śivasya hi || 7 ||
atropamanyuṃ saṃdṛṣṭā tapaṃtaṃ śṛṅga uttame ||
praṇamya bhaktyā sa muniḥ paryapṛcchatkṛtāñjiliḥ || 8 ||
śrīkṛṣṇa uvāca ||
upamanyoḥ mahāprājña śaivapravāraṃ saṃstate ||
putrārthagamaṃ taptuṃ taposa giriśasya hi || 9 ||
śruhi śaṃkaramāhātmyaṃ sadānandaraṃ śṛṇe ||
yacchutvā bhaktitaḥ kuryāṃ tapa aiśvarasuttamam || 10 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
iti śrutvā vacastasya vāsudevasya bhīmataḥ ||
pratyuvāca prasanātmā chupamanyu stasmarañchadam || 11 ||
upamanyuḥ uvāca ||
śṛṇu kṛṣṇa mahāśiva mahimānaṃ maheśithuḥ ||
yamdṛkṣamahaṃ śaṃbhomekticardanmumutyam || 12 ||
tapasthoshaṃ samadṛkṣāt śaṃkaraṃ ca tadāyugāt ||
parivāraṃ samastaṃ ca viṣṣādīnamrādikāt || 13 ||
tribhirśaiśśobhāmanasajalaśukhamaṃvyayam ||
ekapadaṃ mahādṛṣṭaṃ saṃjvālakabaletūlaiḥ || 14 ||
dvisahastramyukṣānāṃ jyotiṣāstitivarājitvam ||
savāśrapravārāṃbhāghamanekāśaṃ sahasrapāt || 15 ||
yassaka lpāntasamaye viśvaṃ saṃhārati dhruvam ||
nāvakyo yasya ca ṃvebhilokye sacarācāre || 16 ||
maheśvarabhujotasṛṣṭaṃ trailokkyaṃ sacarācaram ||
nindedāha śrutakutsnaṃ nimaṣādṛnna saṃśayaḥ || 17 ||
tapasthyo rudrapārśvasthaṃ dṛṣṭavānimantam ||
guhyamatraṃ paraṃ cāsya na tulyamikhikaṃ kañcit || 18 ||
yattacchulamiti khyātaṃ savebhlokeṣu śūlitaḥ ||
vijyānimaghamatyugre saveśāstrāṭṭanāśakam || 19 ||
dārayedyanmahīṃ kutsanāṃ śoṣayedyanmahādighim ||
pātayedakhilaṃ jyotiṣkaṃ yanātra saṃśayaḥ || 20 ||
yovānāśo hato yena māṃdhātā sabalaḥ puṣā ||
cakravartī mahātejāstrailokya vijayo nṛpaḥ || 21 ||
dṛptovikno haihayasya niḥśipto lavaṇāsuraḥ ||
śatruguṃ nṛpatīṃ yuddhe samāhūya samantataḥ || 22 ||
tasmindate ya vinaṣṭe tu rudraiste gataṃ tu yat ||
tacchulamiti

--- Page 7 ---
tīkṣṇāgraṃ saṃtrāsajananam mahat || 23 ||
viśikhān bhṛkuṭīṃ kṛtvā tajayantimaiva sthitam ||
vipughāṃ analasaṃkāśaṃ bālasūryamimodditam || 24 ||
sūryaṃ staminindreśtyaṃ pāśahastimavāntakam |
paraśuṃ tīkṣṇadhāraṃ ca sarporvīśa viśṛṅkhitam || 25 ||
kalpāntadahanākāraṃ tathā puruṣavigraham |
yattadrāgavara masya kṣatriyāntakaraṃ raṇe || 26 ||
rāmo yadbalamaśritya śivadattasya vai purā |
triḥsaptakṛtvo na kṣaraṃ daṃdāha dviṣato muniḥ || 27 ||
sudarśanaṃ tathā cakraṃ sahasravadanaṃ viṣṇom ||
dvidsahasrabhujaṃ devamdrāksaṃ puruṣākṛtim || 28 ||
dvidsahasrabāhuṃ dīptaṃ sahasracaraṇākulam |
koṭisūryapratīkāśaṃ trailokyadahana kṣamamāt || 29 ||
vāñjaṃ mahodbhavaṃ tīkṣṇaṃ śataparvaṃ anuttamamā |
mahāghuḥ pinākaṃ ca sātūṇīraṃ mahājutimā || 30 ||
śaktiṃ khaḍgaṃ ca pāśaṃ ca mahādīptaṃ samākuśam |
gadāṃ ca mahataṃ divyāmanvānyānyāṇi dṛṣṭavān || 31 ||
tathā ca lokapālānāmāstrāṇyetāni yāni ca |
adrākṣaṃ tāni sarvāṇi bhagavaddrudarśanataḥ || 32 ||
savyadeśe tu devasya brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ |
vimānaṃ divyamāsthāya iṃsayuktaṃ manomapamam || 33 ||
vāmapārśve tu tasyaiva śaṃkhacakragadāgharaḥ |
vaiteyaṃ samāsthāya tathā nārāyaṇaḥ sthitaḥ || 34 ||
svāyaṃbhuvādyā manavobhṛgvādyā ṛṣayastathā |
śakrādyā devatāścaiva sarve eva samaṃ yayuḥ || 35 ||
skandhaśaktiṃ samādāya mayūrasyassacaṃṭakaḥ |
devyāssamīpe saṃtasthau dvitīya iva pāvakaḥ || 36 ||
nandī śūlaṃ samādāya bhavagne samavasthitaḥ |
sa vaṃśrutaṇagāṇāśceiva mātaro vividhāḥ sthitāḥ || 37 ||
teṣābhivādya maheśānaṃ parivārye samaṃtataḥ |
astuvannvividhaiḥ stotrairmahadeva tadā surāḥ || 38 ||
yatkiṃcitu jagatatyasmindrśyate śrūyatetha vā |
tatsarve bhagavatpārśve nirīkṣyāhaṃ sunirvismitaḥ || 39 ||
sumaheśvaryamālaṃbya prāñjalirvidviṣaiḥ stotaiḥ |
paramānandasaṃmagno kṛṣṇāhardare || 40 ||
sammukhe śaṃkaraṃ dṛṣṭvā bāṣpagadgadayā girā |
apūjayaṃ suviṣayavadahaṃ śraddhāsamānvitaḥ || 41 ||
bhagavānatha suprītaśaṃkaraḥ parameśvaraḥ |
vācyā madhurāyā prītyā māmāha prahasanniva || 42 ||
na vicālayituṃ śakyo mayā vipra punaḥpunaḥ |
parīkṣitosite sadraṃ te bhavānbhaktyanvito dṛḍhaḥ || 43 ||
tasmātte parituṣṭoṣmi varaṃ varayā subrata |
durlabham sarvedeveṣu na deyaṃ vidhyante tava || 44 ||
sa cāhaṃ tadbhavaḥ śrutvā śaṃboḥ satpremaṃyutam |
devaṃ taṃ prāñjalibhūtvānamaṃ bhaktānukampinam || 45 ||
upamanyuruvāca

bhagavanyadittuṣṭoṣi yadi bhaktiḥ sthirā mayi |
tena satyena me jñānaṃ trikālaviṣayaṃ bhavet || 46 ||
prayaccha bhaktiṃ vipulāṃ tvāyi cānyabhicāriṇīm |
sānvayasyāpi nityaṃ me bhūriḥ kṣīrodanaṃ

--- Page 8 ---
bhavet || 47 ||
mamāstu tava sānidhyaṃ nityaṃ caivāśrame vibho ||
tvaṃ bhakteṣu sakhyaṃ syād anyonyeṣu sadā bhavet || 48 ||
evamuktо māyā śaṃbhurvindhasya parameśvaraḥ ||
kṛpādṛṣṭyā nirīkṣyāśu māṃ sa prāha yadūdṛha || 49 ||
śiva uvāca

upamanyо śṛṇu tāta vijñatastvaṃ bhaviṣyasi ||
jarāmaraṇajaiḥ doṣais sarvakāmānvito bhava || 50 ||
munīnāṃ pūjanīyaś ca yaśo'vanasamnvitaḥ ||
śīlarūpaguṇaiśvaryairmatprasādātpadepade || 51 ||
kṣīrodasāgarasya eva sānidhyaṃ payasānidhiḥ ||
tatra te bhavitā nityaṃ yatrayatrecchase śune || 52 ||
amṛtātmakaṃ tattkṣīraṃ yāvatsaṃprāpyate tataḥ ||
imaṃ baivasvataṃ kalpaṃ paśyase bandhubhiḥ saha || 53 ||
tvadbhoktraṃ cākṣyaṃ cāstu matprasādāt sadaiva hi ||
sānidhyamāśrame te'haṃ kariṣyāmi mahāśune || 54 ||
mandrakis sutirasthirā cāstu sadā dāsyāmi darśanaṃ ||
smṛtaśca bhavata vatsa priyastaṃ sarvetha mama || 55 ||
yathākāmasukhāṃ tiṣṭha notkṇṭhāṃ kartumaṃsi ||
sarve prapoṇetāṃ yātu cintitaṃ nātra saṃśayaḥ || 56 ||
upamanyur uvāca

evamuktaḥ sa bhagavān sūryakoṭisamaprabhaḥ ||
mameśāno varāndatvā tatraivaantardhīyata || 57 ||
evaṃ dṛṣṭo mayā kṛṣṇa parivārasam anvitaḥ ||
śaṃkaraḥ parameśāno muktimuktipradāyakaḥ || 58 ||
śaṃbhunā parameśena yaduktaṃ tena dhīmatā ||
tadvāktaṃ ca me sarve devadevasamāhitā || 59 ||
pratyakṣaṃ caiva te jātānāṃgharvoṃpsarastathā ||
ṛṣīṇāṃ vidyādharāṃścaiva paśya siddhānvyavasthitān || 60 ||
paśya vṛkṣānmanoramyān kinnaragandharvanusugandhinaḥ ||
sarvendu kusumaṃ irmṛdun sadā puṣpaphalānvitān || 61 ||
sarve metanmahābāho śaṃkarasya mahātmanaḥ ||
prasādādevadevasy a viśvaṃ bhāvasamanvitam || 62 ||
mamāsti tvikhilaṃ jñānaṃ prasādāccūlapāṇinaḥ ||
bhūtaṃ bhavyaṃ bhaviṣyaṃ ca sarve jānāmi tattvataḥ || 63 ||
tamahāṃ dṛṣṭvāndevamapi devāḥ sureśvarāḥ ||
yaṃ na paśyantynarādhya ko'nyo dhanyataro mayā || 64 ||
ṣaḍviṃśakamitikhyātaṃ paraṃ tattvaṃ sanātanam ||
evaṃ dhyāyintiṃ vidvānso mahat paramam akṣaram || 65 ||
sarve tattvavijñānajñaḥ sarvatattvārthadarśanaḥ ||
sa eva bhagavāndеvaḥ pradhānapuruṣeśvaraḥ || 66 ||
yo nijādikṣiṇātpāśāndṛhṇāṃ lokakāraṇam ||
vāmādyasṛjadiṣṇuṃ lokarakṣārthamīśvaraḥ || 67 ||
kalpānte caiva saṃprāpte'sṛjadūrne hṛdaḥ prabhuḥ ||
tatassam aharat kutastnaṃ jagatsthāvarajaṃgamam || 68 ||
yugānte sarva bhūtāni saṃvatekartvā ivānalaḥ ||
kālo bhūtvā mahādevo'smānastasmin tiṣṭhati || 69 ||
sarvajñas sarvabhūtātmā sarvabhūtabhodṛbhavaḥ ||
āste sarvagatodevo hṛṣyatsarvaiśca devataiḥ || 70 ||
atastvam putralaṃbhāya samārādhaya śaṃkaram ||
śīghraṃ prasanno bhavitā śivasteṃ bhaktavatsalaḥ || 71 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ kṛṣṇopamanyusaṃvāde svagatavṛṇenaṃ nāma prathamо'dhyāyaḥ || || 1 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca

ityākarṇya muner vākyam upamanyormaharmanasaḥ ||
jātabhaktikarme hādeve kṛṣṇaḥ provāca taṃ munim || 1 ||
śrīkṛṣṇa uvāca

upаmanyo

--- Page 9 ---
śune tāta kṛpāṃ kuru mamopaري ||
yeṣe śivaṃ samārādhya kāmānāpuṣka tānvad || 2 ||
sānatkumāra uvāca ||
ityākṛṣṇyopamantus sa muni śaivaroمa mahān ||
kṛṣṇavākyaṃ śuprśasya pratyuvāca kṛpānidhiḥ || 3 ||
upamanyuruvāca ||
yeṃyebhevārāghanataḥ prāpto hṛtkāma kṣa hi ||
tāṃstānsakto npravkṣyāmi śṛṇu tvaṃ vai yadṛdṛha || 4 ||
śarvātsavāmaireśvaryye hiraṇyakaśipuḥ purā ||
vaṣāṇāṃ daśalakṣāṇi so'ḍalabhaṃdreśekharāt || 5 ||
tasyādyaṃ putrāpravaro nandano nāma viśrutaḥ ||
sa ca śarvendra indraṃ vaṣādhutamaghoṃnayat || 6 ||
viṣṇucakraṃ ca tadror vaḍamābhaṇḍalasya ca ||
śīrṇī purāso'bhavatkkṛṣṇa tadṃgeṣu mahāhave || 7 ||
na śastrāṇi vahanty aṃge ghomantasyo dhīmataḥ ||
mahasyātibalaṃsyājau cakravajramukāni api || 8 ||
ardhaprānāśca vibhūṃghā adheṇa subalīyasā ||
devadattavarā jaghuracchurendrāsurānbhūśram || 9 ||
tuṃṭhe vidyutprabhasya api trailokayeśvarātasmādāt ||
śatavaṃrṣaṃsahasṣāṇi savailokiśvaroḥ sampariḥ || 10 ||
tathā putrasahasṣāṇāmabhutaṃ ca ddau śivaḥ ||
mama cāṭucaro nityaṃ abhaviṣyasya abravīdiha || 11 ||
kuśadvīpe śubhaṃ rājyamaddādabhagavānprabhaḥ ||
sa tasmai śaṃkaraḥ prītyaṃ vāsudevaṃ mahṛdghyaiḥ || 12 ||
ghātrā śṛdyaśatamakho daityyo vaṣaśataṃ purā ||
tapaḥ kṛtvā sahasraṃ tu putrāṇāmalamabhravāt || 13 ||
yājñavalkya iti khyāto gīto vedebhur ve muniḥ ||
arādhya sa mahādevaṃ prāptavānajñānuttamamaṃ || 14 ||
vedavyāsastu yo nāmnā prāptavāntulaṃ yaśaḥ ||
so'pi śaṃkaramārādhya trikālajñānamāptavān || 15 ||
indreṇa bāluvidhyāste paribhūtāstu śaṃkarāt ||
lebhire losamhṛtāraṃ garuḍaṃ savaidurjeyeṣu || 16 ||
āpaḥ avanaghāḥ sarvāṃśca pṛthvīropātkapahidvanaḥ ||
sarvai samakrpālena daivairṛddhā pravartitatā || 17 ||
arthemārthyāṃ cānmūyā tṛīṇi vaṃśaśatāni ca ||
muśleṣu nirāhārā kṣudhā śarvāttataḥ stutān || 18 ||
dattanekaṃ dhunī lebhe candraṃ durvālsena tathā ||
gaṃgāṃ pravṛtyāmāsa citrakūṭe prativatā || 19 ||
vikṛṇeṃśca mahādevaṃ tathāmkttasukhāvabhoṣma ||
prasādya mahantī siddhimāptavānabhyusmrdnan || 20 ||
citraseno hṛpaśśobhūṃ prasādya dṛḍhabhaktimān ||
samastanṛpabhītirbhyobhaye prāpātulaṃ ca kamaḥ || 21 ||
śrīkaro gopikāsupravrepūjāvilokana ||
jātamabhikimahādevye parama siddhmāptavāt || 22 ||
citrāṃgado nṛpatutassomantanyāḥ patiḥhare ||
śivādutprahato maṃtro yatunāyaṃ mṛto na hi || 23 ||
sa ca takṣālaṃ gatvā tanmitroṃ prāpya śuvṛtaḥ ||
āśanātaḥ svagṛhaṃ prīto nānadhanasamanvṛtaḥ || 24 ||
sīmintinapriyā tasya somavratāparāyaṇā ||
śivāsubhṛhataḥ kṛṣṇo lebhe saubhāgyauttamamṛ || 25 ||
tatramabhāvadhṛte tāsmajñako dvijastutaḥ purā ||
kiṃcidktāvataṃ gato lobhātkṛtadārākṛtiśchala || 26 ||
caṃcukā puṃścalī duhā gokarṇa dvijataḥ purā ||
śrutā varmekathaṃ

--- Page 10 ---
śambhoḥ bhaktyā prāpa parāṃ gatim || 27 ||
svarayantugṛhītaḥ pāpī bindugо cañcukāpitaḥ ||
śrutvā śivapurāṇaṃ ca sa sadgatiṃ prāpa śāṃkarīm || 28 ||
piṅgalā māṇikā khyātā madrarāḍho dvijāghamaḥ ||
rauvṛṣabhamabhyarcya lebhāte sadgatim ca tau || 29 ||
mahānandābhighā kācicchreṣyā śivapādāratā ||
dṛḍhātpaṇātsuprāsādy śivaṃ lebhe ca sadgatim || 30 ||
kaikeṭhī dvijabālā ca sādarāhā śivaratā ||
paraṃ hi śukhaṃ prāpa śiveśvarantaguṇāṇāt || 31 ||
vimarṣaṇaśca nṛpatiśśivabhaktiṃ vidhāya vai ||
gatim lebhe parāṃ kṛṣṇa śivānugṛhītaḥ purā || 32 ||
durjanaśca nṛpaḥ pāpī bahustrīlpatṭaḥ khalaḥ ||
śivabhaktyā śivaṃ prāpa nirliṃptaḥ sarvakarmmoṣu || 33 ||
saṃkīrṇeśvaraḥ nāmṇā śaṃkarasya śivaratī ||
citābhasmarato bhaktyā lebhe tadgatisuttamām || 34 ||
saumini nāma cāṇḍālī saṃpūjyājñānato hi sā ||
lebhe śaivīṃ gatiṃ kṛṣṇa śaṃkarānugṛhātparāt || 35 ||
mahākālābhigho vyāgho kirātaḥ parihiṃsakaḥ ||
samabhyarcya śivaṃ bhaktyā lebhe sadgatisuttamām || 36 ||
dvavāṃsā munisādṛśāliśśivānugṛhītaḥ purā ||
tastāra svamataṃ loke śivabhaktiṃ vibhuktidāṃ || 37 ||
kauśikaśca samārādhya śaṃkaraṃ lokasaṃkaram ||
brāhmaṇoḍhatrātriyaśca dvitīya iva pūjyaḥ || 38 ||
śivamabhyarcya sadgatyā virañciśśevasattamaḥ ||
abhūtsaṃgaṃkaraḥ kṛṣṇa sarvalokopitāmahaḥ || 39 ||
mārkāṇḍeyo munivaraściraṃjīvī mahāprabhuḥ ||
śivabhaktavarāḥ śrīmāñśivānugṛhīto hare || 40 ||
devendra hi mahāśaivabhrailokya bhubujo purā ||
śivānugṛhītaḥ kṛṣṇa sarvadevādhipaḥ prabhuḥ || 41 ||
bilipūtro mahāśaivaśśivānugṛhīto vaśī ||
bāṇo babhūva brahmāṇḍanāyakastsakaleśvaraḥ || 42 ||
hariśśaktiśca sadgatyā dīrghicaśca maheśvaraḥ ||
śivānugṛhītoḍhadhūrvasttathā rāmo hi śāṃkaraḥ || 43 ||
kāṇādā bhārgavaścevaṃ gurugauṃtama eva ca ||
śivabhaktyā babhūvuste mahāprabha īśvarāḥ || 44 ||
śākalyaśśāṃsitātmā ca navavarṣaśatānyapi ||
bhavamārābhyāyāsaṃ manoyajñena māghavaḥ || 45 ||
tuloṣa bhagavānnāha granthakartā bhaviṣyasi ||
vatsākṣyā ca te kīrtistrailokye prabhaviṣyati || 46 ||
akṣayaṃ ca kulaṃ teḍastu mahiṣibhiraraṃkṛtam ||
bhaviṣyasi ṛṣiśreṣṭha sūtrakartā tatastataḥ || 47 ||
ityevaṃ śaṃkarātprāpa varaṃ munivararstave ||
trailokye vitatāśāsīrpūjyaśca yadunandana || 48 ||
sāvṛṇīriti vikhyātaṃ ṛṣirāsītkṛte yuge ||
idaṃ tena tapastāpaṃ ṣaṣṭivarṣaśatāni ca || 49 ||
tamāha bhagavānrudrassākṣācchughoḍasmi teḍanagha ||
granthakṛcchlokivikhyāto bhavitāsyajanārāmaraḥ || 50 ||
evaṃviṣṇo mahādevaḥ puṇyapuṣpavairāstataḥ ||
samarcitaṃ śubhānkāmānpradāti yathepsitān || 51 ||
ekenaiva mukhena āhaṃ vaktuṃ sagavato guṇāḥ ||
ye santi tān na śaknomi hyapi varṣaśatairapi || 52 ||
iti śrī śivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāsumāsaṃhitāyāṃ sanatkumāravyāsasaṃvāde upamanyupadesho nāma dvitīyoḍhadhyāyaḥ || 2 ||
sānatkumāra uvāca |
evaṃ śrutvā

--- Page 11 ---
vacas tasya so'śravīt mahāśunimṛ ||
vismayaṃ paramaṃ gatvopamanyuṃ śāntamānasam || 1 ||
vāsudeva uvāca ||
dhanyastvamasi vibhrendra kartvāṃ stotuṃ malaṃ kṛtī ||
yasya devādidevastes sāṃbhīṃ kurute śrame || 2 ||
darśanaṃ munisādṛśa dadyāts bhagavāṃścivaḥ ||
api tāvanmamāpyevaṃ prasādaṃ vā karotvayau || 3 ||
upamanyur uvāca ||
aciреṇaiva kālena mahādevaṃ na saṃśayaḥ ||
tasyaiva kṛpayā tvaṃ vai drakṣyase puruṣottama || 4 ||
ṣoḍaśe māsi suvarān prāpyasi tvaṃ maheśvarāt ||
sapatnīkāt kathaṃ no dāsyate devo varāñhare || 5 ||
pūjyosi devatairapi sarvaiḥ chāghonīyassadā guṇaiḥ ||
jāpyaṃ te'haṃ pravakṣyāmi śraddhānāya vācyutam || 6 ||
tena japaprabāveṇa satyaṃ drakṣyasi śaṅkaram ||
ātmatulyabalaṃ putraṃ lapsyasi maheśvarāt || 7 ||
japo namaśśivāyeti mantrarajibhame hare ||
sarvakamarapradaṃ divyaṃ muktimuktipradāyakam || 8 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
evaṃ kathayatastaṃsya mahādevāśritāḥ kathāḥ ||
dinānyadye prayātāni muhūrtāṃ iva tāpasaḥ || 9 ||
navame tu dine prāpto muninā sa ca dīkṣitaḥ ||
mantramavyāpitaṃ śārvamāthavaṃśirасaṃ mahat || 10 ||
jaṭī muṇḍī ca sadyo'sau vabhuva sussamāhitaḥ ||
prādurguṣṭhoddhṛtatanutaste codhvabhujastathā || 11 ||
saṃprāpte ṣoḍaśe māsi santuṣṭaḥ parameśvaraḥ ||
pārvatya sahitaśrāṃbudevo kṛṣṇāya darśanam || 12 ||
pārvatyā sahitaṃ devaṃ trinetraṃ candraśekharam ||
brahmadyairnuyamānaṃ tu pūjitaṃ siddhakoṭibhiḥ || 13 ||
divyamālyāmbaravaran bhaktanairasurāśuraiḥ ||
praṇataṃ ca viśeṣeṇa nānābhūṣaṇabhūṣitam || 14 ||
svāṃśrayamayaṃ kāntaṃ maheśramajamavyayam ||
nānagaṇānvitaṃ tuṣṭaṃ putrābhyāṃ sthutam praśupaṃ || 15 ||
śrīkṛṣṇaḥ prāñjalirhṛṣṭā vismayotphulloccanaḥ ||
īdṛśaṃ śaṃkaraṃ prītaḥ praṇanāma mahotsavaḥ || 16 ||
nānāvidhaiḥ stutipardaivāṃgamayenāsamyattadā ||
sahasranāmnā devaśaṃ tuṣṭāva natakandharaḥ || 17 ||
tato devāssagaṃdharvā vidyādharamahorагāḥ ||
saṃmuttaḥ puṣpavṛṣṭiṃ ca sādhuvādānmanoganāt || 18 ||
pārtyāśamukhaṃ dṛṣṭvā bhagavānbhaktavatsalaḥ ||
uvāca keśavaṃ tuṣṭo rudraśātha vidojasat || 19 ||
mahādeva uvāca ||
kṛṣṇa jānāmi bhaktaṃ tvaṃ miya nityaṃ daḍhavratam ||
vṛṇīṣva tvaṃ varānmattaḥ puṇyātrailokyadhulabhān || 20 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
tasya tadvacanam śrutvā kṛṣṇaḥ prāñjalirādravat ||
prāha sarveśvaraṃ śaṃbhuṃ supraṇamya punaḥ punaḥ || 21 ||
kṛṣṇa uvāca ||
devadeva mahādeva yācedahaṃ śuttamānvarān ||
tvatto'dya prāmitācātha tvayoddyāhān maheśvara || 22 ||
tava dharmo matirnityaṃ yaśaḥcāpracalaṃ mahat ||
tvatsāmīpyaṃ sthirā bhaktistvāyi nityaṃ mamāstviti || 23 ||
putrāṇi ca daśānānaṃ purāṇāṃ mama santu vai ||
vadhyāśca ripavassarvai saṃgrāme baladīptāḥ || 24 ||
apamāno bhavennaiva kichinme śatrutaḥ prabho ||
yoginām api sarveṣāṃ bhaveyamiti

--- Page 12 ---
vaṣṭabhaḥ || 29 ||
ityevaṃ śuvarāndehiḥ devadeva namostatu te ||
sarvaiśvarastvaṃ mevāsiṃ matpraśuṃca viśeṣataḥ || 26 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
tasya tadvacanam śrutvā tamāha bhagavānbhavaḥ ||
sarvaiṃ bhaviṣyatītyevaṃ punaḥsa prāha śūladhṛk || 27 ||
sāṃbo nāma mahāvīryaḥ putaste bhavitā balī ||
ghorasaṃvartakādityaśśāto munibhaireva ca || 28 ||
māṇuṣe bhavitāsīti sa te putro bhaviṣyati ||
yadyaca prārthitaṃ kiñcitatsarvaṃ ca labhasva vai || 29 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca || ||
evaṃ labdhvā varānsarvāñchīkṛṣṇaḥ parameśvarāt ||
nānāvidhābhirbhītimastutiḥbhiḥsaṃ toṣayat || 30 ||
tamāhātha śivā tuṣṭā pārvatī bhaktavatsalā ||
vāsudavaṃ mahātmānaṃ śaṃśubhaktaṃ tapasvinaṃ || 31 || ||
pārvatyuvāca ||
vāsudeva mahābhudhe kṛṣṇa tuṣṭāsmi teṣānaṃca ||
gṛhāṇa matsvā varānmanoñjānsuvi durlabhān || 32 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityākarṇya vacaststastyāḥ pārvatyāsca yadvṛṃhaḥ ||
uvāca suprasannātmā bhaktiyuktena cetasā || 33 || ||
śrīkṛṣṇa uvāca ||
devi tvaṃ paritūṣṭāsi ceddadāsi varānhi me ||
tapasānenā satyena brāhmaṇānprīti māsmabhūt || 34 ||
dvāepaḥ kadāciddhṛṣṭaṃ tu pūjayethaṃ dvijānsadā ||
tuṣṭo ca mātāpitarou bhavetatṃ mama sarvedā || 35 ||
sarvabhūte ṣvāturkūlyaṃ bhajeyaṃ yatra tatragaḥ ||
kule praśūtirucitā mamārtu tava darśanāt || 36 ||
tapeyayaṃ suraindrādīndaivāt yajñaśatena tu ||
yatīnāmitīrthīnāṃ ca sahasrāṇyatha sarvedā || 37 ||
bhojayet sadā gehe śraddhāpūrvaṃ tu bhojanaṃ ||
bāṃghavaiḥsaha prītistu nityamastu sunirvṛtiḥ || 38 ||
devi māryāṃsaha kṣāṇāṃ bhaveyaṃ prāṇavallabhaḥ ||
akṣīṇā kāṃbyatā tāśu prasādāttava śāṃkari || 39 ||
āsāṃ ca pitaro loke bhaveyuḥ satyaṣāddinaḥ ||
ityādhāḥ śuvarā svaṃtu prasādāttava pāvāni || 40 || ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
tasya tadvacanam śrutvā devī taṃ cāha vismimatā ||
evamastīti bhaṃdhe te śāśvatī sarvakāmadā || 41 ||
taismastāṃśca varāndatvā pārvatīparameśvarau ||
tannaivāntaśca daghatuḥ kṛtvā kṛṣṇasya satkṛpām || 42 ||
kṛṣṇaḥ kṛtārthamātmānamamnayat munī śvara ||
upasmanyoḥśunairāśu prāpaśramamatuttamam || 43 ||
praṇamya śirasā tatra ta muniṃ keśihā tataḥ ||
tathā vṛttaṃ ca tasmai tatsasmācaṣṭopamanyave ||44||
sa ca ta prāha koṃnyastasyācchavid vāñjanāhīn ||
mahādānapatirloke koṃdhe vāstīva duḥsadaḥ || 45 ||
jñāne tapasi vā śauryeṃ stheyaṃ vāpamca eva ca||
śṛṇu śaṃbhostu govinda daivaiśvaryaṃ mahāyaśāḥ || 46 ||
tacchrutvā śraddhāyuktoṃsavacaṃśaṃbhostu bhaktimān ||
papraccha śivamāhātmyaṃ sa taṃ prāha munīśvaraḥ || 47 || ||
upaṃmanyuruvāca ||
bhagavāñśaṃkaraḥ pūrvaṃ brahmaloke mahātmanā ||
stuto nāmasahasreṇa daṇḍinā brahmayoginā || 48 ||
sāṃkhyāḥ paṭhanti taddhī

--- Page 13 ---
taṃ vistīrṇaṃ ca nighaṇṭuvat ||
duḥjñānaṃ māṇuṣāṇāṃ tu stotraṃ tatsarvakāmadaṃ || 39 ||
smaraṇītyaṃ śaṃkaraṃ tvaṃ gaccha kṛṣṇa gṛhaṃ sukhi ||
bhaviṣyasi sadā tāt śivabhaktagaṇāmaṇīḥ || 40 ||
ityuktaṃ taṃ namaskṛtya vāsudevo munīśvaram ||
manasā saṃsmaraṃśaṃsuṃ keśavo dvārakāṃ yayau || 41 ||
sanaткumāra uvāca

evaṃ kṛṣṇasamārādhya śaṃkaraṃ lokaśaṃkaram ||
kṛtārthoṃsphunmunīśreṣṭha sarvāṃjeyoṃsabhavattathā || 42 ||
tathā dāśarathi rāmiśśivamārādhya bhaktitaḥ ||
kṛtārthoṃsphunmunīśreṣṭha vijayī sarvotoṃsabhavat || 43 ||
tapastvasāti vipulaṃ purā rāmo girau śune ||
śivāddvuḥśarāṃ cāpaṃ jñānaṃ vai paraṃ tamam || 44 ||
rāvaṇaṃ sagaṇaṃ hatvā setuṃ baddhvāmbasāṃ nidhau ||
sītāṃ prāpya gṛhaṃ yāto bubhuje nikhilāṃ mahīṣu || 45 ||
tathā ca bhāgaṇo rāmo dvārādhya tapasā viṣṇum ||
nirīkṣya duḥkhitaśśivāttaparaṃ kṣatriyeṇa taiṣṭam || 46 ||
tīkṣṇaṃ sa paraśuṃ lebhe nidinddāha ca tena tān ||
jiśstataḥ kṛtavaḥ kṣatrāṃśa prasannātparameśvarāt || 47 ||
ajeyaśśāmārśaiva soḍhyāpi tapasāṃ nidhiḥ ||
liṅgāccanarato nityaṃ daṃśyate siddhacāraṇaiḥ || 48 ||
mahendraparvate rāmaḥ sthitaḥ ratapāsi tiṣṭhati ||
kalpānte punarevāsāvṛṣibhiḥ sthānamevāpyati || 49 ||
asitasya āvṛjaḥ pūrvai pīḍyā kṛtavāṃstapāḥ ||
mūlagrahena viśvasya devalonāma tāpasaḥ || 60 ||
purandarena śāstṛ tu tapasvi yaśa suṃsthirasam ||
adharmye dharmamalaṃbhiṅgamārādhya kāmadaṃ || 61 ||
cākṣuṣasya manoḥ putre vṛgoṣādhuccata mahastthale ||
vasiṣṭhaśāpāddurasamado daṇḍakāraṇye ekaḥ || 62 ||
hṛdaye saṃsmaranbhaktayā praṇavena yutaṃ śivam ||
tasmānmṛtyumukhākāro gaṇo mṛgaśukhoṃsabhavat || 63 ||
ajarāmaratāṃ nītarattīvāṃ śāpaṃ punaśca saḥ ||
śaṃkareṇa kṛtaḥ śrītyā nityaṃ lambhodarātuṃgaḥ || 64 ||
gārgyo madadāu śavāu mokṣaṃ ca śuve durlabham ||
kāmacāri mahākṣetram kālajñānaṃ mahaddimam || 65 ||
catuṣpādaṃ sarasvatyāḥ pāragataṃ ca śāśvataṃ ||
na tulyaṃ ca sahasraṃ tu puṇyānāṃ madadau śivaḥ || 66 ||
vedavyāsaṃ tu yogīndraṃ putraṃ tuṣṭaḥ pīnākadhṛk ||
parāśarāya ca dadau jarāmṛtyuvivarjitam || 67 ||
māṇḍavyaśśaṃkareṇaiva jīvaṃ datvā visarjitaḥ ||
varṣāṇāṃ daśa lakṣāṇi śūlāśāddavaro pataḥ || 68 ||
dariddro brāhmaṇaḥ kaściṃliśisya guraveṃśmani ||
putraṃ tu gālvaṃ yaśca pūrvamāsīddhaśramī || 69 ||
gṛhato vā munīśālāyāṃ bhikṣurāyāti taddṛham ||
bhāryovāca yaḥ kaściđvaiyaṃ nighṇo yataḥ || 70 ||
sa tu vācyo bhavatya ca na daśyanta iti priyaḥ ||
atithirāgatasya api kiṃ dāsyāmi gṛhe vasam || 71 ||
kadācidtithibhiḥ kaścittkṣuttṛṣāśāmatarṣitaḥ ||
tāṣṭuvāca sabhaṭān te kṛtagaśreiti taṃ ca sā || 72 ||
prāha bhaṭo madīyastu sāṃprataṃ na ca daśyate ||
sa ṛṣiṣṭāsuvāciṃcedaṃ jñātvā divyena cakṣuṣā || 73 ||
gṛhasthitaḥ praticchannatenaiva sa mṛto dvijaḥ ||
viśvāmitrābhyanujñātastatpuṇyo gālavastathā || 74 ||
gṛhamāgatya mātuḥsa śrutvā śāpaṃ sudāruṇam ||
ārādhya śaṃkaraṃ

--- Page 14 ---
devaṃ pūjāṃ kṛtvā tu śāṃbhavīm || 75 ||
gṛhādasau viniṣkrāntasaṃsmaraśśaṃkaraṃ hṛdā ||
atha taṃ tanayaṃ dṛṣṭvā pitā taṃ prāha sāśliṣam || 76 ||
mahādeva prasādāc ca kṛtakṛtyosi ma kṛtārthaḥ ||
dhanavān putravān śiva mṛtosi jīvitaḥ punaḥ || 77 ||
iti vaḥ kathitamareṣo nāhaṃ śaktaḥ samāsato vyāsāt ||
vaktuṃ śaṃbhoś ca guṇāśśeṣasyāpi na sukhāni syuḥ || 78 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ kṛṣṇādiśivabhaktoddhāraṇaśivamāhātmyavarṇanaṃ nāma tṛtīyosi dhyāyaḥ || 3 ||
munaya ūcuḥ |
tātātāt mahābhāga dhanyastvaṃ hi mahāmate ||
adbhuteyaṃ kathā śaṃbhoḥ śrāvitā paramoktidā || 1 ||
punarhi kathāṃ śaṃbhorvyāsapraśnānusārataḥ ||
sarvaijñatvaṃ vyāsasiṣyaḥ śivatattvavivakṣaṇaḥ || 2 ||
sūta uvāca |
evaṃ eva guroryāsaḥ pṛṣṭavān so 'jaṃ saṃvam ||
sanatkumāraṃ sarvajñaṃ śivabhaktaṃ munīśvaram || 3 ||
vyāsa uvāca |
sanatkumāra sarvajña śrāviteyaṃ śubhā kathā ||
śaṃkarasya maheśasya nānālīlāvibhāriṇaḥ || 4 ||
punarhi mahādevamahimānaṃ viśeṣataḥ ||
śraddhā ca mahatī śrotuṃ mama tāta pravartate || 5 ||
mahimā yena śaṃbhostu ye ye loke vimohitāḥ ||
māyayā jñānamāhṛtya nānālīlāvibhāriṇaḥ || 6 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca |
śṛṇu vyāsa mahābuddhe śāṃkarīṃ sukhāṃ kathām ||
yasyāḥ śravaṇamātreṇa śive bhaktiḥ prajāyate || 7 ||
śivasvarvai śvaro devassarvātmā sarvadaśanaḥ ||
mahimā tasya sarvaihi vyātaṃ ca sakalaṃ jagat || 8 ||
śivasvayai va parā mūrtirbrahmāviṣṇvaiśvarātmikā ||
sarveṣūtātmabhūtāśyā liṃgāliṃgarūpiṇī || 9 ||
devānāṃ yonayaścāgre mānuṣī navamī ca yā ||
tiraścāṃ yonayaḥ pañca bhavantye vaṃ caturdaśa || 10 ||
bhūtā vā vartamānā vā bhaviṣyāścaiva sarvataḥ ||
śivātsarvaiṃ pravartate līyante vṛddhimāgatāḥ || 11 ||
brahmendropa indrachandrāṇāṃ devadānavabhoginām ||
gaṃdharvāṇāṃ manuṣyāṇāmanyeṣāṃ vāpi sarvataḥ || 12 ||
bandhumitramathācāryoṃ rakṣetāḥ thaivā ṃ nyaguruḥ ||
kalpaṭṭumos tha vā bhrātā pitā mātā śivo mataḥ || 13 ||
śivasarvamayaḥ puṃsāṃ svayaṃ vedyaḥ parātparaḥ ||
vaktuṃ na śakyate yasya paraṃ cānuparam ca yat || 14 ||
tanmāyā paramā divyā sarvatra vyāpinī śune ||
taddhīnaṃ jagatsarvaṃ sadevāsuramānuṣam || 15 ||
kāmena svasahāyena pravalenamanojavā ||
sarvaiḥ praghiṃsitovīro viṣṇvādiprabalo 'pi hi || 16 ||
śivamāyāprabhāveṇāpubhūdariḥ kāmamohitaḥ ||
parstrīghaṣaṇaṃ cakre bahuvāraṃ munīśvara || 17 ||
indraścivaśapo bhūtvā gautamastrivimohitaḥ ||
pāpaṃ cakāra duṣṭātmā śāpaṃ prāpa munestadā || 18 ||
pāvako 'pi jagacchettho mohitaśśivamāyayā ||
kāmādhīnaḥ kṛto gatvā tattenai va corttutaḥ || 19 ||
jagatprāṇo 'pi garvena mohitaśśivamāyayā ||
kāmena nijito vyāsa cakre 'nyastrīrati purā || 20 ||
caṇḍaraśmistu mātaṇḍo mohitaśśivamāyayā ||
kāmākulobadhvāśu dṛṣṭārhī hayarūpapṛthak || 21 ||
candrasca mohitaśśaṃbhomāyayā kā

--- Page 15 ---
masaṅkulaḥ ||
gurur api jahāra atha yutastenaiva coddhṛtaḥ || 22 ||
pūrve tu mitrāvaruṇau corе tapasi saṃsthitau ||
mohitau tāvapi śunī śivamāyāvimohitau || 23 ||
urvāśī taruṇī dṛṣṭā caskambho'bho babhūvatuḥ ||
mitraḥ kumbhe jahau reto varuṇo'pi tathā jale || 24 ||
tataḥ kumbhātsamutpanno vasiṣṭho mitrasaṃbhavaḥ ||
agastyo varuṇājāto vaḍavāgnisambhūtaḥ || 25 ||
dakṣasya mohitaśaṃbhumāyayā brahmaṇaskṛtaḥ ||
sāvitrimasya bhaginīṃ vai moktukāmo'bhavat purā || 26 ||
brahmā ca bahuvāraṃ hi mohitaḥ śivamāyayā ||
abhavadroktukāmaśca svakṛtatāyāṃ parāstu ca || 27 ||
cyavano'pi mahāyogī mohitaḥ śivamāyayā ||
sukanyayā vijahre sa kāmāsakto babhūva ha || 28 ||
kaśyapaḥ śivamāyāto mohitaḥ kāmasaṅkulaḥ ||
yayāce kanyakāṃ mohāddhanvano nṛpateḥ purā || 29 ||
garuḍaḥ śāṇḍilkī kanyāṃ netukāmarasumohitaḥ ||
vijñātastu tayā saṃgho dagdhapakṣo babhūva ha || 30 ||
vibhāṇḍako munir nārī dṛṣṭā kāmavaśaṃ gataḥ ||
ṛkṣyaśṛṅgasutastarasya mṛgyāṃ jātaḥ śivājñayā || 31 ||
gautamasya muniśaśāmomāyāmohitamān asaḥ ||
dṛṣṭvā śāradvatīṃ nagrāṃ rarāma śubhitastayā || 32 ||
retaḥ skandhaṃ dadhāra svaṃ droṇyāṃ caiva sa tapasaḥ ||
tasmāt kalaśājāto droṇaśastrabhṛtāṃ varaḥ || 33 ||
parāśaro mahāyogī mohitaḥ śivamāyayā ||
matsyodaryāṃ ca cikrīḍe kumāryāṃ dāśakanyayā || 34 ||
viśvāmitro babhūvātha mohitaḥ śivamāyayā ||
reme menakayā vyāsavane kāmavaśaṃ gataḥ || 35 ||
visiṣṭena virogeṇa tu kṛtvā brahmaghcetanaḥ ||
punaḥ śivaprasādācca brāhmaṇo'bhūtasa eva vai || 36 ||
rāvaṇo vaiśravāḥ kāmī babhūva śivamāyayā ||
sītāṃ jahre kṣubudhistu mohito mṛtyumāpa ca || 37 ||
bṛhaspatiścinvaro mohitaḥ śivamāyayā ||
sāvṛpatnyā vaśī reme bhardvājastato'bhavat || 38 ||
iti māyāprabhāvo hi śaṅkarasya mahātmanaḥ ||
viṣṇi taste mayā vyāsa kimanyan chrottumicchasi || 39 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe paṃcamyākhumāsaṃhitāyāṃ śivamāyāprabhāvavarṇanaṃ nāma caturtho'dhyāyaḥ || 4 ||
व्यास उवाच

ye pāpaniratā jīvā mahānarkahetavaḥ ||
bhagavāṃstānsamācakṣva brahmaputra namo'stu te || 1 ||
सनत्कुमार उवाच

ye pāpaniratā jīvā mahānarkahetavaḥ ||
te samāsena kathyante sāvaghānatayā śṛṇu || 2 ||
parastīdravyasaṃkalpaścetasānidhicintanam ||
akāryābhiniveśaśca caturdhaṃ karma mānasam || 3 ||
avibaddhapralāpavamasyatyaṃ cāpriyaṃ ca yat ||
parokṣataśca paiśunyaṃ caturdhaṃ karma vācikam || 4 ||
abhakṣyabhakṣaṇaṃ hiṃsā mithyākāryāniveśanam ||
parasvānāhupādānaṃ caturdhaṃ karma kāyikam || 5 ||
ityetadādaśavidghaṃ karma proktaṃ vināśaghnam ||
asya bhedānu navaikṣye yeṣāṃ phalamananatakaṃ || 6 ||
ye dviṣanti mahādevaṃ saṃsārāṇavaṃ tārakaṃ ||
sumahatpātakaṃ teṣāṃ nirayāṇvagāminām || 7 ||
ye śivajñānav

--- Page 16 ---
kāraṃ nindanti ca tapasvanaṃ ||
gurun pitṝn atho nmattās te yānti narakān ivaṃ || 8 ||
śivanindā guronindā śivajñānasya dūṣaṇam ||
devadravyāpaharaṇaṃ dvijadravyavinā śanam || 9 ||
harati ye ca saṃsthāśiśvajñānasya pustakam ||
mahāti pātakānyāhurananta phaladāni ṣaṭ || 10 ||
nābhinandati ye dṛṣṭvā śivapūjāṃ prakalpitām ||
na namanti cittaṃ dṛṣṭvā śivaliṅgaṃ stuvanti na || 11 ||
yathteṣṭaceṣṭā niśśaṅkās sthitāḥ ramanti ca ||
upacāravinikṛtāśiśvāgre gurusānnidhyau || 12 ||
sthānasaṃskārapūjāṃ ca ye na kurvanti parveṣu ||
vividhacchā gurūṇāṃ ca karmaṇyogavyavasthitāḥ || 13 ||
ye tyajanti śivācāraṃ śivabhaktān dviṣanti ca ||
asaṃpūjya śivajñānaṃ ye adhīyate likhanti ca || 14 ||
anyāyataḥ prayacchanti śṛṇvantyucārayanti ca ||
vikrīḍanti ca lobhena kuñjñānaniyamena ca || 15 ||
asaṃskṛtapradeśeṣu yathecṣṭaṃ svāpayanti ca ||
śivajñānakathāśśaṃkepam yaḥ kurvantyatrapāpate || 16 ||
na bravīti ca yaḥ satyaṃ na pradānaṃ karoti ca ||
aśucivān aśucisthāne yaḥ pravikṣi śṛṇoti cā ||
¹ agurupūjām kurvan eva yaśśāstraṃ śrotum icchati ||
na karoti ca śuśrūṣāṃ māṃ ca bhaktibhāvataḥ || 18 ||
nābhinandati tadavākyasuttaraṃ ca prayacchati ||
gurukarmāṇyasāghyaṃ yattendupeṣāṃ karoti ca || 19 ||
gurumāntaṃ śaktiṃ ca videśaṃ praṣṭhitaṃ tathā ||
vairibhiḥ pariṣṭutaṃ vā yaḥ santyajati pāpakṛt || 20 ||
tadgrāhyāputramitrēṣu yaśśāvaṣṇāṃ karoti ca ||
evaṃ surācakastyāpi gurodhan māntadarśinaḥ || 21 ||
etāni khalu sarvāṇi karmāṇi munisattama ||
su mahatpātakānyāhuśśivanindāsmāni ca || 22 ||
brahmaśca surāpaśca stenī ca gurutalpagaḥ ||
mahāpātakinaste te tatsamyogī ca pañcamaḥ || 23 ||
krodhālobhā bhrayādveṣādbrāhmaṇasya vadhe tu yaḥ ||
marmitakaṃ mahādoṣayuktā sa brahmahā bhavat || 24 ||
brāhmaṇaṃ yaḥ samāhūya datvā yaśāddāti ca ||
nindaiṣaṃ dūṣayet tu sa naro brahmahā bhavet || 25 ||
yaśca vidyābhimānena ni steja yati kujijam ||
udāsīnāṃ sabhāmadhye brahmahā sa prakīrtitaḥ || 26 ||
mithyāguṇaiṃ ātmānaṃ nayatyukta kṣetān balāt ||
guṇānīva nirudhāsya sa ca vai brahmahā bhavet || 27 ||
gavāṃ vṛṣābhitrūtānāṃ dvijānāṃ gurupuṣṭakam ||
yasmāccarate vignaṃ tamāhurbrahmabhāgatakam || 28 ||
devidvijajagvān bhūmin pradattāṃ harate tu yaḥ ||
praṇaṭhāmapi kālena tamāhurbrahmabhāgatakam || 29 ||
devidvijasvadharaṇamanyāyenājitaṃ tu yat ||
brahmahātyāsamaṃ jñeyaṃ pātakaṃ nātra saṃśayaḥ || 30 ||
aḍhīty yo dvijo vedaṃ brahmajñānaṃ śivātmakam ||
yadi tyajati yo mūḍhaḥ surāpānasya tatsamam || 31 ||
yat kiñcid api vrataṃ gṛhya niyamaṃ yajanaṃ tathā ||
santyāgaḥ pañcayajñānāṃ surāpānasya tatsamam || 32 ||
pitṛmātṛparityāgaḥ kūṭasākṣyaṃ dvijānṛtam ||
āmiṣaṃ śivabhaktānāmabhakṣyasya ca

¹ lyabāpēḥ |
--- Page 17 ---
makṣaṇam || 32 ||
vane niraparaghānāṃ prāṇināṃ cāpaghātanam ||
dvijārthe prakṣipetsādhuneṃ dharmārthe niyojayet || 33 ||
gavāṃ mārgaṃ vane grāme yaiśvāgniḥ pradīyate ||
iti pāpāni ghorāṇi brahmahatyāsamāni ca || 35 ||
dīnasarvasvaharaṇaṃ narastrīgajavājināṃ ||
gobhūrajatavastrāṇāmī ṣadhīnāṃ rasasya ca || 36 ||
candanāgarukaṣṭūrīpaṭṭavāsasām ||
vikrayastvavipatto yaḥ kṛto jñānād dvijātibhiḥ || 37 ||
hastainyasāpaharaṇaṃ rūkmasateyasaṃ smṛtam ||
kanyānāṃ varayogyānāmadānaṃ sahasre vare || 38 ||
putramitrakalatraṣu gamanaṃ bhaginīṣu ca ||
kumārisāhasaṃ ghoramadhyapakṣīniṣevaṇam || 39 ||
svarṇādyāśca gamanaṃ gurubhāryāyośasaṃ smṛtam ||
mahāpāpāni coktāni śṛṇu tvamupapātakam || 40 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāsumāsaṃhitāyāṃ mahāpātakavaṃrṇanaṃ nāma pañcamādhyāyaḥ || 5 ||

||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
dvijabrahyāpaharaṇamapi dāyaṃyatikramaḥ ||
atimānośitikopasca dāmbhikattvaṃ kṛtaṃbhata || 1 ||
atyantaviṣayāsaktiḥ kārpaṇyaṃ sādhumatsaram ||
paradārābhigamanaṃ sādhukanyāṣu dūṣaṇam || 2 ||
parivittiḥ parivettā ca yayā ca parividhyate ||
tayodānaṃ ca kanyāyastayoreva ca yājanam || 3 ||
śivāśramatarūṇāṃ ca puṣpārāmavināśanam ||
yaḥ pīḍāmāśramasthānāmācarediṣpakāmapi || 4 ||
sabhṛtyaparivārasya paśughānyaghanasya ca ||
kupyaghānyapa śusteyamapāṃ vyāpāvanaṃ tathā || 5 ||
yajñārāmataḍāgānāṃ dārānpatysya vikrayam ||
tīrthayātrāpavāsānāṃ vratopenayakarmṇām || 6 ||
strīghanānyupajīvinaḥ strībhiratyantanijajīnātāḥ ||
arakṣaṇaṃ ca nārīṇāṃ māyayā strīniṣevaṇam || 7 ||
kālāngatāpradānaṃ ca dhānyavṛkṣopaṣevanam ||
nindītāśca ghanādānaṃ paṇyānāṃ kūṭajīvanam || 8 ||
viṣamāryapajrāṇāṃ satataṃ vṛṣavāhanam ||
utsāṭanābhicāraṃ ca ghānyādānaṃ bhiṣakkrayā || 9 ||
jihvākāmopabhogārthe yastyāraṃbhaḥ sukarmaṃśu ||
mūlena hyāpako nityaṃ vedajñānādikaṃ ca yataṃ || 10 ||
grāhyādivratasyāgaśvānyācārinishevaṇam ||
asacchātrādigamanam śuṣkatarkāvalambanaṃ || 11 ||
devāgnigurusādhuṇāṃ nindyā brāhmaṇasya ca ||
pratyakṣaṃ vā parokṣaṃ vā rājñāṃ maṇḍalinām api || 12 ||
utsannāpitṛdevejaṃyā svakarmātyāginasca ye ||
duḥśīlā nāstikāḥ pāpāssadā vā asatyavādinaḥ || 13 ||
parvaṃkāle divā vāpsu viyo naivau paśuyoniṣu ||
rajasvalaāyonau ca maithūnaṃ yaḥ samācaret || 14 ||
strīpuruṣasaṃprāpte āśāṃ cchedakrayāśca ye ||
janasyāpriyavaktāraḥ krūrasamayavedinañḥ || 15 ||
bhetā taḍāṃgakūpānāṃ saṃkrayāṇāṃ rasasya ca ||
ekapakttisthānānaṃ ca pākamedaṃ karoti yaḥ || 16 ||
ityeteḥ strīnarāḥ pāpairupapātakinaḥ smṛtāḥ ||
yuktā yibhiratathānyeṣpi śṛṇu tāṃstu bravīmi te || 17 ||
ye gobrāhmaṇakanyānāṃ svāmimitratapasvinām ||
vināśayanti

--- Page 18 ---
kāryāṇi te narā nārakāḥ smṛtāḥ || 18 ||
parabhriyābhitapyante ye paradravyasūcakāḥ ||
paradravyaharā nityaṃ taulamithyātusārakāḥ || 19 ||
dvijadुḥkhakharā ye ca prahāraṃ codharanti ye ||
sevante tu dvijāśūdrāṃ surāṃ badhanti kāmataḥ || 20 ||
ye pāpiniratasāḥ krūrāḥ ye'pi hiṃsāpriyā narāḥ ||
vṛttyarthe ye'pi kurvanti dānayajñādikāḥ kriyāḥ || 21 ||
goṣṭhābhijalarasyāsu tarucchāyānageṣu ca ||
tyajanti ye purīṣāṇyāvarāmāyataneṣu ca || 22 ||
lañjāśramaprasādeṣu madyapānarataśca ye ||
kūṭakēlibhujaṅgāśca raṃbhānveṣaṇatatparāḥ || 23 ||
vaṃśeṣṭakāśilākāṣṭhaiḥ śūlaiḥ śaṅkubhireva ca ||
ye mārgamatuṃ dhanti parasīmāṃ haranti ye || 24 ||
kūṭaśāsanakartāraḥ kūṭakarmakriyāratāḥ ||
kūṭapākānravajñānāṃ kūṭasaṃvyavahāriṇaḥ || 25 ||
ghanuṣaḥ śastraśalyānāṃ kartā yaḥ krayavikrayī ||
nirdayostīva bhṛtyeṣu paśūnāṃ damanaśca yaḥ || 26 ||
mithyā pravadato vāca ākarṇayati yaśśanaiḥ ||
svāmimitragurūdrohi māyāvī capalaśṭhaḥ || 27 ||
ye māyāputramittrāṇi bālavṛddkakṣatūrān ||
ghātyantitihibaṃdhūṃśca tyaktkāśnanti bubhukṣitān || 28 ||
yaḥ svayam iṣṭamaśnāti viprebhyo na prayacchati ||
vṛthāpākasas vijñeyo brahmaviduṣu garuhītas || 29 ||
niyamāns svayamādāya ye tyajantyajitetindriyāḥ ||
pravrajyāvāsitā ye ca harastyasya prabhedakāḥ || 30 ||
ye tāḍayanti gāṃ krūrā damyante ṣuḍhuṣuḍhuḥ ||
durbelānye na puṣṇanti satataṃ ye tyajanti ca || 31 ||
pīḍayanti tyatibhāreṇāsahaṃtaṃ vāhayanti ca ||
yojayannakṛtāhārān vismṛcaṃti saṃyatān || 32 ||
ye bhārakṣatrogātān gorvṛṣāṃśca kṣudhāturān ||
na pālayanti yatlena goghāste nārakāssmṛtāḥ || 33 ||
vṛṣāṇāṃ vṛṣaṇānye ca pāpiṣṭhā gālayanti ca ||
vāhayanti ca gāṃ vandhyāṃ mahānārakino narāḥ || 34 ||
āśayā samanu prāptān kṣuttṛṣṇāśramakiśīntān ||
atithīṃśca tathānāthān svatantrān gṛhamāgatān || 35 ||
agnibhilāṣāndīnānvā bālavṛddhakṣatūrān ||
nānukaṃpanti ye mūḍhāste yānti narakārṇavam || 36 ||
gṛheṣvathā nivatento smaśānādiṣu bāṃgaevāḥ ||
sukṛtaṃ duṣkṛtaṃ caiva gacchaṃtamanugacchaṃti || 37 ||
ajāviko māhiṣakasāmandro vṛṣalīpatiḥ ||
śūdravaktranavṛttiśca nārakī syāt dvijāghāmaḥ || 38 ||
śilpanaḥ kārvovo vaidyā hemakārāśca nṛpabhajāḥ abhṛtakāḥ kṛtasaṃyuktāḥ sarve te nārakāḥ smṛtāḥ || 39 ||
yaśścitamatikramya svecchayaivāharenkarmā ||
narake pacyate so'pi yo'pi daṇḍarucinerāḥ || 40 ||
utkoce rucikrītes taskṛtaiśca prapīḍyate ||
yasya rājñaḥ prajā rāṣṭre pacyante nareṣu saḥ || 41 ||
ye dvijāḥ parigṛhṇanti nṛpasya anyāyavartanaḥ te prayānti tu coreṣu nareṣu na saṃśayaḥ || 42 ||
anyāyātsatṣupādāya dvijebhyo yaḥ prayacchati ||
prajābhyaḥ pacyate so'pi nareṣu nṛpo yathā || 43 ||
pāradārikacaurāṇāṃ caṃḍānāṃ vidyate tvaghaṃ ||
par

--- Page 19 ---
dārratasmyāpi rājño bhavati nityaśaḥ || 44 ||
acaureṃ cauravat paśyecchoreṃ vācaureṃ rūpiṇam ||
avicārye nṛpas tasmād dātayaṇarakaṃ vrajet || 45 ||
ghṛta tailābhrapānāti madhumāṃsasurāsavam ||
guḍekṣuśākadugdhāni dīrghamūlaphalāni ca || 46 ||
tṛṇaṃ kāṣṭha patrapu ṣpamauṣadhaṃ cātmobhojanaṃ ||
upānacchatra śakaṭa māsanaṃ ca kamaṇḍalum || 47 ||
tāmrasīsatrapuḥ śaṅkhaṃ śaṅkhādyaṃ ca jalodbhavam ||
vaidyaṃ ca vaiṇavaṃ cānyad dvyaṣṭopakaraṇāni ca || 48 ||
auṇṇakāpāsakauśeyapaṭṭasūtrodbhavāni ca ||
sthūlasūkṣmāṇi vastrāṇi ye lobhāc ca haranti ca || 49 ||
evamādīni cānyāni dravyāṇi vividhāni ca ||
nareṣu dhruvam yānti cāpahrtyālpakāni ca || 50 ||
tad yad vā paradravyam api sarṣapamātrakam ||
apahrtyā narā yānti narakaṃ nātra saṃśayaḥ || 51 ||
evamādairnṛpaiḥ pāpe rtkāntasamanantaram ||
śarīrayātnāthāya sarvākāramavāśuyāt || 52 ||
yamaloke vrajantyete śarīreṇa yamājñayā ||
yasdūtaiḥ saha ghorairnityaniyamānasthitaḥ ||
sthitāḥ || 53 ||
devatīrthairmanurṣyāṇām aghaṃ nirātmanām ||
dharmarājaḥ smṛtaśśāstā sudhorerivividhaiḥ || 54 ||
niyamācāracyutānāṃ pramādārarakhalitātmanām ||
prāyaścitteṣu śāstā na budhairjñāyate yamaḥ || 55 ||
pāradārikacaurāṇāmanvāyavyavahāriṇām ||
nṛpatiśśāsakaḥ proktaḥ pracchannānāṃ sa dharmarāṭ || 56 ||
tasmātkṛtasya pāpasya prāyaścittaṃ samācaret ||
nābhyuktasyānyathā nāśaḥ kalpakotiśatairapi || 57 ||
yaḥ karoti svayaṃ karma kāryecchālumodayet ||
kāyena manasā vācā tasya pāpagatiḥ phalam || 58 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe paścamyāhumāsaṃhitāyāṃ pāpasevadvarṇanaṃ nāma ṣaṣṭho'dhyāyaḥ || 6 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca |
atha pāpenerā yānti yamaloke caturbhiḥ ||
saṃsārajananāṃ ghoraṃ vivvaśāsvaidehinaḥ || 1 ||
garbhesthejotyamāneśca bāleḥ taruṇamadhyamaiḥ ||
strīpuṃpuṃsaiḥ kairjinairjñātavyaṃ sarvajantuṣu || 2 ||
śubhāśubhaphalaṃ cātra dehinām saṃvicāryate ||
citraguptyādinirjasaiḥ vai vāsiṣṭhapratubhaiḥ tathā || 3 ||
na kecit prāṇinas santi ye na yānti yamaṃ kṣayam ||
avaśyaṃ hi kṛtaṃ karma bhoktavyaṃ tadd icchā'pyetām || 4 ||
tatra ye śubhakarmāṇas somyacittā dayāvitāḥ ||
te narā yānti saumyena pūrveṃ yamaniketanam || 5 ||
ye punaḥ pāpakarmāṇaḥ pāpā dānavivarjitāḥ ||
te ghoreṇa pathā yānti dakṣiṇena yamālayam || 6 ||
ṣaḍaśītisahasrāṇi yojanānāmātītya tat ||
vaivasvataṃ puraṃ jñeyaṃ nānārūpamavāsthitam || 7 ||
sambhūpasthimevābhāti narāṇāṃ puṇyakarmāṇām ||
pāpinām atidūrasthaṃ yathā raudrena gacchatām || 8 ||
tīkṣṇakaṇṭakayuktena śarkarāvicitena ca ||
kṣurādhārānibhais tīkṣṇaiḥ pāṣāṇai racitena ca || 9 ||
kvacitpańkena mahatā ukrāṇaiḥ ca pātakaiḥ ||
lohaśūcīnibhair daṃśaiḥ sampannena pathā kvacit || 10 ||
--- Page 20 ---
taṭaprāyātiviṣamaiḥ parvvatairvṛkṣasaṅkulaiḥ ||
pratatsāṅgārayuktena yānti mārggeṇa duḥkhitāḥ || 11 ||
kaścidviṣamagartaiśca kaścicchīṭasuduṣkaraiḥ ||
śrutatvāḷukābhiśca tathā tīkṣṇaiśca śaṅkubhiḥ || 12 ||
anekāśākhāvitattebyāṃ vaṃśarvvanaiḥ kvacit ||
kaṣṭena tamasā mārge nānālamben kvacit || 13 ||
ayaḥśṛṅgāṭakaiḥ stīkṣṇaiḥ kvacidadhāmnā punaḥ ||
kvacittaśilābhiśca kvaciddhyātaṃ himena ca || 14 ||
kvacidḍāḷukayā vyāptamakṭhāntaḥpraveśayā ||
kvacidḍaṃbunā vyāptaṃ kvicca kiraṣāgninā || 15 ||
kvāciccīndairvṛkairvyo'gnaimaśakaiśca sudāruṇaiḥ ||
kvācinmahājalaukābhiḥ kvicñājagares tathā || 16 ||
makṣikābhiśca raudrābhiḥ kvicatsarpairvviṣolbvaṇaiḥ ||
mattamātaṅgayūthaiśca balonmattaiḥ pramāthibhiḥ || 17 ||
panthānaṃbuḍiviḍhiśca śūkarais tīkṣṇadaṃṣṭibhiḥ ||
tīkṣṇaśṛṅgaiśca mahiṣaissarvvabhūtaiḥ śyāpadaiḥ || 18 ||
ḍākinībhiśca raudrābhirvikārālaiśca rākṣasaiḥ ||
vyāḍhibhiśca mahācoraiḥ pīḍyamānā vrajanti hi || 19 ||
mahāgūḍilivimiśreṇa mahācaṇḍena vāyunā |
mahāpāṣāṇavarṣeṇa hvanyamānā nirāśrayāḥ || 20 ||
kvāccidyutrapātena dahyamānā vrajanti ca |
mahatā vāṇavarṣeṇa vidhyamānāśca sarvvataḥ || 21 ||
patidviveṣapātaiśca ulkāpātaiśca dāruṇaiḥ |
pradīptāṅgāravarṣeṇa dahyamānāśca santi hi || 22 ||
mahatā pāṃśuvarṣeṇa pūryamāṇā rudanti ca |
mahāmeghavaraiścoraiśca syante ca śuḍuḍuḍuḥ || 23 ||
niśitāyudhavarṣeṇa bhidyamānāśca sarvvataḥ ||
mahāśārāṃbupārābhissacyamānā vrajanti ca || 24 ||
mahāśītenā marutā rūkṣeṇa paruṣeṇa ca ||
samantāḍādhyamānāśca śuṣyante saṅkucanti ca || 25 ||
itthaṃ mārggeṇa raudreṇa pathyarahitena ca ||
nirālambena durggeṇa nirjjalena samantataḥ || 26 ||
viṣameṇaiva mahatā nirjanāpāśrayeṇa ca ||
tamaskleśena kaṣṭena sarvvadugdhāśrayeṇa ca || 27 ||
nīyante dehinassarve ye mūḍhāḥ pāpakārmiṇaḥ ||
yamdūtairma hāghoraistad ajñākāribhirbalāt || 28 ||
ekākinaḥ parādhīnā mitrabandhuvivarjjitāḥ ||
śocantasvāni karmāṇi rudantaśca śuḍuḍuḥ || 29 ||
pretā bhūtvā vivikṣāśca śuṣkkkaṇṭhauṣṭatālukāḥ ||
asomyā bhavatītāśca dahyamānāḥ kṣudhānvitāḥ || 30 ||
baddhāśṛṅkhalayā keciduttānapādakā narāḥ ||
kṛṣyante kṛṣyamāṇāśca yamdūtairbālotkaṭaiḥ || 31 ||
urasoghomukhaśvānye vṛṣyamāṇāstu duḥkhitāḥ ||
keśapāśanibanddhena saṃkṛṣyante ca rajjunā || 32 ||
laḷāṭe cāṅkuśenānye bhinā duṣyanti dehnaḥ ||
uttānāḥ kaṇṭakapatḥā kvicidaṅgāravartmanā || 33 ||
paścādāhunibaddhāśca jaṭhareṇa prapīḍitāḥ ||
pṛthitāśṛṅkhalābhiśca hastayoḥ sukīlitāḥ || 34 ||
grīvāpāśena kṛṣyante prayāntyanye suduḥkhitāḥ ||
jihvāṅkuśapraveśena rajjvāṅkuṣyant eva te || 35 ||
nāsābhedena ruvā ca tvāṅkuṣyante tathāpare ||
bhinṇāḥ kapōlayo rajjvāṅkṛṣyanteoye tathoṣṭayoḥ || 36 ||
chinnāmapādahasttāśca chinna-

--- Page 21 ---
karṇoṣṭhanāsikāḥ ||
sañchinnāśiśnavṛṣaṇāḥ chinnabhinnāṅgasaṃghayaḥ || 37 ||
ābhidyamānāḥ kuṇṭaiśca bhindhyamānāśca sāyakaiḥ ||
itaścetaśca dhāvantaḥ krandamānā nirāśrayāḥ || 38 ||
mudrairlohadaṇḍaiśca hanyamānāḥ suduḥkhitāḥ ||
kaṇṭakairvividhaiścaivorjvalitanarkasampramaiḥ || 39 ||
bhindhyapālaividhimibhindhyante kvevantaḥ pūyaśoṇitam ||
śaktākukimidagdhāśca nīyante vivaśā narāḥ || 40 ||
yācamānāśca salilamantaṃ vāpi bubhukṣitāḥ ||
chāyāṃ prārthayamānāśca śītārtiśānalaṃ punaḥ || 41 ||
dānāhīnāḥ prayāntyevaṃ prārthayantaḥ sukhaṃ narāḥ ||
gṛhītadānapathaiyāḥ sukhaṃ yānti yamālayam || 42 ||
evaṃ nyāyena kaṣṭena prāptāḥ pretapuraṃ yadā ||
prajñāpitāstato dūtairniviśyante yamāgrataḥ || 43 ||
tatra ye śubhakarmāṇastāṃstu samnānayedyamaḥ ||
svāgatāsandānenā pādyārghyeṇa priyeṇa ca || 44 ||
dhanyā yūyaṃ mahātmāno nigamotpāditakāriṇaḥ ||
yaiśca divyasaukhathāya bhaviṣyatsukte kṛtam || 45 ||
divyaṃ vimānayāruḍhya divyabhogopaśitāṣu ||
svargaṃ gacchantvamalaṃ sarvakāmasaṃanvitam || 46 ||
tatra muktā mahābhogānte puṇyasya saṃkṣayāt ||
yatkiñcidalpapāpaśucaṃ punastadīha mokṣyatha || 47 ||
dharmātmāno narā ye ca mitrabhtā ivātmanaḥ ||
saumyaṃ sukhaṃ prapaśyanti dharmarājānaṃ eva ca || 48 ||
ye punaḥ krūrakarmāṇaste paśyanti bhayānakam ||
daṃṣṭrākarālavadanaṃ śikuṭīkuṭilekṣaṇam || 49 ||
ūrdhvakeśaṃ mahāśmaśruyukthaṃ praghuritādharam ||
aṣṭādaśabhujam kruddhañ nīlāñjanacayopamam || 50 ||
sarvāyudhāḍhṛtakaraṃ sarvadaṇḍena tājayed ||
mahāmahiṣāroḍhaṃ dīptāgnisamalochanam || 51 ||
raktamālyāmbaradharaṃ mahāmerimivochchhṛitam ||
mṛgāyāmbudhinochapaṃ pibantriva mahādṛigham || 52 ||
asantimeva śailendhrasudhīraṃtimivānalam ||
mṛtyośaiva samīpasthāḥ kālānalasamaprasaḥ || 53 ||
kālaśmāśāñjanasaṃkāśāḥ kṛtāṃtaśca bhayānakāḥ ||
mārī cogramahāmārī kālarātriśca dāruṇā || 54 ||
vividhā vyāghrayaḥ kuṣṭhā nānārūpā bhayāvahāḥ ||
śaktiśūlāṅkuśadharāḥ pāśa ca kāsipāṇayaḥ || 55 ||
vajratuṇḍadharā rudrāḥ kṣuratīkṣṇaghanughnṛāḥ ||
nānāyudhagharāssarve mahāvīrā bhayaṃkarāḥ || 56 ||
asaṃkhyātā mahāvīrāḥ kālāgnisamprabāḥ ||
sarvāyughorakarā yamadūtā bhayānakāḥ || 57 ||
anena paricāreṇa vṛtaṃ taṃ ghoradarśanam ||
yaṃ paśyanti pāpiṣṭhāśca śrutaṃ ca bhīṣaṇam || 58 ||
nirbhartsayati cātyantaṃ yamastānpāpakarmmaṇaḥ ||
citraguptaśca bhagavāndharmavākyaiḥ pravoghayet || 59 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ narakalokamārgaṃyadūtasvarūpavaṇanaṃ nāma saptamodhyāyaḥ || 7 ||
citraguptā uvāca

mo mo duṣkṛtakarmāṇaḥ paradravyāpahārakāḥ ||
garvitārūpavīryeṇa paradāravamahñkāḥ || 1 ||
yatsvayaṃ kriyate karma tadidaṃ bhuñjyate punaḥ ||
tatkimātmopacātārthe bhaviṣyaduṣkṛtaṃ kṛtam || 2 ||
--- Page 22 ---
idānīṃ kiṃ pralapsyāmce pīḍyamānāssvakarmabhiḥ ||
bhuñjyantāṃ svāni karmāṇi nāsti doṣo hi kasyacit || 3 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
evaṃ te pṛthivīpālāssaṃgrāhāstatsamīpataḥ ||
svakīyaiḥ karmabhiścairairduṣkarmembalda pīṇaḥ || 4 ||
tānapi krodhasaṃyuktaścitragupto mahāprabhuḥ ||
saṃśikṣayati dharmajño yamarājānuśikṣayā || 5 ||
citragupta uvāca ||
bho bho nṛpā durācārāḥ prajābhighnasākāriṇaḥ ||
alpakālasya rājyasya kṛte kiṃ duṣkṛtaṃ kṛtam || 6 ||
rājyabhogeṇa mohena balādanyāyataḥ prajāḥ ||
yadīṇḍatāḥ phalaṃ tasya bhuñjatāmadhunā nṛpāḥ || 7 ||
ka tadrājyaṃ kalatraṃ ca yadarthagaśubhaṃ kṛtam ||
tatsvaiṃ saṃparityajya yūyamekākiṇaḥ sthitāḥ || 8 ||
paśyāmi tadvulaṃ naṣṭaṃ yena vighnasitāḥ prajāḥ ||
yamadūtaiyorjyamānā adhunā kīdṛśaṃ bhavet || 9 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
evaṃ bahuvidhairvākyairūpalabdhā yamena te ||
svāni karmāṇi śocanti tūṣṇīṃ tiṣṭhanti pārthivāḥ || 10 ||
iti karmani samuddiśya nṛpāṇāṃ dharmarādayaḥ ||
tatpāpapṅkśuddhardhyasmidaṃ dūtānbravīti ca || 11 ||
yamarāja uvāca ||
bho bhoṣaṇḍa mahācaṇḍa gṛhītvā nṛpatīnbalāt ||
niyamena viśuddhacakṣvaṃ krameṇa narakāṃniṣu || 12 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
tataśśīghraṃ samādāya nṛpānsaṃgṛhya pādayoḥ ||
āmiyatvā tu vegeṇa nikṣipyocṣai praṣṭhā ca || 13 ||
sarveṇa prayeṇa mahatātīva tase śilātale ||
āsphālayanti tarasā vajreṇeva mahāṭumān || 14 ||
tatassraktaṃ śroṇeṇa sravate jarjarīkṛtaḥ ||
niḥsaṃjñastu tadā dehī niḥśeṣatsaṃprajāyate || 15 ||
tatassa vāyunā spṛṣṭasstu tairujjīvitaḥ punaḥ ||
tataḥ pāpāviśuddhyarthe kṣipanti narakāṇave || 16 ||
aṣṭāviṃśatisaṃkhyābhiḥ kṣityaghasata koṭayaḥ ||
saptamasya taṃ lasthyānte ghore tamasi saṃsthitaḥ || 17 ||
ghorākhyā prathamā koṭiḥ sughorā tadghaḥ sthitā ||
atighorā mahāghorā ghorarūpā ca pañcamī || 18 ||
ṣaṣṭī talāt lākhyā ca saptamī ca bhayaṃkā ||
aṣṭamī kālarātriśca navamī ca bhayotkṭā || 19 ||
daśamī tadghaṣaṇḍā mahācaṇḍā tato'pyaḥ ||
caṇḍakolāhalā cānyā pracaṇḍā caṇḍanāyikā || 20 ||
padmā padmāvatī bhītā bhīmā bhīṣaṇanāyikā ||
karālā vikarālā ca vajrā viṃśatimā smṛtā || 21 ||
trikoṇā pañcakoṇā ca sudīrghā cākhilātindā ||
samā bhīmabalamoṣṇā dīptaprāyeti cāṣṭamī || 22 ||
iti te nāmataḥ proktā ghorā narakakoṭayaḥ ||
aṣṭāviṃśatirevaittāḥ pāpānāṃ yātanātmikāḥ || 23 ||
tāsāṃ krameṇa vijñeyāḥ pañca pañcaiva nāyakāḥ ||
pratyekaṃ sarvakoṭīnāṃ nāmataḥ sannibodhata || 24 ||
rauravaḥ prathamastepāṃ ruvante yatra dehinaḥ ||
mahārauravapīḍābhirmahatopi rudanti ca || 25 ||
tataśśītan tathā coṣṇaṃ pañcādhā nāthakāssmṛtāḥ ||
--- Page 23 ---
sūcorasṭhamahātīkṣṇastayā saṃjīvanaḥ smṛtaḥ || 26 ||
mahātamo vilomaśca vilopāśvāpi kaṇṭakaḥ |
tīvravegaḥ karālaśca vikrālaḥ prakampanaḥ || 27 ||
mahāvakraśca kālaśca kālasūtraḥ pragaḍajaḥ |
sūcīmukhasthānetiśca kṣādakrasthāmapīḍanaḥ || 28 ||
jarāśimabavanaṃ bherodāsṛkprahitastataḥ |
tīkṣṇatuṇḍaśca śakunimahāsaṃtāṅkaḥ kathuḥ |
tatarjantuḥ paṅkalepaḥ pratimānasarddubhaḥ || 30 ||
ucchvāsasmunirucchvāso rudīrgheḥ kūṭaśālmaliḥ |
duriṣṭasthūmahāvādaḥ pravāhisthūpratāpanaḥ || 31 ||
tato megho gṛṣaḥ śālmalisahastyāragajānanāḥ |
śyaghukarājaṃ diṣaghrakokavṛkānanāḥ || 32 ||
śākhunimīnanakākhyāsalpakumāriyavāyasāḥ |
gṛśolūkahaliñkāryāḥ śārdūlakṛthakāṭāḥ || 33 ||
yandukāḥ putivakāśa rakṣāsaḥ pūtiputrikāḥ ||
kaṇaghūṃrastathāgnīśca kumiganidhavapustatā || 34 ||
agnīpśāpratitṭaśca rudhirābhaśvabhojanaḥ |
lālalamakṣāntrakṣī ca sarve 'mkṣaḥ sudāruṇaḥ || 35 ||
kaṇṭakasthūviśālaśca vikaṭaḥ kaṭapūtanaḥ |
ambārīṣaḥ kaṭāhaśca kaṭhā vaitaraṇī nadī || 36 ||
sutapta lohaśayanaṃ ekapādaḥ praphūraṇaḥ |
asitālavanaṃ ghoramasthyabhaṅgaḥ śupūraṇaḥ || 37 ||
vilātasostu yantrāṇyapi kūṭapāśāḥ pramardanaḥ |
mahācūrṇodaṃsturcūrṇodaṃsapi taptalohamayaṃ tathā || 38 ||
parvataḥ kṣurādhārā ca tathā yamalaparvataḥ |
sūtraviyāśaṅkupaśca kṣārakūpaśca śītalaḥ || 39 ||
ghuṣalotrūkhalaṃ yantraṃ śilāśakaṭalāṅgalaṃ |
tālapatrasigaḍhanaṃ mahāśakaṭamaṇḍapaṃ || 40 ||
saṃmohamastimabhaṅgaśca tatsamalamayoguḍaṃ |
bahuduḥkhaṃ mahākleśāḥ kaśmalaṃ samalaṃ malāt || 41 ||
hālāhalo virūpaśca svaropaśca yamānugaḥ |
ekapādadvipādaśca tīvrāśacīvaraṃ tamaḥ || 42 ||
aṣṭāviṃśatirityete kramaśaḥ pañcavimśakāḥ |
koṭīnāmānupūrvyeṇa pañca pañcaiva nāyakāḥ || 43 ||
rauravāya prabodhyante narakāṇāṃ śataṃ smṛtaṃ |
catvāriṃśaccataṃ proktaṃ mahānarakamaṇḍalaṃ || 44 ||
iti te vyāsa saṃkhyā narakasya sthitirmatā |
prasaṃkhyānaśca vairāgyaṃ śṛṇu pāpagatiṃ ca tām || 45 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ narakalokavarṇanaṃ nāmāṣṭamo 'dhyāyaḥ || 8 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca

śṛṇu pāpāḥ prapaṃcyante śoṣyante narakāgniṣu |
yātnābhirvinicitrābhirāsvakarmaprekṣayā dṛśaṃ || 1 ||
svamalaprakṣayācchraddhayā ghāsyanti ghātavaḥ |
tatra pāpakṣatāpāpā narāḥ kṛmīkuropatāḥ || 2 ||
sugādhaṃ hastayorbaddhā tataḥ śṛṅkalayā narāḥ |
mahāvṛkṣamśākhāsu lambhyante yamakiṅkaraiḥ || 3 ||
tataste sarvayatnena śiktā dolanti kiṅkaraiḥ |
dolyantaścātivegena visaṃjñā yānti yojanaṃ || 4 ||
antarikṣasthitānāṃ ca lohabhāraśataṃ punaḥ |
pādyobbhidhyante teṣāṃ yamadūtermahābalaiḥ || 5 ||
tena bhāreṇa mahatā prabhṛśaṃ tāḍitā narāḥ |
dhyāyanti svāni karmāṇi tūṣṇīṃ tiṣṭhanti niḥśvalaḥ || 6 ||
tatodaṃkuśairagnivariṇairlohādaṇḍaiśca dāruṇaiḥ |
hanyante kiṃkarairghoraissaṃmantātpāpakṛmmiṇaḥ || 7 ||
--- Page 24 ---
tataḥ kṣāreṇa dīptena bahvorapi viśeṣataḥ ||
samantataḥ pralipy ante tīvreṇa tu punaḥ punaḥ || 8 ||
drutenatyantaliṅgena kṛttāṅgā jarjarīkṛtāḥ ||
punarivdārcye cāṅgāni śirasaḥ prabhṛti kamāt || 9 ||
vṛntākavatrapracyante tattalohakuṭāhakaiḥ ||
viṣṭhāpūrṇe tathā kūpe kṛmīṇāṃ nicaye punaḥ || 10 ||
medoʼsṛkpūyapūrṇāyāṃ vāpyāṃ kṣipyanti te punaḥ ||
bhakṣyante kṛmibhistīkṣṇairlohituṇḍaiśca vāyasaiḥ || 11 ||
śibhirdaṃśairvakaiścānyaiḥ raudraiśca vikṛtānanaiḥ ||
pacyante matsyavacchāpi pradīptāṅgarārāśiṣu || 12 ||
bhinnaḥ śūlaiḥ sutīkṣṇaiśca narāḥ pāpena karmaṇā ||
tailayantreṣu cākramya ghoreḥ karmibhirātmanaḥ || 13 ||
tilā iva prapīḍyante cakrāṇye janāpiṇḍakāḥ ||
arjyante cātape tatte lohabhaṇḍeṣvanekadhā || 14 ||
tailapūrṇakaṭāheṣu śuntateṣu punaḥ punaḥ ||
bahudhā pacyate jihvā prapīḍacyorasīn pādayoḥ || 15 ||
yātanāśca mahatyoʼtra śarīrasyāti sarvataḥ ||
niḥśeṣanarkebhyoʼpi kramantiśo narāḥ || 16 ||
narakeṣu ca sarveṣu vicitrā yamayātanā ||
yāmyaiśca drīyate vyāsa sarvāṅgeṣu sukhaṣadā || 17 ||
jvaladaṅgāramādāya mukhame āpūrya tāḍyate ||
tataḥ kṣāreṇa dīptena tāmreṇa ca punaḥ punaḥ || 18 ||
ghṛtenatyantatalena tadā tailena tanmukham ||
itastataḥ pīḍayitvā bhṛśamāpūrya hanyate || 19 ||
viṣṭhābhiḥ kṛmibhiścāpi pūryamāṇāḥ kiñcitkinñcit ||
pariṣvajanti cātyugrāṃ pradīptāṃ lohaśālmalīm || 20 ||
hanyante pṛṣṭhadeśe ca punardīptyormendhāgavaiḥ ||
danturenādikuṇṭhena krakacena balīyasā || 21 ||
śiraḥprabhṛti pīḍyante ghoreḥ karmobhirātmajaiḥ ||
khādyante ca svamāṃsāni pīyate śoṇitaṃ svakam || 22 ||
annaṃ pānaṃ na dattaṃ yaiḥ sarvadā svātmapoṣakaiḥ ||
ikṣuvatte prapīḍyante jarjarīkṛtya mudraiḥ || 23 ||
asitālavane ghore chidyante khaṇḍaśastataḥ ||
sūcībhirbhinnasarvāṅgāstataḥ śūlāropitāḥ || 24 ||
saṃcālyamānā bahuśaḥ kruśyante na mriyanti ca ||
tathā ca taccharīrāṇi suṣaduḥkhasahāni ca || 25 ||
dehādutpāṭya māṃsāni bhidyante svaiśca mudraiḥ ||
danturākṛtibhiścorairyema dūtairbalotkṛtaiḥ || 26 ||
nirghrāṇe nirghṛṇasāstithaṃ narake ciram ||
uttāḍyante tathogrāṇe vāḍukāsadane narāḥ || 27 ||
raurave rodamānāśca pīḍacyante vividhairghoreḥ ||
mahārauravapīḍābhirmehāntaḥ api rudanti ca || 28 ||
parśu vakre gude muṇḍe netrayoścaiva mastake ||
nikhanyante ghanastīkṣṇaiḥ sutamrailohaśaṃkubhiḥ || 29 ||
sūktatavāḍukāyāṃ tu proyajyante suduḥkhubhaḥ ||
jantupaṅke bhṛśaṃ tatte kṣiptāḥ krandanti visvaram || 30 ||
kumbhīpākeṣu pacyante tattataileshu vaiyune ||
pāpinaḥ krūrakarmāṇoʼsaṅkheṣu sarvathā punaḥ || 31 ||
lālābhakṣeṣu pāpāste pātyante duḥkheṣu vai ||
nānāsthāneṣu ca tathā narakeṣu punaḥ punaḥ || 32 ||
sūcīmukhe mahākleśe narake pātyate naraḥ ||
pāpī puṇyavihīnaśca tāḍyate yamārcikairaiḥ || 33 ||
lohakumbhe viniḥkṣiptāḥ śvasantaśca śanaiḥ śanaiḥ ||
--- Page 25 ---
mahāgninā prapacyante svapāpairev mānavāḥ || 34 ||
daḍhaṃ rajvādibhirbaddhā prapīḍyante śilāsu ca |
śiṣyante cāṅgkuśeṣu dṛśyante 'maraistrīśadhū || 35 ||
kṛmibhigābhirṇrasavargāśśataśo jarjarī kṛtāḥ |
sutīkṣṇaśārakūpeṣu kṣipyante tadanantaram || 36 ||
mahājvāleṣu narake pāpāḥ krandanti duḥkhitāḥ |
ita śvetaśca ghāvanti daḍhyamānāstadārṣīṣā || 37 ||
pṛṣṭhe cānīya tuṇḍābhyāṃ vinyastaskaṅghayojite |
tayormadhyena vākuśya śāḍupṛṣṭhena gāḍhataḥ || 38 ||
baddhāḥ parasparaṃ sarvē subhrūśaṃ pāparaṇābhaḥ |
baḍipuṇḍārastu darśyante mahājvāle tu yātanāḥ || 39 ||
rajyābhivīṣṭitāśaiva pāliṣṇāḥ kaddhaṣeṇa ca |
karīṣatūṣa vahṇau ca pacyante na mriyanti ca || 40 ||
sutīkṣṇaṃ cāritāste hi karkeśāsu śilāsu ca |
āsphāla śataśaḥ pāpāḥ pacyante tṛṇavattataḥ || 41 ||
śarīrābhyantaragataiḥ prabhūtaiḥ kṛmibhirnārāḥ |
bhakṣyante tīkṣṇavadanairātmadehaḥkṣayādṛśam || 42 ||
kṛmīṇāṃ niñcaye kṣiptāḥ pūyamaṃsāsthirāśiṣu |
tiṣṭha sthudigrahṛdayāḥ pavetābhyāṃ nipīḍitāḥ || 43 ||
tannena vajralepeṇa śarīramanulipyate |
aghoṣukogharṣapādāśca tātapyante rūpa vihhinā || 44 ||
vadanātaḥ pravinyastāṃ kṣupratapāmayogadām |
te khādanti parādhīnāstaistaḍcante saṣṭhūraiḥ || 45 ||
ityaṃ vyāsa kukarmaṇo narakaṣu pacanti hi |
varṇayāmi vivaraṇaṃ teṣāṃ tarkavāya karmiṇām || 46 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe paṃcyāstumāsaṃhitāyāṃ sāmānyato narakagativṛṇaṃnaṃ nāma navamoadhyāyaḥ || 9 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca |
mithyāgaṃ pravṛttastu dwijihvāṣye ca gacchati |
jihvāddhīkoṣa vistīrṇaṃhūlestīkṣṇaḥ prapīḍyate || 1 ||
nirbhartsyati yaḥ kṣaro mātaraṃ pitaraṃ gurum |
viṣṭhābhiḥ kṛmimīśrābhirṣuṃvapṛtyaṃ hinyte || 2 ||
ye śivāyata nārāmavāpīkūpatadāgakān |
vidrūvanti dvijasthānaṃ narāstatra ramanti ca || 3 ||
kāmāyodṛtanābhyaṃgaṃ snānapānānbhujanaṃ |
krīḍanaṃ maiṭhunaṃ dyūtamācarintamdoḍhatāḥ || 4 ||
peciḥre vividhaiścaṃraiḥkṣuyaṃtrādipīḍanaiḥ |
niryāmiṣu pacyante yāvadāhṛtasaṃpluvaṃ || 5 ||
tenateneva rūpeṇa tāḍyante pāradārikāḥ |
gāḍhamāligya te nārīṃ clutanāṃ lohinimūtām || 6 ||
pūrvākārāśca puruṣāḥ prajvalanti samantataḥ |
duṣṭhāriṇīṃ khiyaṃ gāḍhamāliṅganti rudanti ca || 7 ||
ye śṛṇvanti satāṃ nindāṃ teṣāṃ karṇapraghūraṇaṃ |
agnivarṇairyaḥkīlestairastāśrādiṃnimittaiḥ || 8 ||
tṛpusīsārakūṭādibhiḥ kṣīreṇa ca punaḥ punaḥ |
sutattīkṣṇatailena vajralepeṇa vā punaḥ || 9 ||
karmādāpṛtyaṃ karṇostu narakaṣu ca yātanāḥ |
anukrameṇa sarvaiṃbhavantiyātāḥ samantataḥ || 10 ||
sarvendrayāṇāmapyevaṃ karmātpāpena yātanāḥ |
bhavanti ghorāḥ pratyekaṃ śarīreṇa kṛtena ca || 11 ||
sparśadoṣeṇa ye mūḍhāsta spṛśanti ca paribhrayam |
ateṣāṃ karoṣibhirvāṇobhiḥ pāśubhiḥ pṛcyate bhṛśam || 12 ||
teṣāṃ kṣārādibirassarvaiśśarīramanulipyate |
yātanāśca mahākṣhaṭāssarvaiṣu narakaṣu ca || 13 ||
kurventi pitrorbhūkuṭiṃ karaṇe

