śāṇi ye narāḥ ||
vakāṇi teṣāṃ sāntāni kīryante śaṅkubhiḥ dṛḍham || 14 ||
yaiḥ indriyaiḥ narā ye ca vikurvanti parābhiyam |
indriyāṇi ca teṣāṃ vai vikurvanti tathaiva ca || 15 ||
paradārāṃś ca paśyanti lubdhāḥ tastabhyena cakṣuṣā ||
sūcībhiḥ śāliṃ vaṇānibhiḥ teṣāṃ netraprapūraṇam || 16 ||
kṣāradyaiḥ ca kramāt sarvāṃ ihāiva yamayatanāḥ ||
bhavanti muniśārdūla satyaṃ satyaṃ na saṃśayaḥ || 17 ||
devāmiguruṃ viprebhyaḥ śāninvetya pramujate ||
lohakīlaśataiḥ taiḥ tān tajjihvāsyaṃ ca pūryante || 18 ||
ye devārām puṣpāṇi lobhāt saṃgṛhya pāṇinā ||
jighrati ca narā bhūyaḥ śirasā dhārayanti ca || 19 ||
āpūryante śiraḥ teṣāṃ tatailonityā śaṅkubhiḥ ||
nāsikā vātavahulaiḥ tataḥ kṣārādibhiḥ bhrṣam || 20 ||
ye nindanti mahātmānaṃ vācakaṃ dharmadeśikam ||
devāmigurum uktāṃś ca dharmaśāstrāṃ ca śāśvatam || 21 ||
teṣāṃ asurāsi kaṇṭhe ca jihvāyāṃ dantasandighaṣu ||
tāḍunyoṣṭhe nāsikāyāṃ mūrdhni sarvāṅgasandighaṣu || 22 ||
abhinavanastu tanmānaś ca triśākhā lohāśaṅkavaḥ ||
āvidhyante ca bahuśaḥ sthāneṣu bheṣu kṣudraraiḥ || 23 ||
tataḥ kṣāreṇa dīptena pūryante hi samantataḥ ||
yātanāś ca mahantyo vai śarīrasthāyita sarvataḥ || 24 ||
aśeṣanarkebhyeva kramonti kramaśaḥ punaḥ ||
ye gṛhṇanti paradravyaṃ paṇyāṃ vipraṃ spṛśanti ca || 25 ||
śivopakeraṇaṃ gāṃ ca jñānādibhiḥ likhitaṃ ca yat ||
hastapadādibhiḥ teṣāṃ āpūryate samantataḥ || 26 ||
narkkeṣu ca sarveṣu vicitrā dehayātanāḥ ||
bhavanti bahuśaḥ kaṣṭāḥ pāṇipādas samudravāḥ || 27 ||
śivāyatanaṃ paśyante devārāmeṣu kutraciit ||
sadyosmṛjanti ye pāpāḥ purīṣaṃ mūtram eva ca || 28 ||
teṣāṃ śirśanaṃ satṛṣṇaṃ cūryante lohakṣudraiḥ ||
sūcībhiḥ agni vaṇānibhiḥ tathā tlāghyante punaḥ || 29 ||
tataḥ kṣāreṇa mahatā tīvreṇa ca punaḥ punaḥ ||
drutena pūryante gāḍhaṃ gude śirśane ca dehinaḥ || 30 ||
manasarvaiḥ indriyāṇāṃ ca yasmaḥ duḥkhaṃ prajāyate ||
dhane satyapi ye dānaṃ na prayacchanti tṛṣṇayā || 31 ||
atithiṃ cānvamanyante kāle prāpte gṛhāśrame ||
tasmāt duṣkṛtaṃ prāpya gacchanti narakāḥ śucau || 32 ||
yeṣāṃ datvā hi bhuñjanti na svabhayaḥ saha vāyasaiḥ ||
teṣāṃ ca vidrutaṃ vakraṃ kīlakadyatāḍitam || 33 ||
kākinibhiḥ prāṇibhiḥ ca śailonhaṭuṇḍaiḥ ca vāyasaiḥ ||
upadravaiḥ bahuviddhaiḥ durārataḥ prapīḍyante || 34 ||
śyāmaś ca śabalaś caiva yamadūtānurodhakau ||
yo stau tastābhyāṃ prayacchāmi tau gṛhītvā imaṃ bilam || 35 ||
ye vā varuṇavāyavyā yāmyā naiṛtya vāyasāḥ ||
vāyasāḥ puṇyakarmāṇaḥ te praghṛhṇantu me bilam || 36 ||
śivam abhyarcya yatna na hutavānau vidhipūrvakam ||
śaivaṃ mantraṃ bilam ye ca dadante na ca te yamam || 37 ||
paśyanti tridaivam yānti tasmāt ādhyādine dine ||
maṇḍalaṃ catursam tu kṛtvā gandhādivāsitam || 38 ||
dhanvantaryathā mīśānyā prācyāṃ indrāya nikṣipet ||
yāmyāṃ yamāya vāruṇyāṃ sudakṣomāya dakṣiṇe || 39 ||
pitṛbhyaḥ tu viniḥkṣipya prācyāmaryamaṇa tataḥ |
ghātubhiḥ eva vidhātuś ca dvārddeśe viniḥkṣipet || 40 ||
śvabhyaś ca śvapitṛbhyaś ca vayobhyo vikṣipet dhruvam ||
devaiḥ pitṛmanuṣyaiś ca pretaiḥ bhūtais sa

--- Page 27 ---
guhyakaḥ || 41 ||
vayobhiḥ kṛimikīṭaiśca gṛihasthaścopajīvyate ||
svādhākāraḥ svabhākāro vaṣaṭkārastṛitīyakaḥ || 42 ||
iṃkārastathaivaānyo henvaā stana catuṣṭayam ||
svāhākāraṃ stane devāssvabhāṃ ca pitarastathā || 43 ||
vaṣṭkāraṃ tathevānye devā bhūteśvarāstathā ||
iṃtakāraṃ manuṣyāśca pibanti satataṃ stanam || 44 ||
yastetatān manavo dhetuṃ śraddhayā jhanurṣīṣikām ||
karoti satataṃ kāle sāmitvāyopakalpyate || 45 ||
yastaṃ jahāti vā svastastāmiṣṭe sa tu majjati ||
tasmāttva baliṃ tebhyo dvārasthaścintayetsuṇam || 46 ||
kṣudhātṛimātithi samyagekakṣāminivāsinām ||
bhojayet taśubhānnena yathāśaktyātmabhojanāt || 47 ||
atithiryasya bhrāśo gṛihāttitinivartate ||
sa tasmai duṣkṛitaṃ dattvā puṇyamādāya gacchati || 48 ||
tato'śraṃ priyamevāśannaraḥ śṛṃkhalabānpunaḥ ||
jihvāvegena viddhontra ciraṃ kālaṃ sa tiṣṭhati || 49 ||
yatastaṃ māṃsadudhṛitya tilamātraprāmaṇataḥ ||
khādiduṃ dīyate teṣāṃ bhittvā caiva tu śoṇitam || 50 ||
niḥśeṣataḥ kaśābhistu pīḍyate kramaśaḥ punaḥ ||
bubhukṣayāntikaghaṃ hi tathācāti pipāsayā || 51 ||
evamādhā mahāghorā yātanāḥ pāpakarmṇām ||
ante yatpratipat hi tatsakṣepeṇa śṛṃṇu || 52 ||
yaḥ karoti mahāpāpaṃ dharme carati vai laghu ||
dharme gurutaraṃ vāpi tathāvṛitye tayoḥ śṛṃṇu || 53 ||
sukṛitasya phalaṃ nokttaṃ gurupāpaprabāhvataḥ ||
na minoti sukhaṃ tatra bhogebhairnumiranvitaḥ || 54 ||
tathobhi mohati santato na bhakṣyaimanyte sukham ||
abhāvāddhattoanyasya prātikūlyaṃ dine dine || 55 ||
pumānyo gurudharmāṃspi sopavāso yathā gṛihī ||
vittavān vijānāti pīḍāṃ niyamasaṃsthitaḥ || 56 ||
tāni pāpāni ghorāṇi sānti yeṣāṃ naro śuvi ||
śataghā bhedmāpnoti girivajrahato yathā || 57 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāśumāsaṃhitāyāṃ narakagatibhogavarṇanaṃ nāma daśamodhyāyaḥ || 10 ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
kutapāpā narā yānti duḥkhena mahatānvitāḥ ||
yamamārge sukhaṃ yaiśca tāndharmmānvad me pramo || 1 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
avaśyaṃ hi kṛitaṃ karma mokṣakyamivicārataḥ ||
śubhāśubhamato vakṣye tāndharmmānsukhādāyakān || 2 ||
atra ye śubhakarmāṇaḥ saumyacittā dayānvitāḥ ||
sukhena te narā yānti yamamārge sayāvahaghu || 3 ||
yaḥ pradyāt dvijendraṇāśupānatkāṣṭhapāduke ||
sa naroāśvena mahatā sukhaṃ yāti yamālayam || 4 ||
chandanena gacchanti yathā chandreṇa dehinaḥ ||
śibikāyāḥ pradānena tanmathena sukhaṃ vrajet || 5 ||
śayyāsanapradānena sukhaṃ yāti suvidhrāmam ||
āramaccāyākatārī mārge vā vṛikṣaropakāḥ ||
vrajanti yamalokantā ātatpompi gatakramāḥ || 6 ||
yānti puṣpakayānena puṣpārāmakara narāḥ ||
devāyatanakartāraḥ krīḍanti ca guhodeśre || 7 ||
kartāraṃśca tathā ye ca yatīnāmāśramastyaṃ ca ||
anāthamaṇḍapānāṃ tu krīḍanti ca guhodeśre || 8 ||
devāgniguruvisrāṇāṃ mātāpitroṣca pūjakāḥ ||
pūjyamānā narā

--- Page 28 ---
yānti kāṃśukena yathāsukham || 9 ||
dyotayanto diśaḥ sarvā yānti dīpapradāyinaḥ ||
pratiśrayapradānena mukhaṃ yānti nirāmayāḥ || 10 ||
viśrāmyamāṇā gacchanti guruśuśrūṣakā narāḥ ||
ātoḍyavipradātāraḥ sukhaṃ yānti svake gṛhe || 11 ||
sarvakāmasamṛddhena yathā gacchanti gopradāḥ ||
atra dattātra pānāni tānyāpnoti naraḥ pathi || 12 ||
pādaśaucapradānena sajjalena pathā vrajet ||
pādābhyaṅgaṃ ca yaḥ kuryādśatpūjena gacchati || 13 ||
pādaśaucaṃ tathābhyaṅgaṃ dīpamaṇaṃ pratiśrayam ||
yo dadāti sadā vyāsa nopasarpati taṃ yamaḥ || 14 ||
hemmaratnapradānena yāti durgāṇi nistarann ||
raupyān duṣpradānena yamalokāṃ sukhena saḥ || 15 ||
ityevamādibhirdānaiḥ sukhaṃ yānti yamālayam ||
svarge tu vividhānbhogānprāpnuvanti sadā narāḥ || 16 ||
sarveṣāmeva dānānāmnadānāṃ paraṃ smṛtam ||
sadyaḥ prītikararaṃ hṛdyaṃ balabuddhivivardhanam || 17 ||
nānnadānasamaṃ dānaṃ vidyate munisattama ||
annādrvanti bhūtāni tadabhāve mriyante ca || 18 ||
raktaṃ māṃsaṃ vasā śukraṃ kramādannātpravardhante ||
śukrādrvanti bhūtāni tasmādannamayaṃ jagat || 19 ||
hemmaratnaśnānā gandrairānrīṣaṅkacandanādibhiḥ ||
samastairapi saṃprāptaiḥ ramanti bahuśritāḥ || 20 ||
garbhasthā jāyamānāśca bālavṛddhāśca madhyamāḥ ||
āhāraṃ bhikāṃśanti devadānavarākṣasāḥ || 21 ||
kṣudhā niḥśeṣarogāṇāṃ vyādhiḥ śreṣṭhatamaḥ smṛtaḥ ||
sa cānnauṣadhilepena naśyatīha na saṃśayaḥ || 22 ||
nāsti kṣudhāsamaṃ duḥkhaṃ nāsti rogaḥ kṣudhāsamaḥ ||
nāśnyarogasamaṃ saukhyaṃ nāsti koṣasamo ripuḥ || 23 ||
ata eva mahatpuṇyamanna dāne prakīrtitam ||
tathā kṣudhāmna taptā mriyante sarvadehinaḥ || 24 ||
annadaḥ prāṇadaḥ prokto prāṇadaścāpi sarvadaḥ ||
tasmādannapradānena sarvadānaphalaṃ labhet || 25 ||
yasyānnapānapuṣṭāṅgaḥ kurute puṇyasaṃcayam ||
annapradātustasyārddhe kṛtaśrāddhe na saṃśayaḥ || 26 ||
trailokye yāni ratnāni bhogāśrīvāhanāni ca ||
annadānapradasvairviṃhāsutra ca taccchhet || 27 ||
dharmārthamokṣāṇāṃ dehaḥ paramasādhanam ||
tasmāddvena pānena pālayeddehamātmanaḥ || 28 ||
annameva praśaṃsanti sarvameva pratiṣṭhitam ||
annena sadṛśaṃ dānaṃ na bhūtaṃ na bhaviṣyati || 29 ||
annena dhāryate sarvaṃ viśvaṃ jagadidaṃ mune ||
annaṃrjaskaraṃ loke prāṇā hyanne pratiṣṭhitāḥ || 30 ||
dātavyaṃ bhikṣave cānnnaṃ brāhmaṇāya mahātmane ||
kuṭuṃbaṃ pīḍayitvāpi ātmano tṛptimicchatā || 31 ||
viddāti nidhiśreṣṭhaṃ yo dadādannamārthinne ||
brāhmaṇāyārtarūpāya pāralaukikamātmanaḥ || 32 ||
acchedyadhṛtimānvacchankāle dvijamupasthitam ||
śrāntamabhyāni vṛttyarthe gṛhastha gṛhamāgatam || 33 ||
annadaḥ pūjayedvyāsa suśīlastu vimatsaraḥ ||
kopadyutpātitaṃ hitvā divive ca mahatsukham || 34 ||
nābhiniṃdeddigataṃ na praṇudyātkathañcan ||
api śvapāke śunivā nānnadānaṃ praṇaśyati || 35 ||
śrāntāyādṛṣṭapūrvāya

