ghaṭamadhyāni vartante ||
yo dadyādpārikhiñca sa samṛddhimavāpnuyāt || 36 ||
pitṝṇdevāṃstathā viprānatithīṃśca mahāśune ||
yo naraḥ prīṇayatyebhiḥ tasya puṇyaphalaṃ mahavat || 37 ||
annaṃ pānaṃ ca śūdrāṇāṃ brāhmaṇe ca viśiṣyate ||
na pṛcchedvotracāraṇaṃ svādhyāyaṃ deśameva ca || 38 ||
bhikṣito brāhmaṇeneha dadyādannaṃ ca yaḥ pumān |
saṃyāti paramaṃ svargaṃ yāvadāśrutasaṃbhavam || 39 ||
annasya ca vṛkṣāśca sarvakāmaphalānvitāḥ ||
bhavantīha yathā viprā harṣayuktādiviṣṭape || 40 ||
annadānena ye lokāstanargaiḥ virācitā mune ||
annadāturmahādivyāstāñchṛṇuṣva mahāśune || 41 ||
bhavnāni prakāśante diviṣu teṣāṃ mahātmanām ||
nānāsaṃsthānarūpāṇi nānākāmānvitāni ca || 42 ||
sarvakāmaphalāṃśāpi vṛkṣā bhavanaṃsaṃsthitāḥ ||
hemavāpyaḥ śubhāḥ kūpā dīrghāḥ kāśeva sarvaśaḥ || 43 ||
ghoṣayanti ca pānāni śubhānyatha sahasraśaḥ ||
bhakṣyabhojyamayāśśailā vāsāsyābharaṇāni ca || 44 ||
kṣīraṃ sravanti asritāstathe vādyasya parvvatāḥ ||
prāsādāḥ pāṇḍurābhāsāśśayyāśca kanakaojvalāḥ || 45 ||
tānbhradā śca gacchanti tasmādannaprado bhavet ||
yadīccheda ātmano bhaṃyamaiha loke para ca || 46 ||
ete lokāḥ puṇyakṛtāmannadānāṃ mahāprabhāḥ ||
tasmādannaṃ viśeṣeṇa dātavyaṃ mānavairghruvam || 47 ||
annaṃ prajāpatiḥ sākṣādannaṃ viṣṇustvaṃ haraḥ ||
tasmādannasamaṃ dānaṃ na bhūtaṃ na bhaviṣyati || 48 ||
kṛtvāpi sumahātpāpaṃ yaḥ paścādannadho bhavet ||
viṣṇukṛtsarvapāpebhyastsvargalokaṃ sa gacchati || 49 ||
annapānāśvagobāstrāyācchāsanāni ca ||
pretaloke praśastāni dānānyetau viśeṣataḥ || 50 ||
evaṃ dānaviśeṣeṇa dharmarājapuraṃ naraḥ ||
yasmādgāti vimānena tasmādānaṃ samācaret || 51 ||
etadākhyānamanaghammannadānaprabhāvataḥ ||
yaḥ paṭhetpāṭhayedanyāṃśca sabṛddhaḥ prajāyate || 52 ||
śṛṇuyācchāvaye cchrādde brāhmaṇānyo mahāśune ||
akṣayyamannadānaṃ ca pitṛṇāṃtupatiṣṭhitā || 53 ||
iti śrīśivasaṃhāpurāṇe pañcamyāsumāsaṃhitāyāṃ mannadānamāhātmyavarṇanaṃ nāma trayodaśo'dhyāyaḥ || 13 ||
