sanatkumāra uvāca ||
pānīyadānaṃ paramaṃ dānānāmuttamaṃ sadā ||
sarveṣāṃ jīvaṃjunānāṃ tarppṇaṃ jīvanaṃ smṛtam || 1 ||
prapādanaṃ mataḥ kuryātsuśītodinivāritam ||
jalyaśreyavinirmāṇaṃ mahānandarṃkaraṃ bhavet || 2 ||
iha loke pare vāpi satyaṃ satyaṃ na saṃśayaḥ ||
tasmādapīśa kṛpāśca taḍāgaṃkārayennaraḥ || 3 ||
arddhaṃ pāpasya harati puruṣasya vikrameṇaḥ ||
kūpaḥ pravṛttapānīyaḥ supravṛttasya nityaśaḥ || 4 ||
sarvē tāryante vaṃśaṃ yasya khāte jalāśaye ||
gāvaḥ pibanti viprāśca sāghavaśca narāṃssadā || 5 ||
nidāghakāle pānīyaṃ yasya tiṣṭhatyavāritam ||
mṛdugaṃ viṣamaṃ kṛcchraṃ na kadācidvāpyate || 6 ||
taḍāgānāṃ ca vakṣyāmi kṛtānāṃ ye guṇāḥ smṛtāḥ ||
triṣu lokeṣu sarvatra pūjito yastaḍāgavān || 7 ||
athavā mitrasadane meḍaṃ

--- Page 30 ---
mitrātiṃ vijitaṃ ||
kīrtiṃ saṃjananaṃ śreṣṭhaṃ taḍāgānāṃ niveśanaṃ || 8 ||
dharmasya arthasya kāmasya phalam āhur manīṣiṇaḥ |
taḍāgaṃ śṛṇute yena tasya puṇyam an ntakaṃ || 9 ||
catuṣvidhyānāṃ bhūtānāṃ taḍāgaḥ paramāśrayaḥ |
taḍāgādīni sarvāṇi diśanti śreyaṣṭuttamāgra || 10 ||
devā manuṣyā gandharvaḥ pitaro nāgarākṣ asāḥ |
sthāvarāṇi ca bhūtāni saṃśrayanti jalāśayaṃ || 11 ||
prāvṛṭ taite taḍāge tu salilaṃ yasya tiṣṭhati |
agnihhotraphalaṃ tasya bhavad ity āha cātmabhuḥ || 12 ||
śaratk āle tu salilaṃ taḍāge yasya tiṣṭhati |
gosahasraphalaṃ tasya bhavedatra na saṃśayaḥ || 13 ||
hemante śiśire caiva salilaṃ yasya tiṣṭhati |
sa vai bahu svarṇasya yajñasya labhate phalaṃ || 14 ||
vasante ca tathā grīṣme salilaṃ yasya tiṣṭhati |
atirātrasya medhānāṃ phalam āhur manīṣiṇaḥ || 15 ||
mune vyāsātha vṛkṣāṇāṃ ropaṇe ca guṇān śṛṇu |
proktaṃ jalāśayaphalaṃ jīvaśrīṇana uktamaṃ || 16 ||
atītānāgatān sarvān pitṛṃvaṃśāṃstu tārayed |
kāntāre vṛkṣaropī yastasmādṛkṣāṃstu ropayed || 17 ||
tatra putrā bhavantyete pādapā nātra saṃśayaḥ |
paraṃ lokaṃ gataḥ so'pi lokānāṃ prīti cākṣayaṃ |
|| 18 ||
puṣpaiḥ suraga ṇānāṃ sarvān phalaiḥ cāpi tathā pitṝn |
chāyayā cātihinā sarvān pūjayanti mahīruhāḥ || 19 ||
kiṃ ca rogarakṣāṃsi devagandharvamanusyavāḥ |
tathaivāṣiṇa gaṇāś caiva saṃśrayanti mahīruhāṃ || 20 ||
puṣpatāḥ phalantas ca tarpayantyeha mānavān |
iha loke pare caiva putrāste dharmataḥ smṛtāḥ || 21 ||
taḍāgakṛtakṣarāpī ceṣṭayajñasya yo dvijaḥ |
ete svargannaṃ hyarthaṃ ye cānye satyavādinaḥ || 22 ||
satyam eva paraṃ brahma satyam eva paraṃ tapaḥ |
satyam eva par o yajñas satyam eva paraṃ śrutam || 23 ||
satyaṃ sureṣu jāgataṃ satyaṃ ca paramaṃ padaṃ |
satyenaiva dhṛtā pṛthvī satye sarve pratiṣṭhitaṃ || 24 ||
tapo yajñas puṇyaṃ ca devarṣipitṛpūjane |
āpo vidyā ca te sarve sarve satye pratiṣṭhitam || 25 ||
satyaṃ yajñas tapo dānaṃ mantrā devī sarasvatī |
brahm acaryaṃ tathā satyaṃ oṃkāras satyam eva ca || 26 ||
satyena vāyur bhramyati satyena tapate raviḥ |
satyenāgnir idaṃ dahati svargeḥ satyena tiṣṭhati || 27 ||
pālanaṃ sarvevedānāṃ sarve tīrthāvagāhanam |
satyena vahate loke sarvaṃ āmotyasaṃśayam || 28 ||
aśvamedhasa hasraṃ ca satyaṃ ca tulyayā dhṛtam |
lakṣāṇi kratavośca iva satyam eva viśiṣya te || 29 ||
satyena devāḥ pitaro mānavoragarākṣasāḥ |
prīyante satyatas sarve lokāś ca sacarācarāḥ || 30 ||
satyam āhuḥ paraṃ dharmaṃ satyam āhuḥ paraṃ padaṃ |
satyam āhuḥ paraṃ brahma tasmāt satyaṃ sadā vadet || 31 ||
śṛṇu yas satyaniratās tapas tatsvā śubhuśramaṃ |
satyadharmaratās siddhas tattas svarge ca te gatāḥ || 32 ||
--- Page 31 ---
apsarogaṇasaṃviṣṭairvimānaiḥ parimātṛbhiḥ ||
vakṣyaṃ ca sadā satyaṃ na satyādricyate param || 33 ||
agādhe vipule siddhe satyatīrthe śucicchrade ||
snātavyaṃ manasā yuktaṃ sthānaṃ tatparaṃ smṛtam || 34 ||
ātmārthe vā parārthe vā putrārthe vāpi mānavāḥ |
anṛtaṃ ye na bhāṣante te narāssvargagāminaḥ || 35 ||
vedā yajñāstathā mantrāssanti vipreṣu nityaśaḥ ||
nopāntyapi jhuṃsatveṣu tasmātsatyaṃ samācaret || 36 ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
tapasoyme phalaṃ brūhi punareva viśeṣataḥ |
sarveṣāṃ caiva varṇānāṃ brāhmaṇānāṃ tapodhnam || 37 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
pravakṣyāmi tapodhyāyaṃ sarvakāmārthasādhakam |
suduścaraṃ dvijātīnāṃ tanme nigaditaḥ śṛṇu || 38 ||
tapo hi paraṃ proktaṃ tapasā vidyate phalam |
taporatā hi ye nityaṃ modante saha daivataiḥ || 39 ||
tapasā prāpyate svargastapasā prāpyate yaśaḥ |
tapasā prāpyate kāmastapassvārthsāghanam || 40 ||
tapasā mokṣamāpnoti tapasā vindante mahat |
jñānavijñānasaṃpattiḥ saubhāgyaṃ rūpameva ca || 41 ||
nānāvidhāni vastūni tapasā labhate naraḥ |
tapasā labhante sarve manasā yadyadicchati || 42 ||
nāttapaso yānti brahmalokam kadācana |
nāttatapasāṃ prāpyaśśaṅkaraḥ parameśvaraḥ || 43 ||
yatkāyeṃ kiñcidāsthāya puruṣastapate tapaḥ |
tatsarvaṃ samprāpnoti paraṃ ca mānaḥ || 44 ||
surāpāḥ pāradārī ca brahmaghā gurutalpagaḥ |
tapasā tarante sarve sarvataśca vimuñcati || 45 ||
api sarveśvarasthaṇurvaiṣṇuḥ śaiva sanātanaḥ |
brahmā hutāśanaḥ śakro ye cānye tapasānvitāḥ || 46 ||
aṣṭāśītiṃ sahasrāṇi munīnāmūrdhvarerasām |
tapasā divi modante sametā daivataiḥ saha || 47 ||
tapasā labhyate rājyaṃ sa ca śakrasureśvaraḥ |
tapasāpālayatsvargamahanyahani vṛtraha || 48 ||
sūryaścandramasau devau sarvalokahite ratau |
tapsaiva prakāśete nakṣrāṇi grahāstathā || 49 ||
na cāsti tatsukhaṃ loke yaddinā tapasā kila |
tapasaiva sukhaṃ sarvaṃ iti vedavido viduḥ || 50 ||
jñānaṃ vijñānamārogyaṃ rūpavattvaṃ tathaiva ca |
saubhāgyaṃ caiva tapasā prāpyate sarvadā sukham || 51 ||
tapasā sṛjyate viśvaṃ brahmā viśvaṃ vinā śramam |
pālitvim paṇḍherāspyeti ghatte śeṣokhilāṃ mahīm || 52 ||
viśvāmitro gādhisutastapasaiva mahāmune |
kṣatriyo'thābhavidrāmaḥ prasiddhaṃ tribhave tvadam || 53 ||
ityuktaṃ te mahāprājña tapomāhātmyamuttamam |
śruṃvabhyayaṃ nmahātmyaṃ tapaso'dhikamuttamam || 54 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe paścamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ tapomāhātmyavarṇanaṃ nāma dvādaśo'dhyāyaḥ || 12 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
tapastapati yo'raṇye vanyamūlabhalāśanaḥ |
yo'dhīte ṛcamekāṃ hi

--- Page 32 ---
phalaṃ syāttatsaṃ mune || 1 ||
śruterdhyayanātpuṇyaṃ yadāmoti dvijoттamaḥ ||
taddhyāpanataścāpi dviguṇaṃ phalamaśnute || 2 ||
jagadyathā nirālokaṃ jāyateśaśibhāskaram ||
vinā tathā purāṇaṃ jhādhyeyamarmāpune sadā || 3 ||
tapyamānaṃ sadājñānāgniśraye yo'pi śāstrataḥ ||
sambodhayet lokaṃ tasmātpūjyaḥ purāṇagaḥ || 4 ||
sarvāṣāṃ caiva pātrāṇāṃ madhye śreṣṭhaḥ purāṇavit ||
patanānnāyate yasmāttasmātpātramudāhṛtam || 5 ||
partyaṇḍucchinnaṃ kartavyā purāṇe kadācana ||
purāṇajñasarvavetā brahmā viṣṇurhareḥ guruḥ || 6 ||
ghanaṃ dhānyaṃ hiraṇyaṃ ca vāsāṃsi vividhāni ca ||
deyaṃ purāṇavijñāya pareṇa ca śarmeṇa ca || 7 ||
yo dadāti mahāprītyā purāṇādhyāya sañjanaḥ ||
pātrāya śubhavastrāṇi sa yāti paramāṃ gatiṃ || 8 ||
mahīṃ gāṃ vā syandanāṃśca gajanānśca śobhanān ||
yaḥ prayacchati pātrāya tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu || 9 ||
aśvayānaṃ sarvakāmāṃśca pareṇa ca janmani ||
aśvameghaphalaṃ cāpi sa phalaṃ labhate pumān || 10 ||
mahīṃ dadāti yastasmai kṛtāṃ phalavartīṃ śubhām ||
sa tārayet vai vaṃśyāndaśa pūrvāndaśaparān || 11 ||
iha śrutvākhilānkāmānate divyaśarīravān ||
vimānena ca divyena śivalokam sa gacchati || 12 ||
na yajñaistuṣṭimāyānti devāḥ prokṣaṇakairapi ||
bilībhiḥ puṣpapūjābhirnathā pustakavācanaiḥ || 13 ||
śambhorāyatane yastu kārayeddhambhupustakam ||
viṣṇorkasya kasyāpi śṛṇu tasyāpi tatphalam || 14 ||
rājasūyāśvamedhānāṃ phalaṃ māpnoti mānovaḥ ||
suryalokaṃ ca bhitvāśu brahmalokam sa gacchati || 15 ||
sthitvā kalpañatānyatra rājā bhavati bhūtale ||
bhuṅkte niṣkaṇṭakaṃ bhogānnātra kāyā vicāraṇā || 16 ||
aśvameghāsahasrasya yatphalaṃ saghudāhṛtam ||
tatphalaṃ samavāpnoti devāgre yo japaṃ caret || 17 ||
itihāsapurāṇābhyāṃ śambhorāyatane śubhe ||
nānyatprītikaraṃ śambhostatthānyeṣāṃ divaukasām || 18 ||
tasmātsarvaprayatnena kāryaṃ pustakavācanaṃ ||
tathāsya śravaṇaṃ premṇā sarvakāmaphalapradam || 19 ||
purāṇaśravaṇācchabhmoniṣpāpo jāyate naraḥ ||
śuklā mogānsurvipulāñchivalokamavāpnuyāt || 20 ||
rājasūyena yatpuṇyamabhiṣṭomrśatena ca ||
tatpuṇyaṃ labhate śambhoḥ kathāśravaṇamātrathaḥ || 21 ||
sarvātīthānvagāhena gavāṃ koṭipradānataḥ ||
tava phalaṃ labhate śambhoḥ kathāśravaṇato mune || 22 ||
ye śṛṇvanti kathāḥ śambhoḥ sadā śubhanapavanīm ||
te manuṣyā na mantavyā rudrā eva na saṃśayaḥ || 23 ||
śṛṇvatāṃ śivasakīrtīṃ santāṃ kīrtayatāṃ ca tām ||
padāmbujaragāñśyeva tīrthāni munayo viduḥ || 24 ||
gantuṃ niḥśreyasaṃ sthānaṃ ye'bhivāñchanti dehinaḥ ||
kathāḥ paurāṇikīṃ śaivīṃ bhaktyā śṛṇvantu te sadā || 25 ||
kathāḥ paurāṇikīṃ śrotuṃ yadhyaśaktassadā bhavet ||
niyatātmā pratidinaṃ śṛṇuyāddā muhūrtakam || 26 ||
yadi pratidinaṃ śrotumāśakto mānavobhavet ||
puṇyamāsādiṣu mune śṛṇuyācchāṅkarīṃ kathām || 27 ||
śaivīṃ kathāṃ hi śṛṇvānaḥ

--- Page 33 ---
puruṣo hi munīśvara ||
sa nistarati saṃsāraṃ dagdhvā karmamahāṭavīm || 28 ||
kathā śaivīṃ śṛṇutai vā tadaddhē vā kṣaṇaṃ ca vā ||
ye śṛṇvanti narā bhaktyā na teṣāṃ durgatirbhavet || 29 ||
yatpuṇyaṃ sarvedāneṣu sarvayajñeṣu vā śune ||
śambhoḥ purāṇaśravaṇāttaphaṃ niścalaṃ bhavet || 30 ||
viśeṣataḥ kalau jñāsyeḥ purāṇaśravaṇādhete ||
paro dharmo na puṃsāṃ hi śucikhyānaparaḥ smṛtaḥ || 31 ||
purāṇaśravaṇaṃ śambhonāmasaṃkīrtanaṃ tathā ||
kalpadrumaphalaṃ ramye manuṣyāṇāṃ na saṃśayaḥ || 32 ||
kalau durmedhāsāṃ puṃsāṃ dharmācāroijñatātmanām ||
hitāya viddhe śambhuḥ purāṇākhyaṃ sudhārasam || 33 ||
ekoṣajrāmarsstyādai tibatreṇāmute pumān ||
śambhoḥ kathāmṛtapānātkuśalamevājrāmāram || 34 ||
yā gatiḥ puṇyaśīlānāṃ yajvināṃ ca tapasvīnām ||
sā gatiḥ sadhasā tāta purāṇaśravaṇāt khal || 35 ||
jñānavāsitenedā naṣṭāyogaśāstrāṇi yatnatāḥ ||
adhyetavyāni paurāṇaṃ śāstraṃ śrotavyameva ca || 36 ||
pāpaṃ saṃśīyate nityaṃ dharma eva vivarddhate ||
purāṇaśravaṇājjñānī na saṃsāraṃ prapadyate || 37 ||
ata eva purāṇāni śrotavyāni prayatnatāḥ ||
dharmārthakāmalatbhāya mokṣamārgāttaye tathā || 38 ||
yajjaidainastapobhistu yatphalaṃ tīrthasevayā ||
tatphalaṃ samavāpnoti purāṇaśravaṇāttaraḥ || 39 ||
na bhaveyuḥ purāṇāni dharmamārgekṣaṇāni tu ||
yatra yadṛtī sthātā cātrapātrakaṃ kathāyām || 40 ||
ṣaḍīṃśatipurāṇānāṃ madhyeṣṭyekaṃ śṛṇoti yaḥ ||
paṭhedrā bhiktyuktastu sa mukto nātra saṃśayaḥ || 41 ||
anyo na dṛṣṭasukhadeo hi māgaiḥ purāṇamārgāṃ hi sadā variṣṭhaḥ ||
śāstraṃ vinā sarvvidaṃ na bhāti sūryeṇa hīnā iva jīvalokāḥ || 42 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe paścamyāṃ umāsaṃhitāyāṃ purāṇamāhātmyavarṇanaṃ nāma trayodaśo'dhyāyaḥ || 13 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca

śastāni coradānāni mahādānāni nityaśaḥ ||
pātrebhyastu pradeyāni ātmānaṃ tārayanti ca || 1 ||
hiraṇyadānaṃ godānaṃ bhūmidānaṃ dvijottama ||
granthāṃto vai pavitragāṇi tārayanti svameva tam || 2 ||
suvarṇadānaṃ godānaṃ pṛthivīdānameva ca ||
etāni śreṣṭhadānāni kṛtvā pāpaiḥ pramucyate || 3 ||
tulādānāni śastāni gāvaḥ pṛthvī sarasvatī ||
dve tu tulyabale śaste bādhikā ca sarasvatī || 4 ||
nityaṃ hrāduduo gāvaśchatraṃ vastuupānhai ||
deyāni yācamānebhyaḥ pānamabraṃ tathaiva ca || 5 ||
saṃkalpavihito yo'thāṃ brāhmaṇebhyaḥ pradīyate ||
arthibhyo'pīḍitebhyaśca manasvi tena jāyate || 6 ||
kanakaṃ ca tilā nāgāḥ kanyā dāsī gṛhaṃ rathaḥ ||
maṇayaḥ kapalā gāvo mahādānāni vai daśa || 7 ||
gṛhītvaitāni sarvāṇi brāhmaṇo jñānavitsadā ||
vadānyāṃstārayetsadyo dhyātmānaṃ ca na saṃśayaḥ || 8 ||
suvarṇaṃ ye prayacchanti narāḥ śuddhena cetasā ||
devatāstaṃ prayacchanti sarvamādite me śrutam || 9 ||
agnibhir devatāḥ sarvāḥ suvarṇaṃ ca hutāśanaḥ ||
tasmātsuvarṇaṃ datvā ca dattāssyurssarvadevāḥ || 10 ||
pṛthvīdānaṃ mahāśreṣṭhaṃ sarvakāmaphalapradum ||
sauvarṇaṃ ca viśeṣeṇa yatkṛtaṃ

--- Page 34 ---
pṛthunā purā || 11 ||
dīyamānāṃ prapaśyanti pṛthvīṃ rukmāsamanvitām ||
sarvapāpavinirmuktāste yānti paramāṃ gatim || 12 ||
athānyañca pravakṣyāmi dānaṃ sarvottamaṃ śṛṇe ||
kāntāraṃ yanna paśyanti yamasyā bahuduḥkhadm || 13 ||
kuryātkāntāradānaṃ hi vidhinā śuddhamānasaḥ ||
nyāyārjitena dravyeṇa vittaśāṭhyavivarjitaḥ || 14 ||
tilaprasthamayīṃ kṛtvā gheṭuṃ sarvaguṇānvitām ||
gheṭuvatsaṃ suvarṇaṃ ca sudivyaṃ sarvalakṣaṇam || 15 ||
padmaṣaḍdalaṃ kṛtvā kuṅkumāktaiḥśubhaiḥ ||
pūjayettatra rudrādīnsarvāndevānanubhaktikaḥ || 16 ||
evaṃ saṃpūjya tāṃ dadyādbrāhmaṇāya svaśaktikaḥ ||
saratnaṃ sahiraṇyāṃ ca savibhūṣaṇabhūṣitām || 17 ||
tato nakaṃ samaśrīyādīpāndadyādu vistārāt ||
kārtikyāmiti kartavyaṃ pūrṇimāyāṃ prayatnataḥ || 18 ||
evaṃ yaḥ kurute samyagvibhāgena svaśaktikaḥ ||
yamamārgamayaṃ ghoraṃ narakaṃ ca na paśyati || 19 ||
kṛtvā pāpānyaśeṣāṇi sarvaṃgussatuḥkhajannaḥ ||
divi saṃkrīḍate vyāsa yāvadindrāśvatardeśe || 20 ||
vighato goṣva dānaṃ vai sarvottamamiha smṛtam ||
na tena sadṛśaṃ vyāsa paraṃ dānaṃ prakīrtitam || 21 ||
prayacchate yaḥ kapalāṃ savatsāṃ svarṇaśṛṅgikām ||
kāṃsyapātrāṃ rūpyakṣurāṃ sarvalakṣaṇalakṣitām || 22 ||
taistaiḥ guṇaiḥ kāmadudhāṃ bhūtvā sā gaurūpaitataṃ ||
pradātāraṃ naraṃ vyāsa paratraiha ca janmani || 23 ||
yadyadiṣṭatamaṃ loke yadasti dayitaṃ gṛhe ||
tattaddhanavate deyaṃ tadevaṃ kṣayamicchata || 24 ||
tulāpuruṣadānaṃ hi dānānāṃ dānaśuttamamaṃ ||
tulāsaṃrohaṇaṃ kārye yadīcchecchreyaātmanaḥ || 25 ||
yatkṛtvā mucyate pāpaiḥ ṣaḍbandhakatodbhavaiḥ ||
tulādānaṃ mahatpuṇyaṃ sarvapāpakṣayaṃkaram || || 26 ||
kṛtvā pāpānyaśeṣāṇi tulādānaṃ karoti yaḥ ||
sarvaistu pātakaiḥ muktaḥ sa divaṃ yātyasaṃśayam || 27 ||
apāpaṃ kṛtaṃ yadivaseniśāyāṃ dvissaṃkhyayormadhyadine niśānte ||
kālatraye kāyamanovacobhistulā pumānvai tadupākaroti || 28 ||
vālena vṛddhena mayā hi yuvā viijānartā jñānapareṇa pāpam ||
tatsarvaivamāśu kṛtaṃ madīyaṃ tulāpumānvai haratu smrārāriḥ || 29 ||
pātre prayuktaṃ draviṇaṃ mayādya pramāṇapūrṇī nihitaṃ tulāyām ||
tennaiva sārghaṃ tu mamāvaśeṣaṃ kṛtākṛtaṃ yatsukṛtaṃ sametu || 30 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
evaśu cārthaṃ taṃ dadyāt dvijebhyaḥ sarvadā hitaḥ ||
naikasyāpi pradātavyaṃ na nistārastato bhavet || || 31 ||
dadātyevaṃ tu yo vyāla tulāpuruṣottamam ||
hatvā pāpaṃ divaṃ tiṣṭhyādvadindrāśvatardeśe || 32 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ sāmānyadānavarṇanaṃ nāma caturdaśo'dhyāyaḥ || 14 ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
yenaikena hi dattena sarvaiṣāṃ prāpyate phalam ||
dānānāṃ tanmamākhyāhi mānuṣāṇāṃ hitārthinaḥ || 1 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
śṛṇu kāle pradattasya phalaṃ vindanti mānavāḥ ||
ekasyādapi sarvaiṣāṃ dānānāṃ taddadāmi te || 2 ||
dānānāṃ śuttamaṃ dānaṃ brahmāṇḍaṃ khalu mānavaiḥ ||
dātavyaṃ śaktikāmaistu saṃsārottāraṇāya vai || 3 ||
brahmāṇḍe sakale datte yatphalaṃ labhate naraḥ ||
tadekabhāvādāmīti saptaloka

--- Page 35 ---
dhipo bhavet || 8 ||
yāvaccandridivākarau nabhasivai yāvatsthirā medinī tāvatso'pi naraḥ svavaṃghavutasstvagoṃksāmoṃkasi ||
sarveṣṭeva manorugheṣu kakubhirbrahmāṇḍaḥ krīḍate paścādyāti padaṃ sudulebhataraṃ devaidhṛte māghavaṃ || 5 ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
bhagavanbrūhi brahmāṇḍaṃ yatpramāṇaṃ yadātmakaṃ ||
yadācāraṃ yathābhūtaṃ yena me pratyayo bhavet || 6 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
mune śṛṇu pravakṣyāmi yaduktaṃ tu vistarmaṃ ||
brahmāṇḍaṃ tat saṃkṣepācchrutvā pāpātpramucyate || 7 ||
yattatķāraṇamavyaktaṃ vyaktaṃ śivamnamāyamaṃ ||
tasmātsajāyate brahmā dvidhābhūtāddhiḥ kālataḥ || 8 ||
brahmāṇḍaṃ sṛjati brahmā caturdaśabhavātmakaṃ ||
taddhi ca kamatastat samāsācchṛṇuyanataḥ || 9 ||
pātālāni tu sapta eva bhuvanāni tathordhvataḥ ||
ucchāyo dviguṇastasya jalamadhye sthitasya ca || 10 ||
tasyādhāraḥ sthito nāgaśca viṣṇuḥ prakīrtitaḥ ||
brahmaṇo vacaso hetorbibhati sakalaṃ tvitadṛk || 11 ||
śeṣasya guṇānvaktuṃ na śakyā devadānavāḥ ||
yonantaḥ paṭhyate siddairvārṣagaṇapūjitaḥ || 12 ||
śiraḥsāhasraśrutakasya sarvaṃ vidhyotayandiśaḥ ||
phaṇāmaṇisahasreṇa svastikāmaladṛṣaṇaḥ || 13 ||
madāghūrṇitanetro'sau sāmbhiśete ṣṭhavālaḥ ||
śaṃgī kirīṭī bhrāmati yassadevaiḥ kakuṇḍalaḥ || 14 ||
sāyaṃ gaṅgāpravāheṇa śvetaśailopraśobhitaḥ ||
nīlavāsā madodviktaḥ kailāsādirirvā paraḥ || 15 ||
lāṃgalasaktahastāgro vibhranmuṣalamuttamaṃ ||
yo'rcyante nāgakanyābhissvargaṇavaṇāṃbharādvrāt || 16 ||
saṃkarṣaṇātmako rudro viṣānaśikhalobhajvalaḥ ||
kalpādi niṣkramante yadvarenyobhyoṃ śikhā muhuḥ ||
dagdhvā jagatrayaṃ śāntā bhavantyevanuśuśruma || 17 ||
āste pātālamūlastyas śeṣaḥ kṣitimaṇḍalaṃ ||
bibhrasvapṛṣṭhe bhūteśaśeṣoṃśeṣaguṇācitaḥ || 18 ||
tasya vīryaprabāvasya sākāśāñśidhraiḥśaiḥ api ||
na hi varṇayituṃ śakyaḥ svarūpaṃ jñātumeva vā || 19 ||
āste kusumamaleva phaṇāmaṇiśilāruṇā ||
yasyaiṣā sakalā pṛthvī kastarddhyai vidhyati || 20 ||
yadā vijaṃbhate'nanto madāghūrṇitalocanāḥ ||
tadā calati bhūreṣā sāvṛtoyādhikānanā || 21 ||
daśasāhasramakaṃ pātālaṃ munisattamaṃ ||
atalatalaṃ caiva sutalaṃ ca rasātalaṃ || 22 ||
talaṃ talātalaṃ cāśryaṃ pātālaṃ saptamaṃ mataṃ ||
bhūmerghastastha lokā ime jñeyā vivakṣaṇaiḥ || 23 ||
ucchāyo dviguṇaśreṣāṃ sarveṣāṃ ratnamabhayaḥ ||
ratnavantaḥ'tha prāsādā bhūmayo hemasaṃbhavāḥ || 24 ||
teṣu dānavadaityā nāgānāṃ jātayastathā ||
nivasanti mahānāgā rākṣasā daityasaṃbhavāḥ || 25 ||
prāha svargasadomaghye pātālānīti nāradaḥ ||
svarlokāditaramyāṇi tebhyo'savāgato diviḥ || 26 ||
nānābhūṣaṇabhūṣāstu maṇayo yatra suprabhaḥ ||
āhlādakāni śubhāṇi pātālaṃ kena tatsam || 27 ||
pātāle kasya na prītiritaścetaśca śobhitamaṃ ||
devadānavakanyābhirvimatkasyābhijāyate || 28 ||
divākaraśmayo yatra na bhavanti vibhābhiniśi ||
na śītaṃ ātapo yatra maṇitejobhna kevalaṃ || 29 ||
--- Page 36 ---
bhakṣyabhojyābhrapānāni bhuñjyante khuditairbhṛśam ||
yatra na jñāyate kālo gatopi munisattama || 20 ||
puṃskokilarutaṃ yatra padmāni kamalākarāḥ |
na dyassarāṃsi ramyāṇi dhanyonyavicarāṇi ca || 21 ||
bhūṣaṇānyatiśubhāṇi gaṃdhārbyaṃ cānulepanam |
vīṇāveṇumṛdaṅgānāṃ svanā geyāni ca dvija || 22 ||
daityo raiśca bhuñjyante pātāle vai sukhāni ca |
tapasā samavāpnoti dānavenissiddhāmanaivaiḥ || 23 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ brahmāṇḍakathanepātālalokavaṇane nāma pañcadaśodhyāyaḥ || 15 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca |
teṣāṃ muddhopariṣṭāddhī narkāṃstāñchṛṇuṣva ca |
matto śunivara śreṣṭha pacyante yatra pāpinaḥ || 1 ||
rauravaśśūkaro roghastālo vivasanastathā |
mahājvālastaptyakuṃbho lavaṇopi vilohitaḥ || 2 ||
vaitaraṇī pūyavahā krimibhojanasaḥ |
asīpatravanaṃ ghoraṃ lālābhakṣaḥ ca dāruṇaḥ || 3 ||
tathā pūyavahāḥ prāyo bhinejjvālo dhaghāśśirāḥ |
saṃdaṃśaḥ kālasūtraśca tamaśśāvī cirogdhanaḥ || 4 ||
kvabhojanotha ruṣṭasya mahāraurava śālmalī |
ityādyā bahavastatra narkā duḥkhadāyakāḥ || 5 ||
pacyante teṣu puruṣāḥ pāpakarmāṇastu ye |
kramāddrakṣye tu tānvyāsa sāvadhānatayā śṛṇu || 6 ||
kūṭasākṣyaṃ tu yo vakti vinā viṣṇo surāṃśca gāḥ |
sadāsānṛtavadeḍyastu sa naro yāti rauravam || 7 ||
śruṇahā svaṇahatāṃ ca gorodhī viṣaghātakaḥ |
surāpo brahmahatā ca paradravyāpāharakaḥ || 8 ||
yastattsaṃgī sa vai yāti mṛto nyāsa guroverghāt |
tataḥ kuṃbe svastumātuṃgośśaiva durhitustatthā || 9 ||
sāṅkhyā vikrayakṛtśca vāgdhekī keśavikriyī |
tatlohaiṣu pacyante yaśca bhaktaṃ parityajet || 10 ||
avamantā guruṇāṃ yaḥ paścāddroktā narāghmaḥ |
devadūṣayitā caiva devavikrikayakasya yaḥ || 11 ||
agamyagāmī yaścāti yāti saptabalaṃ dvija |
caurau goghni pitato mayodādṛṣṭakastathā || 12 ||
devadvijagitaddheṣā ratnadūṣayitā ca yaḥ |
sa yāti krimibhakṣaṃ vai krimīnāti duriṣṭhakṛt || 13 ||
pitṛdevagurūn yastu paryaṣṭhāti narāghmaḥ |
lālābhakṣaṃ sa yātyajño yaśśaṭhakūṭakuñjaraḥ || 14 ||
yaścāntyajenaṃ saṃsecyo dhratadrāhī tu yo dvijaḥ |
ayājyayājakascaiva tathevāmakṣyabhakṣakaḥ || 15 ||
rughirauṣve patantyete somavikrayiṇasca ye |
madhuhastrāmahāyāti krūrāṃ vaitaraṇīṃ nadīm || 16 ||
navyauvanamattāśca marthādābhedinasca ye |
te kṛtyaṃ yāntyaśaucāśca kulakājīvinasca ye || 17 ||
asīpatravanaṃ yāti vṛkṣacchedī vṛtheva yaḥ |
khurasrkā mṛgavyāghā vahnejjvāle patanti te || 18 ||
adhacāro hi yo vipraḥ kṣatriyo vaiśya eva ca |
yātyante dvija tatraiva yaḥ śvapākeṣu vahirdaḥ || 19 ||
vratasya lopakā ye ca svāśramāddhyutāśca ye |
saṃdaṃśyātanamādhye patanti bhṛśādāruṇe || 20 ||
vīryaṃ svameṣṭhu skandayuyeṃ narā brahmacāriṇaḥ |
putrā nādhyāpitā yaiśca te patanti śvabhojane || 21 ||
ete cānye ca narkāḥ śataśostha sahasraśaḥ |
yeṣu

--- Page 37 ---
duṣkṛtakarmāṇaḥ pacyante yātanāgatāḥ || 22 ||
tathaiva pāpānyetāni tathānyāni sahasraśaḥ |
bhuJyante yāni puruṣairnarkāntaragoceraiḥ || 23 ||
varṇāśramivibhraṃśaṃ ca karma kurvanti ye narāḥ |
karmaṇā manasā vācā naraye tu patanti te || 24 ||
aghaviśroribhedaiśca ye nārakā divi devatāḥ |
devānaghobhuktvā sarvānaghān paśyanti nārakāḥ || 25 ||
sthāvarāḥ kṛmipākāśca pakṣiṇaḥ paśavo mṛgāḥ |
dhārmikākhidaśāstaddhanmokṣiṇaśca yathākramam || 26 ||
yāvanto jaṃtusvargaṃ tāvanto narakaukasaḥ |
pāpakṛdyāti narakaṃ prāyaścittaparāṅmukhaḥ || 27 ||
guruṇi gurubhiścaiva laghūni laghubhistathā |
prāyaścittāni kālena manusvāyambhuvobravīt || 28 ||
yāni teṣāmaśeṣāṇāṃ karmāṇyuktāni teṣu vai |
prāyaścittamaśeṣeṇa harānusmaraṇaṃ param || 29 ||
prāyaścittaṃ tu yasyaivaṃ pāpaṃ puṃsaḥ prajāyate |
kṛte pāpeṣvutāpośpi śivasaṃsmaraṇaṃ param || 30 ||
māheśvaramavāpnoti madhyāhnādiṣu saṃsmaran |
prātaranniśi ca saṃdhyāyāṃ kṣīṇapāpo bhavennaraḥ || 31 ||
muktiṃ prayāti svargaṃ vā samastaklśasaṃkṣayam |
śivasya smaraṇādeva tasya śambhoramāpateḥ || 32 ||
pāpāntarāyo viprendra japahomacannādi ca |
bhavātyeva na kutrāpi trailokye munisattama || 33 ||
maheśvare mitirjasya japahomārcanādiṣu |
yatpuṇyaṃ tatkṛtaṃ tena devendratvādikaṃ phalam || 34 ||
pumān narakaṃ yāti yaḥ smaranbhaktito mune |
aharniśaṃ śivaṃ tasmāts kṣīṇāśeṣapātakaḥ || 35 ||
narakasvargorasañjāye pāpuṇye dvijottama |
yayostavedaṃ tu duḥkhāyāntyasukhāyodravāya ca || 36 ||
tadeva prītaye bhūtvā punarduḥkhāya jāyate |
tasmādduḥkhātmakaṃ nāsti na ca kiñcitsukhātmakam || 37 ||
manasaḥ pariṇāmośyaṃ sukhaduḥkhopalakoṣaṇam |
jñānameva paraṃ brahma jñānaṃ tattāya kalpate || 38 ||
jñānātmakamidam idaṃ viśvaṃ sakalaṃ sacarācaram |
parivijñānataḥ kiñcidbhūyate na paraṃ mune || 39 ||
evametanmayākhyātaṃ sarve narakamāṇḍalam |
ata ūrdhvaṃ pravakṣyāmi sāṃprataṃ maṃḍalaṃ bhuvaḥ || 40 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe paṃcamyāṃ umāsaṃhitāyāṃ brahmāṇḍavarṇane narokoddhāravarṇane nāma ṣoḍaśośyāyaḥ || 16 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca

pārāśarye susaṃkṣepācchṛṇu tvaṃ vadato mama |
maṃḍalaṃ ca bhuvassamyak saptadvīpādisaṃyutam || 1 ||
jabuḥ plakṣaśālmaliśca kuśāḥ krauñcaśca śākakaḥ |
puṣkarassaptamastairvai samudreḥ saptabhirjvṛtāḥ || 2 ||
lavaṇekṣurasaḥ sarpirvai dighudughajaḥ jalāśāyāḥ |
jaṃbudvīpassamastarānāmetṣāṃ madhyataḥ sthitaḥ || 3 ||
tasyāpi meruḥ kāṃlena madhye kanakoparvataḥ |
praviṣṭaḥ ṣoḍaśāghastādyojanaistasya cocchrayaḥ || 4 ||
caturaśītimānaitastaidrīṃtriśanmūrdhni vistavrtaḥ |
bhūmipṛṣṭhasthyaśailo'yaṃ vistarartatasya sarvantaḥ || 5 ||
mūle ṣoḍaśasāhasraḥ karṇikākārasaṃsthitaḥ |
himavān hemakūṭaśca niṣapaghasya dakṣiṇe || 6 ||
--- Page 38 ---
nīlaḥ śvetaśca śṛṅgī ca uttare varṣaparvataḥ ||
daśasāhasrikā hete ratnavantaḥ aruṇaprabhāḥ || 7 ||
sahasrayojanōtsedhāstāvadvistarāiṇaśca te ||
bhārataṃ prathamaṃ varṣe tataḥ kiṃpuruṣaṃ smṛtam || 8 ||
harivarṣe tataḥ anyad vai merodakṣiṇato mune ||
ramyakaṃ cottare pārśve tasyāṃśe tu hiraṇmayam || 9 ||
uttare kuravāścaiva yathā vai bhārataṃ tathā ||
navasāhasramekaṃ ekametāṣāṃ munisattama || 10 ||
ilāvṛtaṃ tu tanmadhye tanmadhye meruruñchitaḥ ||
meroścaturdikṣaṃ tatra navasāhasraśucchitam || 11 ||
ilāvṛtamṛṣiśreṣṭha catvāraścātra parvatāḥ ||
viṣkambhā racitā merorye ojitāḥ punaruñchitāḥ || 12 ||
pūrve hi mandaro nāma dakṣiṇe gandhamādanaḥ ||
vipulaḥ paścime bhāge supārśvaścottare sthitaḥ || 13 ||
kadaṃbo jambūvṛkṣaśca pippalō vaṭa eva ca ||
ekādaśaśatāyāmāḥ pādapā giriketavaḥ || 14 ||
jambūdvīpasya nāmno vai hetuṃ śṛṇu mahāmune ||
virājate mahāvṛkṣāstatsvabhāvaṃ vadāmi te || 15 ||
mahāgajapramāṇāni jambūstasyāḥ phalāni ca ||
patanti bhūbhṛtaḥ pṛṣṭhe śīghryemāṇāni sarvataḥ || 16 ||
rasena teṣāṃ vikhyātā tatra jambūnadīti vai ||
paritaḥ vartate tatra pīyate tadvaivāsibhiḥ || 17 ||
na svedo na ca daurgandhyaṃ na jarā cendriyagrahaḥ ||
tasyāstāṭe sthitānāṃ tujjanānāṃ tatra jāyate || 18 ||
tīramṛtsnāṃ ca samprāpya sukhavāyuviśoṣitām ||
jāmbūnadākhyaṃ bhavati suvarṇaṃ siddhabhuṣaṇam || 19 ||
bhadraśvaṃ pūrvato meroḥ ketumālaṃ ca paścime ||
varṣe dve tu muniśreṣṭha tayormadhye ilāvṛtam || 20 ||
vanaṃ caitrathaṃ pūrve dakṣiṇe gandhamādanaḥ ||
vibhrājaṃ paścime taduttare nandanaṃ smṛtam || 21 ||
aruṇodaṃ mahābhadraṃ śīnodaṃ mānaṃ smṛtam ||
sarāṃsyetāni catvāri devabhōgyāni sarvaśaḥ || 22 ||
śītāṃśanaḥ kuruṅgaśca kurro mālyavāṃstathā ||
caike kapramukhā meroḥ pūrvataḥ kesarācalāḥ || 23 ||
trikūṭaḥ śiśiraśca eva pataṅgo rucakastathā ||
niṣadhaḥ kapilācāśca dakṣiṇe kesarācalāḥ || 24 ||
sinīvāsaḥ kuṭumbaśca kapilō nāradastathā ||
nāgādyaśca girayaḥ paścime kesarācalāḥ || 25 ||
śaṅkhacūḍoḍya ṛṣabho haṃso nāma mahīdharaḥ ||
kālaṃ jarādyaśca tathā uttare kesarācalāḥ || 26 ||
merorūpari madhye hi śātakoṭiṃ vidhaiḥ puram ||
caturdaśasahasrāṇi yojanāni ca saṃkhyayā || 27 ||
aṣṭānāṃ lokapālānāṃ paritastāmanukramāt ||
yathādiśaṃ yathārūpaṃ puroṣṭhāvupakalpitāḥ || 28 ||
tasyāṃ ca brahmaṇaḥ puryāṃ pātayitvā indu maṇḍalaṃ ||
viṣṇupādavinirkyāntā gaṅgā patati vai nadī || 29 ||
sītā cālakananā ca cakṣubhedrā ca vai kramāt ||
sā tatra patitā dikṣu caturdhaḥ pratyapadyata || 30 ||
sītā pūrveṇa śailaṃ hi nandā caiva tu dakṣiṇe ||
sā cakṣuḥ paścime caiva bhadrā cottarato vrajet || 31 ||
girīn atīlya sakalāṃścaturdikṣu mahāmbudhinam ||
sā yayau prayatā bhūtā gaṅgā tripathagāminī || 32 ||
sunīlaniṣadghau yau tau mālyavaddhaṅghamādanau ||
teṣāṃ madhyagato meruḥ karṇikākāra

--- Page 39 ---
saṃsthitaḥ || 33 ||
bhārataḥ ketumālaśca bhadrāśvaḥ kuravastatthā ||
pañcāṇi lokapañcasya mayādālokparvatāḥ || 34 ||
jaṭharaṃ devakūṭasya āyāme dakṣiṇottare ||
gaṃghamādanakeḷāsau pūrvapścimato gatau || 36 ||
pūrvapścimato merornieṣaṅgho nīlaparvatah ||
dakṣiṇottaramāyātau karṇikāntavyavasthitau || 36 ||
jaṭharādyāḥ sthitā meror yeṣāṃ dvo dvo vyavasthitau ||
kesarāḥ parvatā ute śvetādyāḥ sumanormāḥ || 37 ||
śailānāmuttare droṇyassiddācāraṇasevitāḥ ||
suramyāṇi tathā tāṣu kānnāni purāṇi ca || 38 ||
sarveṣāṃ caiva devānāṃ yakṣagaṃdharvarakṣasāṃ ||
krīḍite devadaite yāśśailapāyeṣvahinīśam || 39 ||
ghiminā mālyā bhūte maumāssvargāḥ prakīrtitāḥ ||
na teṣu pāpakartāro yānti paśyanti kurvacit || 40 ||
yāni kiṃpuruṣādīni varṣāṇyaṣṭau mahāśune ||
na teṣu śoko nāpacyo nedgaḥ kṣudryādikam || 41 ||
svasthāḥ prajā nirātaṃkāssarvaduḥkhavivajitāḥ ||
daśadvaādaśavarṣāṇāṃ sahasrāṇi sthirāyuṣaḥ || 42 ||
kṛtretādikāśchaiva bhomāntyaṃbhāsiṃ sarvetaḥ ||
na teṣu varṣate devastteṣu stthāneṣu kalpanā || 43 ||
sattveteṣu nadyasca sujātāssvarṇavāḷkāḥ ||
śataśassānti kṣudrāśca tāṣu krīḍacchumo janaḥ || 44 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ brahmaṇḍakathane jambūdvīpavarṣavarṇanaṃ nāma saptadaśo'dhyāyaḥ || 17 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
vakṣye'haṃ bhārataṃ varṣaṃ himādreśchaiva dakṣiṇe ||
uttare tu samudrasya bhāratī yatra saṃsthitiḥ || 1 ||
navayojanasāhasro vistāro'sya mahāśune ||
svargāpavargayoḥ karmabhūmiraṣā smṛtā budhaiḥ || 2 ||
ataḥsaṃprāpyate puṃbhisssvargau naraka eva ca ||
bhārasyāpi varṣasya nava bhedānbravīmi te || 3 ||
indradvumaḥ kaseru śca tāmravarṇo gabhastimān ||
nāgadvīpastathā saumyo gaṃdharvastvatha vāruṇaḥ || 4 ||
ayaṃ tu navamastteṣāṃ dvīpasāgarasaṃbhṛtaḥ ||
yojanānāṃ sahasraṃ tu dvīpo'yaṃ dakṣiṇottaraḥ || 5 ||
pūrve kirātā yasya studeś kṣiṇe yavanāḥ sthitāḥ ||
paścime ca tathā jñeyā uttare hi tapasvinnaḥ || 6 ||
brāhmaṇāḥ kṣatriyā vaiśyā madhye śūdrāśca bhūyaśaḥ ||
ijyāyudddhapraṇāsevā varttaṃto vyavasthitāḥ || 7 ||
mahendro malayasadyaḥ mudāmā cakṣeparvatāḥ ||
vindhyasca pāriyātraśca saptatra kulaparvatāḥ || 8 ||
vedasmṛtipurāṇādyāḥ pāriyātrodbhavāmune ||
sarvapāpaharā jñeyā darśanātsparśanādapi || 9 ||
narmadā murasādyāśca saptānyāśca sahasraśaḥ ||
vindhyodbhavā mahānadyassarvapāpaharāśubhāḥ || 10 ||
godāvarī bhīmarathītatāpī praṣukhīniraṃgāḥ ||
girerivinirgantā ṛkṣāttrudyaḥ pāpabhayāpahāḥ || 11 ||
sahyapādodbhavā nadyaḥ kṛṣṇaveṇyādikāstatthā ||
kṛtamālātāmraparṇīpramukhā malayodbhavāḥ || 12 ||
triyāmā cārṣikulyādyā mahendraprabhavassmṛtāḥ ||
ṛṣikulyākumāryādyāḥ śuktimatpādassaṃbhavāḥ || 13 ||
nānājanapādāstteṣu maṇḍaleṣu vasanti vai ||
āsāṃ pibaṃti pānīyaṃ sarassvuviviṅgeṣu ca || 14 ||
catvāri bhārate varṣe yugānyāsanmahāśune ||
kṛtādīni

--- Page 40 ---
na cānyeṣu dvīpeṣu prabhavanti hi || 15 ||
dānāni cātra dīyante śuklaiś ca yājñikaiḥ ||
tapastapānti yatayaḥ paralokārtham ādarāt || 16 ||
yato hi kareṃ bhūreṣā jambūdvīpe mahāśune ||
atrāpi bhāratam śreṣṭhataḥ anyā bhogarūpamayaḥ || 17 ||
kadācic chabhe martyaissahaśraiḥ unisattam ||
atra janmasahasrāṇāṃ māṇuṣyam puṇyasañcayaiḥ || 18 ||
svargopavargaspadamārgabhūte dhanyāstu te bhāratabhumibhāge ||
gāyanti devāḥ kila gītakāni bhavanti bhūyaḥ puruṣāḥ surāste || 19 ||
avāpya māṇuṣyamayaṃ kadācid dhṛtya śambhoḥ paramātmarūpe ||
phalāni sarvāṇi tu karmajāni yāsyāmyahaṃ tattvanutāṃ hi tasya || 20 ||
āpyanti dhanyāḥ khalu te manuṣyāḥ surekṣutāḥ karmaṇi sañniviṣṭhāḥ ||
jabuhīṃ yeṣāṃ khalu bhārate'sti te svargaṃ mokṣobhayalābhavantaḥ || 21 ||
lakṣayojanavistārasya mastaparimaṇḍalaḥ ||
jambūdvīpo mayā khyātaḥ kṣārodadhiparisaṃvṛtaḥ || 22 ||
saṃveṣṭya kṣārasamuddhiṃ śatasāhasrasaṃmitam ||
tato hi dviguṇo brahmapuṣkadvīpaḥ prakīrtitaḥ || 23 ||
gomantaścaiva candraśca nārado dardurāstathā ||
somakastumanāśailo vaijrājaścaiva saptamaḥ || 24 ||
varṣācaleṣu ramyeṣu sthitāssatataṃ prajāḥ ||
vasanti devagaṃdharvāṃ varṣeṣvetteṣu nityaśaḥ || 25 ||
nāghayo vyāghayo vāpi janānāṃ tatra kutrācit ||
daśa varṣasahasrāṇi tatra jīvanti mānavāḥ || 26 ||
atuttā śikhī caiva pāpajñī tridivaṃ kṛpā ||
amṛtā śuktā caiva sanaiścara ca nirnagāḥ || 27 ||
kṣudranacyastathā śailāstatra śatasahasraśaḥ ||
tāḥ pibantu susamṛdhā nadījanpadāstu || 28 ||
na tatrāpi yugāvasthā yathā sthāneṣu saptasu ||
tretāyugasamaḥ kālastu sarvadaiva mahāśune || 29 ||
viparītatvayenāśyāste śūdrāśca munisattam ||
kalpavṛkṣasamānastu tanmadhye surmahātaruḥ || 30 ||
puṣkastatvāmarsajño vai puṣkadvīpo dvijottama ||
ijyate tatra bhagavāñchankaro lokaśaṃkaraḥ || 31 ||
hariśca bhagavān brahmā yajñaiḥ maṃtraiś ca vaidikaiḥ ||
saṃkṣepeṇa tathā bhuyadṛśālmaliṃ tvaṃ niśāmaya || 32 ||
saptavarṣāṇi tatraiva teṣāṃ nāmāni śṛṇu ||
śvetośca haritaścaiva jīmūto rohitastathā || 33 ||
vaikalo mānaścaiva suprasabha saptamo mune ||
śālmalena tu vṛkṣeṇa dvīpaḥ śālmalisañjñakaḥ || 34 ||
dviguṇena samudreṇa satatam saṃvṛtaḥ sthitaḥ ||
varṣābhiryañjakā nadyastāsāṃ nāmāni me śṛṇu || 35 ||
śuklā raktā hiraṇyā ca candrā śubhā vimocānā ||
niṣṛtiḥ saptamī tāsāṃ puṇyatoyāḥ suśītalāḥ || 36 ||
satraiva tāni varṣāṇi catuvarṇānutāni ca ||
bhagavantaṃ sadā śambhuṃ yajante vividhaiḥ mañtraiḥ || 37 ||
devānāṃ tatra sābhiṣyamatīva sumanoraume ||
eṣa dvīpassamudreṇa surodenā samāvṛtaḥ || 38 ||
dviguṇena kuśadvīpaḥ samantādāhutaḥ

