sthitaḥ ||
vasanti tatra daiteya manujeḥ saha dānavāḥ || 39 ||
tathaivadevagandharvo yakṣāḥ kiṃpuruṣādayaḥ ||
varṇāstatra eva catvāro nijānuṣṭhānatparāḥ ||

|| 40 ||
tathaiva ca kuśadvīpe brāhmaṇaṃ ca janārdinam ||
yajanti ca tatheśānaṃ sarvakāmaphalapradam || 41 ||
kuśaśayo hariḥ śaiva dyutimānpuṣpavāṃstathā ||
maṇidhrumo hemśailastamo mandrācalaḥ || 42 ||
nāmāni saptā nāmāni śṛṇu tattvataḥ ||
ghṛtapāpā śivā caiva pavitrasaṃmitastathā || 43 ||
vidyā daṃbhā mahī cānyā sarvapāpaharāstrimāḥ ||
anyāssahasraśaṃsati śubhāpo hemabālukaḥ || 44 ||
kuśadvīpe kuśastambho ghṛtodena samāvṛtaḥ ||
kauśadvīpo mahābhāga śrūyatāṃ cāparo mahān || 45 ||
dviguṇena samudreṇa dighaṃdena cāvṛtaḥ ||
varṣāṃcalā mahābhuddhe teṣāṃ nāmāni me śṛṇu || 46 ||
kauśca vāmanaścaiva tṛtīyaścāṃghakārakaḥ ||
divāvṛtirmanascaiva puṇḍarīkaśca dundubhiḥ || 47 ||
nivasanti nirāntakā varṣaśaileṣu teṣu vai ||
sarveṣāṃ varṇameṣu subhdevagaṇaiḥ prajāḥ || 48 ||
brāhmaṇāḥ kṣatriyā vaiśyāḥ śūdrāśca anukamoditāḥ ||
santi tatra mahānandyastpānyāstu sahasraśaḥ || 49 ||
gaurī kumuddatī caiva sandhyā rātrimanojavā ||
śāntiśca puṇḍarīkā ca yāḥ pibaṃti payaḥśubham || 50 ||
bhagavānpūjyate tatra yogarūdravraropavān ||
dīghamaṇḍodakścāpi śākadvīpena saṃvṛtaḥ || 51 ||
dviguṇenādrayaḥ saptateṣāṃ nāmāni me śṛṇu ||
pūrve tatrodayagiriñcalagdhāraḥ pare yataḥ || 52 ||
pṛṣṭhatovstigiriścaiva jhavikescaśca keśarī ||
śākastatra mahāvṛkṣaḥ siddhargandharvasevitatḥ || 53 ||
tatra puṇyā janapadāścāturvairṇyaṃ samanvitāḥ ||
nāmascātra mahāpuṇyāssarvapāpabhayāpahāḥ || 54 ||
sukumārī kumārī ca nalinī veṇukā tathā ||
ikṣuśca reṇukā caiva gabhastisaptamī tathā || 55 ||
anyāssahasraśastatra kṣudranādyo mahāśune ||
mahīgharāstathā santi śataśotha sahasraśaḥ || 56 ||
dharmadhānine teṣvira svargādāgatya mānavāḥ ||
varṣeṣu teṣu pṛthivīṃ viharanti parasparaṃ || 57 ||
śākadvīpe tu vai sūryyaḥ prītyā janapadessadā ||
yathoktairjyate samyakkarmbhirniyatātmabhiḥ || 58 ||
kṣīrodena āvṛtaḥ so'pi dviguṇena samaṃtataḥ ||
kṣīrāgdhyaḥ savṛto vyāsa puṣkarāhvayena saṃvṛtaḥ || 59 ||
dviguṇena mahāvarṣatatra khyāto'tra mānasaḥ ||
yojanānāṃ sahasrāṇi pañcaivo dhvaṃsaṃbhicchṛtaḥ || 60 ||
tāni caiva tu lakṣāṇi sarvatovalyākṛtiḥ ||
puṣkaradvīpavalayo madhyena vibhajanti ca || 61 ||
tenaiva valyākārā dvīpavarṣasamākṛtiḥ ||
daśavarṣasahasrāṇi tatra jīvanti mānavāḥ || 62 ||
nirāmayā vītaśokā rāgadveṣavivarjitāḥ ||
aghamona matasteṣāṃ na baṃdhavadhakoṃ śune || 63 ||
satyānṛte na tasyāstāṃ sadaiva vasitassadā ||
tulyaveṣāstu manujahemanavavarṇaikaropiṇaḥ || 64 ||
varṣaścāyaṃ tu kāleja bhomasvargopamopamaḥ ||
sarvasya sukhadaḥ kālo jarārogivivarjitaḥ || 65 ||
puṣkare ghātakīkhaṇḍe mahāvīte

--- Page 42 ---
mahāśune ||
nyagrodhaṃ puṣkaradwīpe brahmaṇaḥ sthānamuttamamṛ || 66 ||
tasmin nivasate brahmā pūjyamānaḥ surāsuraiḥ ||
svādudakena nibhinā puṣkaraḥ paribheṣitaḥ || || 67 ||
evaṃ dvīpāssamudrestu sapta saptabhirāvṛtāḥ ||
dvīpāścaiva sakhudāśca samānā dviguṇaiḥ paraiḥ || 68 ||
uktātiriktatā teṣāṃ sakhudreṣu samāni vai ||
paryāsi sarvedāsvapatvaṃ jāyante naṭukadāchanā || 69 ||
sthālīsthyaṃgisaṃyogādgho no munisattamā ||
tathendubuddhau śilalayuddhaṃ bhavati dhruvam || 70 ||
udyāstamane tindorvoṃdhetāyāpo hrasanti cā ||
ato nyūnātiriktatāśca pakṣayoḥ śukrakṛṣṇayoḥ || 71 ||
apāṃ vṛddhikṣayau dṛṣṭau śataśastu daśottaram ||
sakhudāṇāṃ munisreṣṭha sarveṣāṃ kathitaṃ tava || 72 ||
bhojanaṃ puṣkaradwīpe prajāssarvāḥ sadaiva hi ||
khaṇḍasya kurvate vipra tatra svayamupasthitam || 73 ||
svāṃgado yasya puruto nāsti lokarasya saṃsthitiḥ ||
dviguṇā hiraṇmayī bhūmissarvairiṃtuvijiitā || 74 ||
lokālokastataḥśailasasahasrāṇyacalo hi saḥ ||
ucchrūyeṇa hi tāvanti yojanāyutavistṛtaḥ || 75 ||
tamaśchāṇḍakaṭāhena seyamūrdhvī mahāśune ||
pañcāśatkoṭivistārā sadvīpā samahīgharā || 76 ||
āghāraghṛtā sarveṣāṃ sarveṣu guṇādhikā ||
seyaṃ dhātrīca kāleya sarveṣāṃ jagatāmilaṃ || 77 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe paścamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ brahmaṇḍakathane sapadvīpavaṛṇanaṃ nāmāṣṭādaśo'dhyāyaḥ || 18 ||
sānatkumāra uvāca

ravicandramasoryāvānmayūkhā bhāsaṃti hi ||
tāvatsramāṇā pṛthivī mūlokarasstu gīyate || 1 ||
sūmeryojanalaḥse tu saṃsthitaṃ ravimaṇḍalam ||
yojanānāṃ sahasrāṇi sadaiva parirasaṃkhyayā || 2 ||
śaśinastu pramāṇāya jagataḥ paricakṣate ||
rakhūrdhvaṃ śaśī tatstho lakṣayojanasaṃkhyayā || 3 ||
mahāṇāṃ maṇḍalaṃ kṛttasnaṃ śaśorupari saṃsthitam ||
sanakṣatraṃ sahasrāṇi daśaiva paritopīr || 4 ||
budhastasmādatho kāvyastasmādgaurasya maṇḍalam ||
bṛhaspatistadrūrdhvaṃ tu tasyopāri śanaiścaraḥ || 5 ||
saptarṣimaṇḍalaṃ tasmāccakaṃśeṇaikena saṃsthitam ||
ṛṣibhyastu sahasrāṇāṃ śatādūrdhve dhruvaḥ sthitaḥ || 6 ||
meḍhībhūtaḥ sa yastasya jyotiścakrasya vai dhruvaḥ ||
dhrubhuvaḥ svarita jñeyaṃ dhruvam ūrdhvaṃ dhruvādvāk || 7 ||
ekayojanakotiṭastu yatra te kalpavāsinaḥ ||
dhruvādūrdhvaṃ maharlokasanmete brahmaṇaḥ sutāḥ || 8 ||
sanakāśca sanandāśca tṛtīyaśca sanātanaḥ ||
kapilāśca āsuraiścaiva voḍuḥ pañcaśikhaḥ tathā || 9 ||
uparisthāttataḥ śuko dvvilakṣābhyantare sthitaḥ ||
dvilakṣayojanaṃ tasmādaghaḥ somasutaḥ smṛtaḥ || 10 ||
dvilakṣayojanaṃ tasmādūrdhvaṃ bhauma sthito mune ||
dvilakṣayojanaṃ tasmādūrdhvaṃ jīvaḥ sthito guruḥ || 11 ||
dvilakṣayojanaṃ jīvādūrdhvaṃ saurirityevasthitaḥ ||
ete saptaragrahāḥ proktāssvarasvarāśiṃcayavasthitāḥ || 12 ||
rudralakṣeṣu yojanataḥ sanmoghrūmṛṣayaḥ sthitāḥ ||
viśvalakṣeṣu yojanato dhruvasthitiruhdāhṛtā || 13 ||
--- Page 43 ---
caturguṇottare cārdhe janolokāt tapaḥ smṛtam ||
vairājā yatra devā vai sthitā dāhivivarjitāḥ || 14 ||
ṣaḍguṇena tapolokāt satyaloko vyavasthitaḥ ||
brahmalokāḥ sa vijñeyo vasantya malacetasaḥ || 15 ||
satyadharmatāśaiva jñānino brahmacāriṇaḥ |
yadrāminośtha bhūlokāt trivisanti hi mānavāḥ || 16 ||
śuva loke tu saṃsiddhā munayo devarūpiṇaḥ ||
svargaloke surādityā maruto vasavo'śvinau || 17 ||
viśvedevās tathā rudrās sādhyā nāgāḥ khagādyaḥ |
navagrahā s tatas tatra ṛṣayo vītakalmaṣāḥ || 18 ||
ete saptamahālokāḥ kathitās tava ||
pātālāni ca saiva brahmāṇḍasya ca vistaraḥ || 19 ||
dviṣu kṣaphalaṃ yaddṛtiśroṅghvam ghastathā ||
etadaṇḍakaṭāhena sarvanto vai samāvṛtam || 20 ||
payasā daśaguṇena sarvatas tat samāvṛtam ||
vahninā vāyunā cāpi nabhasā tamasā tathā || 21 ||
bhūtādināpi mahatā diguṇottaravestiṭāḥ ||
mahāntaṃ ca samāvṛtya pradhānaṃ puruṣaḥ sthitaḥ || 22 ||
anantasya na tasyāsti saṃkhyāpi paramātmanaḥ |
tenānantaṃ iti khyātaḥ pramāṇaṃ nāsti vai yataḥ || 23 ||
hetubhūtas samastasya prakṛtis sā parā mune ||
aṇḍānāṃ tu sahasrāṇāṃ sahasrā nyutāni ca || 24 ||
īdṛśānāṃ prabhūtāni tasmādavyaktajanmanaḥ ||
dāruṇyagnis tile tailaṃ payassu ca yathā ghṛtam || 25 ||
tathāsau paramātmā vai sarvaṃ vyāptyātmavedanaḥ ||
ādivījāt prasuvate tatas tebhyaḥ pareṇḍajāḥ || 26 ||
tebhyaḥ putrās thānyeṣāṃ vījānyanyāni vai tataḥ ||
mahṛdādyo viśe pāntās tadrvanti surādayaḥ || 27 ||
vījādṛkṣa praroheṇa yathā nāpacayas taroḥ ||
sūryakāntamaṇeḥ sūryādbṛddhiḥ prajāyate || 28 ||
tadvatsa ñjāyate sṛṣṭiḥ śivas tatra na kāmayat ||
śivaśaktis samāyoge devādyāḥ prabhavanti hi || 29 ||
tathā svakarmāṇaikena prarohasuparyāntī vai ||
brahmā viṣṇuśca rudraśca sa śivaḥ parigīyate || 30 ||
tasmādudṛte sarve yasm iśca layameṣyati ||
katā kriyāṇāṃ sarvāsāṃ sa śivaḥ parigīyate || 31 ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
sana tkumāra sarveṣa chidhi me saṃśayaṃ mahat ||
santi lokā hi brahmāṇḍāduparidhānaṃ vā mune || 32 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
brahmāṇḍāduparīdhācca santi lokāḥ munīśvara ||
tāñchṛṇu tvaṃ viśeṣeṇa vācyam teṣahaṃ samāgataḥ || 33 ||
vikhilokāt pare loko vaikuṇṭha iti viśrutaḥ ||
virājate mahādīrghā yatra viṣṇuḥ pratiṣṭhitaḥ || 34 ||
tasyopariṣṭāt kaumāro loko hi paramādbhutaḥ ||
senānīḥ ṣaṇmukha tanayo rājate yatra suprabhaḥ || 35 ||
tataḥ paraśumāloko mahādivyo virājate ||
yatra śaktirvidhātrikā tridevajannanī śivā || 36 ||
parātparā hi prakṛtī rajassattvatamomayi ||
nirguṇā ca svayaṃ devī nirviṃkārā śivātmikā || 37 ||
tasyopariṣṭādviśveśyaśśivalokassanātanaḥ ||
avināśī mahādivyo mahāśobhānvitas sadā || 38 ||
virājate paraṃ brahma yatra śaṃbhumaheśvaraḥ ||
tridevajanakassvāmī sarveṣāṃ triguṇātparaḥ || 39 ||
tata ūrdhvai na lokāśca golokastats amīpataḥ ||
gomātarassuśīlākhyās tatra

--- Page 44 ---
santi śivapriyāḥ || 40 ||
tatpālaḥ kṛṣṇanāmā hi rājate śaṅkarājñayā |
pratiṣṭhitiśśaveneva śatyā svacchandacāriṇā || 41 ||
śivalokoṣṭhuto vyāsa nirādhāro manoharaḥ |
atinavacanīyaśca nānāvastuvirajitaḥ || 42 ||
śivastu tadadhiṣṭhātā sarvadevśiromaṇiḥ |
viṣṇubrahmahareśca sevyaḥ paramātmā niraṃjanaḥ || 43 ||
iti te kathitā tāta sarvabrahāṇḍasaṃsthitiḥ |
tadṛdhyai lokasaṃsthānaṃ kimanyacchrotumicchasiḥ || 44 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe paṃcamyāsumāsaṃhitāyāṃ lokavarṇanaṃ nāmaikonāviṃśodhyāyaḥ || 19 ||
vyāsa uvāca |
sanatkumāra sarvaṃ tatprāptiṃ vad sattama |
yadṛtvā na nivartante śivabhaktiyutā narāḥ || 1 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca |
parāśarasuta vyāsa śṛṇu prītyā śubhāṃ gatim |
vrataṃ hi śuddhabhaktānāṃ tathā śuddhaṃ tapasvināṃ || 2 ||
ye śivaṃ śuddhakamāṇassuśuddhatapasānvitāḥ |
samarcayanti taṃ nityaṃ vandyāste sarvasthānavaham || 3 ||
nātastatapaśo yānti śivalokamanāmayam |
śivānugrahsaṃdehustapaḥ eva mahāmune || 4 ||
tapasā divi modante pratyakṣaṃ devagaṇāḥ |
ṛṣayo munayaścaiva satyaṃ jānīhi madvacastat || 5 ||
sudurdhuraṃ durārādhyaṃ sudhuraṃ duratikramam |
tatsvai tapasā sādhyaṃ tapo hi duratikramam || 6 ||
sṛṣṭistatapasvī brahmā nityaṃ viṣṇuharistatathā |
devā devyokhilāḥ prāpāstapaśā durlabhaṃ phalam || 7 ||
yena yena hi bhāvena sthitvā yatkriyate tapaḥ |
tatassaṃprāpyateśau tairha loke na saṃśayaḥ || 8 ||
sāttvikaṃ rājasaṃ caiva tāmasaṃ trividhaṃ smṛtam |
vijñeyaṃ hi tapo vyāsa sarvapāpaghanaśaghnam || 9 ||
sāttvikaṃ daivatānāṃ hi yatīnāṃ smṛtairatasyāṃ |
rājasaṃ dānavānāṃ hi manuṣyāṇāṃ tathaiva ca |
tāmasaṃ rākṣasāṇāṃ hi narāṇāṃ kurakarmmaṇām || 10 ||
trividhaṃ tatphalaṃ proktaṃ munibbhistattvadarśibhiḥ |
japo dhyānaṃ tu devānāmaceñcaṃ bhaktitacchubham || 11 ||
sāttvikaṃ taddhi nirddiṣṭamaśeṣaphalasādhanam |
iha loke pare caiva manobhipretsādhanam || 12 ||
kāmanāphalabhuddiśya rājasaṃ tapa ucyate |
nijadehaṃ susaṃpīḍya dehaśoṣakaduḥssaḥhaiḥ || 13 ||
tapastāmasamuddiṣṭaṃ manobhipretasādhanam || 14 ||
uttamaṃ sāttvikaṃ vidyāddharmmabuddhiśca niścalā |
snānaṃ pūjā japo homaḥ śuddhaśaucamidaṃ sanam || 15 ||
vrātopavāsacaryāṃ ca maunamaindriyanigrahaḥ |
dhīravidyā satyamakroghō dānaṃ kṣāntidemomodyā || 16 ||
vāpīkūpataḍāgādeḥ prāsādasya ca kalpanā |
kṛcchraṃ cāndrāyaṇaṃ yajñasumtīrthānyāśramāḥ punaḥ || 17 ||
dharmasthānāni caitāni mukhadāni manīṣiṇāṃ |
sudharmmaḥ paramo vyāsa śivabhaktaśca kāraṇam || 18 ||
saṃkālitiviṣuvayogo nādmuke niyujyatāṃ |
dhyānaṃ trikālikaṃ jyotirunmanībhāvadhāraṇā || 19 ||
recakaḥ pūrakaḥ kumbhaḥ prāṇāyāmastrīdhā smṛtaḥ |
nāḍīsaṃcāravijñānaṃ pratyāhāraniroghnam || 20 ||
turīyaṃ tadgho buddhiraṇimādyaṣṭasaṃyutam |
prāvāttamaṃ samādhiṣṭhaṃ parajñānaprasādhanam || 21 ||
kāṣṭhāvasthā mṛtāvasthā itīritā veti kīrtitāḥ |
nānopalaṃbhayo ḍhetā

--- Page 45 ---
svaiḥ pāpapraṇāśanāḥ || 22 ||
nārī śayyā tathā pānaṃ vastraghapavilepanam |
tāmbūlamakṣaṇaṃ pañca rājaiśvaryaṃ vibhūtayaḥ || 23 ||
hemabhārastathā tāmraṃ gṛhāśca ratnaghanatvāḥ |
pāṇḍityaṃ vedaśāstrāṇāṃ gītanṛtyaviḍhūṣaṇam || 24 ||
śaṃkhavīṇāmṛdaṅgāśca gajendraḥ chatraṃcāmere |
bhogārūpāṇi caitāni pumān śokodvarajyate || 25 ||
ādṛśaṃ vanuḥ snehai stalavatsa niṣpīḍyate |
araṃ gaccheti cāpyenaṃ kurute jñānamohitaḥ || 26 ||
jānvapīha saṃsāre bhrāmate ghaṭīyantrāvat |
sarvayoniṣu duḥkhārtastathāvareṣu careṣu ca || 27 ||
evaṃ yoniṣu sarveṣu pratikmya dharmena tu |
kālāntaravaśādyāti mānuṣyamatidurlabham || 28 ||
vyuktameṇāpi mānuṣyaṃ prāpyate puṇyagauravāt |
vicitrā gatayaḥ proktāḥ karmaṇāṃ gurulāghavāt || 29 ||
mānuṣyaṃ ca samāsādya svargamokṣaprasādhanam |
nācaret yātmanaḥ śreyasca mṛtaśocyate ciram || 30 ||
devāsurāṇāṃ sarveṣāṃ mānuṣyaṃ cātidurlabham |
tatsamprāpya tathā kuyāna gacchernarkaṃ yathā || 31 ||
svargāpavargalābhāya yadi nāsti sadudyamaḥ |
durlabhaṃ prāpya mānuṣyaṃ dhṛthā tajjanya kīrtitam || 32 ||
sarvasya mūlaṃ mānuṣyaṃ caturvargasya kīrtitam |
samprāpya dharmato nyāsa tadannādanupalāyet || 33 ||
dharmamūlaṃ hi mānuṣyaṃ labdhvā svārthesādhanam |
yadi lābhāya yatnaḥ syānmūlaṃ rakṣetsvayaṃ tataḥ || 34 ||
mānuṣyepi ca vipratvaṃ yaḥ prāpya khalu durlabham |
nācaret yātmanaḥ śreyaḥ koḍhyaṃstāsmāt cetanaḥ || 35 ||
dvīpānāmeva sarveṣāṃ karmaṇā bhariyamucyate |
itaḥ svargañca mokṣaśca prāpyate satupājitaḥ || 36 ||
deśesminnabhārate varṣe prāpya mānuṣyamdhruvaṃ |
na kuyādātmanaḥ śreyastenātmā khalu vañcitaḥ || 37 ||
karmaṇāmiramitvam vipra phaladhūmirasau sthitā |
iha yatkriyate karma svarge tadvubhujyate || 38 ||
yāvatsvāsthyaṃ śarīrasya tāvaddharmam samācaret |
asvasthaścoditosyanyenāṃ kiñcitkaṭuṃ rutasahedṭam || 39 ||
adhruveṇa śarīreṇa dhruvaṃ yo na prasādhayet |
dhruvaṃ tasya paribraṣṭamadhruvañca śrameva ca || 40 ||
āyuṣaḥ khaṇḍakhaṇḍāni nipatantīṃti tadagratāḥ |
ahorātropadeśena kimarthaṃ nāvabujyate || 41 ||
yadā na jñāyate mṛtyuḥ kadā kasya bhaviṣyati |
ākasmikaṃ hi maraṇo ghnanti vindati kastathā || 42 ||
parityajya yadā sarvamekhākī yāsyati dhruvaṃ |
na dadāti kadā kasmātpātheyāthāmindaṃ ghanaṃ || 43 ||
gṛhītadānapātheyaḥ sukhaṃ yāti yamālaym |
anyathā kliśyate jantuḥ pātheyarahite pathi || 44 ||
yeṣāṃ kāleya puṇyāni pāripūrṇāni sarvatāḥ |
gacchantāṃ svargadeśaṃ hi teṣāṃ lābhaḥ padepadem || 45 ||
iti jñātvā naraḥ puṇyaṃ kuyātpāpaṃ vivarjayet |
puṇyena yāti devatvamapuṇyo narakaṃ vrajet || 46 ||
ye manāgapi deveśaṃ prapaṇnaśaraṇaṃ śivam |
teṣāmapi ghoraṃ na paśyanti yamaṃ na narakaṃ tathā || 47 ||
kintu

--- Page 46 ---
pāpairmahāmohaiḥ kiñcitkāle śivājñayā ||
vasanti tatra manuṣyāstatato yānti śivāspadaṃ || 48 ||
ye punarsvabhāvena pratipannā maheśvaraṃ ||
na te lipyanti pāpena padmapatramivāmbhasā || 49 ||
uktaṃ śiveti yenāma tathā harihareti ca ||
na teṣāṃ narakādīti tyamādhi munisattama || 50 ||
paralokaasya pāthayyaṃ mokṣopāyamanāmayaṃ ||
puṇyasaṃcaikanilyaṃ śiva ityakṣaradvayyam || 51 ||
śivanāmaivasāramahārogaikśāmakam ||
nānyatsaṃsārorasya śāmakaṃ darśyate mayā || 52 ||
brahmahatyāsahasrāṇi purā kṛtvā tu pulkaśaḥ ||
śiveti nāma vimalaṃ śrutvā mokṣaṃ gataḥ purā || 53 ||
tasmādvicchinnaktimīśvare satataṃ budhaḥ ||
śivabhaktyā mahāprājña muktiṃ muktiṃ ca vindati || 54 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ matuuviśeṣakathanaṃ nāma viṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 20 ||
vyāsa uvāca

brāhmaṇatvaṃ hi duṣprāpyaṃ nisargādbrāhmaṇo bhavet ||
īśvarasya mukhalākṣyo vākubhyāmūrto viśaḥ || 1 ||
pādyāṃ śūdrassamutpanna iti tasya mukhalacchūtiḥ ||
kiṃtu sthitimadhaḥ sthānādāguvanti hato vad || 2 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca

duṣkṛtena tu kāle ya sthānāddṛśyanti mānavāḥ ||
śreṣṭhaṃ sthānaṃ samāsādya tasmāddṛkṣeta paṇḍitaḥ || 3 ||
yastu vipratvaṃ śrutya kṣatriyonyāṃ prasūyate ||
brāhmaṇyātsa paribrāṣṭaḥ kṣatriyatvaṃ niṣevate || 4 ||
adharmasevānānmūḍhastathāiva parivartate ||
janmāntarasahasrāṇi tamasya āviśate yataḥ || 5 ||
tasmātprāpya paraṃ sthānaṃ pramādena tu nāśayet ||
svasthānaṃ sarvadā rakṣetprāpyāpi vipadro naraḥ || 6 ||
brāhmaṇatvaṃ śubhaṃ prāpya brāhmaṇyaṃ yo'vasanyate ||
bhogyābhogyaṃ na jānāti sa pumānkṣatriyo bhavet || 7 ||
karmaṇā yena medhāvī śūdro vaiśyo hi jāyate ||
tatte vakṣyāmi nikhilaṃ yena varṇottamo bhavet || 8 ||
śūdrakarmayyathōditaṃ śūdro bhūtvā samācaret ||
yathāvatparicaryayoṃ tu triṣu varṇeṣu nityada || 9 ||
kurute kāmayānstu śūdro'pi vaiśyatāṃ vrajet ||
yo yojayeddhanaivaiśyo dhyānastha yathāvidhi || 10 ||
agnihotramupādāya śeṣānaktabhojanaḥ ||
sa vaiśyaḥ kṣatriyakule jāyate nātra saṃśayaḥ || 11 ||
kṣatriyo jāyate yajñaissaṃskṛtairācchaddakṣiṇaiḥ ||
adhīte svargamanvicchannṛgvetāmiśaraṇaṃ sadā || 12 ||
ārdraistaptapado nityaṃ śitiṃ dharmeṇa pālayet ||
ahnukālābhigāmī ca svabhāvyādhamanatparaḥ || 13 ||
sarvātirthyaṃ trivargasya bhūtebhyo dīyatāmiti ||
gobrāhmaṇagārmaṇo'sti hi saṃgrāmābhihato bhavet || 14 ||
tenāgnimantraputātmā kṣatriyo brāhmaṇo bhavet ||
vighatato brāhmaṇo bhūtvā yājakasttu prajāyate || 15 ||
svakarmanirato nityaṃ satyavādī jitendriyaḥ ||
prāpyate vipulassvargo devānāmapi vallabhaḥ || 16 ||
brāhmaṇatvaṃ hi duṣprāpyaṃ kuṇḍreṇa sādhyate naireḥ ||
brāhmaṇyā

--- Page 47 ---
tsalaṃ prāpyaṃ mokṣaṃ cāpi munīśvara || 17 ||
tasmāt sarveṣu prayatnena brāhmaṇo dharmatatparaḥ |
sādhanena sarvavargasya rakṣedrājaññayuktamapi || 18 || ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
saṃgrāmasyeha māhātmyaṃ tvayoktaṃ munisattama |
etatdiccāhyaṃ śrotuṃ brūhi tvaṃ vadatāṃ vara || 19 ||

||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
agnihomadimiḥ śāriṣṭhā vipuladakṣiṇaiḥ |
na tatphalaṃ avāpnoti saṃgrāme yadvāpnuyāt || 20 ||
iti tattvavido prāhuryajñakarmāṇi daṃśadā |
tasmātte pravakṣyāmi yatphalaṃ śastrājīvinām || 21 ||
dharmālābho'theṃ lābhaśca yaśolābhastathaiva ca |
yaśśūro vāñchate yuddhaṃ viṣṭhūrnanparvāhinīm || 22 ||
tasya dharmārthe kāmasya yajñasyaiva sadakṣiṇaḥ |
paraṃ hyabhimukhaṃ datvā tadyānaṃ yo'dhirohaiti || 23 ||
viṣṇuloke sa jāyeta yaśca yuddheṣu parājitaḥ |
aśvamedhānavāpnoti caturo na ghṛtasya cet || 24 ||
yastu śastramutṛjya śriyate vāhinīmukhe |
saṃmukho vartate śūrasya svargāṃna nivartatai || 25 ||
rājā vā rājaputro vā senāpatirathāpi vā |
hataḥ kṣatreṇa yaḥ śūrastasya lokodakṣayo bhavet || 26 ||
yāvanti tasya romāṇi bhidyante'śvaimeṃhāhve |
tāvato labhate lokānsarvaikāmaduṣhāskhyān || 27 ||
vīrāsanaṃ vīraśayyā vīrasthānasthitiśca sthirā |
sarvadā bhavati vyāsa iha loke para ca || 28 ||
gavārthe brāhmaṇārthe ca sthānassvāmyartheṣeva ca |
ye mṛtāste sukhaṃ yānti yathāmuktinanastathā || 29 ||
yaḥ kaścidbrāhmaṇaṃ hatvā paścātprāṇānparityajet |
tatrāsau svapate'nde sa svargāṃna nivartatai || 30 ||
kaṇyādedaitimischeva hatasya gatiruttamā |
dvijagossvāmināmarthe bhavedvipuladākṣyā || 31 ||
śaknotivaha samarthaśca yaṣṭuṃ kratusatairapi |
ātmadehaparityāgaḥ katai śubhiṃ suduṣkaro || 32 ||
yuddhaṃ puṇyatamaṃ svargye rūpajñaṃ sarvetoṣukṣam |
sarvāṃ cāmeva varṇānāṃ kṣatriyasya viśeṣataḥ || 33 ||
bṛśaṃ caiva pravakṣyāmi yuddhadharmaṃ sanātanam |
yādṛśāya grahaṭavyaṃ yādṛśaṃ parivarjanīyat || 34 ||
ātatāyinaṃ māyāntamapi vedāntaṃ dvijam |
jighāṃsantaṃ jighāṃsetu na tena brahmaghā bhavet || 35 ||
haṃtāpyasau na haṃtavyaḥ pānīyaṃ yaśca yācate |
raṇe hatvāturāṇvyāsaḥ sa naro brahmaghā bhavet || 36 ||
vyāghātaṃ durbaraṃ bālaṃ strīnāthaṃ kṛpaṇaṃ dhruvam |
ghanubernaṃ chinnaguṇaṃ hatvā vai brahmaghā bhavet || 37 ||
evaṃ vicārye saddhīmānbhave'prītyā raṇapriyaḥ |
sa janmanaḥ phalaṃ prāpya parce'ha pramodate || 38 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe paścamyāsumāsaṃhitāyāṃ raṇaphalavarṇanaṃ nāmaikaviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 21 ||

||
vyāsa uvāca ||
vividha tāta vadeydānīṃ jīvajanmavighānataḥ |
garbhe sthitiṃ ca tasyāpi vairāgyārthe munīśvara || 1 ||

||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
śṛṇu vyāsa samāsena śāstrasāramaśeṣataḥ |
vakṣyāmi suvairāgyaṃ mumukṣorbhavabandhanut || 2 ||
pākapātrasya madhye tu ghṛtapatnaṃ pathagjalasya |
agneruddhe jalaṃ sthāpyaṃ tadagnaṃ ca jalopari || 3 ||
jalasya ghāpharasya cāgniṃ sthito'gniṃ ghāmyate śanaiḥ |
vāyunā ghāmyamāno'gni

--- Page 48 ---
ratyuṣṇaṃ kurute jalam || 8 ||
tadaśuṣṇatoyena samantātpacyate punaḥ ||
dvidhā bhavati tatpakaṃ pṛthakkīṭaṃ pṛthagrasaḥ || 9 ||
malaiḥ dvādaśabhiḥ kiṃcit bhinnaṃ dehādadhirbhaveva ||
rasastu dehe sarati sa pṛṣṭhastena jāyate || 6 ||
karṇāśchinānasikā jihvā dantāḥ śiśno gudaṃ nakhāḥ |
malāśrayaḥ kaphaḥ svedo viṇmūtraṃ dvādaśa smṛtāḥ || 7 ||
hatpadme pratibaddhāśca sarvanāḍyassaṃtatāḥ ||
jñeyā rasmavāhinyastanmakāraṃ bruṃve śune || 8 ||
tāsāṃ mukheṣu taṃ sūkṣmaṃ prāṇasthāpayate rasam ||
rasena tena nāḍīstāḥ prāṇaṃ pūryate punaḥ || 9 ||
punaḥ prayāti saṃpūrṇaḥ tāśca dehaṃ samantataḥ ||
tatassanāḍīmadhyasthyaśśarīrīṇātmanā rasaḥ || 10 ||
pacyate pacyamānācca bhaveatpākadvaṃ punaḥ |
tvak tayā veṣṭyate pūrvai ruhiraṃ ca prajāyate || 11 ||
raktācchomāniṃ māṃsaṃ ca keśāni snāyuśca māṃsataḥ |
snāyutaśca tathāsthīni nakhā mañjāsthisaṃbhavāḥ || 12 ||
mañjākāraṇavaikalyaṃ śukraṃ hi prasavātmakam ||
iti dvādaśādharmasya pariṇāmaḥ prakīrtitaḥ || 13 ||
śukrośrājāyate śukrādivyadehasyaca saṃbhavaḥ ||
ṛtukāle yadā śukraṃ nirdoṣaṃ yonisaṃsthitam || 14 ||
tadā tadāyussaṃspṛṣṭaṃ strīraktenaikataṃ vrajet ||
visaṅgakāle śukrasya jīvaḥ kāraṇasaṃyutaḥ || 15 ||
saṃvṛtaḥ prāviśoddhinī karmābhiḥsvairiṇyojitaḥ ||
tacchukarktamekasthyamekāhātkililaṃ bhavet || 16 ||
pañcarātreṇa kililaṃ budbudākārtāṃ vrajet ||
bududassaptarātreṇa māṃsapeśī bhavetpunaḥ || 17 ||
aṅgavā śiraśca skandhau ca pṛṣṭhavaṃśastathobdaram ||
pāṇipādantathā pārśve kaṭigātraṃ tathaiva ca || 18 ||
dvimāsābhyantareṇaiva kramaśassaṃbhavedīha ||
tribhirmāsaiḥ prajāyante sarvaṃ aṅkurasaṅghayaḥ || 19 ||
māsaiścaturabhirangulayaḥ prajāyante yathākramam ||
mukhaṃ nāsā ca karṇau ca māsaiḥ pañcabhireva ca || 20 ||
dantapaṃktistathā guḍhaṃ jāyate ca nakhāḥ punaḥ |
karṇayostu bhavetcchidraṃ ṣaṇmāsābhyantareṇa tu || 21 ||
pāyumedhassupaṣṭhaṃ ca nābhiśrābhyupajāyate ||
saṃghayo ye ca gātreṣu māsaijāyanti sabhiḥ || 22 ||
aṅgapratyaṅgasaṃpūrṇaḥ paripakvasya tiṣṭhati ||
udare māturācchādro jarayau munisattama || 23 ||
māturāhāracauryeṇa ṣaḍguṇena rasena tu ||
nābhimālinibaddhena vardhate sa dinedine || 24 ||
tatrasthitiṃ labheñjīvassaṃpūrṇeṃsimaśśarīrake ||
mukhaṃ duḥkhaṃ vijānāti nidrāsvaṃ purā kṛtam || 25 ||
mṛtaśśainaṃ punarajātaḥ punaśśainaṃ punamṛtaḥ ||
nānāyonisahasrāṇi mayā dṛṣṭhāni jāyatām || 26 ||
addhunā jātamātrohaṃ prākasaṃskāra eva ca ||
śreyosmunā kariṣyāmi yena garbhe na saṃbhavaḥ || 27 ||
garbhasthiścintayatyevamahaṃ garbhodvinirgatāḥ ||
anveṣyāmi śivajñānaṃ saṃsāravinivartakam || 28 ||
evaṃ saṃ garbheduḥkhena mahatā paripīḍitaḥ ||
jīvaḥ karmaśādāste mokṣopāyaṃ vicintayan || 29 ||
yathā girivarakāntaḥ kaścidduḥkhena tiṣṭhati ||
tathā jarayuṇā dehī duḥkhaṃ tiṣṭhati veṣṭitaḥ || 30 ||
* jāyamānanityarthe |
