patitassāgare yadduḥkhamāste samākulaḥ ||
garmbhondakena siktāṅgasarvedākulitastadā || 31 ||
lohakumbhe yathā nyastaḥ pacyate kaścidagnhinā ||
garbhakumbhe tathā śiptaḥ pacyate jaṭharāgninā || 32 ||
sūcībhiraghnivāṇibhirnirmbhinnasya nirantaram ||
yaduḥkhaṃ jāyate tasya tatra saṃsthasya cādhikam ||

|| 33 ||
garbhāvāsātparaṃ duḥkhaṃ kaṣṭaṃ naivāsti kutracit ||
dehināṃ duḥkhabhūlaṃ sughoramitisaṃkaṭam || 34 ||
ityetatsumahadduḥkhaṃ pāpi

nāṃ parikīrtitam ||
