garbhātsdulaṃ duḥsaṃ yoniyantranipīḍanāt ||
bhavetpāpātmanā

vyāsa na hi dharmbhayutātmanāṃ || 36 ||
ikṣuvatpīḍyamānasya yantreṇaiva samantataḥ ||
śirasā tāḍyamānasya pāpasudrakaṇa ca || 37 ||
yantreṇa pīḍita yadagnissāraststhutisthalā kṣaṇāt ||
tathā śarīraṃ nissāraṃ yoniyantranipīḍanāt || 38 ||
asthipādulatāstaṃbhaṃ snāyubandhena yantritam ||
raktamāṃsamṛdāliṃ viṣṇutradravyabhājanasam || 39 ||
keśaromanakhacchadrṃ rogāyatanamāturasam ||
vadanaika mahādvāraṃ gavākṣādakabhūṣitam || 40 ||
oṣṭhadvayakapāṭa

ca tathā jihvāgaṃlānvitam ||
bhogatṛṣṇātura mūḍha rāgadveṣavaśānugam || 41 ||
saṃvitittāṅgapratyanagaṃ jarāyupariṃveṣṭitam ||
saṃkateṇāvivikten yonimārgaṇa

nirgantam || 42 ||
viṣṇutaraktasiktāṅgaṃ vikośekasamudbhavam ||
asthipañjarivikṣyātamasmin jñeyaṃ kalevarasam || 43 ||
śataṃ ṣaṣṭyādhikaṃ pañcapeśīśatā

ni ca ||
sārdhibhistisamibhiśchanaṃ samantādromakōṭibhiḥ || 44 ||
śarīraṃ sthūlasukṣmābhirheśthāhṛśya hi tāssmṛtāḥ ||
etāvatībhirnāḍībhiḥ koṭibhista

tsamantataḥ || 45 ||
asveda maśubhiyāmbhirantasathaḥ sravate bahiḥ ||
dvādaśadaśanāḥ proktā viṃśatiśca nakhāsmṛtāḥ || 46 ||
pittasya kuḍavaṃ jñeyaṃ kafasyāthā

kaṃ smṛtam ||
vasāyāśca palaṃ viṃśataddhe kapilasya ca || 47 ||
pañcādhe tu tulā jñeyā palāni daśa medasaḥ ||
palatrayaṃ mahāraktaṃ mañjāyāśca caturguṇam ||

|| 48 ||
śukrocche kuḍavaṃ jñeyaṃ taddbījaṃ dehināṃ balam ||
māṃsasya caikapīḍena palasāhasraśucyate || 49 ||
raktaṃ palaśataṃ jñeyaṃ viṣṇumatraṃ yatpramāṇataḥ ||
aña

layaśca catvāraśatvāro munisattama || 50 ||
iti deha gṛhaṃ jñetaghnityasyanityamātmanaḥ ||
