iti śrī

śivamahāpurāṇe paśmyāśumāsaṃhitāyāṃ dehōtpattivarṇenaṃ nāma dvāviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 22 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
śṛṇu vyāsa mahābuddhe dehastyāśu

citāṃ śṛṇe ||
mahatvaṃ ca svabhāvasya samāsātakathāyamhaṃ || 1 ||
śukraśoṇitasaṃyogāddehasaṃjāyate yataḥ ||
nityaṃ viṣṇutrasambhūṇaste nāyamaśuci

ssmṛtaḥ || 2 ||
yathāntiviṣṭhayā pūrṇaḥ śucimāna bahirghaṭaḥ ||
śodhyamāno hi deho'yaṃ tenāyamaśucistatataḥ || 3 ||
saṃgrāpyātipavitrāṇi pañcagavyaṃ harviṣi ca ||
aśucitvam kṣaṇābhāṃti kimanyaḍaśucistatataḥ || 4 ||
hṛdyānyapyavrapānāni yaṃ prāpya surabhīṇi ca ||
aśucitvam prayāntyāśu kimanyaḍaśuci

--- Page 50 ---
stataḥ || 5 ||
he janāḥ kiṃ paśyanti yajñriyānti dine dine ||
svadehāt kaśmalaṃ pūtis tadādhāraḥ kathaṃ śuciḥ || 6 ||
dehaḥ saṃśodhyamāno'pi pañcagavyakuśāmbubhiḥ ||
ghṛṣyamāṇa ivāṅgāro nirmalatvaṃ na gacchati || 7 ||
śrotāṃsi yasya satataṃ prabhavanti girera iva ||
karpūrapurīṣādyais taddehaḥ śudhyate katham || 8 ||
sarvāṃ śucinidhānasya śarīrasya na vidyate ||
śucirekāḥ pradeśo'pi viṣṇmasyeva hṛtereva || 9 ||
smṛdātmadeśaśrotāṃsi mṛtyoyeḥ śodhyate karaḥ ||
tathāpy aśucimāṃ dasya na vibhraṃśyanti kiṃkarāḥ || 10 ||
kāyasugandhadhūpādyair nenaapi susaṃskṛtaḥ ||
na jahāti svabhāvaṃ sa śvapucchim iva nāmitam || 11 ||
yathā jātyaiva kṛṣṇo'rthaḥ śuktrasya yāntryupāyataḥ ||
saṃśodhyamānāpi tathā bhaved vṛttirnirmalā || 12 ||
jighrann api svadurgandhaṃ paśyann api svakaṃ malam ||
na virajyet loko'yaṃ pīḍayann api nāsikām || 13 ||
aho mohasya māhātmyaṃ yenedaṃ chāditaṃ jagat ||
śīghraṃ paśyan svakaṃ doṣaṃ kāyasya na virajyate || || 14 ||
svadehasya vigandhen na virajyet yo naraḥ ||
virāgakāraṇaṃ tasya kimetadupādiśyate || 15 ||
sarvatraiva jaganmadhye deha evāśucirbhavet ||
tanmalāvayavasparśāc chuciracyaśucirbhavet || 16 ||
gandhalepa pānodārthe śaucaṃ dehasya kīrtitam ||
dravyasya apagamāc chuddhi śuddhas parśādiśudhyati || 17 ||
gaṅgātoyena sarveṇa mṛdvaraiḥ pavitopamaiḥ ||
āmṛtyorā caret chaucaṃ bhāvadugdhe na śudhyati || 18 ||
tīrthesnānais tapobhirvā duṣṭātmā naiva śudhyati ||
śhṛtitaḥ śālitā tīrthe kiṃ śudhimāvigacchati || 19 ||
antarbhāva pradughasya viśato'pi hutāśanam ||
na svargaṃ nāpavargaṃ ca dehinirdehanaṃ param || 20 ||
sarveṇa gaṅgena jalena samyag mṛtpavitetanāpyatha bhāvadduṣṭaḥ ||
ājānmanaḥ jñānaparo manuṣyo na śudhyatītyeva vayaṃ vadāmaḥ || 21 ||
prajvālya vahniṃ ghṛtatailasiktaṃ pradakṣiṇāvartitaśvanaṃ mahāntam ||
praviśya dagdhas tvapi bhāvadugdhe na dharmamāpnoti phalaṃ na cānyat || 22 ||
gaṅgāditīrtheṣu vasanti matsyā devālaye pakṣigaṇāś ca nityam ||
bhāvoijñatāste na phalaṃ labhante tīrthāvagāhāc ca tathaiva dānāt || 23 ||
bhāvaśuddhiḥ paraṃ śaucaṃ pramāṇaṃ sarvakarmaṇu ||
anyathāsliṅgyate kāntā bhāvena duhitānyathā || 24 ||
manaso bhedyate vṛttir bhinneṣv api vastuṣu ||
anyathaiva sutaṃ nārī cintayatyanyathā patim || 25 ||
paśyatva masya bhāvasya mahābhāgyam aśeṣataḥ ||
pariṣvakto'pi yajñāyāṃ bhāvahīnaṃ na kāmayet || 26 ||
nādhādibhir viṣamantraiś ca bhakṣyāṇi surabhīṇi ca ||
yadi cintā samādhatte citte kāmādiṣu triṣu || 27 ||
gṛhyate tena bhāvena naro bhāvādibhir ucyate ||
bhāvataḥ śuciḥ śuddha ātmā svargaṃ mokṣaṃ ca vindati || 28 ||
bhāvenaikātmaśuddhātmā dahaṃś ca dhrastruvan smṛtaḥ ||
jñānavāsiterāpyāśu lokāṃs tu bahuyājinām || 29 ||
jñānamalaṃ bhasā puṃsāṃ sadrāgya smṛdā punaḥ ||
avidyārāgaviṣmṛtrilepagandhaviśoghanam || 30 ||
evam etac charīraṃ hi nisargādaśuci smṛtam ||
--- Page 51 ---
tvaṅmātrasāraṃ nissāraṃ kadlīsārasannibham || 31 ||
jñātvaivaṃ doṣavadehaṃ yaḥ prājñiśśithilo bhavet |
dehabhogodrvaṅnāvācchamicittaḥ prasaṅgdhīḥ || || 32 ||
so'tikāmati saṃsāraṃ jīvanmukttaḥ prajāyate |
saṃsārakadlīsārahadmaḻavatiṣṭhate || 33 ||
evametanmahākaṣṭaṃ janmaduḥkhaṃ prakīrtitam ||
puṃsāmajñānadoṣeṇa nānākarmavaśena ca || 34 ||
śokārddena tu vakṣyāmi yaduktaṃ granthakoṭibhiḥ |
mameti paramaṃ duḥkhaṃ na mameti paraṃ sukham || 35 ||
bahvopīha rājānaḥ paraṃ lokaṃ ito gatāḥ |
nirmamatvametāstu baddhāśśatasahasraśaḥ || 36 ||
garbhasya sthitiyonisītsā ca tasya praṇaśyati |
saṃśucitena duḥkhena yoniyantanipīḍanāt || 37 ||
bāhyena vāyunā vāsya mohasaṅgena dehinaḥ |
spṛṣṭamātreṇa ghoraṇa jvarassaṃupajāyate || 38 ||
tena jvareṇa mahātā sammohāśca prajāyate |
sammūḍhasya smṛtibhraṃśaśśīghraṃ saṃjāyate punaḥ || 39 ||
smṛtibhraṃśāttastasya smṛtibhraṃśo'pūrvakarmmaṇaḥ |
ratiḥ saṃjāyate tūrṇaṃ jantostatraiva janmani || 40 ||
raktto mūḍhasya lokovāyaṃ na kāryye sampravartate |
na cātmānaṃ vijānāti na paraṃ na ca daivatam || 41 ||
na śṛṇoti paraṃ śreyassiti karṇairapi sanśune |
na paśyati paraṃ śreyassiti cakṣuṣi tatksame || 42 ||
same pathi śanairgancchan skhalalīva padepade |
satyāṃ buddhau na jānāti bodhyamāno budhairapi || 43 ||
saṃsāre kṣiyate tena garbhalobavasādugaḥ |
garbhasṛtena pāpena sasṛñjhatmaniḥ pumān || 44 ||
itthaṃ mahatparaṃ divyaṃ śāstraṃ muktaṃ śivena tu |
tapasaḥ kathanāthāya svargamokṣaprasādhanam || 45 ||
ye satyasmanniṣṭhave jñāne sarvaekāmārthasādhane |
na kurvanttyātmanaḥ śreyastadatra mahad dhutam || 46 ||
avyaktendriyavṛttittvāḍhāle duḥkhaṃ mahatpunaḥ |
icchārapi na śaknoti vaktuṃ kaccū pratikrīyām || 47 ||
dantotthāne mahāduḥkhamalpena vyāghnā tathā |
bālarogaiśca vivviddhaiḥ pīḍā bālagrairapi || 48 ||
kiñcitkunudrupīrīṭāṅgaḥ kiñcicchatitasaṃraṭan |
viṣṇupratabhakṣaṇāyaṃ ca mohāddālaṣṭa mācareta || 49 ||
kaumāre karṇapīḍāyāṃ mātāpitrośca sāgnaiḥ |
akṣarādhyayanādyaiśca nānāduḥkhaṃ pravartate || 50 ||
bālye duḥkhamtīrthyaiva paśyannapi vi mūḍhadhīḥ |
na kurvannnātmanaḥ śreyastadā mahaddutam || 51 ||
pravṛttendriyavṛttittvātkāmarogaprapīḍanāt |
tadprāpte tu satataṃ kutaḥsaukhyaṃ tu yauvane || 52 ||
īrṣyayā ca mahāduḥkhaṃ mohādvikttrasya tasya ca |
netrasya kupitasyeva tyāgī duḥkhāya kevalam || 53 ||
na rātrau vindante nidrāṃ kāmāgniparivedditaḥ |
divāpi ca kutaḥsaukhyamathopadārgennicintayā || 54 ||
kṣīṇabhyāsitacittasya ye puṃsaḥ śuṣkabindavaḥ |
te sukhāya na manyante svedajā iva te tathā || || 55 ||
kṛmibhistudyamānasya kuṣṭhino vānarasya ca |
kaṇḍūyanābhitāpena yadbhavettakṣīṣu tadviduḥ || 56 ||
yādṛśaṃ manyate saukhyaṃ gaṇḍe prītivinigamāt |
tādṛśaṃ strīṣu mantavyaṃ nādhikaṃ tatra vidyate || 57 ||
viṇmūtrasya samutpthagātsukhaṃ bhavati yādṛśam |
tādṛśaṃ strīṣu vijñeyaṃ mūḍhaiḥ kalpitamanyathā || 58 ||
--- Page 52 ---
nārīṣvavastubhūtāsu sarvadoṣāśrayāsu ca ||
nāṇumātraṃ sukhaṃ tāsu kithaṃ pañcacūḍyā || 59 ||
sammānanāvamānābhyāṃ viyogeneṣṭasaṃgamāt ||
yauvanañ jarayā grastaṃ ka saukhyamanupadhvam || 60 ||
valīpalitakhālitatyaiśśithilīkṛtavigrham ||
sarvakriyāsvāsaktiñ ca jarayā jarjarīkṛtam || 61 ||
strīpuṃsayauvanañ hṛdyamanyoānyasya priyaṃ purā ||
tadeva jarayāgrastamanayorapi na priyam || 62 ||
apūrvavastvaātmānaṃ jarayā parivṛttitam ||
yaḥ paśyannapi rajyeta ko'nyastasyādcetanaḥ || 63 ||
jarābhijhūtaḥ puruṣaḥ putrīputrādibāndhavaiḥ ||
asaktatvādurāgheṣānbhṛtaiśca parityajate || 64 ||
dharmeāarthe ca kāmaṃ vā mokṣaṃ vātitajarātuḥ ||
aśaktassādhuṃ tacmāyuvā dharme samācaret || 65 ||

||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāṃśumāsaṃhitāyāṃ saṃsāracikitsāyāṃ dehāśucitvabālyādyavasthāduḥkhavaṇanaṃ nāma trayoviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 23 ||

||
vyāsa uvāca ||
kutistatā yoṣidarthe yatsaṃproktaṃ pañcacūḍyā |
tanme brūhi samāsena yadi tuṣṭo'si me mune || 1 ||

||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
strīṇāṃ svabhāvaṃ vakṣyāmi śṛṇu vipra yathātatham ||
tasya śravaṇamātreṇa bhavedeirāgyamuttamam || 2 ||
striyo mūlaṃ hi doṣāṇāṃ laghucittāḥ sadā mune ||
tadāsaktiñ kārtavyā mokṣepsumiratandritaiḥ || 3 ||
atrāpyudāharaṇīmimitihāsaṃ purātanam ||
nāradasya ca saṃvādaṃ puṃścalyā pañcacūḍyā || 4 ||
lokānparicaran dhīmāndeviṣīnāradaḥ purā ||
daddarśāpsarasaṃ bālāṃ pañcacūḍāmruttamām || 5 ||
papracchāpsarasaṃ sujhūṃ nārado munisattamaḥ ||
saṃśayo hṛdi me kaściccanyebrūhi samakṣyame || 6 ||
evamukta tu sā vipraṃ pratyuvāca varāpsarāḥ ||
viṣaye sati vakṣyāmi samarthau manyase'tha mām || 7 ||

||
nārada uvāca ||
na tvāmviṣaye bhadre niyokṣyāmi kathaṃcana ||
strīṇāṃ svabhāvamicchāmi tvattaḥ śrotuṃ samakṣyame || 8 ||

||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
etacchrutvā vacastasya devarṣeḥ parrottamā ||
pratyuvāca munīśaṃ taṃ devarṣiṃ munisattamam || 9 ||

||
pañcacūḍovāca ||
mune śṛṇu na śakyā strī satī vai ninditum striayā ||
vididitāste striyo yāśca yādṛśyaśca svabhāvataḥ || 10 ||
na māmaheṃsi devarṣe niyoktuṃ praśnameṃdṛśam ||
ityuktā sāābhavacchūrṇī pañcacūḍāpsarovarā || 11 ||
atha devarṣeḥvacyo hi śrutvā tadvākyamuttamam ||
pratyuvāca punasstān vai lokānāṃ hikāmyayā || 12 ||

||
nārada uvāca ||
mṛṣāvāde bhavedoṣassatye doṣā na vidyate ||
iti jānīhi satyaṃ tvaṃ vadātastattavamakṣyame || 13 ||

||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
ityuktā sā kṛtamatī rabhasā cāruhāsinī ||
strīdoṣāñśāśvatānsatyānbhāṣituṃ saṃpracakrame || 14 ||

||
pañcacūḍovāca ||
kulīnā nāthavantayaśca rūpavatyaśca yoṣitaḥ ||
maryādāṣu na tiṣṭhanti sa doṣaḥ strīṣu nārada || 15 ||
na strībhyaḥ kiñcidanyaddhe pāpīyastaram asti hi ||
striyo mūlaṃ hi pāpānāṃ tathātmamapi vetya ha || 16 ||
samājñātānarthe

--- Page 53 ---
vataḥ pratirūpāc cathepisitāt ||
yatīnāntaramasādya nālaṃ nārye pratīkṣituṃ || 17 ||
asaddharmestavyaṃ strīṇāmasmākaṃ bhavati prabho ||
pāpī yaśo narātra yadde lajjāṃ tyaktvā bhajāmahe || 18 ||
śriyaṃ ca yaḥ prārthyate sannikṣe ca gacchati |
īrṣyā kurute sevāṃ tamevechchanti yoṣitaḥ || 19 ||
anarthitvānmanurṣyāṇāṃ bhayātpritajanasya ca ||
mayadāyāmamayodāḥ stvayistithaṃ bhavetṣu || 20 ||
nāsāṃ kaściṣṭamānyoṣista nāsāṃ vayasi niścayaḥ ||
svarūpaṃ vā kurūpaṃ vā pumāṃsasmupabhuñjate || 21 ||
na bhayādatha vākoṃśānārthahetoḥ kathaṃcana ||
na jñātikulasambandharitsrayistithaṃti bhavetṣu || 22 ||
yovane vartamānānāmiṣṭābharaṇavāsasāṃ ||
nārīṇāṃ svairavṛttīnāṃ spṛhayanti kulastriyaḥ || 23 ||
yā hi śabdābhūmatā rakṣyante dīyitāḥ striyaḥ ||
api tāḥ samprasajjante kubjāṃghajaḍavāmane || 24 ||
paśupvapi ca devaiśe ye cānye kutsitā narāḥ ||
strīṇāmagamyo lokeṣu nāsti kaścinmahāśune || 25 ||
yadi puṃsāṃ gatirheṣu kaṃtaṃciṃnopadyate ||
apyanyonyaṃ pravartante na ca tiṣṭhanti bhavetṣu || 26 ||
alābhātpuruṣāṇāṃ ca bhayātparijānasya ca ||
vadhvabandhavabhayāce va tā bhagnāśā hi yoṣitaḥ || 27 ||
calatsvabhāvā duṣṭeṣu durmohā bhāvastasthā ||
prājñasya puruṣasyeha yathāritiparigrahat || 28 ||
nāgniṣtuṣyati kāṣṭhānāṃ nāpagānāṃ mahodadhiḥ ||
nāntakasarvabhūtānāṃ na puṃsāṃ vāmalocanāḥ || 29 ||
idamanyac ca devaiśe rahasyaṃ sarvayoṣitāṃ ||
hadyaiva puruṣaṃ svayo yoniḥ prakrīyate striyāḥ || 30 ||
susthātaṃ puruṣaṃ dṛṣṭvā sugandhaṃ malavarjitaṃ ||
yoniḥ prakrīyate strīṇāṃ hateḥ pātrādivodakam || 31 ||
kāyānāmapi dātāraṃ karttāraṃ mānasāntvayoḥ ||
rakṣitāraṃ na mṛṣyanti bhartāraṃ paramaṃ striyaḥ || 32 ||
na kāmabhogotkharaparamāṇalakārārthasaṃcayāt ||
tathā hitaṃ na manyante yathā ritiparigrahat || 33 ||
antakaśśamano mṛtyuḥ pātālaṃ vaḍavānalaṃ ||
kṣurāghārāṃ viṣaṃ sarpe vahniritcayekatah striyaḥ || 34 ||
yataśca bhūtāni mahāṃti pañca yataśca loko vihito vidhātrā ||
yataḥ pumāṃsaḥ pramadāśca nirmitāḥ sadaiva doṣaḥ pramadāsu nārada || 35 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
iti śrutvā vacastaasyā nāradasthuṣṭamānasaḥ ||
tathyaṃ matvā tatastaddhe virakoṣṇuddhi tāṃśu ca || 36 ||
ityukteḥ strīsvabhāvaste pañcabudoktaṃ ādrāt ||
vairāgyakāraṇaṃ vyāsa kimanyaṃcchottumahīsi || 37 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe paṃcamyāṃumāsaṃhitāyāṃ strīsvabhāvavavarṇanaṃ nāma caturviṃśodhyāyaḥ || 24 ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
sanatkumāra savaiñca tvatsaghāśānmayā śrune ||
strīsvabhāvaḥ śrutaḥ prītyā kālajñānaṃ vadasva me || 1 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
idameva purāṣpṛcchitpārvatī parameśvaram ||
śrutvā nānākathāṃ divyāṃ prasannā supraṇamya tam || 2 ||
pārvatyuvāca ||
bhagavantvatprasādena jñātaṃ me sakalaṃ mataṃ ||
yathācanaṃ tu te deva yairvaitnaiśca yathāvidhi || 3 ||
adyāpi saṃśayastvekah kālacakraṃ prati prabho ||
mṛtyucihnaṃ

--- Page 54 ---
yathā deva kiṃ pramāṇaṃ yathāyuṣaḥ || 4 ||
tathā kathaya me nātha yad ahaṃ tava vatsalā ||
iti pṛṣṭastayā devyā pratyuvāca maheśvaraḥ || 5 ||
īśvara uvāca

satyaṃ te kathayiṣyāmi śāstraṃ sarvottamaṃ priye ||
yena śāstreṇa deveśi naiḥ kālaḥ prabujhyate || 6 ||
adhaḥ pakṣaṃ tathā māsaṣaṭkaṃ cāyanavatsarau ||
sthūla sūkṣmagativaiśiṣṭyeṣu bhrāntargateṣu tathā || 7 ||
tatteṣāṃ sampravakṣyāmi śṛṇu tattvena sundari ||
lokānāṃ upakārārthaṃ vairāgyārthameṣadhunā || 8 ||
akasmātpāṇḍuraṃ dehaṃ śṛṅgaṃ samantatāḥ ||
tadā mṛtyuṃ vijānīyāt ṣaṇmāsābhyantare priye || 9 ||
śuṣkaṃ karṇau tathā cakṣurjihvāstambho yadā bhavet ||
tadā mṛtyuṃ vijānīyāt ṣaṇmāsābhyantare priye || 10 ||
rauravāt agataṃ bhadre dhvaniṃ nākarṇayeḥ kṛtam ||
ṣaṇmāsābhyantare mṛtyujñātavyaḥ kālavedibhiḥ || 11 ||
ravisomāgniṃ yogacakradyotaṃ na paśyati ||
kṛṣṇaṃ sarvai samastāṃ ca ṣaṇmāsaṃ jīvitaṃ tathā || 12 ||
vāmahasto yadā deviṃ saptāhaṃ spandate priye ||
jīvitaṃ tu tadā tasya māsamekaṃ na saṃśayaḥ || 13 ||
unmīlayanti gātrāṇi tālukaṃ śuṣyate yadā ||
jīvitaṃ tu tadā tasya māsamekaṃ na saṃśayaḥ || 14 ||
nāsā tu bhavate yasya tridoṣe pakṣajīvitam ||
vakraṃ kaṇṭhaṃ ca śuṣyet ṣaṇmāsānte gatāyuṣaḥ || 15 ||
sthūlajihvā bhavet yasya dvijāḥ krudhyanti bhāmini ||
ṣaṇmāsājjāyate mṛtyuḥ śivaiḥ tairūpalakṣayet || 16 ||
aṅgulyalaghusthaṃ tu darpaṇe varavaraṇini ||
na paśyati yadātmānaṃ vikṛtaṃ palameva ca || 17 ||
ṣaṇmāsāyuś ca vijñeyaḥ kālacakraṃ vijānatā ||
anyac ca śṛṇu deveśi yena mṛtyurvibujhyate || 18 ||
śirodhīnāṃ yadā chāyāṃ svakīyāṃ upalakṣayet ||
atha vā chāyayā hīnaṃ māsamekaṃ na jīvati || 19 ||
āṅgikāni mayoktāni mṛtyucihāni pārvati ||
bāhyasthāni bruve bhadre cihnāni śṛṇu sāṃprataṃ || 20 ||
raśmihīnaṃ yadā devaṃ bhanet soryārkamāṇḍalyam ||
dṛśyate pāṭalākāraṃ māsārdhena vipadyate || 21 ||
aruṃdhatī mahāyāniṃ duṃ lakṣaṇavarjitam ||
adṛṣṭatārakoyo asau māsamekaṃ sa jīvati || 22 ||
dṛṣṭe arke ca dikmohaḥ ṣaṇmāsājjāyate dhruvam ||
utasthyaṃ na dhruvaṃ paśyediṃ vā ravīmaṇḍalam || 23 ||
rātrau ghaṭuyendā paśyenma dyāhne colkāpātanam ||
veṣṭyate gṛhakākaiś ca ṣaṇmāsāyune saṃśayaḥ || 24 ||
ṛṣayaḥ svargapanthāś ca dṛśyante naiva cāmbare ||
ṣaṇmāsātu vijānīyāt puruṣaiḥ kālavedibhiḥ || 25 ||
akasmādgrāhitā śastraṃ mṛtyorvā somena ca ||
dikṣacakraṃ śrāntavat paśyet ṣaṇmāsān nīyate sphuṭam || 26 ||
nīlābhimasiktakā bhiṣa jhakasmādreṣṭyate pumānaḥ ||
māsamekaṃ hi tasya āyuḥ jñātavyaṃ paramārthataḥ || 27 ||
gṛdhrakākaḥ kapotaś ca śiraḥ ākramya tiṣṭhati ||
śīghraṃ tu mriyate jantu māsikena na saṃśayaḥ || 28 ||
evaṃ cāriṣṭabhedaḥ tu bāhyasthaḥ samuderitaḥ ||
mānuṣāṇāṃ hitārthāya saṃkṣepena vadāmyaham || 29 ||
hastatayoḥ ubhayoḥ deviṃ yathā

--- Page 55 ---
kālaṃ vijānate ||
vāmadakṣiṇayormadhye pratyakṣaṃ cetyudāhṛtam || 3 ||
evaṃ pakṣau sthitau dvau tu samāsātsuraśundari ||
śucirbhūtvā smarannenaṃ sukhātassaṃyatendriyaḥ || 31 ||
hastau prakṣālya dugdhenaālaktakena vimardayet ||
gandhaiḥ puṣpaiḥ karau kṛtvā mṛgayecca śubhāśubham || 32 ||
kaniṣṭhāmāditaḥ kṛtvā yāvadaṅguṣṭhakaṃ priye ||
parvatrayo'ktrameṇaiva hastayorbhayorapi || 33 ||
pratipadādidivanyasya tithi pratipadādtataḥ ||
saṃpuṭākārahastauto tu pūrvidikṣukhassaṃsthitaḥ || 34 ||
smaret svātmakaṃ mantraṃ yāvaddhetrataraṃ śātmā niriīkṣyettato hastau pratiparveṇa yatnatāḥ || 35 ||
atratasmimparveṇa sā rekhā dṛśyate bhuṃgasaṃbhā ||
tithyo hi dṛtitirgyā kṛṣṇaśukle tathā priye || 36 ||
adhunanādajaṃ vakṣye saṃkṣepātkāllakṣaṇam ||
gamāgamaṃ viditvā tu karma kuryācchṛṇu priye || 37 ||
ātmavidyānaṃ śuśroṇi cāraṃ jñātvā tu yatanataḥ ||
kṣaṇaṃ truṭilavaṃ caiva nimeṣaṃ kāṣṭhakālikam || 38 ||
muhūrtakaṃ tvahorātraṃ pakṣamāsatuvatssaram ||
abjaṃ yugaṃ tathā kalpaṃ mahākalpaṃ tathaiva ca || 39 ||
evaṃ sa harate kālaḥ paripāṭyā sadāśivaḥ ||
vāmadakṣiṇamadhye tu pathe trayimadaṃ smṛtam || 40 ||
dināni pañca cāraṃsya pañcaviṃśāhinā vādhe ||
vāmācaragatau nādaḥ pramāṇaṃ kathitaṃ tava || 41 ||
bhūtarandrādaśaśaiva dhvajasya varavāṇini ||
vāmacāragato nādaḥ pramāṇaṃ kālavedanaḥ || 42 ||
ṛtodidaṃkārbhūtāśca guṇāstraieva bhāmini ||
pramāṇaṃ dakṣiṇaṃ proktaṃ jñātavyaṃ prāṇavedibhiḥ || 43 ||
bhūtasaṃkhyā yadā prāṇāncahate ca daḍādyaḥ ||
varṣasyāmyantare tasya jīvitaṃ hi na saṃśayaḥ || 44 ||
daśavasrapravāheṇa hrādbamānaṃ sa jīvati ||
pañcadaśapravāheṇa hrāndrmekam gatāyuṣam || 45 ||
viṃśatidnapravāheṇa ṣaṇmāsaṃ lakṣayettadā ||
pañcaviṃśatidanimataṃ vahate vāmanāḍikā || 46 ||
jīvitaṃ tu tadā tasya trimāsaṃ hi gatāyupaḥ ||
ṣaṭtriṃśaddanamānena māsardvya mṛdāhṛtam || 47 ||
saptaviṃśadinimataṃ vahetedyatitividramā ||
māsmekam samākhyātaṃ jīvitaṃ vāmagocared || 48 ||
etadpramāṇaṃ vijñeyaṃ vāmavāyupramāṇataḥ ||
sarvyetare dinānyeva catvāraśyānupūrvaśaḥ || 49 ||
catuḥsthāne sthitā devi ṣoḍaśatāḥ prakīrtitāḥ ||
teṣāṃ pramāṇaṃ vakṣyāmi sāmprataṃ hi yathārthatāḥ || 50 ||
ṣaḍdinānyāditaḥ kṛtvā saṃkhyāyāśca yathāvidhi ||
etaddaṃtargate caiva vāmarambhe prakāśitam || 51 ||
ṣaḍdināni yadāruḍhaṃ dvirdvarṣe ca sa jīvati ||
māsānadhyai vijānīyāddinānyaṣṭa ca tāni tu || 52 ||
prāṇaḥ śatadaśe caiva viddhi varṣe na saṃśayaḥ ||
samāmāsānvijānīyāddineḥ ṣaḍbhine saṃśayaḥ || || 53 ||
aṣṭavasraprabhedena dvirdvarṣe hi sa jīvati ||
caturmāsā hi vijñeyāścaturviṃśatidināvadhiḥ || 54 ||
yadā naivadanaṃ prāṇā vahantye'va trimāsakaṣṭhu ||
māsardvaṃ ca dve māse dinā dvādaśa kīrtitāḥ || 55 ||
pūrvaivakathitā ye tu kālaṃ teṣāṃ tu pūrvakam ||
avāntaradanā ye tu tena māsena kathyate || 56 ||
ekādaśa pravāheṇa varṣamekaṃ sa jīvati ||
māsā nava tathā proktā dinānyaṣṭamitānyapi || 57 ||
dvādaśena pravāheṇa varṣamekaṃ sa jīvati ||
māsāna

--- Page 56 ---
saptaviānīyāt ṣaḍghaṭīśāṃ yudāharet || 58 ||
nāḍī yadā ca vahati trayodaśadinānāvādhiṃ ||
saṃvatsaraṃ bhavet tasya caturmāsāḥ prakīrtitāḥ || 59 ||
caturviṃśatidināṃ reṣaṃ jīvitaṃ ca na saṃśayaḥ ||
prāṇavāhā yadā vāme caturdaśadinānani tu || 60 ||
saṃvatsaraṃ bhavettasya māsāḥ ṣaṭ ca prakīrtitāḥ ||
caturviṃśatidinānyeva jīvitaṃ ca na saṃśayaḥ || 61 ||
pañcadaśapravāheṇa nava[māsānsa jīvati ||
caturviṃśatidinānyeva kathitaṃ kālavedibhiḥ ||

|| 62 ||
ṣoḍaśāhapravāheṇa daśamāsānsa jīvati ||
caturviṃśatidinādikaṃ kathitaṃ kālavedibhiḥ || 63 ||
saptadaśapravāheṇa navamāsāṃ gatāyuṣam ||
aṣṭādaśadinānyatra kathitaṃ sāṃketibhiḥ || 64 ||
vāmacāraṃ yadā devi dvādaśadinānāvādhiḥ ||
jīvitaṃ cāṣṭamāsaṃ tu gatvā dvādaśa kīrtitāḥ ||

|| 65 ||
caturviṃśatidinānyatra niścayenāvādhāraya ||
prāṇavāho yadā devi trayoviṃśatidināvādhiḥ || 66 ||
catvāraḥ kathitā māsāḥ ṣaḍdinānani

tatottare ||
caturviṃśapravāheṇa trīnmāsāṃśra sa jīvati || 67 ||
dinānyatra daśādho ca saṃhṛantye va cārataḥ ||
avāntaradine yastu saṃkṣepāte

prakīrtitaḥ || 68 ||
vāmacāraḥ samākhyāto dakṣiṇaṃ śṛṇu sāṃpratam ||
aṣṭāviṃśapravāheṇa tithimānena jīvati || 69 ||
pravāheṇa daśāhena

tatsaṃsthena vipadyate ||
triṃśaddarśapravāheṇa pañcāhena vipadyate || 70 ||
ekatriṃśadyadā devi vahte ca nirantaram ||
dinadvayaṃ tadā tasya jīvitaṃ hi na

saṃśayaḥ || 71 ||
dvātriṃśatprāṇasaṃkhyā ca yadā hi vahate raviḥ ||
tadā tu jīvitaṃ tasya dvidinnaṃ hi na saṃśayaḥ || 72 ||
dakṣiṇaḥ kathitaḥ

prāṇo madhyasthaṃ kathayāmi te ||
ekabhāgagato vāyupravāho mukhamaṇḍale || 73 ||
ghāvamānapravāheṇa dinasmekṃ sa jīvati ||
cakrameta tparāsohin purāvi

ddirruda hatam ||74||
etatte kathitaṃ devi kālacakraṃ gatāyuṣaḥ ||
lokānāṃ ca hitārthāya kimanyacchotumicchasi ||75||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyā

umāsaṃhitāyāṃ kālajñānavarṇanaṃ nāma pañcaviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 25 ||
devyuvāca ||
kathitaṃ tu tvayā deva kālajñānaṃ yathārtataḥ ||
kālasya vacanaṃ

brūhi yathā taccena yoginaḥ || 1 ||
kālastu sannikṛṣṭo hi varttate sarvajantūṣu ||
yathā cāsya na mṛtyuśra vañcate kālamāgatam || 2 ||
tathā katha me

deva prītiṃ kṛtvā mamopāri ||
yogināṃ ca hitāya tvaṃ brūhi svasti sukha prad || 3 ||
śaṅkara uvāca ||
śṛṇu devi pravakṣyāmi pṛṣṭo'haṃ yat tvayā śive ||
samāsena

ca sarvveṣāṃ māṇuṣāṇāṃ hitārthetaḥ || 4 ||
pṛthivyāpastejaḥ tejo vāyurākāśameva ca ||
eteṣāṃ hi samāyogaḥ śarīraṃ pāñcamautikaṃ || 5 ||
ākāśastu

tato vyāpī sarvveṣāṃ sarvvagaḥ sthitaḥ ||
ākāśe tu vilīyete saṃbhavanti punastataḥ || 6 ||
viyoge tu sadā kasya svaṃ dhāma pratipedire ||
tasya

nisthiratā cārita saṃpātasya sundarī || 7 ||
jñānino'pi tathā tatra tapomantravaladapi ||
te sarve suvijānanti sarvametanra saṃśayaḥ || 8 ||
devyuvāca ||
--- Page 57 ---
khaṃ tena yacchyati ghorarūpaḥ kālaḥ karālabhinnadevaikānāthaḥ ||
dagdhastayā tvaṃ punareva tuṣṭaḥ stotraiḥ stutaḥ svāṃ prakṛtiṃ sa lebhe || 9 ||
tvayā sa

coktaḥ kathayā janānāmadaṣṭarūpaḥ pracariṣyasīti ||
daṣṭastayā tatra mahāprabhāvaḥ pramoḥ vegācca punaruttithastha || 10 ||
taddhya bhoḥ kāla ihāsti

kiñcinnirhriyate yena vadasva tanme ||
tvaṃ yogivaryaḥ prabhurātmatantraḥ paropakārattaturmahīśa || 11 ||
śaṅkara uvāca

na hriyate devavairestu daityaiḥ svayakṣarakṣoraṅgamānuṣaiśca ||
ye yogino dhyānaparāstadehā bhavanti te śrāmyanti sukhena kālam || 12 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca

etacchrutvā tribhuvanaguroḥ prāha gaurī vihasya satyaṃ tvaṃ me vad kathamso hriyate yena kālaḥ ||
śuśrūṣatāmāha sadyo himakarvadane yogino ye kṣipanti kālavyālaṃ sakalamanaghāstacchuṇuṣpaikacittā || 13 ||
śaṅkara uvāca

pañcabhūtātmako dehasadā yuktu stadguṇaiḥ ||
utpādyate varārohe tādṛśīno hi pārthivaḥ || 14 ||
ākāśājjāyate vāyurvāyostejaśca jāyate ||
tejaso'mbu vinirdiṣṭaṃ tasmāddhī pṛthivī bhavet || 15 ||
pṛthivyādīni bhūtāni gacchaṃti kramaśaḥ param ||
dharā pañcaguṇā proktā hhyāpaścaiva caturguṇāḥ || 16 ||
triguṇaṃ ca tathā tejo vāyudviguṇa ṣaṭ ca ||
śabdaikaguṇamākāśaṃ pṛthivyādiṣu kīrtitam || 17 ||
śabdaḥ sparśaśca rūpaṃ ca raso gandhaśca pañcamaḥ ||
vijahāti guṇaṃ svaṃ svaṃ tadā bhūte vipadyate || 18 ||
yadā guṇaṃ vijahāti prādurbhūtaṃ taducyate ||
evaṃ jānīhi devīśa pañcabhūtāni tattvataḥ || 19 ||
tasmādhi yoginā nityaṃ svastvakalāṃśajā guṇāḥ ||
cintanīyā prayatnena devi kālajigatguṇā || 20 ||
devyuvāca

kathaṃ jīriyate kālo yogibhiryogavitprabho ||
dhyānena cātha mantreṇa tatservai kathayasva me || 21 ||
śaṅkara uvāca

śṛṇu devi pravakṣyāmi yogināṃ hitakāmyayā ||
prajñānaprakathanam na deyaṃ yasya kasyacit ||22||
śraddhānāya dātavyaṃ bhaktiyuktāya dhīmate ||
anāstikāya śuddhāya dharmānityāya svāmini ||23||
sukhāsena suśayyāyāṃ yogaṃ yuñjīta yogavit ||
dīpaṃ vināṃdhakāre tu prajāḥ śruteṣu dhārayet ||24||
tarjanīyā pidhitau karṇau pīḍayitvā muhūrtakam ||
tasmātsaṃśrūyate śabdasturdunvāhuiṣaṣṭudhavaḥ || 25 ||
saṃghyāto bhuktvaivaṃ hi cāvasannaṃ kṣaṇādapi ||
sarvarogāgnirhantyāśu jvaraopadravakānbahūn || 26 ||
yaśchopalakṣyedbinityairākāraṃ ghaṭikādvayam ||
jitvā mṛtyuṃ tathā kāmaṃ svecchayā paryaṭediha || 27 ||
sarvajñasarvadaśī ca sarvasiddhimavāpnuyāt ||
yathā nadite khedo hi prāmṛgaḍibhrassusamyataḥ ||28||
taṃ śrutvā mucyate yogī sadyaḥ saṃsārabandhanāt ||
tatassa

yogābhiñcintyaṃ sūkṣmātsūkṣmataraṃ bhavet || 29 ||
eṣa te kathito devi śabdabrahmavidhikramaḥ ||
palāliṃvā ghānyārthī tyajeddhānaghamaśeṣataḥ || 30 ||
śabd

--- Page 58 ---
brahma tvidaṃ prāpya ye kecid brahma kāṅkṣiṇaḥ ||
śrānti te muṣitenākāśaṃ kāmayante kṣudhā tṛṣā || 31 ||
jñātvā parimitaṃ brahma sukhadaṃ mukti kāraṇam ||
abrahma kṣaraṃ caiva sarvopādhivivarijtam || 32 ||
mohitāḥ kālapāśena mṛtyupāraavaśaṃ gatāḥ ||
śabdabrahma na jānanti pāpinas te kubud dhayaḥ || 33 ||
tāva d bhavanti saṃsāre yāvadbrahma na vindante ||
vidite tu pare tattve mucyate janmabandhanāt || 34 ||
nidrālas yaṃ mahāvighnaṃ jitvā śacaṃ prayatnataḥ ||
sukhāsane sthito nityaṃ śabdabrahm ābhyasinniti || 35 ||
śatavṛddhaḥ pumāñchrutvā yāvadāyussam abhyaset ||
mṛtyujñayavapu stambha ārogyaṃ vāyuvardhanam || 36 ||
pratyayo dṛśyate vṛddhe kiṃ punastaruṇe jane ||
nacaṃkāro na mantro'pi naivaṃ bījaṃ na cākṣaram || 37 ||
anāhatamanucyārthye śabdabrahma śivaṃ param ||
dhyāyante devī satataṃ sudhiyā yatnataḥ priye || 38 ||
tasmācchraddhā nava śroktāḥ prāṇividhbhistu lakṣitāḥ ||
tānpravakṣyāmi yatnena nādasiddhi manukramāt ||

|| 39 ||
ghoṣaḥ 1 kāṃsyaṃ 2 tathā śṛṅgaṃ 3 ghaṇṭāṃ 4 vīṇā 5 divaṃśa jāt 6 ||
dundubhi 7 śaṃkha 8 śabdaṃ tu navamaṃ meghagirjitam 9 || 40 ||
nava śabdān parityajya ṭuṃkāraṃ tu samabhyaset ||
dhyāyanbhraṃ sadā yogī puṇyaiḥ pāpairnna lipyate || 41 ||
na śṛṇoti yadā śṛṇvan yogābhyāsena deviike ||
kriyate bhyasmānastu yogī tiṣṭhedivāniśam || 42 ||
tasmādutpadyate śabdo mṛtyujiitsatibhīdhanaiḥ ||
sa vai navavidho devi taṃ bravīmi yathārthatāḥ || 43 ||
prathamaṃ nādate ghoṣamātmaśuddhikaraṃ param ||
sarvaṃ vyādhiharaṃ nādaṃ vaśyākarṣaṇasuttamam || 44 ||
dvitīyaṃ nādate kāṃsyastam bhyetprāṇīnāṃ gatiśam ||
viṣaṃ bhūtagrahānsarvānbadhnīyātnātra saṃśayaḥ || 45 ||
tṛtīyaṃ nādate śṛṅgamabhicāri niyojayet ||
vidrāḍucchāṭane śatromāraṇe ca prayojayet || 46 ||
ghaṇṭānādaṃ caturthaṃ tu vadate parameśvaraḥ ||
ākarṣetsarvadedevānāṃ kiṃ punar mānuṣā bhuvi || 47 ||
yakṣagandharvakinnaryas ca tasyākṛṣṭā daddantyahi ||
yathepsiitāṃ mahāsiddhi yogine kāmato'pi vā || 48 ||
vīṇā tu pañcamo nādaḥ śrūyate yogibhistadā ||
tasmādutpadyate devi dūrdarśanameva hi || 49 ||
dhyāyato vaṃśanādaṃ tu sarvattvaṃ prajāyate ||
dundubhi dhyāyamānastu jarāmṛtyuvi varjitaḥ || 50 ||
śaṃkhaśabdena deveśa kāmarūpaṃ prapadyate ||
yogino meghanādena na vipatsaṃgamo bhavet || 51 ||
yaścaikamanas ā nityaṃ ṭuṃkāraṃ brahmarūpiṇam ||
kimasādhyaṃ na tasyāpi yathāmita varānane || 52 ||
sarva jñassarvadaṛśī ca kāmarūpī vrajatyasau ||
na vikāraiḥ prahuyeta śiva eva na saṃśayaḥ || 53 ||
etattte parameśāni śabdabrahmasvarūpakam ||
navadhaā sarvaṃ mākhyātaṃ kiṃ bhūyaḥ śrotumicchaśi || 54 ||
--- Page 59 ---
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ kālaśañcanavargaṇaṃ nāma ṣaḍviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 26 ||
देव्युवाच

vāyostu padmamīti yogākāśasaṃbhavam |
tanme sarvaṃ samācakṣva prasrastavyaṃ yadi prabho || 1 ||
शंकर उवाच

purā me sarvamākhyātaṃ yogināṃ hitakāmyayā |
kālaṃ jigāya yassaṃyagvāyoliṅgaṃ yathā bhavet || 2 ||
tena jñātvā dinaṃ yogī prāṇāyāmaparāsthitaḥ |
sa jayatyāgataṃ kālaṃ māsārdhenaiva sundari || 3 ||
atastu vāyussadā vahnerīpakasso'ṣṭupāvakaḥ |
sa vāhyābhyantaro vyāpī vāyussarvagato mahān || 4 ||
jñānavijñānasutsādaḥ sarve vāyoḥ pravarttante |
yenehanijitonitu vāyustena sarvamidam jagat || 5 ||
dhāraṇāyāṃ sadā tiṣṭhejaramaṛtyujighāṃsayā |
yogī yogarataḥ saṃyagdhāraṇādhyānatatparaḥ || 6 ||
lohakāro yathā bhastrāpūryaṃ mukhato śune |
sādhayeddhāyunā karmaṃ taddhyogī samabhyaset || 7 ||
devasahasrake netrapādahastsahasrakaḥ |
granthinā ha sarvaṃ māvṛtya so'gre tiṣṭhedśāṅgulam || 8 ||
gāyatrīṃ śirasā sārdhaṃ japedyāhitiṣṭhivikāṃ |
trivāramāyatprāṇāḥ prāṇāyāmassucyate || 9 ||
gatāgatā nivarttante candrasūryādayo mahāḥ |
adyāpi na nivarttate yogadhyānaparāyaṇāḥ || 10 ||
śatamandaṃ tapastaptvā kuśāgrapaḥ pibedbhijaḥ |
tadāmoti phalaṃ deviṃ viṣṇāṇāṃ dhāraṇakyayā || 11 ||
yo dvijaḥ kalyaśutyāya prāṇāyāmaikamācaret |
sarvaṃ pāpaṃ nihatyāśu brahmaloke sa gacchati || 12 ||
yo'ṣṭāndritassadaikite prāṇāyāmaparo bhavet |
jarāṃ mṛtyuṃ vinijinya vāyugaḥ khecarīti saḥ || 13 ||
siddhasya bhajate rūpaṃ kāntiṃ meghaṃ parākraman |
śauryeṃ vāyusamaṃ gatyā saukhyaṃ śchāghyaṃ paraṃ sukham || 14 ||
etatakathitamaśeṣaṃ vāyossiddhi yadāpnute yogī |
yattejaso'pi labhate tatte vakṣyāmi deveśi || 15 ||
sthitvā śukhāsanastheṃ śetajanavacanahīne tu |
śiśiraviyutayātejāḥ prakāśayanmadhyamedeśe || 16 ||
vihṛgataṃ bhrūmadhye prakāśate yastvartanditoyogī |
dīpaiḥśīnaṣbhānti paśyetyūnamasaṃśayaṃ loke || 17 ||
netraḥ karaśākhābhiḥ kiñcitsaṃpīḍya yatanato yogī |
tāraṃ paśyeddhyāyenmuhūrtamardhaiṃ tamekabhāvo'pi || 18 ||
tatastumasi dhyāyanpaśyate jyotirebhvaraṃ |
śvetaṃ raktaṃ tathā pītaṃ kṛṣṇamindrāghaṭuprabham || 19 ||
dhruvomedhye laḷātasthaṃ bālārkasmatejasam |
taṃ viditvā tu kāmāṃgī krīḍate kāmarūpadhṛk || 20 ||
kāraṇaprśamāveśaṃ parakāyapraveśanam |
aṇimādiuguṇāvāptirmanasā cāvalocanam || 21 ||
dūraśravaṇavijñānamadarth bahudhūpapṛthuk |
santābhyāsayogena khecaratvaṃ prajāyate || 22 ||
śrutādhyayanasaṃpannā nānāśāstravśāradāḥ |
jñānino'pi viśuṣyante pūrvakarmaṃvaśānugāḥ || 23 ||
paśyanto'pi na paśyanti śṛṇvānā badhirā yathā |
yathāṃghā manuṣā loke mūḍhāḥ pāpavimohitāḥ || 24 ||
--- Page 60 ---
vedāhametaṃ puruṣaṃ mahāntamādityavarṇaṃ tamasaḥ parastāt ||
tameva viditvātimṛtyumeti nānyaḥ panthā vidyate ayanāyā || 25 ||
eṣa te kathitaḥ samyaktejaso viṣṇorutramā ||
kālaṃ jitvā yathā yogī cāmaratvaṃ prapadyate || 26 ||
punaḥ parataraṃ vakṣye yathāmṛtyunāṃ jāyate ||
sāvadhānatayā devi śṛṇuṣvaikāgramānasā || 27 ||
turīyāḥ devi bhūtānāṃ yogināṃ dhyānināṃ tathā ||
sukhāsane yathāsthānaṃ yogī niyatamānasaḥ || 28 ||
saṃcumbataśarīroḍapi sa baddhākarasaṃpuṭam ||
cañcvākāreṇa vakreṇa pibenvāyuṃ śanaiḥ śanaiḥ || 29 ||
prasavanti kṣaṇādāpastāluṣṭhā jīvadāyikāḥ ||
tā jighrāyunādāyāmṛtaṃ tacchītalaṃ jalam || 30 ||
pibannudiraṃ yogī na mṛtyuvaśago bhavet ||
divyakāyo mahātejāḥ pipāsāśuddhivarjitaḥ || 31 ||
valena nāgasturago javena dṛṣṭyā suparṇastuṣṭhistu durāt ||
ākuñcitākuṇḍaliṅkṛṣṇakeśo gaṃdharvividyāghartulya varṇaḥ || 32 ||
jīvanro varṣaśataṃ surāṇāṃ sumeghasa vākpitinā samatvam ||
evaṃ caranve carataṃ prayāti yatheṣṭacārī sukhitassadaiva || 33 ||
punaranyatpravakṣyāmi vighaṃnaṃ yatcchurairapi ||
gopitaṃ tu prayatnena tacchṛṇuṣva varānane || 34 ||
samākuñcyābhyasedyogī rasanāṃ tālukaṃ prati ||
kiñcitkālāntareṇaiva kramāprāpnoti lambikām || 35 ||
tataḥ prasavate sā tu saṃspṛṣṭā śītalāṃ sudhām ||
pibanneva sadā yogī so'maratvaṃ hi gacchati || 36 ||
repha laṃbakāgraṃ karatalaghaṭanaṃ śuṣkapañcasya bindostenanākṛṣṭā sudheyaṃ patitaparapade devatānandakārī ||
sāraṃ saṃsāratāraṃ kṛtakluṣataraṃ kālatāraṃ satāraṃ yenedaṃ plāvitāṅgaṃ sa bhavati na mṛtaḥ śrutipapāsāvidhīnaḥ || 37 ||
abhiṣekā caturbhiḥ kṣitigharataṇaye yogibhirvaṃ ghareṣā cairyāṇicattyaṃ kuto'ntaḥ sakalamapi jagacchatsukṣaprapāṇāya ||
svapne denhī vipantte sakalamapi sadā māyanyacca duḥkhaṃ svarge bhovaṃ dharitriyāḥ prabhavati ca tato vā sa kiñcitkṣaṇāt || 38 ||
tasmānmantraistapoabhirvanaitniyamayutairauṣadhairyogayuktadhātrī raktā manuṣyeniyavanayuktidhā mānvidhiḥ krameṇa ||
bhūtānāmādidevo na hi bhavati calaḥ saṃyuto vai caturbhiḥ tasmādevaṃ pravakṣye vidhamanu gāditaṃ chāyikaṃ yacchavākyam || 39 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe paśvamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ kālavañcanīśivapāstitvarṇanaṃ nāma saptaviṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 27 ||
devyuvāca ||
devadeva mahādeva kathitaṃ kālavañcanam ||
śabdabrahmasvarūpaṃ ca yogalakṣaṇasuttamam || 1 ||
kathitaṃ te samāsena chāyikaṃ jñānasuttamam ||
vistareṇa samākhyāhi yogināṃ hitakāmayā || 2 ||
śaṃkara uvāca ||
śṛṇu devi pravakṣyāmi chāyāpuruṣalakṣaṇam ||
yajjñātvā puruṣaḥ samyaksarvenpāpaiḥ pramucyate || 3 ||
sūrye hi pṛṣṭhataḥ kṛtvā somaṃ vā varavarṇini ||
śuklāmbhardharasmaghvī gaṃdhadhūpādivāsitaḥ || 4 ||
navātmakaṃ piṇḍabhūtaṃ svāṃ chāyāṃ sānirīkṣayet || 5 ||
dṛṣṭvā tāṃ punarākāśe śvetavarṇatvārupiṇīm ||
sa paśyatyekabhāvastu śivaṃ paramakāraṇam || 6 ||
--- Page 61 ---
brahmaprātibhāvetasya kālavijñāritīritam ||
brahmahatyādikaiḥ pāpaiḥ mucyate nātra saṃśayaḥ || 7 ||
śirohinaṃ yakṣā paśyetviḍmāṃsairbhūtvakṣayaḥ ||
samastaṃ vā imayaṃ tasya yoginnastu yathā tathā || 8 ||
śukte dharme vijānīyātkṛṣṇe pāpaṃ vinirdiśet ||
rakte bandhaṃ vijānīyātpīte vidviṣamādiśet ||9||
vivāho bandhanāśastyadhituṇḍe caiva śuddrayam ||
vikaṭo naśyate bhāryā vijṃghe ghanameva hi || 10 ||
pādābhāve vindeśastyadityetatkathitaṃ mayā ||
tadvicāryaṃ prayatnena puruṣeṇa maheśvari || 11 ||
samyaktaṃ puruṣaṃ dṛṣṭvā saṃniviśyātmanātmāni |
japennvātmakaṃ mantraṃ hṛdayaṃ me maheśvari || 12 ||
vatsare vigate mantrī tanniārita yanna sāghayet ||
aṇimādiguṇānaśnute khecaratvaṃ prapāḍyate || 13 ||
punaranyatpravakṣyāmi śaktiṃ jñātuṃ durāsadām ||
pratyakṣaṃ dṛśyate loke jñānināmabhataḥ sthitam || 14 ||
adbhyeyā likhyate loke yā sarpīkṛtakuṇḍalī ||
sā mātrā yānasaṃsthāpi dṛśyate na ca pacyate || 15 ||
brahmāṇḍagrādhi gā yā ca stutā vedaistu nityaśaḥ ||
jananī sarvavijñānāṃ guptāvijñoti gīyate || 16 ||
khecarā sā vinirdiṣṭā sarvāṇiṣu saṃsthitā ||
dṛśyā dṛśyācalā nityā vyaktāvyaktā sanātanī || 17 ||
avṛṇāṃ varṇasaṃyuktā procyate biṃdumālinī ||
tāṃ paśyantsarvadā yogī kṛtakṛtyobhijāyate || 18 ||
sarvātīrthakṛtasnānadānaveddānasya yatphalam ||
sarvayajñaphalaṃ yaṃca māliṃnyā darśanāttadā || 19 ||
prāpnotyatra na saṃdehaḥ satyaṃ vai kathitaṃ mayā ||
sarvātīrthaṣu yatsnātvā datvā dānāni sarvaśaḥ || 20 ||
sarvajñāṃ devi yajñānāṃ yatphalaṃ tacchhetpumān ||
kiṃ bahutayā maheśāni sarvānkāmānsaṃśnute || 21 ||
tasmājjñānaṃ yathāyogamabhyasetsatataṃ budhaḥ ||
abhyāsājjāyate siddhiryogobhyāsātpravartate || 22 ||
saṃvicitraṃmbyaselabhyateabhyāsādbhyāsān mokṣamabhyaśnute ||
abhyāsastataṃ kāryaṃ dhīmatā mokṣakāraṇam || 23 ||
ityetatkathaṃ devi bhuktimuktiphalamadam ||
kimanyatpṛcchyate tattvaṃ vad satyaṃ bravīmi te || 24 ||
sūta uvāca ||
iti śrutvā brahmaputravacanaṃ paramārthadam ||
prasannoabhūdita vyāsaḥ pārāśaryyo munīśvarāḥ || 25 ||
sanatkumāraṃ sarvajñaṃ brahmaputraṃ kṛpānidhigam ||
vyāsaḥ paramasantuṣṭaḥ praṇanāma śuśrūṣuḥ || 26 ||
tatastudghāta taṃ vyāsaḥ kāleyasamunīśvaraḥ ||
sanatkumāraṃ munayaḥ sura vijñānasāgaram || 27 ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
kṛtārthobhahaṃ muniśreṣṭha brahmatvaṃ me tvayā kṛtam ||
namastebhyastu namastebhyastu dhanyastvam brahmavittama || 28 ||
sūta uvāca ||
iti stutvā sa kāleyo brahmaputraṃ mahāśunim ||
tṛṣṇīṃ babhūva suprītaḥ paramānandanibhaiḥ || 29 ||
brahmaputrastamāmantrya pūjitastena śaunaka ||
yayau svadhāma suprīto vyāsobhapi prītamānasaḥ || 30 ||
iti me vaṇito viprāḥ sukhadaḥ paramārthayuk ||
sanatkumārakāleyasaṃvādo jñānavarddhanaḥ || 31 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāhumāsaṃhitāyāṃ chāyāpuruṣadarśanavārṇenaṃ nāmāṣṭāviṃśobhyadhyāyaḥ || 28 ||
śaunaka uvāca ||
--- Page 62 ---
śrutaṃ me mahādākhyānaṃ yat tvayā parikīrtitam ||
sanatkumārakāleyasaṃvādaṃ paramārthadam || 1 ||
ato'haṃ śrotumiccāmi yathā sargastu brahmaṇaḥ ||
ssmṛtapaṃtu me brūhi yathā vyāsāc ca śrutam || 2 ||
sūta uvāca ||
mune śṛṇu kathāṃ divyāṃ sarvapāpapraṇāśinīm ||
kathyamānāṃ mayā citrāṃ bahvarthāṃ śrutivistarām || 3 ||
yajñenāṃ pāṭhayettāṃ ca śṛṇuyādvā'pyabhīkṣṇaśaḥ ||
svaṃśadhāraṇaṃ kṛtvā svargaloke mahīyate || 4 ||
pradhānaṃ puruṣo yattritvyaṃ sadṛśadātmakam ||
pradhānapuruṣo bhūtvā nirbheme lokabhāvanaḥ || 5 ||
sraṣṭāraṃ sarvabhūtānāṃ nārāyaṇaparāyaṇam ||
taṃ vai viddhi muniśreṣṭha brahmaṇamimitaujasam || 6 ||
yasmādkalpayet kalpāt samaśaśucayo yataḥ ||
bhavanti muniśārdūla namastasmai svayaṃbhuve || 7 ||
tasmai hiraṇyagarbhāya puruṣāyeśvarāya ca ||
namaskṛtya pravakṣyāmi bhūyaḥ sargamuttamam || 8 ||
brahmā sraṣṭā hariḥ pātā saṃhartā ca maheśvaraḥ ||
tasya sargasya nānyaḥ sti kālekāle tathā gate || 9 ||
so'pi svayaṃbhūrbhagavān sisṛkṣurvividhāḥ prajāḥ ||
apa eva sasajānde tāṣu vīryamavāsṛjat || 10 ||
āpo nārā iti proktā āpo vai narasūnavaḥ ||
ayanaṃ tasya tāḥ pūrvai tena nārāyaṇaḥ smṛtaḥ || 11 ||
hiraṇyavarṇaṃ bhavattat daṃbhudakeśayam ||
tatra jajñe svayaṃ brahmā svayaṃbhūriti viśrutaḥ || 12 ||
hiraṇyagarbho bhagavān adhiṣṭhitvā parivaṃtasaram ||
tadaṃḍamakarodbhedam divyaṃ bhūmiṃ ca nirbheme || 13 ||
agho'rdhorddhvaṃ prayuktāni bhuvanāni caturdaśa ||
tayoḥ śakalayormadhyamākāśamaṛtjatprabhuḥ || 14 ||
apsu pāriṣuvā pṛthvīṃ diśaśca daśaghā divi ||
tatra kāle mano vācaṃ kāmakrōdhāvathō ratiṃ || 15 ||
marīcamatryangirasau pulastyaṃ pulahaṃ kratuṃ ||
vasiṣṭhaṃ tu mahātejāsso'sṛjatsama mānasān || 16 ||
sapta brahmāṇa ityete purāṇe niścayaṃ gatāḥ ||
tato sṛjatpunarbrahā rudhrānkrodhavaśodbhavān || 17 ||
sanatkumāraṃ ca ṛṣiṃ sarvveṣāmapi pūrvajaṃ ||
sapta caite prajāyante paścādudārāśca savantaḥ || 18 ||
atastu sanatkumārastu tejassaṃkṣipya tiṣṭhati ||
teṣāṃ sapta mahāvaṃśā divyā devarṣipaṃjitāḥ || 19 ||
prajāyante kriyāvanto maharṣibhiralankṛtāḥ ||
viṣṇuto'śnin meghaṃśa rohitendrāghanūṣipa ca || 20 ||
payāṃsi ca sasajānde parjenyaṃ ca sasajā ha ||
ṛcaḥ yajūṃṣi sāmāni nirbheme yajñasiddhaye || 21 ||
pūjyāṃstairyagjandavānitvayvamanuśuśruma ||
mukhadevānjanayatpitṛṃśivātha vakṣasāḥ ||
prajanaśca manuṣyānvai jaghnaṃbhirmeḍhurān || 22 ||
uccāvacāni bhūtāni gātre bhyastasya jijñire ||
āpavatasya prajāsargaṃ sṛjato hi prajāpateḥ || 23 ||
sṛjyamānāḥ prajāścaiva nāvarddhanta yadā tadā ||
dvighā kṛtvātmano dehaṃ strī caiva puruṣo'bhavat || 24 ||
samṛjeatha prajāssarvāṃ mahimā vyāpya viśvataḥ ||
virājamṛjatadṛkṣyussma sṛṣṭaḥ puruṣo virāṭ || 25 ||
dvitīyaṃ taṃ manuṃ viddhi manorantarameva ca ||
sa vairājaḥ prajāssarvāṃssasarje puruṣaḥ prabhuḥ || 26 ||
nārāyaṇivasargasya

--- Page 63 ---
prajāstasyāpyayonijāḥ ||
āyuṣmānkīrtimāndhanayaḥ prajāvaśābhavattataḥ || 27 ||
ityevamādisargāste vaṇito munisattama ||
ādisar̄gai viditvaivaṃ yathārghāṃ prāśuyādritim || 28 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe paṃcamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāmādisar̄gavārṇanaṃ nāma ekānatr̄iṃśodhyāyaḥ || 29 ||
sūta uvāca || ||
saṃtr̄ṣṭaśca prajāśceva āpvoṣṭhya prajāpatiḥ ||
lebhe vai puruṣaḥ patnīṃ śatarūpāmayonijām || 1 ||
āpavastya mahiṣṇā tu divamāghṛtya tiṣṭataḥ ||
dharmeṇaiva mahātmā sa śatarūpāpyajāyat || 2 ||
sā tu varṣaśataṃ tathvā tapaḥ paramaduścaram ||
bhartāraṃ dīptitapasaṃ puruṣaṃ pratyapadyata || 3 ||
sa vai svāyaṃbhuvo jajñe puruṣo manurucyate ||
tasyaikasaptitiyugaṃ manvantarimihocyate || 4 ||
vairājātpuruṣāddhīrā śatarūpā vyajāyata ||
priyavratottānapādau vīrakāyāmajāyatāsṛ || 5 ||
kāmyā nāma mahābhāgā karddamasya prajāpateḥ ||
kāmyāputrākhyaratvāsansamākhāśirivitṛprabhuḥ || 6 ||
uttānapādojanayatpurāṃśckrasmānprabhuḥ ||
dhruvaṃ ca tanayaṃ divyamātmānandaśuvarcasam || 7 ||
dharmasya kanyā suśroṇī sunītirnāma viśrutā ||
utpannā cāpi dharmeṇa dhruvasya jananī tathā || 8 ||
dhruvo varṣasahasrāṇi trīṇi divyāni kānane ||
tapastape sa bālastu prārthayannsthanambhavyam || 9 ||
tasmai brahmā dadau prītasthānātmāsaṃmaṃ prabhuḥ ||
acalaṃ caiva puratassamarṣīṇāṃ prajāpatiḥ || 10 ||
tasmādyutiṣṭhira dhānyaśca dhuvātputrau vyajāyatāstu ||
yutiṣṭhrevaṃ saṣṭhāyāḥ pañcaputrānakalmṣāt || 11 ||
ripuṃ ripuṃjayaṃ viprataṃ vṛkalaṃ vṛṣatejasam ||
riporevaṃ ca mahiṣī cākṣuṣaṃ savaiṃtodiśam || 12 ||
ajo janatupakāriṇyāṃ varuṇa cākṣuṣo manuḥ ||
manorjāyanta daśa naḍūlāyāṃ mahojasaḥ || 13 ||
kanyāyāṃ hi munisreṣṭha vaiśyajanma prajāpateḥ ||
purumoṣaḥ śatadyumnastapasvi satyavitkaviḥ || 14 ||
agniṣṭhamo'tiratnaṃśātimanustrayaśā daśa ||
purorjanayatputrāṇaṣaḍagreyi mahāprabhān || 15 ||
aṅgaṃ sumanasoṃ khyātaṃ srutimṛgirāsaṃ gayam ||
aṅgātstunīthā bhāryā vai venamekamāsuyat || 16 ||
apacāreṇa venasya kopatestṛṣāṃ mahānbhūt ||
huṃkāreṇaiva taṃ jaghnuṣūnayo dharmatparāḥ || 17 ||
atha prajāthemṛṣayaḥ prārhitāśca śunīthayā ||
sārasvatāstadā tasya marmābhudēkṣīṇaṃ krabuḥ || 18 ||
venasya pāṇo mathite saṃbabhūva tataḥ pṛthuḥ ||
sa ghanvī kavacī jātastejasādityasaṃbhavaḥ || 19 ||
avatārastha viṣṇorihaṃ prajāpalanehetav ||
dharmasaṃrakṣaṇārthāya duṣṭānāṃ daṃḍahetave || 20 ||
pṛthunaintyastadā pṛthivīmarkaṣatṛkṣatṛpṛrvaiḥ ||
rājasūyābhiṣikānāmādhyasya vaṣṭughāpatiḥ || 21 ||
tasmāccaiva sahutpannau nipuṇau śrutamārgadhau ||
teneyaṃ gaumuniśreṣṭha dugdhā savihitāyā vai || 22 ||
sarveṣāṃ vṛttidaśābhūdaivaiśsurarkṣasām ||
manuṣyāyāṃ viśeṣeṇa śatayajñakaro nṛpaḥ || 23 ||
pṛthoḥ putrau tu jajñāte dharmiṇau bhuvi pārthivau ||
vijitāśvaśca hayeśo mahāvīrau sthāviśrutau || 24 ||
śikhaṇḍinī cājanayatputre

--- Page 64 ---
prācīnabarhiṣu ||
prācīnāgnāḥ kuśāstasya pṛthivītalacarīṇaḥ || 25 ||
samudratanayā tena dharmatastuvivaāhitā ||
rejeṣighakataraṃ rājā kṛtadāro mahāprabhuḥ || 26 ||
samudratanayāyāstu daśa prācīnabarhiṣaḥ |
bahuputrastanayā divyā bahuyajñakarasya vai || 27 ||
sarve prācetasā nāmnā ṣaṭpañcāśasya pāragāḥ ||
adaghamāncaraṇāstoṣṭyaṃt mahatpaḥ || 28 ||
daśavarṣasahasrāṇi samudrasililośayāḥ ||
rudragītaṃ japatnaśca śivahyānapārāyaṇāḥ || 29 ||
tapaścaratsu pṛthivyāmabhavanśca mahīruhāḥ ||
arakṣyamāṇāyāṃ pṛthvyāṃ babhruvatha prajākṣayaḥ || 30 ||
tāndṛṣṭvā tu nivṛttāste tapaso laghusadhrāḥ ||
uṣkuṣṭhiniśādṛlā dagdhukāmāstapobalaḥ || 31 ||
prācetasā sukhebhyaste prāmṛjannagnimārutau ||
vṛkṣānunmṛdya vāyustānadahaddhavyavāhinaḥ || 32 ||
vṛkṣakṣayaṃ tato dṛṣṭvā kiñcicceṣu śākiṣu ||
upagantvā3vadītarājā somaḥ pratāpavān || 33 ||
soma uvāca ||
kopaṃ yacchata rājānastvam prācīnabarhiṣaḥ ||
adabhrātānukantheyaṃ vṛkṣāṇāṃ varavarṇinī || 34 ||
bhaviṣyaṃ jānatā sā tu dhruvā garbheṇa vai mayā ||
bhāryā vo'stu mahābhāgāssomavanśivavardinī || 35 ||
asyāśutpatsyate vidvāndakṣo nāma prajāpatiḥ ||
sṛṣṭikartā mahātejā brahmaputraḥ purātanaḥ ||36 ||
yuṣmākaṃ tejasārddhena mama cānena tejasā ||
brahmatejomayo bhūpaḥ prajāḥ saṃvardhiṣyati || 37 ||
tatassomastya vacanājagṛhustu pracetasaḥ ||
bhāryāṃ dharmeṇa tāṃ prītyā vṛkṣajāṃ varavarṇinīm || 38 ||
tebhyastasyāstu saṃjajñe dakṣo nāma prajāpatiḥ ||
so'pi jajñe mahātejāstsomastyaṃśena vai śṛṇue ||39 ||
acarāṃśca carāṃścaiva dvipadośca catuṣpadaḥ ||
saṃsmṛtya manasā dakṣo maithunīṃ sṛṣṭimārabhat || 40 ||
vīraṇasya sutāṃ nāmnā vīraṇīṃ sa prajāpateḥ ||
upayeme śuvidhena sugharmeṇa prativratām || 41 ||
hayyeśānayutaṃ tasyāṃ suta tṛṇyayānajījanat ||
te viraktā bahūbhuśca nāradasyopajeśataḥ || 42 ||
tacchrutvā sa punardakṣastu balāśvānajījanat ||
nāmatastanayāṃstasyāṃ sahasraparisaṃkhyayā || 43 ||
te'pi bhātṛpathā yātāstanśuneropaśataḥ ||
nāgaminpitṛsābhikhyaṃ viraktā bhikṣumārgiṇaḥ || 44 ||
tacchrutvā śāpamākuddho munaye duḥsahaṃ dadau ||
kutracinnaṃ labhasveti saṃsthitiṃ kalahpriya || 45 ||
śāntvato'tha vighāprahiḥ sa paścādṛjatriḥ thyaḥ ||
mahājvālāsvarūpeṇa guṇeśvāpi munīśvara || 46 ||
dadau sa daśa dharmāya kaśyapāya trayodaśa ||
dve caiva brahmaputrāya dve caiva dvirasate tadā ||47||
dve kuśāśāya viduṣe munaye munisattama ||
śiṣṭāssomāya dakṣo'pi nakṣatrākhyā dadau prabhuḥ || 48 ||
tābhyo dakṣasya putrībhyo jātā

--- Page 65 ---
devāsurādayaḥ ||
bahuvastanayāḥ syātāstaiḥsarvaiḥ pūritaṃ jagat || 49 ||
tataḥprabhuti vigreṇdra prajā maithunasaṃbhavāḥ ||
saṃkalpādarśanātsparśāntpūrvaiḥ vā sṛṣṭirucyate || 50 || ||
śaunaka uvāca ||
aṅguṣṭhādbrāhmaṇo jajñe dakṣaścoktastvayā purā ||
kathaṃ prācetasatvaṃ hi punarlemhe mahātapāḥ || 51 ||
śrutaṃ me saṃśayaṃ sūta pratyākhyātuṃ tvamarhasi ||
citramaitatasya kathaṃ śaśvuratāṃ gataḥ || 52 ||
sūta uvāca ||
utpattīśca nirāghasca nityaṃ bhūteṣu vartate ||
kalpe kalpe bhavantye sarve dakṣādayo mune || 53 ||
imāṃ visṛṣṭiṃ dakṣasya yo vidyātsa carācarām ||
prajāvānāyuṣā pūrṇaḥsvargaloke mahīyate || 54 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ sargavarṇanaṃ nāma triṃśaḥadhyāyaḥ || 30 ||
śaunaka uvāca ||
devānāṃ dānavānāṃ ca gandharvāṇāṃ rakṣasām ||
sṛṣṭiṃ tu vistaraṇemāṃ sūtaputra vadāśu me || 1 ||
sūta uvāca ||
yadā na vavrṛdhe sā tu vīraṇasya prajāpatiḥ ||
śutāṃ śutapasuā yukta kāmāhvayatsargekāraṇāt || 2 ||
sa maithunena dharmeṇa sasarja vividhāḥ prajāḥ ||
tāḥ śṛṇu tvaṃ mahāprājña kathayāmi samāsataḥ || 3 ||
tasyāṃ putrasahasrāṇi vīriṇyāṃ pañca vīryavān ||
āśritya janayāmāsa dakṣa eva prajāpatiḥ || 4 ||
etānsmṛṣṭāṃstu tāndṛṣṭvā nāradaḥ prāha vai śānīn ||
sarvān sa tu satkutpaṇṇo nāradaḥ parameṣṭhinaḥ || 5 ||
śrutavānvā kaśyapādīn puṃsāṃ sṛṣṭibhṛviṣyati ||
dakṣasyaiva duhitṛṣu tasmāttānbravītu saḥ || 6 ||
ajānantaḥ kathaṃ sṛṣṭiṃ bāliśā vai kariṣyatha ||
diśaṃ kāṃcidajānantastasmadiñjāya tāṃ bhuvaḥ || 7 ||
ityuktāḥ prayurassarve āśāṃ vijñātumojasā ||
tadantaṃ na hi saṃprāpya na nivṛttāḥ pitṛgṛham || 8 ||
tajjñātvā janayāmāsa punaḥ pañcaśatānśutān ||
tānuvāca punarsoapi nāradasya sarvadarśanaḥ || 9 ||
nārada uvāca ||
bhuvā mānmajānantaḥ kathaṃ sṛṣṭiṃ kariṣyatha ||
sarve hi bāliśāḥ kiṃ hi sṛṣṭiṃ kartuṃ samarthyatāḥ || 10 ||
sūta uvāca ||
te api tadvacanaṃ śrutvā niyatāssarvetodiśaṃ ||
suvalāśvā dakṣasutā hyevaṃ eva te purā || 11 ||
anantaṃ puṣkaraṃ prāpya gatāsteapi parābhavaṃ ||
adhyāpi na nivartante samudrebhya ivāpagāḥ || 12 ||
tadāprabhūti vai bhrātā bhrāturanveṣaṇe rataḥ ||
grayāto naśyati mune tanna kāryaiḥ vipaścitā || 13 ||
tānśāpi naṣṭānvijñāya putrāndakṣaḥ prajāpatiḥ ||
sa ca krodhāddadau śāpaṃ nāradāya mahātmane || 14 ||
kuñciña lamasvetī sthitiṃ kalahapriya ||
tava sāṃnidhyato loke bhavedca kalahasrathā || 15 ||
śāntvitośya vidhātrā hi sa dakṣastu prajāpatiḥ ||
kanyāḥ ṣaṣṭheṣu jatpaścādbhīriṇyāmiti naḥ śrutam || 16 ||
dadau sa daśa dharmāya kaśyapāya trayodaśa ||
saptaviṃśati somāya caturviṃśatiraṣṭanimine || 17 ||
dve caivam brahmaputrāya dve caiva

