dhire se tadā ||
he kṛśāśāya viduṣe tāsāṃ nāmāni me śṛṇu || 18 ||
aruṃdhatī vasudhyoṃ milaṃbā bhānurmerṃ utvatī ||
saṃkalpā ca muhūrtāṃ ca saṃdhyā viśvā ca vai śune || 19 ||
dharmapratnyo śune tvetāstāsvapratyāni me śṛṇu ||
viśvedevāstu viśvāyāssādhyānsādhyā vai jāyat || 20 ||
marutvatāṃ marutvanto vasostū vasavastathā ||
bhānostu bhānavaḥ sarve muhūrtāyāṃ muhūrtajāḥ || 21 ||
lambāyāścaiva voṣoṣaṭha nāgavīthāṃ ca yāmiñjā ||
pṛthivīviṣamastatyāmaruṃghatyāmajāyat || 22 ||
saṃkalpāyāstu satyātmā jajñe saṃkalpaṃ eva hi ||
ayādayo vasoḥ putrā aṭhau tāñśṛṇu śaunaka || 23 ||
ayo dhruvaśca somaśca dharaścaivānilośnalaḥ ||
pratyuṣaśca prabhāsaśca vasoraṣṭau ca nāmataḥ || 24 ||
ayasya putro vaitaṇḍaḥ śramaḥ śānto munistatthā ||
dhruvasya putro bhagavānkālo lokapramāvanaḥ || 25 ||
somasya bhagavānvaco varcasvī yena jāyate ||
dharasya putro dravīṇo hutahavyavahastatthā || 26 ||
manoharāyāśiśiraḥ prāṇoṣṭha ramaṇastatthā ||
anilasya śivā bhāryā yasya putraḥ purojavaḥ || 27 ||
avijñātagatiścaiva dau putrāvinilasya tu ||
agniputraḥ kumārastu śarastaṃ be śriyāvṛte || 28 ||
tasya śākho viśākhaśca naigameyaśca pṛccthataḥ ||
apatye kṛttikānāṃ tu kārtikeya iti smṛtaḥ || 29 ||
pratyuṣasya tvabhūtputra ṛṣirnāmnā tu devalaḥ ||
dvau putrou devalaṃsyāpi prajāvantau manīṣiṇau || 30 ||
bṛhaspatestu maṃginī varastrī brahmacāriṇī ||
yogasiddhā jagatkṛtsnaṃ samantādvyacarttadāṃ || 31 ||
prabhāsasya tu sā bhāryā vasuunāmaṣṭamasya ca ||
viśvakarmnā mahābhāga tasya jajñe prajāpatiḥ || 32 ||
kartā śilpasahasrāṇāṃ tridaśānāṃ ca vārddhikaḥ ||
bhūṣaṇānāṃ ca sarveṣāṃ kartā śilpavatāṃ varaḥ || 33 ||
yassvāṃsāṃ vimānāni devatānāṃ cakāra ha ||
manuṣyāścopajīvanti yasya śilpaṃ mahātmanaḥ || 34 ||
matāntara māha |
raivato'jo bhavo bhīmo nāma umo vṛṣākipiḥ ||
ajaickapādahirbudhnyau bahurupo mahāniti || 35 ||
sarupāyāṃ prasūtasya bhāryā rudrāṃśca koṭiśaḥ ||
tataicakādaśāmuktyāṃstu tannāmāni śune śṛṇu || 36 ||
ajaickapādahirbudhnyastvavṛtā rudrasya vīryavān ||
harasya bahurupasca tryaṃbakaścāparājitaḥ || 37 ||
vṛṣākipiśca śaṃbuśca kaparddī raivatastatthā ||
ekādaśaite kathitā rudrāstribhuvaneśvarāḥ || 38 ||
śataṃ tvevaṃ samākhyātaṃ rudrāṇāmimitojasām ||
śṛṇu kaśyapapratnīnāṃ nāmāni munirsattama || 39 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ sagaṇavarṇanaṃ nāmaikaviṃśodhyāyaḥ || 21 ||
sūta uvāca ||
aditirditiśca surāsāriṃścaila dvaureṃ ca ||
surabhirvinnata celā tāmrā koṃcavaśā tathā || 1 ||
kadrumuniśca viprendrā tāsvapatyāni me

--- Page 67 ---
śṛṇu ||
pūrvamantare śreṣṭhe dvādaśāsuruttamāḥ || 2 ||
tuṣitā nāma te'nyonyabhūtvai vastvantare ||
upasthite suyaśasśākhupasvāntare manoḥ || 3 ||
hitāya sarvalokānāṃ samāgamya parasparaṃ ||
āgacchatastu tānūcuriditiṃ ca praviśya vai || 4 ||
manvantare pralayāmastāṃ śreyo bhaviṣyati ||
evamuktā stu te sarve cākṣupasvāntare manoḥ || 5 ||
mārīcātkaśyapājātāste'dityāṃ dakṣakanyayā ||
taṃ viṣṇuśca śaṃkaśca jajñāte punareva hi || 6 ||
aryamā caiva ghātā ca tvaṣṭā pūṣā tathaiva ca ||
vivasvānsavitā caiva mitrāvaruṇa eva ca || 7 ||
aṃśo bhagaścātitejā āditya dvādaśa smṛtāḥ ||
cākṣupasvāntare pūrvamāsanye tuṣitāsurāḥ || 8 ||
pureva tasyāntare tu ādityā dvādaśa smṛtāḥ ||
iti proktāni kramaśo'dityapatyāni śaunaka || 9 ||
saptaviṃśatiṃ yāḥ proktāssomapattyo'tha śubratāḥ ||
tāsāmapatyānyabhavandvitrayoṃ'mittatejasaḥ || 10 ||
ariṣṭanemipattnīnāmapatyāniha ṣoḍaśa ||
bahuśasya viduṣaśca tasyā yāstu smṛtāḥ || 11 ||
kṛśāśvasya tu deveṣu devapraharṇāḥ smṛtāḥ ||
bhāryāyāmiciñpi mune dhūmrakeśastatheva ca || 12 ||
svagā satī ca dvau patnyau svagha jyeṣṭhā satī parā ||
svaghamūt pitṝnvedamathorāñcirasaṃ satī || 13 ||
ete yugasahasrānte jāyante punareva hi ||
sarvendevanīkāyaśca trayiṃśatu kāmajāḥ || 14 ||
yathā sūryasya nityaṃ hi udayāstamayāvivai ||
evaṃ devanīkāyāste saṃbhavanti yuge yuge || 15 ||
dityāṃ babhūvatuḥ putrau kaśyapāditinaḥ śrutam ||
hiraṇyakaśipuścaiva hiraṇyākṣaśca vīryavān || 16 ||
siṃhikā kramavatcanyā vipracciteḥ parigrahaḥ ||
hiraṇyakaśipoḥ putrāścatvāraḥ prathitaujasaḥ || 17 ||
anudvādaśa dvādaśa saṃhādaścaiva vīryavān ||
prahlādaścārujastaṃra viṣṇubhaktinicāragdhīḥ || 18 ||
anudvādasyā sūryāyāṃ pulomā mahiṣastathā ||
dvādasyā dhaminibhāryāsuta vātāpirmilavalmaḥ || 19 ||
saṃhvādasyā kṛtibhāryāsuta pañcajanaṃ tataḥ ||
virocanastya prahlādiddaivyātasyāmavadhāliḥ || 20 ||
baleḥ putrāśataṃ tvāsīdśanāyāṃ munīśvara ||
balirasīnmahāśivaḥ śivabhaktiparāyaṇāḥ || 21 ||
dānaśīla udāraśca puṇyakīrtistapaḥ smṛtaḥ ||
tatputro vāṇanāmā yaṣṣo'pi śaivavarasuddhīḥ ||
yastaṃtoṣya śivaṃ samyaggāṇapatyamavāpa ha || 22 ||
sā kathā śrutapūrvaṃ te vāṇasya hi mahātmanaḥ ||
kṛṣṇaṃ yassmaro vīrarasuprasaṃ cakāra ha || 23 ||
hiraṇyākṣasutāḥ pañca paṇḍitāstumahābalāḥ ||
kukuruḥ śakuniścaiva bhūtasantāpanastathā || 24 ||
mahānādaśca vikrāntaḥ kālanābhastatheva ca ||
ityuktā dittipuṭrāśca danoḥ putrānmune śṛṇu || 25 ||
abhavandvipuṭrāśca śataṃ tīvraparākramāḥ ||
ayomukhaśśaṃbaraśca kapolo vāmanastathā || 26 ||
vaiśvānareḥ pulomā ca vidravāṇa

--- Page 68 ---
mahāśirau ||
svarbhānuṛṣaparvā ca viśvacitta śca vīryavān || 27 ||
ete sarve danoḥ putrāḥ kaśyapādanujajñire |
eṣāṃ putrāñśṛṇu mune prasaṅgādvimiteṣṭanaġha || 28 ||
svarbhānostu prabhā kanyā pulomnāstu śacī sutā ||
upadānavī hayaśirā śarmiṣṭhā vāṣpavaiṇī || 29 ||
pulomā pulomikā caiva vaiśvānara sute ube ||
bāhupātye mahāvīryai māricīstu parigrahaḥ ||30||
tayoḥ putraśahasrāṇi ṣaṣṭidānava nandanāḥ ||
marīcijenayāmāsa mahatā tapasānvitaḥ ||31||
paulomāḥ kālakhaṃjāśca dānavānāṃ mahābalāḥ ||
avaddhyā devatānāṃ ca hiraṇyapuravāsinnaḥ ||32||
pitāmahaprāsādena ye hatāḥ savyasācinā ||
siṃhikā yāmathōtpannā viśracittasutāstatthā ||33||
daityatānavasaṃyogāddhātāstīvraparākramāḥ ||
saiṃhikeyā iti khyātāstayor daśa mahābalāḥ ||34||
rāhuḥ śalyo

mubālinaḥ balaśreiva mahābalaḥ ||
vātāpirnamuciścevatheḥ valaḥ svasṛpas tatthā ||35||
ajikaḥ narakaśreiva kālanābhastathaiva ca ||
śarmaṇaścarakarpaśca ete vaṃśavivardhanāḥ ||36||
eṣāṃ putrāśca pautrāśca danuvaṃśavivardhanāḥ ||
bahvaṃśaṃ saṃpraduktā vistaratvānna varṇitāḥ ||37||
sandhādastya tu daiteyā nivātakavacāḥ kule ||
utpannā marutas tarṣmas tapasā bhāvitātmanaḥ ||38||
ṣaṇmukhadyā mahāsattvāstāmāyāḥ parikīrtitāḥ ||
kākī śyenī ca bhāsī ca gṛdhrīvī ca śukī tathā ||

|| 39 ||
śṛddhikāśī ḍhulkī ca tāmrākanyāḥ prakīrtitāḥ ||
kākī kākānajanayaduḍhulkī pratyulṇṇakakāv ||40||
śyenī śyenāṃstatthā bhāsī bhāsānṛddhī tu gṛdhrakāv ||
śukī śukānajanayadgṛdhrīvī śubhapakṣiṇaḥ || 41 ||
aśvāruṣūṇgādiṃśaṃ tāmrā ca kaśyapriyā ||
janayāmāsa caiteyevaṃ tāmrāvaṃśāḥ prakīrtitāḥ ||42||
vinatāyāśca putrau dvāvaruṇo garuḍas tathā ||
suparṇaḥ patanāṃ śreṣṭho nāruṇasvena karmaṇā ||43||
surasāyāssahasraṃ tu sarpāṇāmamitaujasām ||
anekāśirasāṃ teṣāṃ khecārāṇāṃ mahātmanām || 44 ||
yeṣāṃ pradhānā rājānāḥ śeṣavāsukitakṣakāḥ ||
airāvato mahāpadmaḥ kambalāśvataraṇubhau || 45 ||
elāputra statthā padmaḥ karkoṭakadhanaṃjayau ||
mahānīlamahākarṇau dhṛtarāṣṭro balāhakaḥ || 46 ||
kuheraḥ puṣpadantaśca durmukhastūṣṭumukhastathā ||
bahuśāḥ kharromā ca pāṇiretyadevamādyayaḥ ||47||
gaṇāḥ koṭavaśāyāśca tasyāssarve ca dṛṣṭiṇaḥ ||
aṇḍajāḥ pakṣiṇoṭañjāśca varāyāḥ paśavo matāḥ || 48 ||
anāśupāyāḥ putrāśca pañcāśacca mahābalāḥ ||
abhavanbalṛttau ca vikṣaṇgeṭha bṛhaṃs tathā || 49 ||
śaśāṃstu janayāmāsa surabhi rmedhiṃśās tathā ||
ilā vṛkṣāñ chatā

vallīs tṛṇajātīs tu sarvaśaḥ || 50 ||
khaśā tu yakṣarakṣāṃsi munirapsaras as tathā ||
ariṣṭāsūta sarpāṃśca prabhāvaimanvavottamān || 51 ||
ete kaśyapadā

--- Page 69 ---
yādāḥ kīrtitāste munīśvarāḥ ||
yeṣāṃ putrāśca pautrāśca śataśośatha sahasraśaḥ || 52 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāṃ umāsaṃhitāyāṃ kaśyapaṃśavarṇanaṃ nāma dvātriṃśodhyāyaḥ || 32 ||
sūta uvāca

eṣa manvantare tāta sargassvārocipe smṛtaḥ ||
vaivasvate tu mahiti vāruṇe vitite kṛtau || 1 ||
brahmānasya brāhmaṇo vai prajāsargam ihoñyate ||
pūrvaṃ yānatha brahmarṣīnutpannānstu mānasān || 2 ||
putrānve kalpayāmāsa svayameva pitāmahaḥ ||
teṣāṃ virodhe devānāṃ dānavānāṃ mahārṣe || 3 ||
ditirvīnṛtapuruṣā tu kaśyapaṃ samupasthitā ||
tāṃ kaśyapaḥ prasannātmā samyagārādhitastathā || 4 ||
vareṇa cchandayāmāsa sā ca vavre varaṃ tadā ||
putramindravighātāya samarthamitojasamṃ || 5 ||
sa tasye ca varaṃ prādātprāyitaṃ sumahātapāḥ ||
brahmacaryādidinyamaṃ prāha caitra śataṃ samāḥ || 6 ||
dhārayāmāsa garbhaṃ tu śuciḥsā varavarṇinī ||
brahmacaryādidinyamaṃ ditirgarbhe tatheva vai || 7 ||
tatastāghāya sodhityāṃ garbhe taṃ śaṃsita vrataḥ ||
jagāma kaśyapastaptuṃ tapassamṣṭhamānasaḥ || 8 ||
tasyāścaivāntare premsuḥsodhbhavapākaśāsanaḥ ||
ūnavarṣe śate cāsyā dadharśāntarameva saḥ || 9 ||
akṛtvā pādayoḥ śaucaṃ ditirvinikṣarāstadā ||
nidrāmāhārayāmāsa bhāvinodhyasya gauravāt || 10 ||
etasminnantre śakrastasyāḥ kukṣiṃ praviśya saḥ ||
vajrapāṇistu taṃ garbhe saptadhā hi nyakuntata || 11 ||
sa pāṭyamāno garbhotha vajreṇa prarurodra ha ||
rudantaṃ saptadhaikaikaṃ mārodīriti tānpunaḥ ||
cakre vajrapāṇistāmbheva maṣustathāpi te || 12 ||
te tapruḥ pātyamānāssarve prāṃjalayo mune ||
no jighāṃsāsi kiṃ śakra bhrātaro marutastava || 13 ||
indreṇa svīkṛtāste hi bhrātṛtve sarve ṣva ca ||
tatryorjaidrtyabhāvaṃ te vibhreṣe śaṃkareḥchayā || 14 ||
maruto nāma te devā bahubhujsumahābalāḥ ||
khagā eko napañcāśatsahāyā vajrapāṇinaḥ || 15 ||
teṣāmeva prabṛddhānāṃ hariḥ prādātprajāpatiḥ ||
kramaśastāni rājyāni pṛthupṛthai śṛṇuṣa tat || 16 ||
ariṣṭapuruṣo vīraḥ kṛṣṇo jiṣṇuḥ prajāpatiḥ ||
parjaniyastu ghanādhyakṣastasya sarvamidam jagat || 17 ||
bhūtasargamimam samyagvocarṃ te mahāmune ||
vibhāgaṃ śṛṇu rājyānāṃ kramaśastaṃ bhuvekṣuṇā || 18 ||
abhiṣicyādhirājye tu pṛthuṃ vaiṃnyaṃ pitāmahaḥ ||
tataḥ krameṇa rājyāni vyādadhuḥkṣupacakrame || 19 ||
dvijānāṃ vīrudhāṃ caiva nakṣatrāhrayostathā ||
yajñānāṃ tapasāṃ caiva somaṃ rājyebhyaṣecayat || 20 ||
apāṃ tu varuṇaṃ rājye rājñā vaiśravaṇaṃ prasuṃ ||
ādityānāṃ tathā viṣṇuṃ vasunāmatha pāvakam || 21 ||
prajāpatīnāṃ dakṣaṃ tu marutāmatha vāsavam ||
daityānāṃ dānavānāṃ ca prahrādamitojasamṃ || 22 ||
vaivasvataṃ pitṝṇāṃ ca yamaṃ rājyebhyaṣecayat ||
mātṝṇāṃ ca bratānāṃ ca mantrāṇāṃ ca tathā gavām || 23 ||
yakṣāṇāṃ rākṣasānāṃ ca pārthavānāṃ tathaiva ca ||
sarvabhūtapiśācānāṃ giriśaṃ śūlapāṇinam || 24 ||
śailānāṃ himavantaṃ ca nadīnāmatha sāgaram ||
mṛgāṇāmatha śā

--- Page 70 ---
dūlaṃ goṭṛṣaṃ tu gaṇāmapi || 25 ||
vanaspatīnāṃ vṛkṣāṇāṃ vaṭaṃ rājye'bhyaṣecayat ||
iti dattaṃ prajeśena rājyaṃ sarvatr vai kramāt || 26 ||
pūrvastyāṃ diśi putraṃ tu vairājasya prajāpateḥ |
sthāpayāmāsa sarvātmā rājye viśvapatirvibhuḥ || 27 ||
tathaiva khunuiśāḍūla kardamasya prajāpateḥ ||
dakṣiṇasyāṃ tathā putraṃ subhagvānnamacīkupat || 28 ||
paścimāyāṃ diśi tathā rajasaḥ putraṃ cyutam ||
ketumantaṃ mahātmānaṃ rājānaṃ vyādiśatprabhuḥ || 29 ||
tathā hiraṇyaromāṇaṃ parjannyasya prajāpateḥ ||
udīcyāṃ diśi rājānaṃ duḥkheṣe so'bhyaṣecayat || 30 ||
tasya vistaramākhyātaṃ pṛthoryainnyasya śaunaka ||
mahaddhyaitatdigṣṭhānaṃ purāṇaṃ parikīlitam || 31 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ sargavarṇanaṃ nāma trayastriṃśattamo'dhyāyaḥ || 32 ||
śaunaka uvāca

manvantarāṇi sarvāṇi vistareṇānukīrtaya ||
yāvanto manavaścaiva śrotumicchāmi tānaham || 1 ||
sūta uvāca

svāyaṃbhuvo manuścaiva tatassavārocicastathā ||
uttamatāmasceiva raivatāścākṣusastathā || 2 ||
ete ca manavaḥ ṣaṭ te saṃproktā munipuṃgava ||
vaivasvato munisreṣṭha sāṃprataṃ manurucyate || 3 ||
sāvarṇiśca manuścaiva tato raucyastathaparaḥ ||
tathaiva brahmasāvarṇiścavāro manavastathā || 4 ||
tathaiva dharmasāvarṇīṃ rudrasāvarṇireva ca ||
devasāvarṇirākhyāta indrasāvarṇireva ca || 5 ||
atītā vartamānāśca tathaivānāgatāśca ye ||
kīrtitā manavaścāpi mathyaite yathā śrutāḥ || 6 ||
mune catuḥśītatāni trikālānugatāni te ||
proktānyebhirmitaḥ kalpo yugasāhasraparyayaḥ || 7 ||
ṛṣīṃstesāṃ pravakṣyāmi putrāndevagaṇāṃstathā ||
śṛṇu śaunaka samītyā kramaśastānyaśasvanaḥ || 8 ||
marīciritribhṛṅgavānāṅgirāḥ pulahaḥ kratuḥ ||
pulastyaśca vasiṣṭhaśca saptaite brahmaṇasutāḥ || 9 ||
uttarastyāṃ diśi tathā mune saptarṣyastathā ||
yāmā nāma tathā devā āsansvāyaṃbhuvāntare || 10 ||
āgnīdhraścāgniibāhuśca megha meghātithersuḥ ||
jyotiṣmāndyutimandhavyaḥ savanaśśubra eva ca || 11 ||
svāyaṃbhuvasya putrāste manodaṃśa mahātmanaḥ ||
kīrtitā munuiśāḍūla tanrendro yajña ucyate || 12 ||
prathamaṃ kathitaṃ tāta divyaṃ manvantaraṃ tathā ||
dvitīyaṃ te pravakṣyāmi tannibodhya yathātathyam || 13 ||
ūrjastambhaḥ parastambha ṛṣayo vasumāṃstathā ||
jyotiṣmandyutimāṃścaiva rociṣmānsaptamastathā || 14 ||
ete maharsayo jñeyāstantrandro rocanastathā ||
devāśca tuṣitā nāma smṛtāḥ svārociṣāntare || 15 ||
hariṇaḥstutikṛtajyotistrayo murtiratyamayaḥ ||
prathitaśca manastyaśca nabhastūryaṃstatheva ca || 16 ||
svārociṣasya putrāste manodaṃśa mahātmanaḥ ||
kīrtitā munuiśāḍūla mahāvīryaparākramāḥ || 17 ||
dvitīyametatkathitaṃ mune manvantaraṃ mayā ||
tṛtīyaṃ tava vakṣyāmi tannibodhya yathātathyam || 18 ||
vasiṣṭhaputrāḥ saptāsanvāsiṣṭhā iti viśrutāḥ ||
hiraṇyagarbhasya sutā ūrjā nāma mahojasaḥ || 19 ||
ṛṣayo'tra

--- Page 71 ---
samākhyātāḥ kīrtyamānābhivoṣa me ||
auttameyā ṛṣiśreṣṭha daśa putrā manoḥ smṛtāḥ || 20 ||
iṣa ūrjitaūrjaṃśva mṛṣumāṃgatra eva ca ||
śuciśśukravṛhaśśaiva namaśo nabha eva ca || 21 ||
ṛṣabhastaira devāśca satyaveduṣṭatādayaḥ |
tatrendra ssatyajijñāna trailokyādhipatīrbhuvane || 22 ||
tṛtīyametaparaṃ manvantaraṃ mudāhṛtaṃ ||
manvantaraṃ caturthe te kathayāmi mune śṛṇu || 23 ||
gārgye ḥ pṛthusthā vāgmī janyo ghātā kapīnakaḥ ||
kapīnāṃsanta ṛṣayaḥ satya devagaṇāstathā || 24 ||
tatrendraśśiśivo jñeyo manupūtrānmune śṛṇu ||
śrutipotarassoitapasyastapasśūlaśca tāpanaḥ || 25 ||
taporitrakarmaṣo ghanvī khaḍī mahāṛṣiḥ ||
tāmasasya smṛtā ete daśa putrā mahāvratāḥ || 26 ||
tāmasasyāntaraṃ caiva mano me kathitaṃ taṃ |
caturthe pañcaṃ tāta śṛṇu manvantaraṃ paraṃ ||

|| 27 ||
devabāhurvajrayaścaiva munirveṃdiśarāstathā ||
hiraṇyaromā parjanya ūrdhvabāhuśca somapāḥ || 28 ||
satyanetrataśrānyeye ete satarṣeyopare ||
devāśca bhūtarajasastapobhṛkutayastathā || 29 ||
tatrendra viṣṇunāmā ca trailokyādhipatistatthā ||
raivataśyo manustatra jñeyastāmasasodraḥ || 30 ||
arjenaḥ pāṃktiviṣyyo vā dayāyāstanayā mune ||
mahatā tapasā yuktā merupṛṣṭhe vasanti hi || 31 ||
ruceḥ prajāpatiḥ putro raucyo nāma manuḥ smṛtaḥ ||
dhṛtyā cotpādito devyā bhautyo nāmābhavatsuḥ || 32 ||
anāgatāśca saptaite kalpe'sminmanavasmṛtāḥ ||
anāgatāśca saptaiva smṛtā diviṃ maharṣayaḥ || 33 ||
rāmo vyāsastathātreyo dīptimānkṣubṛhaḥ suṭāḥ ||
bharadvājastatthā droṇirṛśatyāmā mahāyutiḥ || 34 ||
gautamastyātmajaścaiva śāradgāna gautamas kṛpaḥ ||
kauśiko gālavarśaiva ruruḥ kaśyapa eva ca || 35 ||
ete sapta mahātmāno bhaviṣyā munisattamāḥ ||
devāśanānagatāstatra trayaḥ proktāssvayaṃbhuvā || 36 ||
mārīcyaścaiva putrāste kaśyapasya mahātmanaḥ ||
teṣāṃ virocanasuṭo baliriṃdro bhaviṣyati || 37 ||
viṣaṇḍuśravāṇīvāṃśca śuṃyaṃto dhṛtimānvasuḥ ||
śūriḥ surāṣṭyo viṣṇuśca rājā sumitireva ca || 38 ||
sāvarṇeśca manoḥ putrā bhaviṣyā daśa śaunaka ||
ihaṣṭaṃ hi kathitaṃ navaṃ cāntaraṃ śṛṇu || 39 ||
prathamaṃ dakṣasāviṇiṃ pravakyāmi saduṃ śṛṇu ||
medhātithiśca paulastyo vasuḥ kaśyapa eva ca || 40 ||
jyotiṣmānbhārgavāścaiva dhṛtimāngirastathā ||
svanaścaiva vāsiṣṭha ātreyohavya eva ca || 41 ||
pulahastanta ityete ṛṣayo rohitaitare ||
devtānāṃ gaṇāstatra traya eva mahāśune || 42 ||
dīkṣāputrasya putrāste rohitasya prajāpateḥ ||
dhṛṣṭaketurditiketuḥ pañcahasato nirākṛtiḥ || 43 ||
pṛthuśravā dhṛriṣṭumno ṛcīko bṛhato garyaḥ ||
prathamasya tu sāvarṇenāiva putrā mahāujasaḥ || 44 ||
daśame'ttha paryāye dvitīyasyāntare manoḥ ||
haviṣmānpulahascaiva prakṛtiścaiva bhārgavaḥ || 45 ||
āyo muktistatthātreyo vasiṣṭhaścāvyayas smṛtaḥ ||
paulastyas prayatiścaiva bhāmāraścaiva kaśyapaḥ || 46 ||
aṅgirānainasasatyaḥ saptaite paramārṣayaḥ ||
devtānāṃ gaṇāśvāpi dviṣaṃgataṃśca ye smṛtāḥ || 47 ||
teṣāmindrastathāsmṛtaḥ

--- Page 72 ---
śaṃbhurattvayameva maheśvaraḥ ||
akṣatvānuttamaujaśca bhūrirṣeṇaśca vīryavān || 48 ||
śatānīko niśāmitro vṛṣaseno jayadrathaḥ |
bhūridyumnaḥ kuvarcīścitāṃdaśa tvete manoḥ sutāḥ || 49 ||
ekādaśe tu payoye tṛtīyasyāntare manaḥ ||
tasyāpi sapta ṛṣayaḥ kīrtyamānānnibodhame || 50 ||
ikaviṣmānkaśyapaścāpi vaṭupaścaiva vāruṇaḥ |
ātreyo'tha vasiṣṭhaśca dyunayastvaṅgirāstathā || 51 ||
cārudhuṣyaśca paulastyonirḥsvaro'gnirtu tejasaḥ ||
sapteite ṛṣayaḥ proktāśca yo devagaṇāḥ smṛtāḥ || 52 ||
brāhmaṇastu sutāste hi ta ime vaidhṛtāḥ smṛtāḥ |
sarveṅgaśca suśarmā ca devānīkastu kṣemakaḥ || 53 ||
daṃḍeṣu khaṇḍako daśaḥ kuṭumboho manaḥ smṛtāḥ ||
sāvarṇasya tu pautra vai tṛtīyasya nava smṛtāḥ || 54 ||
caturthasya tu sāvarṇenābhinsa nibodhame ||
dyutivasiṣṭhapūtreśca ātreya sutapāstathā || 55 ||
aṅgirāsatapaso dhyātīntapasvī kaśyapastathā ||
tapodhanāśca paulastyaḥ pulahāśca taporitaḥ || 56 ||
bhārgavasaptamastesāṃ vijñeyatapaso nidhiḥ ||
pañca devagaṇāḥ proktā mānasā brahmanarasutāḥ || 57 ||
ṛtadhāmā tadindro hi trilokīrājyaklutsukī ||
dvādaśe caiva payoye māvye raocyāntare mune || 58 ||
aṅgirāścaiva dhṛtimānpaulastyo havyavānstu yaḥ ||
paulahastatvadaśīṃ ca bhārgavaśca niraṃtsavaḥ || 59 ||
niṣprapaṃcastathā trayo nindāhaḥ kaśyapastathā ||
sutapāścaiva vāsiṣṭharasatevaite maharṣayaḥ || 60 ||
traya eva gaṇāḥ proktā devatānāṃ svayaṃbhuvā ||
divaspatistadindro vai vicitracittra eva ca || 61 ||
nayo varṇadhṛtāṃśca sunetre kṣatavṛddhakaḥ ||
nirbhayastutapā droṇo mano raocyasya te sutāḥ || 62 ||
caturdaśe tu payoye satyastvevāntare manaḥ |
āmīdhraḥ kāśyapaścaiva paulastyo māgadhaśca yaḥ || 63 ||
mārgavo'pyitavācaśca śucirāṅgirāstathā ||
yuktaścaiva tathātrayaḥ pautro vāsiṣṭha eva ca || 64 ||
ajitaḥ pulahāścaiva dhātyāssutaṣayaśca te ||
pavitravāksatpuṣā devāḥ śucirindro bhaviṣyati || 65 ||
eteṣāṃ kalya utthāya kīrtanāttukharmeghate ||
atītānāgatānāṃ vai maharṣīṇāṃ naraiḥ sadā || 66 ||
devatānāṃ gaṇāḥ proktāśśṛṇu pañca mahāmune ||
taraṃgabhīrbudhānaśca tanuśroḍanūya eva ca || 67 ||
atimānī pravīṇaśca viṣṇusaṃkrandanastathā ||
tejasvī sabalāścaiva satyastvete manoḥ sutāḥ || 68 ||
bhaumastye'vādhikāre vai pūrvakalpastu khyūpūyate ||
ityete'nāgatāstitā manavaḥ kīrtitā mayā || 69 ||
uktāssanatkumāreṇa vyāsāyāmittatejasā ||
pūrṇe yugasahasrānte paripālyaḥ svaghamṛntaḥ || 70 ||
prajābhistapasā yuktā brahmaloke vrajanti te ||
yugāni saptistvekaṃ sāmānyantaruktate ||71||
caturdaśaite manavaḥ kīrtitāḥ kīrtivardhanāḥ ||
manvantareṣu sarveṣu saṃhārite punarbbhavaḥ || 72 ||
na śakyamantaraṃ teṣāṃ vaktuṃ varṣaśatairaḥ ||
pūrṇe śatasahasre tu kalpo niḥśeṣa ucyate || 73 || || 74 ||
tatra sarvāṇi bhūtāni dagdhānyādityaraśmibhiḥ ||
brahmaṇamṛtaḥ kṛtvā sadādityagaṇaiḥ śune || 75 ||
praviśanti surareśṭha hariṃ nārāyaṇaṃ
61

--- Page 73 ---
param ||
ṣaḍdhāraṃ sarvabhūtānāṃ karṣatīṣu punaḥ punaḥ || 76 ||
bhūyopi bhagavān rudrassaṃhartā kāla eva hi ||
kṛpānte tatpravakṣyāmi manovaivasvatasya ca || 77 ||
iti te kathitaṃ sarvaṃ manvantarasamudbhavam ||
visargī puṇyamākhyānaṃ dhanyaṃ kulivavarddhanam || 78 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāṃ umāsaṃhitāyāṃ sarvmanvantarānukīrtanaṃ nāma catustriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 34 ||
sūta uvāca

vivasvānkaśyapājñe dākṣāyaṇyāṃ mahārṣeḥ |
tasya māyāsambhavatsaṃjñā tvaṣṭrī devī sureṇukā || 1 ||
munessahasraśunā tena tejasā dussahena ca |
martarūpeṇa nātuṣyadrūpayauvanśālinī || 2 ||
ādityasya hi tadrūpam asahasraśunustejasaḥ |
dahyamānā tadodyagamakarodravaṇinī || 3 ||
ṛṣeḥ syāṃ trīṇyapatyāni janayāmāsa bhāskaraḥ |
saṃjñāyāṃ tu manuḥ pūrvaṃ śrāddhadevaprajāpatiḥ || 4 ||
yamaśca yamunā caiva yamalau saṃbabhūvatuḥ |
evaṃ hi trīṇyapatyāni tasyāṃ jātāni suryataḥ || 5 ||
saṃbhatulaṃ tu tadrūpaṃ dṛṣṭvā saṃjñā vivasvataḥ |
asahantī tataśchāyāmātmanassāsmṛjacchabham || 6 ||
māyāmayī tu sā saṃjñāmovacadraktitatsuṃbhe |
kiṃ karomīha kāryaṃ te kathayasva śuciśmite || 7 ||
saṃjñovāca

ahaṃ yāsyāmi bhadraṃ te mameva bhavanaṃ pituḥ |
tvayaitadbhavane satyaṃ vastravyaṃ nirviṅkārataḥ || 8 ||
imau me bālakau sādhu kanyā ceyaṃ sumadhyamā |
pālanīyāḥ susenenaiva mama cedichasi priyam || 9 ||
chāyovāca

ākeśagrahaṇādeva sañharṣyeham sudurdharśatam |
nārpayiṣyāmi mataṃ tubhyaṃ gaccha devi yathāsukham || 10 ||
sūta uvāca

ityuktā sāgamaddevī śrīḍitā sannidhau pituḥ |
pitrā nirmaṃtritā tatra niyuktā sā punaḥpunaḥ || 11 ||
agacchaddvaḍvā bhūtvāṣacchādya rūpaṃ tatassvakaṃ |
kurvantadottarān prāpya nṝṇāṃ madhye cacāra ha || 12 ||
saṃjñāṃ tāṃ tu ravibhūtvā chāyāyāṃ suṣuptāṃ tadā |
janayāmāsa sāvarṇīṃ manuṃ vai savitā kila || 13 ||
saṃjñānuprārthitā chāyā sā svapurevoapi nityaśaḥ |
cakārabyadhikaṃ snehaṃ na tathā prāvaje sute || 14 ||
anujānāmastaccu yamastāṃ naiva cakṣame |
sa saroṣastu bālāya bhāvitosthasyai gaurṇāv || 15 ||
chāyāṃ saṃtajeyāmāsa yadā vaivasvato yamaḥ |
taṃ śaśāpa tataḥ krodhācchāyā tu kaṭuṣīkṛtā || 16 ||
caraṇaḥ patatāmeṣa taveti bhṛśaroṣitaḥ |
yamastataḥ pitussarvaṃ prāñjaliḥ pratyavedayat || 17 ||
bhṛśaṃ śāpabhayodvignaḥsaṃjñāvākyairviciṣṭitaḥ |
mātrā snehena sarvebhyo vartanīyaṃ sutebhyo vai || 18 ||
snehamastmāsca pākṛtya kanīyāṃsaṃ bibharti sā |
tasmānmayocyate pādastadravān kṣantumarhati || 19 ||
śaṃśoham asmi deveśa janannyā tapataḥ param |
tava prasādāccaraṇo na patenmama gopate || 20 ||
savitovāca

asaṃśayaṃ putra mahādvipratyatra kāraṇam |
yena tvāmavijñātakoṣo dharmajñaṃ satyavādinam || 21 ||
na śakyate tanmithyā vai kartuṃ mātṛvacastatva |
kṛmayo māṃsamādāya gamiṣyanti mahītale || 22 ||
tadbhākyaṃ

--- Page 74 ---
bhaviتā satyaṃ tvaṃ ca trāto bhaviṣyasi ||
kuru tāta na sandehaṃ manaśśāśvāsya svaṃ prabho || 23 ||
sūta uvāca

ityuktā tanayaṃ sūryau yamasaṃjñaṃ munīśvara ||
ādityaścāṇḍavīttāntu chāyāṃ krodhasanvitaḥ || 24 ||
sūrya uvāca

he priye kumate caṇḍi kiṃ tvayāśśca ritaṃ kila ||
kiṃ tu me'bhyaṣikaḥ sneha etadākhyātumarhasi || 25 ||
sūta uvāca

sā raveṣeñcanaṃ śrutvā yāthātatthyaṃ nyavedayat ||
nirdagdhā kāmaraviṇā sāṃtvayāmāsa vai tadā || 26 ||
chāyovāca

tavātitejasā dagdhā idaṃ rūpaṃ na śobhate ||
asahantī ca tatsaṃjñā vane vasati śādvale || 27 ||
chāyā yogabalope tā yogamāsādya gopate |
anukūlastu deveśa saṃdiśyātmamayyaṃ matam || 28 ||
rūpaṃ nivartayāmyadya tava kāntaṃ karomyahaṃ ||
sūta uvāca

tacchrutvāpagataḥ krodho mārteṇḍasya vivasvataḥ || 29 ||
agrimamāropya tattejasḥ śātayāmāsa vai śuniḥ ||
tato viśrājitaṃ rūpaṃ tejasā saṃvṛtena ca || 30 ||
kutaṃ kāntataraṃ rūpaṃ tvaṣṭā tacchubhe tadā ||
tatobhiyogamāsthāya svāṃ bhāryāṃ hi dadṛśe hā || 31 ||
adṛṣyāṃ sarvabhūtānāṃ tejasā niyamena ca ||
so'śvarūpaṃ samāsthāya gatvā tāṃ maithunecchayā || 32 ||
maithunāya viceṣṭantīṃ parañjuśobhaśaṃkayā ||
mukhato nāsikāyāṃ tu śukraṃ tattvyadagha nune || 33 ||
devau tataḥ prajāyetāmaśvinau bheṣajāṃ varau ||
nāsatyau tau ca dakṣo ca smṛtau dvāvaśvināvapi || 34 ||
tau tu kāntena rūpeṇa daśāyāmāsa bhāskarāḥ ||
ātmānaṃ sā tu taṃ dṛṣṭvā pragṛhya pātimādravat || 35 ||
patyā tena gṛhaṃ prāgatsvaṃ satī mudidānanā ||
sumuditestha tau prītyā daṃpatī pūrvatodhikaṃ || 36 ||
yamastu karmaṇā tena bhṛśaṃ pīḍitamānasaḥ dharmeṇa ||
rañjayāmāsa dharmarāja imā prajāḥ || 37 ||
lebhe sa karmaṇā tena dharmarājo mahāśrutiḥ ||
pitṝṇāmādhipatyaṃ ca lokapālatvameva ca || 38 ||
manuḥ prajāpatistavāsītsāvāṇīnasa tapodhanaḥ ||
bhāvyaḥ sa karmaṇā tena manotsāvāṇīṃketare || 39 ||
merupṛṣṭhe tapo ghoramadyāpi carate prabhuḥ ||
yavīyasī tayoryā tu yamī kanyā yaśasvinī || 40 ||
abhavatsā suriñchreṣṭhā yamunā lokapāvanī ||
manuritycuyate loke sāvāṇīriti cocyate || 41 ||
ya idaṃ janma devānāṃ śṛṇuyāddhārayettu vā ||
āpadaṃ prāpya mucyeta prāśnuyātsumadaṃgaśaḥ || 42 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāsumāsaṃhitāyāṃ manvantarakīrtane vaivasvatavarṇanaṃ nāma pañcatriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 35 ||
sūta uvāca

manorvaivasvatasya sanputrā vai nava tatsamāḥ ||
paścānmaheṃbratā dhīrāḥ kṣatradharmaparāyaṇāḥ || 1 ||
ikṣvākuḥ śibirnābhāgo dhṛṣṭaḥ śaryātiriva ca ||
nariṣyanto'tha nābhāgaḥ karuṣaśca priyavrataḥ || 2 ||
akarotputrakāmastu manuriṣṭiṃ prajāpatiḥ ||
anutpanneṣu putreṣu taneṣṭyāṃ munipuṃgava || 3 ||
sā hi divyāṃbaradharā divyābharaṇabhūṣitā ||
divyasaṃhananā caivimalā jaghe hi viśrutā || 4 ||
tāmiṭetyeva hovāca manuḥ daṇḍadharastathā ||
anugacchasva mā meti tamidā

--- Page 75 ---
pratyuvāca ha || 5 ||
indra uvāca ||
dharme yuktimidam vākyaṃ putrakāmaṃ prajāpatim ||
mitrāvaruṇayorśailajāntasmin vadatāṃ vara || 6 ||
tayosskaśaṃ yāsyāmi na me dharme rucibhāmeva ||
evaṃ tukā satī sā tu mitrāvaruṇayostataḥ || 7 ||
gatvātikaṃ varāroha prāñjalirvākyamabravīt ||
aśāstu yuvayo jātā manuye mahāśunī || 8 ||
āgatā bhavatoriti śrutaṃ kiṃ karavāṇi vām ||
anyānputrānsṛja vibho taivaiśaste bhaviṣyati || 9 ||
sūta uvāca ||
tāṃ tathā vādinīṃ sākhīmidaṃ manadhvaroreravām ||
mitrāvaruṇanāmāno munī ūcaturādarāt || 10 ||
mitrāvaruṇāvūcatuḥ ||
anena tava dharmeṇa praśrayeṇa damena ca ||
satyena caiva suśroṇi prītau dvo varavarṇini || 11 ||
āvayostvam mahābhāge khyātiṃ caiva gamiṣyasi ||
manovaṃśakaraḥ putrastvaiva ca bhaviṣyasi || 12 ||
sudyumna iti vikhyātastriṣu lokeṣu viśrutaḥ ||
jagatritayo dharmaśīlo manuvaṃśivardhannaḥ || 13 ||
sūta uvāca ||
nirgatā sā tu tacchrutvā gacchantī pituraṃtike ||
bhuvanenāntaramāsādya maithunāyopamantritā || 14 ||
somāputrāttato jajñe tasyāṃ rājā purūravāḥ ||
putroticandraḥ prāja urvaśīpitarurbhataḥ || 15 ||
janayitvā ca sā tatra purūrvasamādarāt ||
putraṃ śivaprasādāttu punaḥsudyumnāṃ gataḥ || 16 ||
sudyumnasya tu dayādāñcayaḥ paramadhārmiṇaḥ ||
utakalaśca gayaścāpi vinatāśvasca vīryavān || 17 ||
utakalaśyotkala viprā vinatāśvasya paścimāḥ ||
digdvāraṃ muniśālādhvaṃ gaya itu gāyāḥ smṛtāḥ || 18 ||
praviṣṭe tu manau tāta divākaratanuṃ tadā ||
daśadhā tatra tatakṣetramakrotpṛthivīṃ manuḥ || 19 ||
ikṣvākuḥ śreṣṭhādāyādo madhyadeśamavāstavān ||
viśiṣṭavachanādāsītpratiṣṭhānaṃ mahātmanaḥ || 20 ||
pratiṣṭhāṃ dharmarājyasya sudyumnotha tato dadau ||
tatpurūrvasase grādadrājyaṃ prāpya mahāyaśāḥ || 21 ||
mānavo yo munisreṣṭhāḥ strīpuṃsolakṣaṇaḥ prabhuḥ ||
niraṣyaṃtacchakaḥ putrā nabhasya sutobhavat || 22 ||
anbarīṣastu bāheyo bāhakaṃ kṣatramāstavān ||
śaryātimiśrathunena tvāsīdāntarnaṃ nāma viśrutaḥ || 23 ||
puṃssukanyā kanyā ca yā patnī cyavanasya hi ||
ānan tasya hi dāyādo raiṣmo nāma sa raiavataḥ || 24 ||
ānanteṃviṣaye yasya purī nāma kuśasthalī ||
mahādivyā saptapurāmadhye yā saptamī matā || 25 ||
tasya putaśataṃ tvāsītkakuzmī jyeṣṭha uttamaḥ ||
tejasvī subalāḥ pāro gharminiṣṭho brahmapalakāḥ || 26 ||
kakuzinastu saṃjātā revatī nāma kanyakā ||
mahālāvaṇyasaṃyuktā divyalakṣmīrivāparā || 27 ||
pṛṣṭhu kanyāvaram rājā kakuzmī kanyayā saha ||
brahmaloke vidhes samyak savādhīśo jagāma ha || 28 ||
āvartamāne gāndhave sthito labdhalakṣaṇaḥ kṣaṇam ||
śuśrāva tatra gāndhave nartane brahmaṇoṃtikaṃ || 29 ||
muhūrtabhūtaṃ tatkāle gataṃ bahuyugaṃ tadā ||
na kiñcidbubuhe rājā kakuzmī munayastu ha || 30 ||
tadāsau vidhimānamya svāmibhrāyaṃ kṛtāñjaliḥ ||
nyavedayaddhinītātmā brahmaṇe paramātmane || 31 ||
tadabhim

--- Page 76 ---
prāyamākaṇye sa brahmasya prajāpitaḥ ||
kaścijjinamamhārājaṃ samābhāṣya samabravīt || 32 ||
brahmovāca ||
śṛṇu rājñebhyasuta kaścijjinpṛthivīpate ||
madvacastvam mītitastasatyaṃ pravakṣyāmi viśeṣataḥ || 33 ||
kālena saṃhatāste vai varā ye te kṛtā hṛdi ||
na tadvaitraṃ hi tatrāsti kālassarvasya bhakṣakaḥ || 34 ||
tvatpuryepi hatā puṇyajanaiḥssā rākṣasairṛpa ||
aṣṭāviṃśadāpareoḍya kṛṣṇena nirmitā punaḥ || 35 ||
kṛtādvāravatī nāmā bahudrārā manoramā ||
bhojabṛṣṭyandhakaituḍā vāsudevapuroragamaiḥ || 36 ||
tadṛcchaḥ tatra prītātmā vāsudevāya kanyakām ||
baladevaāya dehi tvamimaṃ svatanayāṃ nṛpa || 37 ||
sūta uvāca ||
ityādidiṣṭo nṛpodhyaṃ taṃ natvā tāṃ ca purīṃ gataḥ ||
gatānbahunyugānñjñātvā vismitaḥ kanyayā yuvā || 38 ||
tatasttu yuvatiṃ kanyāṃ tāṃ ca svāṃ śubhāghānataḥ ||
kṛṣṇānte balāyāśu prādāttatra sa revatīm || 39 ||
tato jagāma śikharaṃ meroridivyaṃ mahāprabhuḥ |
śivamārādhayāmāsa sa tṛpastapasi sthitaḥ || 40 ||
ṛṣaya ūcuḥ ||
tatra sthito bahuṃyugaṃ brahmaloke sa revataḥ |
yuvaivāgānmartyalokametarnaḥ saṃśayo mahān || 41 ||
sūta uvāca ||
na jarā kṣutipāsā vā vikārāstatra santi vai ||
apaśrutane keṣāṃcinmunayo brahmaṇoṃstitake || 42 ||
ato na rājā saṃprāptajarāṃ mṛtyuṃ ca sā sutā ||
sa yuvairvāgatastatra saṃmatya tanayāvaram || 43 ||
gatvā dvāravatīṃ divyāṃ purīṃ kṛṣṇavinirmitām ||
vivāhaṃ kāryayāmāsa kanyāyāḥ sa balena hi || 44 ||
tasya putraśataṃ tvāsīddārmikasya mahāprabhoḥ ||
kṛṣṇasyāpi sutā jātā bahuśrībhyosmitāstataḥ || 45 ||
anuvāyo mahāṃstatra dvayorapi mahātmanoḥ ||
kṣatriyā dikṣu sarvāṃsu gatā ṣaṭāsupārmikāḥ || 46 ||
iti prokto hi śayāṃtavaiṃśodhnyeṣāṃ vadāmyaham ||
mānavānāṃ hi saṃkṣepāccṛṇutādrato dvijāḥ || 47 ||
nāmāgo dīrghapuṃtrodhūrtta tu brāhmaṇatāṃ gataḥ ||
svakṣatravraṃśaṃ saṃsthāpya brahmakaṃbhirāvṛtaḥ || 48 ||
dṛṣṭādaṣṭambhutakṣetraṃ brahmadhūyaṃ gataṃ śritau ||
kārūṣasya tu kārūṣāḥ kṣatriyā yuddhumandāḥ || 49 ||
nṛgo yo manupuṃtrastumahādātā viśeṣataḥ ||
nānāvasvunāṃ śubhītvā viprabhyaśca gavāṃ tathā || 50 ||
godānanvatyayāyastu svakubuddhcā svapāpataḥ ||
kukalaśatvaṃmāpatrāḥ śrīkṛṣṇena saṃbuddhitaḥ || 51 ||
tasyaikoddhṛtasutas śreṣṭhas prayātirdhaṃmivatstathā ||
iti śrutaṃ mayā vyāsātatprokataṃ hi samāsataḥ || 52 ||
vṛṣṇastu manoḥ putro gopālo guruṇā kṛtaḥ ||
pālayāmāsa gā yattro rājyāṃ vīrāsanabbrataḥ || 53 ||
sa ekadāgataṃ goṣṭhe vyāghraṃ gā hiṃsituṃ balī ||
śrutvā gokaṃdanaṃ buddhohantum taṃ khaḍgaṃ dhṛgayatyau || 54 ||
ajānabahunandabhroṃśiśārśaśāṭūlaśaṅkayā ||
niḥśkāma sambhīvyāṃśo hṛṣṭā taṃ khiḍnaṃ prabhum || 55 ||
manyamāno hataṃ vyāghraṃ svasthanāṃ sa jagāma ha ||
rājyāṃ tasyāṃ bhramāpanno varṣavatividuṣaghīḥ || 56 ||
vyuṣṭhāyāṃ niśi coṣṭhāya prāge tatra gato hi saḥ ||
--- Page 77 ---
अद्राक्षीत्स इतां बष्टुं न व्याघ्रं दुःखितोऽभवत् || ४७ ||
श्रुत्वा तदुक्तमाज्ञाय तं शश्राप कृतागसम् ||
अकामतो विचाय्योति शूद्रो भव न क्षत्रियः || ४८ ||
एवं शप्तस्तु गुरुणा कुलाचार्येण कोपतः ||
निःसृतश्च पृषभ्रस्तु जगाम विपिनं महत् || ४९ ||
निर्विण्णः स तु कष्टेन विरक्तोऽभूत्स योगवान् ||
वनांशौ दग्धदेहश्च जगाम परमां गतिम् || ६० ||
कविः पुत्रो मनोः प्राञ्जिश्वाजुमहतोऽभवत् ||
इह भुक्त्वा सुखं दिव्यं मुक्तिं प्राप सुदुर्लभाम् || ६१ ||
इति श्रीशिवमहापुराणे पञ्चम्यांशुमासंहितायां मनुनवपुत्रवंशवर्णनं नाम षट्त्रिंशोऽध्यायः || ३६ ||
सूत उवाच ||
पूर्वस्तु मनोर्जज्ञे इक्ष्वाकुशोणतस्सुतः ||
तस्य पुत्रशतं त्वासीदिक्ष्वाकोर्धुरिदक्षिणायु || १ ||
तेषां पुरस्ताद्भवन्नाप्यायवन्तं नृपा द्विजाः ||
तेषां विकुक्षिर्यज्ञस्तु सोऽयोध्यायां नृपोऽभवत् || २ ||
तत्कर्म श्रृणु तत्प्रीत्या यज्ञातं वंशतो विधेः ||
श्राद्धकर्मणि चोद्दिष्टे ह्रकुते श्राद्धकर्मणि || ३ ||
भक्षयित्वा शशं शीघ्रं शशादत्वमतो गतः ||
इक्ष्वाकुणा परित्यक्तशश्राद्धो वनमाविशत् || ४ ||
इक्ष्वाकोर्संस्थिते राजा वसिष्ठवचनाद्धृत् ||
शकुनिप्रमुखास्तस्य पुत्राः पञ्चदश स्मृताः || ५ ||
उत्तरापथदेशस्य रक्षितारो महीक्षिताः ||
अयोघस्य तु दायादः ककुत्स्थो नाम वीर्यवान् || ६ ||
अरिनाभः ककुत्स्थस्य पृथुरेतस्य वैषुतः ||
विघ्राश्वः पृथोः पुत्रस्तस्मादिन्द्रः प्रजापतिः || ७ ||
इन्द्रस्य युवनाश्वस्तु श्रावस्तस्य प्रजापतिः ||
जज्ञे श्रावस्तकः प्राञ्श्रावस्ती येन निर्मिता ||
श्रावस्तस्य तु दायादो बृहद्वशो महायशाः || ८ ||
युवनाश्वस्तुतस्तस्य कुवलाश्वश्च तत्सुतः ||
स हि धुन्धुवधाद्धुतो धुन्धुमारो नृपोत्तमः || ९ ||
कुवलाश्वस्य पुत्राणां शतमुत्तमघन्विनाम् ||
बधूवाथ पितराज्ये कुवलाश्वं न्ययाजयत् || १० ||
पुत्रसंकामितश्रीको वनं राजा समाविशात् ||
तषुतंकोऽथ राजर्षिः प्रयांतं ग्रत्यवारयत् || ११ ||
उत्तंक उवाच ||
भवता रक्षणं कार्यं पृथिव्या धर्मतः श्रृणु ||
त्वया हि पृथिवी राजन्रक्ष्यमाणा महात्मना || १२ ||
भविष्यति निरुद्विग्ना नारायणं गन्तुमहसि ||
ममाश्रमसमीपे तु हिमेषु मरुघन्वसु || १३ ||
समुद्रवालुकापूर्णे दानवो बलदर्पितः ||
देवतानामवध्यो हि महाकायो महाबलः ||
॥१४॥

अन्तर्भूमिगतस्तत्र वालुकान्तर्हितः स्थितः ||
राक्षसस्य मन्थोः पुत्रो धुन्धुनामा सुदारुणः || १५ ||
शेते लोकविनाशाय तपः अस्थाय दारुणम् ||
संवत्सरस्य पर्यन्ते स निःश्वासं विक्षुञ्चति || १६ ||
यदा तदाभूश्चलति सशैलवनकानना ||
सविस्फुलिंगं सांगारं सधूममपि वारुणम् || १७ ||
तेन राजञ्शक्नोमि तस्मिन् स्थातुं स्वःआश्रमे ||
तं वारय महाबाहो लोकानां हितकाम्यया || १८ ||
लोकास्स्वस्था भवन्त्वद्य तस्मिन्विनिहते त्वया ||
त्वं हि तस्य वधायैव समर्थः पृथिवीपते || १९ ||
विष्णुना च वरो दत्तो महानपुरुषयुगेऽनघ ||
तेजसा स्वेन ते विष्णुस्तेज आप्यायिष्यति || २० ||
पाल°

--- Page 78 ---
idaṃ mahādharmaḥ prajānāmiha darśyate ||
na tathā darśyateṣraṇye mā teṣāmbhudbudhirīdṛśī || 21 ||
īdṛśo na hi rājendra kiñciddharmaḥ pravidyate ||
prajānāṃ pālane yādṛk purā rājabhirbhiḥ kutaḥ || 22 ||
sa evamuktο rājabhiruttarkeṇa mahātmanā ||
kuvalāśvaḥ sutaṃ prādāttasmai śuṃśumārvāraṇe || 23 ||
bhagavatyastataśrohamayaṃ tu tanayo mama ||
bhaviṣyati dvijśreṣṭha śuṃśumāro na saṃśayaḥ || 24 ||
ityuktvā putramādiśya yayau sa tapase nṛpaḥ ||
kuvalāśvasya sotsāho yayau śuṃśuminigṛhe || 25 ||
tamāviśattadā viṣṇurbhagavāṃstejaśā prabhuḥ ||
uttarkasya niyogādvai lokānāṃ hitakāmyayā ||

|| 26 ||
tasminprayāte duḥkhaiḥ diviṃ śakro mahānbhṛt ||
eṣa śrīmānnṛpasuto śuṃśumāro bhaviṣyati || 27 ||
divyairmalyaiśca taṃ devāssamantātsamavārayaṃ ||
praśaṃsāṃ cakre tasya jaya jīveti vādina || 28 ||
sa gatvā jayanāṃ śreṣṭhastanayaiḥsaha pārthivaḥ ||
samudrāṃ khanayāmāsa vāṭukāṇāṃtrammadhyataḥ || 29 ||
nārāyaṇasya vipraraistejaśāpyāyitastu saḥ ||
babhūva sumahātejā bhūyo balasaṃvitaḥ || 30 ||
tasya putraiḥ khandiṣṭu vāṭukāntargatastu saḥ ||
śuṃśurāsāditο brahmaṃ diśamāśritya paścimām || 31 ||
mukhajenāgninā koṭhāṃślokānsaṃvartayaṃniva ||
vāriṃ suṣrāva vegena vigheḥ kaghiravādaye || 32 ||
tatośnalairanibhahataṃ dagdhaṃ putraśataṃ hi tat ||
tray ṣaṣṭhāvāriśatāśca teṣu madhye munīśvara || 33 ||
tatassa rājā triprendr rākṣasaṃ taṃ mahābalaṃ ||
āssasāda mahātejā śuṃśuṃ vipravinaśanam || 34 ||
tasya vārimayaṃ vegamāpīya sa nāgādhipaḥ ||
vahnibāṇena vahniṃ tu śamayāmāsa vāriṇā || 35 ||
taṃ nihatyā mahākāyaṃ baleno dakrākṣasam ||
uttarkasyekṣayāmāsa kṛtaṃ karma nāgādhipaḥ || 36 ||
uttarkastu varaṃ prādāttasmai rājñe mahātmane ||
adadcākṣayaṃ vittaṃ śatṛbhiśāparājayam || 37 ||
dharme matiṃ ca satataṃ svargevāsaṃ tathākṣayam ||
putrāṇāṃ cākṣayaṃ lokaṃ rakṣasā ye tu saṃhatāḥ || 38 ||
tasya putrāstrayiśiṣṭhāḥ dṛḍhāśvāḥ śreṣṭhā ucyate ||
haṃsāśvākapilāśvau ca kumārau tatkānīyasau || 39 ||
śuṃśumāridṛḍhāśvo yo hṛdyeśvasya cātmajaḥ ||
hṛdyeśvasya nikuṃbhobhūtputro dharmārtasadā ||

|| 40 ||
saṃhatāśvo nikuṃbasya putro raṇaviśāradaḥ ||
aśāśvasca kṛtāśvasca saṃhatāśvasutośbhavat ||41||
tasya haimāvatī kanyā satāṃ mānyā vṛṣadvatī ||
vikhyātā triṣu lokeṣu putrasstasyāḥ prasenijat || 42 ||
lebhe prasenijādvāryai gaurīṃ nāma pativratāṃ ||
abhikṣaṇtā tu sā bhatriṃ nadī sā vāhuḍā kṛtā || 43 ||
tasya putro mahānāsīdyuvanāśvo mahīpatiḥ ||
māṃdhātā yuvanāśvasya triṣu lokeṣu viśrutaḥ || 44 ||
tasya caitrathī bhāryā śaśabinduśutāśbhavat ||
pativratā ca jyeṣṭhā ca bhrātṛṇāmayutaṃ ca saḥ || 45 ||
tasyāmutpādayāmāsa māṃdhātā dvau sutau tadā ||
purukutsaṃ ca dharmajñaṃ mucukuṃdaṃ ca

--- Page 79 ---
dhārmikaṃ || 46 ||
purukutsat sutastatvāsīddhrāṃśryyāruṇiḥ kivaḥ ||
tasya satyavrато nāma kumāro'bhūn mahābalī || 47 ||
pāṇigrahaṇamantrāṇāṃ vighnaṃ cakre mahātmābhiḥ ||
yena bhāryā hṛtā pūrvaiḥ kṛtodvāhaḥ parasya vai || 48 ||
balātkāmāc ca mohāc ca saṃpāc ca madotkkaṭāt ||
jahāra kanyāṃ kāmāc ca kasya cituruvāsinaḥ || 49 ||
adharmeṇa'ṅginaṃ taṃ tu rājā trayāruṇistya janat ||
apadvaṃseti bahuśo'vadatkopasmanvitaḥ || 50 ||
pitaraṃ so'tvarvīnmukttaḥ ka gacchāmīti vai tadā ||
vasa śvapākinikate rājā prāheti taṃ tadā || 51 ||
sa hi satyavratasten śvapākāvasthāntike ||
pitrā tyaktto'vasaddhīro dharmmapālena bhujaḥ || 52 ||
tatastarayāruṇī rājā virattaḥ putrakarmmaṇā ||
sa śaṃkaratapah kañcit sarvaṃ tyaktvā vanaṃ yayau || 53 ||
tatastasya svaviṣaye nāvarṣatpākaśāsanaḥ ||
samā dvādaśa vipreṣoṃ tenādhameṇa vai tadā || 54 ||
dārastasya tu viṣaye viśvāmitro mahātapāḥ ||
saṃtyajya sāgarānūpe cacāra vipulaṃ tapaḥ || 55 ||
tasya patnī gale baddhvā madhyamaṃ putramūrcchasthā śeṣasya bharaṇārthāya vikrīṇādviṃśatena ca || 56 ||
tāṃ tu dṛṣṭvā gale baddhaṃ vikrīṇantīṃ svamātmajaṃ ||
mahirṣiputtro dharmātmā mocayāmāsa taṃ tadā || 57 ||
satyavrato mahābāhurbhareṇaṃ tasya cākaro'tat ||
viśvāmitrasya tuṣṭacaryenmanukoṃśārthemena ca || 58 ||
tadārabhya sa puttrastu viśvāmitrasya vai muneḥ ||
abhavaddālavo nāma galanbandhānmahātapāḥ || 59 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe paśvabhyāsumāsaṃhitāyāṃ manuvaṃśavarṇenaṃ nāma paṃciṃśo'dhyāyaḥ ||

|| 37 ||
sūta uvāca ||
satyavratastu tadantyayā kṛpayā ca pratiñjayā ||
viśvāmitrakalatraṃ ca poṣayāmāsa vai tadā || 1 ||
hatvā mṛgānvarāhāṃś ca mahiṣāṃś ca vanecaran ||
viśvāmitrāśramābhyāśe tanmāṃsaṃ cākṣipanmune || 2 ||
atīrthe gaṃ caiva rātraṃ ca tathevāntaḥpuraṃ muniḥ ||
yājyopādhyāyasaṃyogādviśiṣṭhaḥ patyarakṣat || || 3 ||
satyavratya vākyāddha bhāvinorthantya vai balāt ||
vasiṣṭho'bhyadhikaṃ manyuṃ dhārayāmāsanityaśaḥ || 4 ||
pitrā tu taṃ tadā rāṣṭrātpāritya kttaṃ svamātmajaṃ ||
na vārayāmāsa munirvvasiṣṭhaḥ kāraṇena ca || 5 ||
pāṇigrahaṇamantrāṇāṃ niṣṭhā syātsaptame pade ||
na ca satyavratatstasya tatsupāṃśubuddhyat || 6 ||
tasminsaṃ parittoṣāya pittrāsīnmahātmanaḥ ||
kulasya niṣkutirvipra kṛtavānvai bhaveditiḥ || 7 ||
na taṃ vasiṣṭho bhagavānpitrā tyaktaṃ nyavārayat ||
abhiṣekyāmyahaṃ putrasasyā naivābravīnmuniḥ || 8 ||
sa tu dvādaśa varṣāṇi dīkṣāṃ tāśuddhaddhalī ||
abhidyamāne maṃsi tu vasiṣṭhasya mahātmanaḥ || 9 ||
sarvainkāmaduhā doghrīṃ dadaśa sa tṛpātmajaḥ ||
tāṃ vai kodhāc ca lobhāc ca śramādvai ca kṣudhānvitaḥ || 10 ||
dāśadharmmaṃgato rājā tāṃ jagvān sa vai mune ||
sa taṃ māṃsaṃ svayaṃ caiva viśvāmitrasya cātmajaṃ || 11 ||
bhojayāmāsa tacchuttvā vasiṣṭho hṛtasya bubhukṣe ||
uvāca ca muniśreṣṭhastaṃ tadā kopasamyutaḥ || 12 ||
vasiṣṭha uvāca ||
--- Page 80 ---
pātayeyam ahaṃ kūraṃ tava śaṅkumayomayam ||
yadi te dvāvimau śaṅkū naśyetāṃ vai kṛtau purā || 13 ||
pitṛśāparitośeṇa guroḥ doṣabhīvacena ca ||
aprekṣitopayogācca trividhaṃste vyatikramaḥ || 14 ||
triśaṅkurita hovāca triśaṅkurita sa smṛtaḥ ||
viśvāmitrastu dārāṇāmāgato bharaṇe kṛte || 15 ||
tena tasmai varaṃ prādānmuniḥ prītistriśaṅkave ||
chandyamāno vareṇātha varaṃ vere nṛpātmajaḥ || 16 ||
anavṛṣṭibhaye cāsmiṃnjāte dvādaśavārṣike ||
abhiṣicya pitṛ rājye yājayāmāsa taṃ muniḥ || 17 ||
miṣatāṃ devatānāṃ ca valiṣṭhasya ca kauśikaḥ ||
saśarīraṃ tadā taṃ tu divam āroḥyatrabhūḥ || 18 ||
tasya satryasthānam abhāryāṃ kekayavaṃśajā ||
kumāraṃ janayāmāsa hariścandramakarmaṣam || 19 ||
sa vai rājā hariścandro triśaṅkava iti smṛtaḥ ||
āhṛto rājasūyasya samāḍita ha viśrutaḥ || 20 ||
hariścandrasya hi śruto rohito nāma viśrutaḥ ||
rohitasya vṛkaḥ putro vṛkādbahustu jijñavān || 21 ||
haihayāstālajaṃcāśva nirasyantiṃ sma taṃ nṛpam ||
nātmārthe dhārmikaḥ vigrahū sa ha dharmaparoṣabhavat || 22 ||
sagaraṃ sasutaṃ bāhujajñe sahagareṇa vai ||
auvaiśyāśramamāsādya bhārgaveṇābhirakṣitaḥ || 23 ||
āgreyam acaṃ labdhvā ca bhārgavātsagaro nṛpaḥ ||
jigāya pṛthivīṃ hatvā tālajaṃcān sahaihayān || 24 ||
śakāṃvahūḍakāṃścaiva pāradāntakaṇān kaśān ||
sudharme sthāpayāmāsa śaśāsa vṛṣataḥ kṣitim || 25 ||
śaunaka uvāca

sa vai gareṇa sahitaḥ kathaṃ jātastu kṣatriyāt ||
jitavānita dākṣṇa vistareṇa hi sūtaja || 26 ||
sūta uvāca

parīkṣitena saṃpṛṣṭo vaiśaṃpāyana eva ca ||
yadācaṣṭa sma tadakṣye śṛṇuṣvaikamana mune || 27 ||
pārīkṣitovāca

kathaṃ sa sagaro rājā gareṇa sahito mune ||
jātaḥ sa jijñavāndhyānita dākṣyātumahīsi || 28 ||
vaiśaṃpāyana uvāca

bāholyāṃsini nastāt hṛtaṃ rājyambhūtikalam ||
haihayaiḥ stālajaṃcaiśca śakaiḥ sārdhaṃ viśāṃpate || 29 ||
yavanāḥ pāradāścaiva kāmbojāḥ pāhlavāstathā ||
bahuḍakāśca pañcaiva gaṇāḥ proktāśca rakṣasām || 30 ||
ete pañca gaṇā rājañ haihayārtheṣu rakṣasām ||
kṛtvā parākramān bāhor rājyaṃ tebhyo daduḥ balāt || 31 ||
hutarājyastatato rājā sa vai bāhuvenaṃ yayau ||
patnayā cānugato duḥkhī sa vai prāṇān avāsṛjat || 32 ||
patnī yā yādavī tasya sagabhāṃ pṛṣṭhato gatā ||
sapatnayā ca garastasyai dattaḥ pūrvamutarṣayā || 33 ||
sā tu bhaviṣṭhitāṃ kṛtvā jvalanam cāvarohat ||
auvaiḥstāṃ bhārgaṇo rājanakāraṇyātsamavārayat || 34 ||
tasyāśrame sthitā rājñī garbharakṣaṇahetave ||
siṃheve munivarye taṃ smarantī śaṅkaraṃ hṛdā || 35 ||
ekadā khalu tadgarbho gareṇaiva saha cyutaḥ ||
susmṛhate sulagreṃ ca pañcoṣagrahasaṃyute || 36 ||
tasmiṃścagre ca vilinaṃ savethā munisattamam ||
vyajāyata mahābāhuḥ sa naraḥ nāma pārthivaḥ || 37 ||
auvaistu jātakamādi tasya kṛtvā mahātmanaḥ ||
adhyāpya vedaśāstrāṇi tato 'naṃ pratayapādayat || 38 ||
āmreyaṃ taṃ mahā

--- Page 81 ---
bhāgo hyamairapi duḥsaham ||
jagāha vighna prītyā sagarosau nṛpottamaḥ || 39 ||
sa tenāśvabalanenāiva balena ca samantritaḥ ||
daihyānvijaghanāśu saṃkruddhoḥśvabalen ca || 40 ||
ājahāra ca lokeṣu kīrtiṃ kīrtīmatāṃ varaḥ ||
dharme sthāpayāmāsa sagarosau mahītale || 41 ||
tataḥ śakāstayavanāḥ kāmbojāḥ pāhlavāstathā ||
hanyamānāstadā te tu viśiṣṭaṃ śaraṇaṃ yayuḥ || 42 ||
viśiṣṭo vaṃcanāṃ kṛtvā sma yena mahāśrutiḥ ||
sagaraṃ vārayāmāsa teṣāṃ dattvābhayaṃ nṛpam || 43 ||
sagarastvāṃ pratijñāṃ tu gurorvākyaṃ niśamya ca ||
dharme jagahāna teṣāṃ vai keśānyatvaṃ cakāra ha || 44 ||
arddhāñ śakānāṃ śirasāo muṇḍaṃ kṛtvā vyasajayat ||
yavanānāṃ śiraḥsavai kāmbojānāṃ tathaiva ca || 45 ||
pāradā muṇḍakeśāśca pāhlavāśmaśrudhāriṇaḥ ||
niḥsvadhyāyavaṣaṭkārā kṛtāstena mahātmanā || 46 ||
jitā ca sakalā pṛthvī dharmastena bhuśujā ||
sarve te kṣatriyāstāt dharmaहīnāḥ kṛtāḥ purā || 47 ||
sa dharmavijayī rājā vijitvemāṃ vasuṃdharām ||
aśvaṃ saṃskārayāmāsa vājimegdhāya pārthivaḥ || 48 ||
tasya cārayataḥ so'śvassamudre pūrvadakṣiṇe ||
gataḥ ṣaṣṭisahasrestu tatputrairanvito mune || 49 ||
devrarājene śakreṇa so'śvohṛtaḥ svārthhasādhināt ||
velāsamīpe papatāṃ bhūmim caiva praveśitaḥ || 50 ||
mahārājo'tha sagarastaddyhyānveṣaṇāya ca ||
sa taṃ deśaṃ tadā putraiḥ khānyāmāsa savistaiḥ || 51 ||
āseduste tataḥ taṃ khanyamāne mahāgṛhe ||
tamādidhyuruṣaṃ devaṃ kapalaṃ viśvarūpiṇam || 52 ||
tasya cakṣuḥsaṃspṛṣṭhyena vihinā pratidugdhyataḥ ||
dagdhāḥ ṣaṣṭisahasrāṇi catvārastvavaśeṣitāḥ || 53 ||
harṣaketuḥ suketuśca tathā dharmarathopraḥ ||
śūraḥ pañcajanaścaiva tasya vaṃśakarā nṛpāḥ || 54 ||
prādāc ca tasmai bhagavān hariḥ pañcavarānsvayam ||
vaṃśaṃ medhāṃ ca kīrtiṃca sakhudraṃ tanayaṃ ghanam || 55 ||
sāgaratvaṃ ca lebhe sa karmeṇa tasya tena vai ||
taṃ cāśvamedhikaṃ so'śvaṃ saṣṭhādupalaṃbhavān || 56 ||
ājahārāśvamedhānāṃ śataṃ sa tu mahāyaśāḥ ||
ījje śaṃbhuṃ vibhūtīśca devatāstatra suvratāḥ || 57 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe paścamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ satyavrātādisagaraparyantavaraṇavaṃnarṇaṃ nāmāṣṭātriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 58 ||
śaunaka uvāca ||
sagarasyātmajā vīrāḥ kathaṃ jātā mahābalāḥ ||
vikrāntāḥ ṣaṣṭisāhasrā vighnānā kena vā vad || 1 ||
sūta uvāca ||
dve patnyau sagarasyāstāṃ tapasā dagdhakilvise ||
audhavastayorvaiṃ prādāttauṣito munisattamaḥ || 2 ||
ṣaṣṭhiputrasahasrāṇi ekā vavre tariṣvinām ||
ekaṃ vaṃśakaraṃ tveikā yatheṣṭaṃ varaśālinī || 3 ||
tatrāivā gatya tāñchuṃkhyā putrāñchurānbahūṃstadā ||
sā caiva suṣuve tumbhāṃ bījapūrṇaṃ pṛthakkṛtam || 4 ||
te sarve hi svaghātrībhiṃ vṛṣuśa yathākramam ||
ghṛtapūrṇeṣu kumbheṣu kumārāḥ prītivardhanāḥ || 5 ||
kapilāgnipradadghānāṃ teṣāṃ tatra mahātmanām ||
ekaḥ pañcajano nāma putro rājā babhūva ha || 6 ||
tataḥ pañcjanasyāsī

--- Page 82 ---
daṃśumātrām vīryavān ||
dīlīpastanayastasya putro yasya bhagīrathaḥ || 7 ||
yastu gaṅgāṃ sariccreṣṭhāmaśātārayat prabhuḥ ||
saṣṭhramānayaceṃāṃ duhitatvamaka rpayat || 8 ||
bhagīrathastuto rājā śrutasena iti śrutaḥ ||
nāmāgastu śrutastasya putraḥ paramaghamarmikaḥ || 9 ||
aṃbarīṣastu nābhāgissiṃbāḍīpastato 'bhavat ||
ayutājittu dāyādarsiṃsaṭhḍīpasya vīrthyavān || 10 ||
ayutājitśrutastvāmīdatupāṇaṃ mahāyaśāḥ ||
divyākṣardayajño 'sau rājā nalasukho 'bhavat || 11 ||
ṛtupāṇaśchutastvāsīdatupāṇaṃ mahādyutiḥ ||
tasya kalmāṣapādo vai nāmnā mitrasahastathā || 12 ||
kalmāṣapādasya śrutassarveṃkmeriti viśrutaḥ ||
anarāṇyastu putro 'ṣāḍhiśrutaḥ ssvaiśrāmāṇaḥ || 13 ||
anarāṇyasuto rājā vidvānbhuṇḍiṭhuhā 'bhavat ||
niṣadhastasya tanayo rītiḥ khaḍgāṅka ityapi || 14 ||
yena svargaṃ daśagatya śubhe prāpya jīvitam ||
trayopi saṃcitā lokā buddhyāṃ satyena cānagha || 15 ||
dīrghabāhuśrutastasya ragurastasyā bhavatsutaḥ ||
ajastatya tu putro 'ṣṭuttasmāddaśaratho 'bhavat || 16 ||
rāmo daśaravajñe gharmātmā yo mahāyaśāḥ ||
sa viṣṇvaṃśo mahāśaiva paulasmyo yena ghātitaḥ || 17 ||
taccaritaṃ ca bahudhā purāṇeṣu pravaṇītam ||
rāmāyaṇe prasiddhaṃ hi nātaḥ śloktu vistarāt || 18 ||
rāmasya tanayo jajñe kuśa ityati viśrutaḥ ||
atithistu kuśājjajñe niṣadhastasya cātmajaḥ || 19 ||
niṣadhasya nalaḥ putro namaḥ putro nalasya tu ||
namasaḥ puṇḍarīkakṣa kṣemaghanvā tattasstṛtāḥ || 20 ||
kṣemaghanvāsutastvāsīddavānīkaḥ pratāpavān ||
āsīdahīnaghunaṃ devānīkātmajaḥ prabhuḥ || 21 ||
ahīnagosttu dāyādassahasavā grāmaṃ vīryavān ||
vīraseṇātmajastasya yaśreṣvākukulodbhavaḥ || 22 ||
vīraseṇasya dāyādaḥ pāriyātro babhūva ha ||
tato balākhyastanayastasya llastasmādbhūtasutaḥ || 23 ||
akauśasaṃbhavastastmātputro yakṣaḥ pratāpavān ||
tatśrutasstaguṇastvāsīttasmāddhṛtirātmajaḥ || 24 ||
hiraṇyanāmastadputro yogācāryaṃ babhūva ha ||
sa śiṣyo jaiminiśunedhātmavidyāviśāradaḥ || 25 ||
kauśalyo yājñavalkyo 'tha yogamadhyākhyasaṃjñakam ||
yato 'dhyaganārūpavarāddhudayamantibhedanam || 26 ||
tattuto puṣyanāmā hi dhruvasaṃjñastadātmajaḥ ||
agnivarṇaśśrutastasya śrīranāmā śrutastataḥ || 27 ||
maruṇāmā śrutastasya yogasiddho vaṣṭūva ha ||
aṣṭāvāstarteṣṭhyapi prabhuḥ kalpagramasaṃjñake || 28 ||
taddhāsibhiśra munibhiḥ kalerante sa eva hi ||
punarabhāvayitā naṣṭaṃ sūryavaṃśaṃ viśeṣataḥ || 29 ||
praśuśrutaśca tatputrassaṃghastasya śrutaḥ smṛtaḥ ||
amarṣaṇaśśrutastasya marutvāṃstacchruto 'bhavat || 30 ||
viśvasāhaśśrutastasya tatśruto 'dhṛptasenojinat ||
takṣakastasya tanayastatsuto hi bṛhaddhalaḥ || 31 ||
eta ikṣvākuvaṃśīyā atītāḥ saṃprakīrtitāḥ ||
śṛṇu tānāgatānbhūtāṃstadaṃśyānghamaṃ vicittamān || 32 ||
bṛhaddhallasya tanayo bhaviṭā hi bṛhaddhraṇaḥ ||
bṛhaddhraṇasutastasyorukṛtyo hi bhaviṣyati || 33 ||
--- Page 83 ---
vatsavṛddhasutastasya pratiṣṭhyomṛtastataḥ ||
bhānustattanayo bhāvī divāko vāhinīpatiḥ || 24 ||
sahdebvasutastasya mahāvīro bhaviṣyati ||
tatsuto vṛddhaśo hi bhānumāṃstatsuto balī || 25 ||
suto bhānumato bhāvī pratīkāśvadha vīryavān ||
supratīkasutastasya bhaviṣyati ṛṣottamaḥ || 26 ||
marudevasutastasya sunakṣatro bhaviṣyati ||
tatsutaḥ puṣkarastasyāntarikṣastatsuto dvijāḥ || 27 ||
sutapāstatsuto vīro mitracitrasy cātmajaḥ ||
vṛhadrājasutastasya bahinimā tadātmajaḥ || 28 ||
kṛtañjayasutastasya tatsuto hi raṇañjayaḥ ||
sañjayastu mayastasya tasya śākyo hi cātmajaḥ || 29 ||
śuddhodastanayastasya lāṅgalastu tadātmajaḥ ||
tasya prasenajitputro tatsutaḥ śūdrakāhvayaḥ || 40 ||
raṇako bhavitrā tasya surayastattsutaḥ smṛtaḥ ||
śubhavratatsuto bhāvī vaṃśaniṣṭhānta eva hi || 41 ||
śumitrāṃ prāpya rājānaṃ sa tadvaṃśaśubhaḥ kalau ||
saṃsthāṃ prāpsyati tadbāhle vakṣyati punaḥ kṛte || 43 ||
etadaivavṛtte vaṃśe rājāno dhūridiśiṇāḥ ||
ikṣvākuvaṃśaprabhavāḥ prādhānyena prakīrtitāḥ || 44 ||
puṇyeyaṃ paramā sṛṣṭirādityasya vivasvataḥ ||
śrāddhadevasy devasya prajānāṃ puṣṭidasya ca || || 45 ||
paṭhaṃśṛṇuvānimāṃ sūdhimādityasya ca mānavāḥ ||
prajāvāniti sāhāryamiha śuklā śubhaṃ param || 46 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ vaivasvatavoṃśodbhavārājavarṇanaṃ nāmaikonacatvāriṃśodhyāyaḥ || 39 ||
vyāsa uvāca ||
ityākarṇya śrāddhadevavāsūryānvayamuttamam ||
papracchurmuniśreṣṭhaśaunakasutamādarāt ||
ḥ 1 ||
śaunaka uvāca ||
satasūta ciraṃ jīva vyāsaśiṣya namotu te ||
śrāvitā paramā divyā kathā parampāvanī || 2 ||
tvayā proktaḥ śrāddhadevasyaḥ sadvaṃśavardhanaḥ ||
saṃśayastatra me jātastaṃ bravīmi tvadagratāḥ || 3 ||
kuto vai śrāddhadevamādityasya vivasvataḥ ||
śrotumicchāmi tatprītyā chiṃdhi me saṃśayaṃ tvamam || 4 ||
śrāddhastyāpi ca māhātmyaṃ tatphalaṃ ca vad prabho ||
prītāśca pitaro yena śreyasā yojayanti tam || 5 ||
etacca śrotumicchāmi pitṝṇāṃ sargamuttamam ||
kathaya tvaṃ diśeṣeṇa kṛpāṃ kuru mahāmate || 6 ||
vañcima tatteśakhilam prītyā pitṛsargaṃ tu śaunaka ||
mārkaṇḍeyena kathitaṃ bhīṣmāya paripṛcchate || 7 ||
gītaṃ sanatkumāreṇa mārkeṇḍeyāya dhīmate ||
tattehaṃ saṃpravakṣyāmi sarvakāmaphalapradam || 8 ||
yudhiṣṭhireṇa saṃpṛṣṭo bhīṣmo dharmasmṛtāṃ varaḥ ||
śaraśayyāsthitaḥ pronce tacchṛṇuṣva vadāmi te || 9 ||
yudhiṣṭhira uvāca ||
puṣṭikāmena puṃsā vai kathaṃ puṣṭiravāpyate ||
etacchotusomicchāmi kiṃ kurvāṇo na rīdṛti || 10 ||
sūta uvāca ||
yudhiṣṭhireṇa saṃpṛṣṭaṃ praśnaṃ śrutvā sa dharmavit ||
bhīṣmaḥ provaṃca supītyā sadaiṣa

--- Page 84 ---
śṛṇvatāṃ vacaḥ || 11 ||
भीष्म उवाच

ye kurvanti narāḥ śrāddhāny api prītyā yudhiṣṭhira ||
śrāddhaiḥ prīṇāti tatsan vai pitṛṇāṃ hi prasādataḥ || 12 ||
śrāddhāni caiva kurvanti phalakāmārs sadā narāḥ ||
abhisaṃdhāya pitaraṃ pitṛśca pitaraṃ tathā || 13 ||
pituḥ pitāmahaścaiva triṣu piṇḍeṣu nityada ||
pitaro dharmakāmasya prajākāmasya ca prajām || 14 ||
puṣṭikāmasya puṣṭiṃ ca prayacchanti yudhiṣṭhira || 15 ||
युधिष्ठिर उवाच

vatante pitaraḥ svarge keśāṃcin nārake punaḥ ||
prāṇināṃ niyataṃ cāpi karmajaṃ phalabhujyate || 16 ||
tāni śrāddhāni dattāni kathaṃ gacchanti vai pitṝn ||
kathaṃ śaktās tāmāhārtai narakasthāḥ phalaṃ punaḥ || 17 ||
devā api pitṝn svarge yajanty iti me śrutam ||
etad icchāmy ahaṃ śrotuṃ vistareṇa bravīhi me || 18 ||
भीष्म उवाच

atra te kīrtayiṣyāmi yathāśrutam arinandama ||
pitrā mama purā gītaṃ lokāntaragatena vai || 19 ||
śrāddhakāle mama pitṛmṛtyā piṇḍasya śucyataḥ ||
matpitā mama hastena bhitvā bhūmim upāgachat || 20 ||
naiṣa kalpavividheṣṭha iti niścitya cāpy aham ||
kuśeṣv eva tataḥ piṇḍaṃ dattavān avicārayann || 21 ||
ataḥ pitā me santuṣṭo vācā madhurayā tadā ||
uvāca bhārataśreṣṭha prīyamāṇo mayānagha || 22 ||
atvayā dāyādvān asmi dharmajñena vipāśritā ||
antāritaḥ ahaṃ tu jijñāsā kṛtā me puruṣottama || 23 ||
pramāṇaṃ yādṛc kurute gharocāreṇa pārthivaḥ ||
prajāstadanu vartante pramāṇacaritaṃ sadā || 24 ||
śṛṇu tvaṃ bhārataśreṣṭha veddharmāṃśca śāśvatān ||
pramāṇaṃ veddharmasyā putra nirṇīttaṃ tvayā || 25 ||
tasmāt tvāhaṃ suprītaḥ prītyā varamanuttamaṃ ||
dadāmi tvaṃ pratīkṣasva triṣu lokeṣu durlabham || 26 ||
na te prabhavitā mṛtyur yāvaj jīvitum icchasi ||
tvatto 'bhyanujñāṃ saṃprāpya mṛtyuḥ prabhavitā punaḥ || 27 ||
kiṃ vā te prārthitaṃ bhūyo dadāmi varabhuttamaḥ ||
tad brūhi bharataśreṣṭha yatte manasi vartate || 28 ||
ityuktvāti tāṃs mastu abhivādya kṛtāñjaliḥ ||
avocaṃ kṛtakṛtyohaṃ prasanne tvayi mānada ||
praśnaṃ pṛcchāmi vai kiñcid acchyassambhavitā svayam || 29 ||
स मार्कुवाच

tad brūhi yadīcchasi dadāmi te ||
ityuktena mayā tatra pṛṣṭaḥ provāca tanṛpaḥ || 30 ||
शंतनुरुवाच

śṛṇu tāta pravakṣyāmi praśnaṃ teṣāṃ yathārthataḥ ||
pitṛkulpaṃ ca nikhilaṃ mārkaṇḍeyena me śrutam || 31 ||
yacca pṛcchasi māṃ tāta tadevāhaṃ mahāmunim ||
mārkaṇḍeyaṃ pṛccha hi sa māṃ provāca dharmavit || 32 ||
मार्कण्डेय उवाच

śṛṇu rājan mayā hyaṣṭaṃ kadācit paśyatā divam ||
vimānaṃ mahadāyāntam antareṇa girestad || 33 ||
tasmin vimāne patheṣaṃ jvalitāṅgāravarcasam ||
mahātejasā prajvalantaṃ nirviśeṣaṃ manoharaṃ || 34 ||
apaśyaṃ caiva tatrāhaṃ śayānaṃ dīptatejasom ||
aṅguṣṭhāmatraṃ puruṣam aghravimāhitam || 35 ||
so 'haṃ tasmai namaḥ kṛtvā praṇamya śirasā prabhuṃ ||
apṛcchaṃ caiva tamahaṃ vidyāmartalam kathaṃ vibho || 36 ||
स मार्युवाच

dharmātmā te na tadṛśyate tapaḥ ||
yena tvaṃ

62

--- Page 85 ---
bujhyase māṃ hi śune vai brahmaṇas sutam || 37 ||
sanatkumāram iti māṃ viddhi kiṃ karavāṇi te ||
ye tvanyebrahaṇaḥ putrāḥ kanīyāṃs tu te mama || 38 ||
bhrātaras sapta duḥkheṣā yeṣāṃ vaṃśāḥ pratiṣṭhitāḥ ||
vayaṃ tu yatidharmāṇas saṃyamyātmānam ātmani || 39 ||
yathottapaṃs tathaivahaṃ kumāra iti sthitaḥ ||
tasmāt sanatkumāraṃ me nāmaitatkathitaṃ śune || 40 ||
yakṛtyā te tapaśśīrṇaṃ mama darśanakāṅkṣayā ||
eṣa haghoḍasya bhadraṃ te kiṃ kāmaṃ karavāṇi te || 41 ||
ityuktavantaṃ taṃ cāhaṃ prāvocan tvaṃ śṛṇu prabho ||
pitṛṇāmādi sarge ca kathayasva yathātathyam || 42 ||
ityuktasya tu māṃ prāha śṛṇu sarvaṃ yathātathyam ||
vakṣye te tattvatas tāt pitṛsarge śubhāvaham || 43 ||
sana tkumāra uvāca

devān purāṣṭau dṛḍhā māṃ yakṣasvaṃ sa cāha tān ||
tatṣaṭsṛjya tam ātmānam ayajaṃste phalārthinaḥ || 44 ||
te śaptā brahmaṇā mūḍhā naṣṭasaṃjñā bhaviṣyatha ||
tasmāttaṃ kiñcid ajānanto naṣṭasaṃjñāḥ pitāmaham || 45 ||
procustāṃ praṇatās sarve kuruṣvānugṛhāṇa hi naḥ ||
ity uktastānuvācedam prāyaścittārtham eva hi || 46 ||
putrāṃs tvā nupāripṛcchdhvaṃ tato jñānam avāpsyatha ||
ityuktā naṣṭasaṃjñās te putrān papracchur ojasā || 47 ||
prāyaścittārthamevaḥkhilaṃ vacasaṃjñā diveśasaḥ ||
gamyatāṃ putrakā evaṃ punaruktāśca te naṅ ca || 48 ||
abhiśāpāstu te devāḥ putrakāmena vedasam ||
papracchur uktāḥ putraiṣṭe gatāste putrakā iti || 49 ||
tatastān bravīt devo devān brahmā sasaṃśayān ||
śṛṇudhvaṃ nijairāssarvaiḥ yūyaṃ na brahmavādinaḥ || 50 ||
tasmādyuktaṃ yuṣmākaṃ putrais tejāninaṃs tatairmaiḥ ||
santavyaṃ saṃśayaṃ tyaktvā tathā na ca tadanyathā || 51 ||
devāśca pitarīścaiva yajasvaṃ tridivaśasaḥ ||
parasparam mahāśrītyā sarvakāmaphalapradāḥ || 52 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca

tataste chidrasan dehāḥ prītimantaḥ parasparam ||
vahuṣṭubhir niśādīlaiḥ brahmavākyāt sukha pradāḥ || 53 ||
tato devā hi procustāny adyuktāḥ putrakaḥ vayam ||
tasmāt dravantaḥ pitaro bhaviṣyatha na saṃśayaḥ || 54 ||
pitṛśrāddhe kriyāṃ kiñcitkariṣyati na saṃśayaḥ |
śrāddhaiḥ āpyāyitassomo lokān āpyāyayiṣyati || 55 ||
sāṣṭaudrāṃ parvatanam jaṅgamājaṅgamaiḥ gṛtam ||
śrāddhāni puṣṭikaiścaiva ye kariṣyanti mānavāḥ || 56 ||
tebhyaḥ puṣṭipradaiścaiva pitaraḥ prīṇitāssadā ||
śrāddhe ye ca pradāsyanti trīṇipiṇḍānāmago vrataḥ || 57 ||
sarvatraṃ vartamānāste pitaraḥ śripitāmahāḥ ||
bhaviṣyanti satataṃ śrāddhadānena tarpitāḥ || 58 ||
iti tadvacanaṃ satyaṃ bhavatatha diveśasaḥ ||
putrāśca pitarścaiva vayaṃ sarve parasparam || 59 ||
evaṃ te pitaro devā dharmataḥ putrān gatāḥ ||
anyonyaṃ pitaro caite prathitāḥ kṣitimaṇḍale || 60 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāṃ umāsaṃhitāyāṃ śrāddhakarye pitṛprabhāvavavarṇanaṃ nāma catvāriṃśodadhyāyaḥ || 40 ||
--- Page 86 ---
||
sanatkumāra uvāca ||
sata te tapatāṃ śreṣṭha svarge pitṛgaṇāssmṛtāḥ ||
catvāro mūrtimanto vai trayaścaiva bhasmūrtayaḥ || 1 ||
tānyajante devagaṇā ādyā vipradayastathā ||
ākhyāyante te pūrvaiḥ somaṃ yogabalena vai || 2 ||
tasmācchraddhāni deyāni yogināṃ tu viśeṣataḥ ||
sarveṣāṃ rājataṃ pātramathavā rajatānvitam || 3 ||
dattaṃ svagha purodhāya śrāddhe prīṇāti vai pitṝn ||
vahneḥ prāpyāyanaṃ kṛtvā somasya tu yamasya vai || 4 ||
udagāyanamapyaghnasvayambhāvedaṣṭamū vā punaḥ ||
pitṝnprīṇāti yo bhaktyā pitaraḥ prīṇayanti tam || 5 ||
yacchanti pitaraḥ puṣṭiṃ prajāśca vipulāstathā ||
svargamārogyavṛddhiṃ ca yadanyadapi cepiṣṭam || 6 ||
devakāryādapi mune pitṛkāryaṃ viśiṣyate ||
pitṛbhaktoऽsi viprāṇāṃ tena tvamajāramaraḥ || 7 ||
na yogena gatirssā tu pitṛbhaktasya yā mune ||
pitṛbhaktivinirdeṣeṇa tasmātkāryaṃ mahāmune || 8 ||

||
mārkaṇḍeya uvāca ||
hyavaśukāśu deveśo devānāmapi durlabham ||
cakṣurdatvā savijñānaṃ jagāma yaugikīṃ gatim || 9 ||
śṛṇu bhīṣma purā bhūyo bhāradwājātmajā dvijāḥ ||
yogadharmānuprāpya ṣaṭha duścaritena vai || 10 ||
vāgduṣṭaḥ krodhaṃ hiṃsāḥ piśunāḥ kaṅkeriva ca ||
svaśuṣāḥ pitṛvarttī ca nāmābhiḥ karmabhiḥ tathā || 11 ||
kauśikasya sutāstāt śiṣyā gargasya cābhavan ||
pitaryabhūprate sarvaiḥ pravasantas tadābhavan || || 12 ||
viniyogādguroḥ tasya gāṃ doghrīṃ samakālayan ||
samānavarṣāṃ kapilāṃ sarveṣāṃ nyāyagātāstadā || 13 ||
teṣāṃ pāthakṣaghātānāṃ bāhyānmohācca bhārata ||
krūrā buddhissamutpannā tāṃ gāṃ vai hiṃsituṃ tadā || 14 ||
tāṃ kiṃsvastvaṃspṛṣṭaścaiva yācete neti vai tadā ||
na cāśakyāstu tābhyāṃ vā tadā vārayituṃ nijāḥ || 15 ||
pitṛvarttī tu yasteṣāṃ nityaṃ śrāddhabhūko dvijaḥ ||
sa sarvānbraveītkopāt pitṛbhaktisamanvitaḥ || 16 ||
yadyaśakyaṃ prakartavyaṃ pitṛbuddhyā sādhyatāṃ ||
prakuvīto hi śrāddhaṃ tu sarvaṃ eva samāhitāḥ || 17 ||
evameṣā ca godharme prāpyate na tatra saṃśayaḥ ||
pitṝnamyacyaṃ dharmaṇa nādharmo no bhaviṣyati || 18 ||
hyavaśukāśca te sarvaṃ prokṣayitvā ca gāṃ tadā ||
pitṛbhyaḥ kalpayitvā tu kṣupāyujata bhāratā || 19 ||
upabhujya ca gāṃ sarvaṃ guroḥ tasya nyavedayan ||
śārdūlena itā ghaṇurvatsā vai gṛhyatāmiti || 20 ||
ātatvatsā tu taṃ vatsaṃ pratijagāha vai dvijaḥ ||
mithyopacārtaḥ pāpamabūteṣāṃ ca gopratāṃ || 21 ||
tataḥ kālena kiyatā kāladharmaṃ upāgatāḥ ||
te sapta śāntarastāt basmubhustvāyuṣaḥ kṣaye || 22 ||
te vai krūratayā heṇyāt svānānyatvadbhūrostathā ||
hyaḥ hiṃsāvibhārāśca jātāssapta sahodarāḥ || 23 ||
lubdhakasya sutāstāvadvalvanto manasvinaḥ ||
jātā vyādhadarśāṇeṣu sapta dharmaivicakṣaṇāḥ || 24 ||
svadharmairataḥ sarvaiḥ mṛgā mohavivarjitāḥ ||
āsannudrogasaṃvighna ramye kālañjare girau || 25 ||
tamevārthaṃ manuṣyāya jñānaṃ maraṇasaṃbhavam ||
āsanvanacārāḥ śāntā nirddvandvā niṣparigraghāḥ || 26 ||
te sarvaiḥ śubhakarmāṇaḥ saddharmāṇo vanecārāḥ ||
vidharmācāraṇairhīnā jātismaraṇasiddha

--- Page 87 ---
yaḥ || 27 ||
pūrvajātiṣu yo dharmaḥ śruto gurukuleṣu vai ||
tathaiva cāsthitā buddhiḥ saṃsāreṣvyinivartane || 28 ||
girimadhye jahuḥ prāṇāṃścatvāhārastapa svanaḥ ||
teṣāṃ tu patitānāṃ ca yāni sthānāni bhārata || 29 ||
tathaivācāpi haṭyante girau kālañjare nṛpa ||
karmaṇā tena te jātāḥ śubhāśubhamiva jñakāḥ || 30 ||
śubhāśubhatarāṃ yoniṃ cakravākatvaāgatāḥ ||
śubhe deśe saridbīpe sasevaāsanlokasaḥ || 31 ||
tyaktā sahacārīdharmaṃ munayo dharmadhāriṇaḥ ||
niḥsaṅgā nityamāśāntā nirdhaidhā niṣparigrahaḥ || 32 ||
niṛvṛttinivṛttāścaiva śakkunā nāmataḥ smṛtāḥ ||
te brahmacāriṇassarve śakkunā dharmadhāriṇaḥ || || 33 ||
jātismaraḥ susaṃvṛttāssathaiva brahmacāriṇaḥ ||
sthitā ekatra saddharmaṃ vikārarahitāssadā || 34 ||
viprayonau tu yanmohānmithyāpacāritaṃ gurau ||
tiryagyonau tathā janma śrāddhājñānaṃ ca lebhire || 35 ||
tathā tu pitṛkāryārthaṃ kṛtaṃ śrāddhaṃ vyavasthitaiḥ ||
tadā jñānaṃ ca jātiṃ ca kramaprāptaṃ guṇo ttaraṃ || 36 ||
pūrvajādiṣu yadṛddhaṃ śrutaṃ gurukuleṣu vai ||
tathaiva saṃsthitajñālaṃ tasmā jñānaṃ samabhyaset || 37 ||
sumanaśca śuvākkuddhaḥ pañcamiścaddha śaṅkaḥ ||
svataṃtraśca suyajñaśca kulīnā nāmataḥ smṛtāḥ || 38 ||
teṣāṃ tatra vihaṃgānāṃ caratāṃ dharmadhāriṇām ||
kuvṛttambhavattatra tacchruṭuṣva mahāmune || 39 ||
nīpanāmīśvaro rājā prabhāveṇa samanvitaḥ ||
śrīmānantaḥpuravṛto vanaṃ tatrāviveśa ha || 40 ||
svataṃtracakravākasya spṛhayāmāsa taṃ nṛpatir ||
hṛdā yāntaṃ sukhopetaṃ rājyaśobhāsamanvitam || 41 ||
yadyasti su kṛtaṃ kiñcit tapo vā niyamo'pi vā ||
khinnohamupavāsena tapasā niścalena ca || 42 ||
tasya sarvasya puṇyena phalenaiva kṛtena hi ||
sarvasaubhāgyapātrasya bhaveyamahamedrśaḥ || 43 ||
mārkāṇḍeya uvāca ||
tatastau cakravākau dvāvāsatuḥ sahadhāriṇau ||
āvāṃ vai sacivau syāva tava priyahitaiṣiṇau || 44 ||
tathetsuktā tu tasyārtsittadā yogātmano gatiḥ ||
evaṃ tau cakravākau ca svavākyaṃ pratyabhāṣetāṃ || || 45 ||
yasmātkarmendruvāṇastaṃ yogadharmaṃvāpya tam ||
evaṃ varaṃ prārthayase tasyādhākyaṃ nibodha me || 46 ||
rājā tvaṃ bhavitā tāta kāmpilye nagarottame ||
etau te sacivau syātāṃ vyabhicāraprādharṣitau || 47 ||
na tānucchayo rājyaṃ catuḥsahadāriṇaḥ ||
sa prasādaṃ punaśca ke tanmadhye sumano'brāvīt || 48 ||
antavoṃ bhavitā śāpaḥ punarnaṃgamavāpyatha ||
sarventveva suyajñasya svataṃtro'yaṃ bhaviṣyati || 49 ||
pitṛprasādādyuṣmābhissampātaṃ kṛtaṃ bhavet ||
gāṃ prokṣayitvā dharmeṇa pitṛbhyaścopyopakalpitāḥ || 50 ||
asmākaṃ jñānasaṃyogassarveṣāṃ yogasādhanaṃ ||
idaṃ ca vākyaṃ saṃrdhaṃ ślokaṃ ekṃ kṣudāhṛtam || 51 ||
puruṣāntaritaṃ śrutvā tato yogamavāpsyatha ||
ityuktvā sa tu maunoṣuddidhaṃgarasumano 'budhaḥ || 52 ||
mārkāṇḍeya uvāca ||
lokānāṃ svastyai tāta śāntanupravaratmaja ||
--- Page 88 ---
ityuktaṃ tac caritraṃ me kiṃ bhūyaś śrotum icchasi || 23 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ pitṛsagaṇvarṇanaṃ saṃkhyādhagativarṇanaṃ nāmaikacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 41 ||
bhīṣma uvāca

mārkandeyaṃ mahāprāñ pitṛbhaktiśrutāṃ vara |
kiṃ jātaṃ tu tato bruhi kṛpayā munisattama || 1 ||
mārkandeyaḥ uvāca

te dharme yoginirataṃ tās tatra mānasacāriṇaḥ |
vāyubhakṣāṃs tatataṃ śarīrakṣupaśoṣayañ || 2 ||
sa rājāntaḥpuravṛto nandane maghava iva |
krīḍitvā suciraṃ tatra sabhāryeṣvavapuraṃ yayau || 3 ||
anūho nāma tasyāsīt putraḥ paramadhārmikaḥ |
taṃ vaiśrājaḥ sutaṃ rājye sthāpayitvā vanaṃ yayau || 4 ||
tapaḥ katthuṃ samārebhe yatra te sahacāriṇaḥ |
sa vai tatra nirāhāro vāyubhakṣo mahātapāḥ || 5 ||
tato viśrājitaṃ tena viśrājaṃ nāma tad vanaṃ |
babhūva kṣipraṃ siddhaṃ hi yogasiddhipradāyakam || 6 ||
tatraiva te hi śakunās caturvāro yogadhārmiṇaḥ |
yogaśraddhaś ca dhairyeṇa dehatīyāgakṛto'bhavan || 7 ||
kāñcilye nagare tu brahma dattapurogamāḥ |
jātāṃ tāṃ mahātmānaḥ sarve vigatakalmaṣāḥ || 8 ||
śrutimaṃto'tra catvāraś ca yaste parimohitāḥ |
svataṃtrasya hṛtyo jāto brahma datto mahaujas || 9 ||
chidra darśī sunetrastu vedavedāṅgapāragau |
jātau śrotriyā dāyādau pūrvajātisahopitau || 10 ||
pañcālo bahucatvāṃsīdācāryatvaṃ cakāra ha |
dvivedaḥ puṇḍarīkaś ca chandogodgāthyūreva ca || 11 ||
tato rājā sutaṃ hṛṣṭa brahma dattamakalmapṛ |
abhiṣicya svarājye tu parāṃ gatimavāptavān || 12 ||
pañcālaḥ puṇḍarīkastu putrou saṃsthāpya mandire |
vividhastuvenaṃ tatra gatau parimikāṃ gatiḥ || 13 ||
brahma dattasya bhāryau tu saṃghinanāṃ bhārata |
sā tvekabhāvasaṃyuktā reme bhatre sahaiva tu || 14 ||
śeṣāstu cakravākā vai kāñcilye sahacāriṇaḥ |
jātāḥ śrotriyā dāyādā daridrasya kule nṛpa || 15 ||
dhṛtimān sumahātmā ca tatvadarśī nirutsukah |
vedādhyayanasampaṃnāś catvāriś chidra darśinaḥ || 16 ||
te yoginirataṃ siddhāḥ prasthitāṃ sarve eva hi |
āmaṃtraṃ ca mithaḥ śambhoḥ padāmbhojaṃ praṇamya tu || 17 ||
śūrā ye sampradyante atunabhevakāṃkṣiṇaḥ |
pāpapraṇāśayan tvadya tacchambhoḥ paramapadaṃ || 18 ||
śarīre mānase caiva pāpe vāñje mahāśune |
kṛte samyagidambhaktyā paṭhecchradddhāsamanvitaḥ || 19 ||
mucyate sarvapāpebhyaś śivā nāmānukīrtanāt |
uccāryyamāṇa etasmindevadevasya tasya vai || 20 ||
vilayet pāpamāyāti bhāmabhāṇḍimbhāmbhasi |
tanmātratsu cinte pāpe samānāntarameva ca || 21 ||
japtavyametapāpasya praśmāya mahāśune |
nāreḥ śraddhālu bhirbuyas sarve kāmaphalāptaye || 22 ||
puṣpacathurmimam adhyāyaṃ paṭhedenaṃ śṛṇoti vā |
mucyate sarvapāpebhyo mokṣaṃ yāti na saṃśayaḥ || 23 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ pitṛkalpe pitṛprabhāvavarṇanaṃ nāma dvācatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 42 ||
śaunaka uvāca

ācāryyeṣu janaṃ

--- Page 89 ---
I'll carefully transcribe the mūla text from this page, which appears to contain the end of one chapter and the beginning of another in the Umāsaṃhitā.

ब्रूहि सूत व्यासगुरोऽधुना ||
अन्यस्य श्रवणान्ते हि किं कर्तव्यन्तदप्यहो || १ ||
सूत उवाच

पूजयेद्विघ्नवदत्त्याचार्यं श्रुत्वा कथां पराम् ||
अन्यान्ते विघ्नवद्भ्यादाचार्यांय प्रसन्नभीः || २ ||
ततो वक्तारमानम्य संपूज्य च यथाविधि ||
भूषणैस्तकणानां वक्षसोम्यादिभिस्तुभीः || ३ ||
शिवपूजासमासौ तु दद्यादेवं सवित्सकाम् ||
कृत्वासनं सुवर्णस्य पलमानस्य साम्बरम् || ४ ||
तत्रास्थाप्य शुभं ग्रन्थं लिखितं लिलिताक्षरैः ||
आचार्याय सुधीदेयान्युक्तः स्याद्बवबन्धनैः || ५ ||
ग्रामो गजो हयश्चापि यथाशक्त्यपराणि च ||
मुने सर्वाणि देयानि वाचकाय महात्मने || ६ ||
विधानस्य हितं सम्यक्छुतं हि सफलं स्मृतम् ||
पुराणं शोनकर्तुने सत्यमेवोदितं मया || ७ ||
तस्माद्विधान्युक्तं तु शृणुयाद्भक्तितो मुने ||
पुराणं निगमार्थांच पुण्यदं हृदये श्रुतेः || ८ ||
इति श्रीशिवमहापुराणे पञ्चम्यासुमासंहितायां व्यासपूजनप्रकारो नाम त्रिचत्वारिंशोऽध्यायः || ४३ ||
मुनय ऊचुः

व्यासोत्पत्तिं महाबुद्धे ब्रूहि सूत दयानिधे ||
कृपया परया स्वामिन्कृतार्थान्निष्कुरु प्रभो || १ ||
व्यासस्य जननी प्रोक्ता नाम्ना सत्यवती शुभा ||
विवाहिता तु सा देवी राज्ञा शन्तनुना किल || २ ||
तस्यां जातो महायोगो कथं व्यासः पराशरात् ||
सन्देहोऽत्र महाशातस्तं भवाञ्छे तुमर्हति || ३ ||
सूत उवाच

एकदा तीर्थयात्रायां व्रजन्योगी पराशरः ||
यहच्छयागतो रम्यं यमुनायास्तटं शुभम् || ४ ||
निषादमाह धर्मात्मा कुरैन्तं तुमर्हति ||
मोजनन्तदाऽनयस्व यमुनापारं जलयानेन माम्रम् || ५ ||
इत्युक्तो मुनिना तेन निषादस्स्वसुतां जगे ||
मत्स्यगन्धामृतं बाले पारं नावा नय हुतव || ६ ||
तापसोऽयं महाभागे हंश्यन्तीगभेसम्भवः ||
तितीषुरस्ति धर्मांश्च शतुराशायपारगः || ७ ||
इति विज्ञापिता पित्रा मत्स्यगन्धा महामुनिम् ||
संवाहयति नौकायामासीनं सूर्येरोचिषम् || ८ ||
कालयोगान्महायोगी तस्यां कामातुरोऽभवत् ||
दृष्ट्वा योऽप्सरसां रूपं न कदापि विमोहितः || ९ ||
ग्रहीतुकामः स मुनिदाशकन्यां मनोहराम् ||
दक्षिणेन करेणैतामस्पृशद्दक्षिणे करे || १० ||
तस्मावाच विशालाक्षी वचनं स्मितपूर्वकम् ||
किमिदं क्रियते कर्म वाच्यतम विगर्हितम् || ११ ||
विसिष्ठस्य कुले रम्ये त्वं जातोऽसि महामते ||
निषादजा त्वहम्ब्रह्मन्कथं संगो घटेत् नौ || १२ ||
दुर्लभं मातृपं जन्म ब्राह्मणत्वं विशेषतः ||
तत्रापि तापसत्वं च दुर्लभं मुनिसत्तम || १३ ||
विद्यया वपुषा वाचा कुलशीलेन चान्वितः ||
कामबाणवशं यातो महदाश्चर्यमत्र हि || १४ ||
प्रवृत्तमप्यस्तकर्म कर्तुमेनं न कोऽपि ह ||
मुनिं वारयितुं शक्तः शापभीत्यास्य योगिनः || १५ ||
--- Page 90 ---
iti saṃcintya hṛdaye nijagāda mahāmunim ||
tāvaddheyi kuru svāminn yāvatkāṃ pārayāmi na || 16 ||
sūta uvāca ||
iti śrutvā vacas tasyā yogirājaḥ parāśaraḥ ||
tatyāja pāṇintarasā sinyoḥ pāraṃ gataḥ punaḥ || 17 ||
punar jagrāha tāṃ bālāṃ muniḥ kāmaprapīḍitaḥ ||
kampmānā tu sā bālā tam uvāca dayānidhim || 18 ||
durgandhaṃ muniśreṣṭha kṛṣṇavarṇī niṣādajā ||
bhavāṃstu pramودāravicarō yogisattamaḥ || 19 ||
nāvayoḥ cete sañjño kācakāñcana yoriva ||
tulya jātyākṛtikayoḥ saṃgaḥ saukhyaprado bhavet || 20 ||
ity uktena tayā tena kṣaṇamātreṇa kāminī ||
kṛtā yojanagandha tu ramyarūpā manoramā || 21 ||
punar jagrāha tāṃ bālāṃ sa muniḥ kāmapīḍitaḥ ||
mahītu kāmaṃ taṃ dṛṣṭvā punaḥ provāca vāsavī || 22 ||
rātrau vyavāyaḥ kartavyo na diveti śrutir jagau ||
divāsaṃge mahāndoṣo nindā cāpi durāsadā || 23 ||
tasmāt tāvat pratīkṣasva yāvad dvāti yāminī ||
paśyanti mānavāḥ atra pitā me ca taṭe sthitaḥ || 24 ||
tayo ktam idamākarṇyaṃ vacanaṃ munipuṃgavaḥ ||
nīhāraṃ kalpayāmāsa sadyaḥ puṇyavalena vai || 25 ||
nīhāre ca samu tpanne tamasā rātrisannibhe ||
vyavāyacakitā bālā punaḥ provāca tanmunim || 26 ||
yoginaḥ moghavīryaḥ tvaṃ muktvā gantāsi māṃ yadi ||
saṃbho ryāṃ taśā svāminka gatiṃ me bhavediti || 27 ||
kanyāvantaṃ mahābuddhe mama naṣṭo bhaviṣyati ||
ṛṣiṣyanti tadā lokāḥ pitaraṃ kiṃ bravīmyaham || 28 ||
parāśara uvāca ||
re bāle mayā sārdhaṃ svacchandaṃ kāmajair rasaiḥ ||
svīyābhilāpamākhyāhi pūrayāmyadhunā priye || 29 ||
madajñāsatyakaraṇābhāsma satyavatī sva ||
vandanīyā tathā śeṣair yogibhir bhuvidaśairapi || 30 ||
satyavatī uvāca ||
jānate na pitā mātā na vānyebhuvi mānavāḥ ||
kanyāgharmō namo hanyādādi svīkuru yāntadā || 31 ||
putras tvatsamō nātha bhavedadbutaśaktimān ||
saugandhyaṃ sarvaṃ aṃge me tāruṇyaṃ ca navaṃnavam || 32 ||
parāśara uvāca ||
śṛṇu priye tadābhīṣṭaṃ sarvaṃ pūrṇaṃ bhaviṣyati ||
viṣṇuvamśasaṃbhavaḥ putro bhavitā te mahāyaśāḥ || 33 ||
kiṃcideva kāraṇaṃ viddhi yato'haṃ kāmapīḍitaḥ ||
dṛṣṭvā cāpsarasāṃ rūpaṃ nāśujhānye manaḥ kvacit || 34 ||
mīnagandhaṃ samālakṣya tvāṃ mohavaśago'bhavam ||
na bāle bālapaṭastho brahmalekho'nyathā bhavet || 35 ||
purāṇaktorā putras te vedaśākhāvibhāgakṛt ||
bhaviṣyati varārohe khyātakīrtir jagatttraye || 36 ||
ity uktvā tāṃ suramyāṃ giṃ muktvā yogaviśāradaḥ ||
vavrāja śīghraṃ yamunājale snātvā mahāmuneḥ || 37 ||
sā'pi garbhaṃ dadhārāśu dvādaśātmasamaprabham ||
asmut

--- Page 91 ---
sūryajāḍīpe kāmdevīmivātmajaṃ || 38 ||
vāme kamaṇḍaluṃ viśradakṣiṇe daṇḍasuttamaṃ ||
piśaṅgīmibhajantābhiśca rājito mahāśaṃ cayaḥ || 39 ||
jātamātrastejasvi mātaraṃ pratyabhāṣata |
gaccha mātaryathākāmaṃ gacchāsyahamatḥ paraṃ || 40 ||
mātayenḍā bhavetārthaṃ tava kiñciddarīpasatam ||
saṃskṛta śrāgamiṣyāmi tvadīcchāpūtirhetave || 41 ||
ityuktā mātṛcaraṇāvicavādya taponidhiḥ |
jagāma ca tapaḥ kacau tīrthe pāpaviśodhanam || 42 ||
sāpi pitṛgṛhantakaṃ yātā putrasnehākulā satī ||
smarantī ciraṃ sunorvarṇayantī svabhāgyakam || 43 ||
dvāpe jāto yato vālastena dvīpāyanosabhavat ||
vedaśākhābhipajanādvedavyāsaḥ prakīrtitaḥ || 43 ||
tīrtharājaṃ prathamato dharmakāmārthamokṣadaṃ ||
naimiṣaṃ ca kurukṣetraṃ gaṅgādvāramacintakam || 45 ||
ayodhyāṃ mathurāṃ caiva dvārakāmarasavatīm ||
sarasvatīṃ sindhusakṛṃ gaṅgāsāgarasaṃgamam || 46 ||
kāñcīṃ ca tryambakaṃ cāpi sattagodevārītatam ||
kālaṃjaraṃ prabhāsaṃ ca tathā badarikāśramam || 47 ||
mahālayantarkoṅkakṣetraṃ vai pauruṣottamam ||
gokarṇaṃ bhṛgukaṭchaṃ ca bhṛgutugaṃ ca puṣkaram || 48 ||
śrīparvvataṃ tithivāni dharātīrthaṃ tathaiva ca ||
gatvāvaṅgāha vidhīnā cacāra paramantapaḥ || 49 ||
evaṃtīrthānyanekaṃ nānādeśasthitāni ha ||
parycaṭankālikāmeru prāpadvāraṇasīmpurīm || 50 ||
yatra viśveśvaraḥ jāṣādvrapūrṇo maheśvarī ||
bhaktānāmakṣatandātuṃ virājate kṛpānidhī || 51 ||
prāpya vāraṇasītīrthaṃ haṭha ya maṇikarṇikām ||
koṭijanmajitaṃ pāpaṃ tatyāja ca sa munīśvaraḥ || 52 ||
haṭhāṃ liṅgāni sarvāṇi viśveśapramukhāni ca ||
snātvā sarveṣu kuṇḍeṣu vāpīkūpasarastu ca || 53 ||
natvā vināyakānsarvāngaurīḥ sarvāḥ praṇamya ca ||
sampūjya kālarājaṃ ca bhairaṃ pāpabhaṃsanam || 54 ||
daṇḍanāyaka mukhyāṃśca gaṇānstutvā prayatnataḥ ||
ādikeśavabhurukyāṃśca keśavānpāritoṣya ca || 55 ||
lolākeśarurumukyoṃśca praṇamya ca punaḥ punaḥ ||
kṛtvā piṇḍapradānāni sarvatīrtheṣvatandritaḥ || 56 ||
sthāpayāmāsa puṇyātmā liṅgaṃ vyāseśvarābhigham ||
yaddarśanādvedvidhānā naro vidyātu vākpatiḥ || 57 ||
liṅgānyabhyarcya viśveśapramukhāni subhaktikaḥ ||
asaktaścintayāmāsa kiṃ liṅgaṃ kṣiprasiddhidam || 58 ||
yamārādhya mahādevaṃ vidyāḥ sarvaṃ labhemahi ||
purāṇakalyetāśaktirmmāstu yadunmahāt || 59 ||
śrīdamoṃkāranāthaṃ vā kṛttivāseśvaraṃ kiṃtu ||
kedāreśantu kāmeśaṃ candreśaṃ vā trilocanaṃ || 60 ||
kāleśaṃ vṛddhakāleśaṃ kalaśeśvarmena vā ||
jyeṣṭheśaṃ jambhakeśaṃ vā jegīṣupreśvarantu vā || 61 ||
daśāśvamedhamīśānaṃ humivaṇḍeśameva vā ||
harkeśaṃ garuḍeśaṃ vā gokarṇeśaṃ gaṇeśvaram || 62 ||
prasannavadenśaṃ vā dharmeśaṃ tārakeśvaram ||
nandīkeśaṃ nivāseśaṃ patnīśaṃ prītikeśvaram || 63 ||
parvateśaṃ paśupatin

