hāṭakeśvarameva vā ||
bṛhaspatīśvaraṃ vātha tilaabhāṇḍeśameva vā || 63 ||
bhārabhūteśvaraṃ kiṃ vā mahālakṣmīśvaraṃ tu vā ||
maruteśantu mokṣeśaṃ gaṇḍeśaṃ nambideśvaryaṃ || 64 ||
kṛṣṇeśaṃ parameśānaṃ ratneśvaramathāpi vā ||
yāmuneśaṃ lāṅgalīśaṃ śrīmadviśveśvaraṃ triṣuṣ || 65 ||
avimukteśvaraṃ vātha viśālākṣīśameva vā ||
vyāghreśvaraṃ varāheśaṃ vidyeśvaramathāpi vā || 67 ||
varuṇeśaṃ vidhīśaṃ vā harikeśeśvarantu vā ||
bhavānīśaṃ kapardīśaṃ kandukośamajeSvaraṃ || 68 ||
viśvakarmeSvaraṃ vātha vīreśvaramathāpi vā ||
nādeśaṃ kapileśaṃ ca bhuvaneśvarmeva vā || 69 ||
vāṅkulīśaṃ mahādevaṃ siddheśvaramathāpi vā ||
vindhyadeveśvaraṃ vīrabhadreśaṃ bhairaveśvaram || 70 ||
amṛteśaṃ satīśaṃ vā pārvatīśvarmeva vā ||
siddheśvaraṃ mataṅgeśaṃ bhūtīśvarmathāpi vā || 71 ||
āṣāḍhīśaṃ prakāmeśaṃ koṭirudreśvarantathā ||
mṛdālaśeśvaraṃ caiva tilaparṇeśvaraṃ kiṃ su || 72 ||
kiṃ vā hiraṇyagarbheśaṃ kiṃ vā śrīmaddhyameśvaraṃ ||
ityādi koṭiliṅgānāṃ madhyehaṃ kṣuṇupāśraye || 73 ||
iti cintāturobhyāsaḥ śivabhaktiraṭātmavān ||
kṣaṇaṃ vicārayāmāsa dhyānasthiściracetasā ||
73ḥ||
ā jñātaṃ vistrṛtaṃ tāvidbhraṣṭapañño me manorthaḥ ||
siddhaiḥ saṃpūjitaṃ liṅgaṃ dharmakāmārthamokṣadaṃ ||75||
darśanātsparśanādyasya ceto nirmalatāmiyāt ||
udghāṭitaṃ sadā dvāraṃ svargasya yatra hi || 76 ||
avimukta mahākṣetre siddhakṣetre hi tatparam ||
yannāste paraṃ liṅgaṃ madhyameśvarasaṃjñakam ||77||
na madhyameśrādanyadliṅgaṃ kāśyāṃ hi vidyate ||
yadśonāthebhāyānti devāḥ parṇeṇaparṇeṇi || 78 ||
ataḥ seṃnyo mahādevo madhyameśvarasaṃjñakaḥ ||
antyārāghana to diprā vahavaḥ siddhibhāgatāḥ || 79 ||
yaḥ pradhānatayā kāśyāṃ madhye tiṣṭhati śaṅkaraḥ ||
svaśurījanasaukhyārthamato'si madhyameśvaraḥ || 80 ||
tuṣṭurūnaima gaṃbhavoṃ deva piṣṇānardastathā ||
athumaṃrādhya saṃpanno gānavidyāviśārdaṃ || 81 ||
athumaiva samārādhya viṣṇumonpradoabhaval ||
brahmā viṣṇuśca rudraśca kṣatṛpālaka hārakāḥ || 82 ||
ghānādhīśaḥ kuberoapi vāmadevo hi śeśvarāṭ ||
khaḍgāngo nāma bhūpālonapatayonapatayavānabhūt || 83 ||
apsarāścandrabhmāsāryā nṛtyantī nijabhāvataḥ ||
sadehā kokilaṭalāpā liṅgamadhye layaṃ gatā || 84 ||
śrīkaro gopikāprabhūḥ sevitā madhyameśvaram ||
gāṇapatyaṃ samālebhe śivasya karuṇātmanaḥ || 85 ||
bhārgavo gīṣpatiśreṣṭhāmai devau daityasurāñcitau ||
vidyāpāraṃgamau jātau prasādānmadhyameśituḥ || 86 ||
ahaṃ patra saṃbhūjya madhyameśvarmīśvaraṃ ||
purāṇakṛtāśaṃkiṃ prāpyāmi tarasā dhruvam || 87 ||
iti kṛtvā matiṃ dhīro vyāsaḥ satyavatīsutaḥ ||
bhagīrathyambhasi snātvā jagāha niyamaṃ vratī || 88 ||
kācitpraṇāśano bhūtvā phalaśākāśanaḥ kvacit ||
vātabhugjalabhukkāpi kiñcinniraśanavratī || 89 ||
ityādaniyamairyo'ngī trikālaṃ madhyameśvaram ||
pūjayāmāsa dharmātmā nānābhūṣodraṃvaiḥ phalaiḥ || 90 ||
ityaṃ bahutithekāle vyatīte kālikāśrutaḥ ||
snātvā tripathagātoye

--- Page 93 ---
yāvadāyāti sa ṅge || 91 ||
madhyameśvaramīśānaṃ bhaktābhīṣṭavarapradam ||
tāvaddaśī puṇyātmā madhyeliṅgaṃ maheśvaram || 92 ||
umādhiṣitanāmāṅgaṃ vyāghracarmottarīyakam ||
jaṭājaṭacaladgānaraṅgeśāruvirūpraham || 93 ||
lasacchāradvalenducandrikācāndratālakam ||
masmoddhṛtasavāṅkaṃ kapūrārjūnavirūpraham || 94 ||
karṇāntāyatanetraṃ ca vidhumāruṇadacchadam ||
pañcavarṣakṛtiṃ bālaṃ bālakocitabhūṣaṇam || 95 ||
dṛghānaṃ koṭikandarppadarppadhāni tavutitam ||
namaṃ prahasitāsyābjaṃ gāyantaṃ sāma līlayā || 96 ||
karuṇāpārāpathordhi bhaktavatsalanāmakam ||
āśutoṣamukāntaṃ prasādacchutukam haraṃ || 97 ||
samālocya stutiṃ cakre premaglhayā girā ||
yogināmapyagamyantaṃ dīnabandhuṃ cidātmakam || 98 ||
vedavyāsa uvāca ||
devadeva mahābhāga śaraṇāgatavatsala ||
vāṅmanaskarmenduspāpa yogināmapyagocar || 99 ||
mahimānaṃ na te vedā vidāmāsturamate ||
tvameva jagataḥ kartā ghartā hartā tatheiva ca || 100 ||
tvamādyaḥ sarvadevānāṃ saccidānanda īśvaraḥ ||
nāmagotre na vā te staḥ sarvaṅjosi sadāśiva || 101 ||
tvameva paraṃ brahma māthāpāśānivartakaḥ ||
guṇatrayainaṃ liṃpastaṃ padmapratimābhasā || 102 ||
na te janma na vā śīlaṃ na deśo na kulaṃ ca te ||
itthaṃbhūtopīśvarastvaṃ trilokayāḥ kāmamāvaheḥ || 103 ||
na brahmā na ca lakṣmīśo na ca sendrā diveśasaḥ ||
na yogīndrā vidrastavaṃ yasya taṃ tvāsupāsmahe || 104 ||
tvataḥ sarve tvaṃ hi sarve gaurīśastaṃ purāntakaḥ ||
tvaṃ bālastaṃ yuvā vṛddhastaṃ tvā hṛdi sunajyahem || 105 ||
namastasmai maheśāya bhaktadheyāya śaṃbhave ||
purāṇapuruṣāyaddhā śaṃkarāya parātmane || 106 ||
iti stutvā kṣitau yāvaḥdaṇḍavaṭnipatāt saḥ ||
tāvants bālo hṛdyātmā vedavyāsamabhāṣata || 107 ||
varaṃ vṛṇīṣva bho yoginyaste manasi vartate ||
nādeyaṃ vidyate kiṃcidakādhīno yatodsmayham || 108 ||
tata utthāya hṛdātmā munivyāso mahātapāḥ ||
pratyabruvītkimajñātaṃ sarvaṃjasya tava prabho || 109 ||
sarvāntarātmā bhagavāṃsarvaiḥ sarvaprado bhavān ||
yācñāṃ pratiniṣedhukomāṃ kimīśo dainyakāriṇośu || 110 ||
iti śrutvā vacantasya vyāsastyāmalacetasaḥ ||
śuci smṛtvā mahādevo bālarūpagharo'bravīt || 111 ||
bāla uvāca ||
tvayā brahmāvidāṃ śreṣṭha yo'bhilāṣaḥ kuto hṛdi ||
acireṇaiva kālena sa bhaviṣyatyasaṃśayaḥ || 112 ||
kaṇṭhe sthitvā tava brahmanṛtayā myahamīśvaraḥ ||
setihāsapurāṇāni samyaṅnirmāpayāmyaham || 113 ||
abhilāṣāṣṭakaṃ puṇyaṃ stotrameta-ccayeritam ||
varṣe trikālaṃ paṭhanāt kāmadaṃ śambhusamjāni || 114 ||
etastotraasya paṭhanaṃ vidyābuddhivivardhhanam ||
sarvesaṃpattkaraṃ proktaṃ dharmadaṃ mokṣadaṃ vṛṇām || 115 ||
prātarutthāya susnāto liṅgamabhyarcya śāstraram ||
varṣe paṭhitadaṃ stotraṃ mukhodapi syādṛhaspatiḥ || 116 ||
striyā vā puruṣeṇāpi niyamāccliṅgasanniddhau ||
varṣe japtimidaṃ stotraṃ buddhiṃ vidyāca

--- Page 94 ---
vardhyeta || 117 ||
ityuktvā sa mahādevo bālo liṅge nyalīyata ||
vyāso'pi muñcaṃśruṇi śivapremākuloḍabhavat || 118 ||
evaṃ laṅghavaro vyāso maheśānmadhyameśvarāt ||
aṣṭādaśa purāṇāni praṇiṇāya svlīlayā || 119 ||
brahmā pādaṃ vaiṣṇavaṃ śaivaṃ bhāgavataṃ tathā ||
bhaviṣyaṃ nāradīyaṃ ca mārkaṇḍeyamataḥ paraṃ || 120 ||
āgneyaṃ brahmaivataṃ liṅgaṃ vārāhameḥ ca ||
vāmanāsyaṃ tataḥ kaumaṃ mātsyaṃ gāruḍameva ca || 121 ||
skāndaṃ tatheḥa brahmāṇḍāryaṃ purāṇaṃ ca kīrtitam ||
yaśasyaṃ puṇyadaṃ nṝṇāṃ śroṃtṝṇāṃ śāṃkaraṃ yaśaḥ || 122 ||
sūta uvāca

aṣṭādaśa purāṇānāmpūrve nāmoditaṃ tvayā ||
kuru nirvacanaṃ teṣāmidānīmvedivittam || 123 ||
vyāsa uvāca

ayameva kṛtaḥ praśrāstaṇḍanā brahmayoninā ||
nandikesvaramuddiśya sa yadāha bravīmitad || 124 ||
nandakeśvara uvāca

yatra vaktā svayantaṇḍe brahmā sākṣāccatuṣmukhavaḥ ||
tasmādbrahmaṃ samākhyātaṃ purāṇaṃ prathamaṃ śṛṇe || 125 ||
padmakalpasya māhātmyantatra yasyāśudāhṛtam ||
tasmātpadmaṃ samākhyātaṃ purāṇaṃ ca dvitīyakam || 126 ||
parāśarakṛtaṃ yatu purāṇaṃ viṣṇubodhakaṃ ||
tadeva vyāsakathitaṃ putrāpitrormedhatāḥ || 127 ||
yatra putrāuttare khaṇḍe śivasya caritaṃ bahu ||
śaivametadpurāṇaṃ hi purāṇajñā vadanti ca || 128 ||
bhagavatyāśca durgāyāścaritaṃ yatra vidyate ||
tadu bhāgavataṃ proktaṃ nanu devīpurāṇakam || 129 ||
nāroktaṃ purāṇantu nāradīyaṃ pracakṣate ||
yatra vaktāḥabhavattaṇḍe mārkaṇḍeyo mahāmuniḥ || 130 ||
mārkaṇḍeyapurāṇaṃ hi tadākhyātaṃ ca sattamam ||
āgneyogāttadāgneyaṃ bhaviṣyoke'bhibhaviṣyakam || 131 ||
vivartanādbrahmaṇastu brahmaivate mucyate ||
liṅgasya caritoktvātpurāṇaṃ liṅgamucyate || 132 ||
vārāhasya ca vārāhaṃ purāṇaṃ dvādaśaṃ śṛṇe ||
yatra skandaḥ svayaṃ śrotā vaktā sākṣānmaheśvaraḥ || 133 ||
tadu skāndaṃ samākhyātaṃ vāmanasya tu vāmanam ||
kaumaṃ kūrmansya caritaṃ mātsyaṃ matsyena kīrtitam || 134 ||
garuḍastu svayaṃ vaktā yattvadgāruḍasaṃgraham ||
brahmāṇḍacaritoktvādbrahmāṇḍaṃ parikīrtitam || 135 ||
sūta uvāca

ayameva mayāskāri praśro vyāsāya dhīmate ||
tataḥ sarvapurāṇānāṃ mayā nirvacannaṃ śrutam || 136 ||
evaṃ vyāsaḥ suputraparaḥ satyavatryāṃ parāśarāt ||
purāṇasaṃhitāśrake mahābhāratamuttamam || 137 ||
parāśareṇa saṃyogaḥ punaḥ śāntanunā yathā ||
satyavatyā iha brahmaṇaḥ saṃśayitumaheṣi || 138 ||
sakāraṇayutpattiḥ kathitāścaryadkāriṇī ||
mahantaṃ caritaṃ caiva guṇā jñātvā vicakṣaṇaiḥ || 139 ||
idaṃ rahasyaṃ paramaṃ yaḥ śṛṇoti paṭhtyapi ||
sa sarvāpāpinirmuktaḥ ṛṣiloke mahīyate || 140 ||
iti śrī śivamahāpurāṇe paṃcamyāsumāsaṃhitāyāṃ vyāsotpattirvaraṇaṃ nāma catuścatvāriṃśodhyāyaḥ || 44 ||
munaya ūcuḥ

śrutā śambhoḥ kathā ramyā nānā

--- Page 95 ---
khyānasambhavitāṃ ||
nānāvatārasaṃyuktāṃ muktimuktiprādāṃ vṛṇām || 1 ||
idānīṃ śrotumicchāmastavato brahmavidāmbara ||
cāritraṃ jagadambāyā bhagavatyā manoharaṃ || 2 ||
parabrahmadeśasya śaktirādhyā sanātanī ||
umā yā sabhikhyātā trailokyajanjanī parā || 3 ||
satī haimavatī tasyā avatāradartheṃ śrutau ||
aparānvatāreṃstvaṃ brūhi sūta mahāmate || 4 ||
ko virajyeta matimān guṇaśravaṇakārṇiṇa ||
śrīmātṛjāninno yān na tyajanti kadācana || 5 ||
sūta uvāca

dhanayā yūyaṃ mahātmānaḥ kṛtakṛtyāḥ stha sarvadā ||
yatpṛcchatha parāmbāyā umāyāśritaṃ mahat || 6 ||
śṛṇvatāṃ pṛcchhatāṃ caiva tathā vācayatāṃ ca tad ||
pādāmbujarajāṃsyeva tīrthāni munayo viduḥ || 7 ||
te dhanyā kṛtakṛtyāḥ khyādhanyā teṣāṃ prasaḥ kulaṃ ||
yeṣāṃ cittaṃ samveśīnaṃ śrīdevyāṃ parasaṃvidi || 8 ||
ye na stuvanti deveśīṃ sarvakāraṇakāraṇāṃ ||
māyāguṇairmohitāḥ te dukhitabhāgyā na saṃśayaḥ || 9 ||
na bhajantti mahādevīṃ karuṇārasasāgarāṃ ||
andhakūpe patantyete ghore saṃsārakṣipiṇi || 10 ||
gaṅgāṃ vidhāya tṛpyarthe madvāri yathā vrajet ||
vidhāya devīṃ tadbhṛṃśe tathā devāntaraṃ vrajet || 11 ||
yasyāḥ smaraṇamātreṇa puruṣārthacatuṣṭayaṃ ||
anāyāsena labhate kasyajettāṃ narottamaḥ || 12 ||
ṣaṭatṛṣṭaḥ purā meghāssurathena mahātmanā ||
yaduktaṃ medhhasā pūrvaṃ tacchṛṇuṣva vadāmi te || 13 ||
svārociṣāntare pūrve viratho nāma pārthivaḥ ||
surathasya putrodhvam hābalapārākaramaḥ || 14 ||
dānaśauṇḍaḥ satyavādī svadharmaṃkuśalaḥ kṛtī ||
devībhakto dayāsinduḥ prajānāṃ paripālakaḥ || 15 ||
pṛthivīṃ śāsattasya pākaśāsanatejaḥ ||
babhuvaneva ye bhūpāḥ pṛthvyāgrahaṇatatparāḥ || 16 ||
kolānāṃ rājadhanī ruruṣuṣasya bhūpateḥ ||
taiḥ samantatulaṃ yuddhaṃ sampadyata dāruṇaṃ || 17 ||
yuddhe sa nijito bhūpaḥ prabalaistairdṛṣadruṇaiḥ ||
ujjāsitaṃśca kolāyā hatvā rājyamaśeṣataḥ || 18 ||
sa rājā svapurīmityā krodhrājyaṃ svamantribhiḥ ||
tatrāpi ca mahāpakṣīvipakṣaiḥ parājitaḥ || 19 ||
daivacchrutamāpannairmantyapraśubhirgaṇaiḥ ||
kośasthitaṃ ca yadicittaṃ tatsarve cātmanā ktaṃ || 20 ||
tatassa nigato rājā nagarānnmṛgayāchalāt ||
asahāyo'śvamāruḍhya jagāma gahanaṃ vanaṃ || 21 ||
itastatatstra gacchannrājā munivarāśramaṃ ||
dadarśa kusumagrāmabhojitaṃ sarvato diśaṃ || 22 ||
vedaghvinasaṃmākīrṇaṃ śāntajantusaṃmāśritaṃ ||
śiṣyaiḥ praśiṣyaiḥ cchiddhyaiḥ samantatpariṣṭhitaṃ || 23 ||
vyāghradayo mahāvīryo alpavīryān mahāyate ||
tadāśrame na bādhante dvijavaṃryaprabāvataḥ || 24 ||
uvāsa tatra nṛpatimadhyākāruṇiko budhaḥ ||
saṃskṛto muninātena suvacobhoja janasanaiḥ || 25 ||
ekadā sa mahārājāṃ tapāpa durātyayāṃ ||
aho

--- Page 96 ---
me hīnabhāgyasya duḥkhendriyairnitejaṣaḥ || 26 ||
hataṃ rājyamaśeṣeṇa śatruvargairdaloddhutaiḥ ||
matpūrvaiḥ rakṣitaṃ rājyaṃ śatrubhirbhuñjyate'dhunā || 27 ||
māhṛśaścatraṃ śeṣmanna koṣyāsīnmahīpatiḥ ||
kiṃ karomi kva gacchāmi kathaṃ rājyaṃ labheya hi || 28 ||
amātyā mantriṇaścaiva māmakā ye sanātanāḥ ||
na jāne kaṃ ca nṛpatiṃ samāsādyādhunāste || 29 ||
vināśya rājyamadhunā na jāne kāṃ gatiṃ gatāḥ ||
raṇabhūmimahōtsāhā arivargainikartanāḥ || 30 ||
māmakā ye mahāśūrā nṛpamanyaṃ bhajanti te ||
parvantābhā gajā aśvā vātavdegagāminaḥ || 31 ||
pūrvaiḥpūrvairjitaḥ kośaḥ pālyate tairnvādhunā ||
evaṃ moha vaśaṃ yāto rājā paramabhārmikāḥ || 32 ||
etasminnanantare tatra vaiśyaḥ kaścitsamāgataḥ ||
rājā papraccha kastvam bho kimatthimīha cāgataḥ || 33 ||
durmanā lakṣyase kasmādidanme brūhi sāmpratam ||
ityākarṇya vacaḥ ramyaṃ narapālena bhāṣitam || 34 ||
haṃbhyāṃ viṣūcandruṇi samādhicaivaiśyapuṃgavaḥ ||
pratyuvāca mahīpālaṃ praṇayāvantā giram || 35 ||
vaiśya uvāca ||
samādhināma vaiśyo'haṃ dhanavaṃśasamudbhavaḥ ||
putradārādibhistyakto dhanalobanmadhīpate || 36 ||
vanamadhyagato rājendra duḥkhitaḥ svena karmaṇā ||
so'haṃ putrapautrāṇāṃ kalāṇānāṃ tathaiva ca || 37 ||
bhrātṝṇāṃ bāndhavānāṃ pareṣāṃ suhrdam tathā ||
na vemi kuśalaṃ samyak karuṇāsāgara prabho || 38 ||
rājovāca ||
niṣkāsito yaiḥ putradyairdurvacairdhanagardhibhiḥ ||
teṣu kiṃ bhavtā prītiḥ kriyate mūrṣajantuvat || 39 ||
vaiśya uvāca ||
samyuktaṃ tvayā rājanvacaḥ sārarthaṃruhitam ||
tathāpi snehapaśena mohasya'stīva me manaḥ || 40 ||
evaṃ mohākulau vaiśyapāthiṃvau śuniṣattam ||
jagmatuṣṭhunivaryasya meghasaḥ sabṛiṃghintadā || 41 ||
sa vaiśyarājasahito nanarājaḥ pratāpavān ||
praṇanāma mahādhīraḥ śirasā yogināṃ varam || 42 ||
baddhāñjalimāmāṃ vācaṣṭuvāca nṛpatiṣṭhinam ||
bhagavannāvayormohaṃ chettumarhasi sāmpratam || 43 ||
ahaṃ rājyaśriyā tyakto gahanaṃ vanamāśritaḥ ||
tathāpi kṣatrājyasya toṣo naivābhijāyate || 44 ||
ayaṃ ca vaiśyassvajanairdārādyairnirṛtaskṛto gṛhāt ||
tathāpyetasya mamatā na niṣṭhutiḥ samakhute || 45 ||
kimatre kāraṇaṃ brūhi jñāninoṛpi no manaḥ ||
mohena vyākulaṃ jātaṃ mahateṣā hi mukhetā || 46 ||
ṛṣir uvāca ||
mahāmāyā jagaddhātrī śaktirūpā sanātanī ||
sā mohayati sarvāṃ sarvāṃ sarvālakṣya manānsi vai || 47 ||
brahmādayastu rāsteṃ yanmāyamohitāḥ prabho ||
na jānanti paramtaraṃ ca manuṣyāṇāṃ ca kā tathā || 48 ||
sā sṛjattyakhilaṃ viśvaṃ saiva pālayatīti ca ||
saiva saṃharate kāle triguṇā parameśvarī || 49 ||
yasyoṃpāre prasannā sā varadā kāmarūpiṇī ||
sa eva mohamtyeti nānyathā nṛpasattam || 50 ||
rājovāca ||
kā sā devī mahāmāyā yā ca moha yateṣakhilān ||
kathaṃ jātā ca sā devī kṛpayā vad me śrune || 51 ||
ṛṣir uvāca ||
jagadyekāpaṇe jāte śepamāstīrthaṃ yogarāt ||
yoginidha

62

--- Page 97 ---
mupāśritya yadā suṣvāpa keśavaḥ || 52 ||
tadā dvāvasurou jātau viṣṇoḥ karṇamalena ve ||
madhuketabhanāmānau vikhyātau pṛthivītale || 53 ||
pralayāke prabhou chorau mahākāyau mahāhṛu ||
dṛṣṭākarālavadanau bhakṣayantau jaganti vā || 54 ||
tau dṛṣṭvā bhagavannābhipadme kamalāsanam ||
hannanāyodhatāvāstāṃ karttuṃ morite vādinou || 55 ||
samālokya tu tau daityau surajyeṣṭho janārdanaḥ ||
śayānaṃ ca payobhoghoṃ tuṣṭāva parameśvarīm || 56 ||
brahmovāca ||
rakṣa rakṣa mahāmāye śaraṇāgatavatsale ||
etābhyāṃ cārarūpābhyāṃ daityābhyāṃ jagadambike || 57 ||
praṇāmi mahāmāyāṃ yoginīdrāṣṭumāṃ satīm ||
kālarātriṃ mahārātriṃ moharātriṃ parātparām || 58 ||
tridevajanannīṃ nityāṃ matkābhīṣṭaphalapradām ||
pālinīṃ sarvadaivānāṃ karuṇāvaruṇālayām || 59 ||
tvat praḥmāvāda brahmā māghavo girijāpatiḥ ||
hṛjyayavita saṃsāraṃ kāle saṃhratīti ca || 60 ||
tvaṃ svāhā tvaṃ svaghā tvaṃ dhrīstvaṃ buddhirvimalā matā ||
tuṣṭiḥ puṣṭistvaṃ mevāmba śāntiḥ kṣāntiḥ kṣudhā dayā || 61 ||
viṣṇumāyā tvamevāmba tvameva cetanā matā ||
tvaṃ śaktiḥ paramā proktā lajjā tṛṣṇā tvameva ca || 62 ||
śāntistvam smṛtirūpā tvaṃ māturūpeṇa saṃsthitā ||
tvaṃ lakṣmīrbhavane phuṃsāṃ puṇyācārapravartinām || 63 ||
tvaṃ jātistvam matā vṛttyorjośitarūpā tvameva hi ||
tvameva cittarūpeṇa vyāpya kṛtsnaṃ pratiṣṭhitā || 64 ||
sā tvameto durāghṣāvasurou mohyāmibike ||
prabodha jagadyone nārāyaṇamajaṃ viṣṇum ||

|| 65 ||
ṛṣirovāca ||
brāhmaṇā prārthitā seyaṃ madhuketabhanāśane ||
mahāvidyā jagaddhátrī sarvavidyādhidaivātā || 66 ||
dvādaśyāṃ phālgunasyaiva śuklāyāṃ sambhūnarūpa ||
mahākālīti vikhyātā śaktistrailokayamohinī || 67 ||
tato'bhavadvivṛddhvāṇī mā bhaiṣīḥ kamalāsana ||
kaṇṭakaṃ nāśayāmyadya hatvājau madhukeṭabhau || 68 ||
ityuktā sā mahāmāyā netravalṃkādito hareḥ ||
nigamya darśane tasthau brahmaṇo'vyaktajanmanaḥ || 69 ||
uttasthau ca hṛṣī keśo devadevo janārdanaḥ ||
sa dadraśa puro daityau madhukeṭabhasaṃjñakau || 70 ||
tābhyāṃ pravṛṇute yuddhaṃ viṣṇoratulatejasaḥ ||
pañcavarṣasahasrāṇi bāhuyuddham dhṛttadā || 71 ||
mahāmāyāprabhāveṇa mohitau dānavottamau ||
jagrḥpatū ramākāntaṃ gṛhāṇa varmīṃsitam || 72 ||
nārāyaṇa uvāca ||
mati prasannau yadi vāṃ dīyatāmeṣa me varaḥ ||
mama vadhyānubhau nānye yuvābhyāṃ prārthaye varam || 73 ||
ṛṣirovāca ||
ekāṇaivāṃ mahīṃ dṛṣṭvā procatuḥ keśavaṃ vacaḥ ||
āvāṃ jahi na yannasou ghṛraṇī payasāḍoḍhutā || 74 ||
tathāstu bhocya bhagavāṃśakṣutyāpya sūjjvalam ||
chiccheda śirasī kṛtvā svakīyajaghanetayoḥ || 75 ||
evante kathito rājankhālikāyāssasmṛdddhavaḥ ||
mahālakṣmyāstathā'utpatti niśāmaya mahāmate || 76 ||
nirviṃkārāṇi sākārā nirākā

--- Page 98 ---
rāpi devyumā ||
devānāṃ tāpanāśārthaṃ prādurāsīttugeyuge || 77 ||
yadīcchāvaiṃbhavaṃ sarvaṃ tasyā dehamahraḥ smṛtaḥ ||
līlayā sāpi bhaktānāṃ guṇavarṇanadevatā || 78 || ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe paścamyāsumāsaṃhitāyāṃ maṭhukeṭamavaghe mahākālikāvatāravarṇanaṃ nāma pañcacatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 45 ||
ṛṣaya ūcuḥ

āsīddaṃbhāsuro nāma daityavaṃśaśiromaṇiḥ ||
tasmājjāto mahātejā mahiṣo nāma dānavaḥ || 1 ||
sa saṃgrāme surānsarvānjijitvya danujadhipaḥ ||
cakāra rājyaṃ svaloke mahendāsanasaṃsthitaḥ || 2 ||
parājitāstatato devā brahmaṇaṃ śaraṇaṃ yayuḥ ||
brahmāpi tānsasmādāya yayau yatra vṛṣakapī || 3 ||
tatra gatvā surāssarve natvā śaṅkarakeśavau ||
svavṛttaṃ kathayāmāsurtyāvadanupūrvaśaḥ || 4 ||
bhagavanto vayaṃ sarve mahiṣeṇa durātmanā ||
ujjāsitāśca svalokā nirjitvya samarāṅgaṇe || 5 ||
bhramāmo marttyaloke'sminno labhemahe śaṃ kiñcit ||
kāṅkṣāṃ na duḥśāṃ nītā devā indrapurogamāḥ || 6 ||
sūryaścandramasau pāśī kubero yama eva ca ||
indrābhivātagardhvā vidyādharāścāraṇāḥ || 7 ||
eteṣāmaparreṣāṃ ca vidheyaṃ karma soṣuruḥ ||
svayaṃ karoti pāpātmā daityapa kṣābhayaṃkaraḥ || 8 ||
tasmāccharaṇamāpannāndevānastrātumarhatthaḥ ||
vadhoparāṃ ca tasyāśu cintayetthaṃ yuvāṃ prabhu || 9 ||
iti devavacaḥ śrutvā dāmodarasatīśvarau ||
cakratuḥ paramaṃ kopaṃ roṣāghūrṇitalocano || 10 ||
tatotikopapu  ṇṇasya viṣṇorvaktraḥ ||
tathānyeṣāṃ ca devānāṃ śarīrāṇirgataṃ mahaḥ || 11 ||
atīva mahasaḥ puñjaṃ jvalantaṃ daśādiṣu ca ||
apaśyaṃstridaśāssarve dugogdhyānaparāyaṇāḥ || 12 ||
sarvadevāśarīrotthaṃ tejastadatibhīṣaṇam ||
saṃghībhūyābhava nārī sākṣānmahiṣamardinī || 13 ||
śaṃtejasa utpannaṃ mukhasmasyāḥ subhāsvaram ||
yāmyena bālā abhavannaiṣṇavena ca bāhavaḥ || 14 ||
candramastes jasā tasyāḥ stanayugmaṃ vyajāyata ||
madhyamendreṇa jaṃghorau vāruṇena babhūvatuḥ || 15 ||
bhūtejasā nitaṃboru śrāddheṇa caraṇadvayam ||
ārkkeṇa caraṇāṃgulyaḥ karāṃgulyaśca vāstavāt || 16 ||
kuberatejasā nāsā rdanāśca prajāpateḥ ||
pāvakīyena nayanatrayaṃ sāṃkhyena bhrūdvayam || 17 ||
ānilenobhre'ndraṃ tathānyeṣāṃ svarokasamṛ ||
tejasāṃ sabhavaḥ paścālayā sā parameśvarī || 18 ||
tato nikhiladevānāṃ tejorāśisaṣuṃdrvāṃ ||
tāmālokya surāssarve paraṃ harṣe prapedire || 19 ||
nirāyudhāṃ ca tāṃ dṛṣṭvā brahmādyāstridevāśvarāḥ ||
sāyudhaśāntāṃ śivāṃ kartuṃ manaḥ sandigdhe śurāḥ || 20 ||
tataḥ śūlaṃ maheśāno mahāśānye samarpayat ||
cakraṃ ca kṛṣṇo bhagavāñśaṅkaṃ pāśaṃ ca pāśabhṛt || 21 ||
śaktiṃ hutāśano'yaacchanmārutaḥśāpameva ca ||
bāṇapūrṇatuṇī caiva vajraghaṇṭe śacīpatiḥ || 22 ||
yamo dadau kāladaṇḍamaḥ mālāṃ prajāpatiḥ ||
brahmā kamaṇḍaluṃ prādādrommarśamindivākaraḥ || 23 ||
kālaḥ khaḍgaṃdadau tasyai phalakaṃ ca samujjvalam ||
kṣīrābdhī ruciraṃ hāramare ca tathābhare || 24 ||
cūḍāmaṇiṃ kuṇḍale ca kaṭakāni tathaiva ca ||
arddhacandraṃ ca keyurābhūrī ca manoharau || 25 ||
--- Page 99 ---
śreveykamāṇḍulīṣu samastāsvaṇḍulīyakam ||
viśvakarmā ca paraśuṃ dadau tasmai manoharaṃ || 26 ||
akṣāṇyanekaini tathāmedyaṃ caiva tanuśchadaṃ ||
surabhy asārasāṃ mālaṃ paṃkajaṃ cāmbudhardadau || 27 ||
dadau siṃhaṃ ca himavāṃstaninīni vividhāni ca ||
surayā pūritaṃ pātraṃ kuberotsyai samarpayat || 28 ||
śeṣaś ca bhoginām netā vicitraracanāṃśitam ||
dadau tasmai nāgahāraṃ nānāsanmaṇibhūṣitam || 29 ||
etaiścānyaiś ca suraiḥ devī bhūṣaṇarāśuḥ sthā ||
sakṛtotecainā nādāsau sāṭṭahāsaṃ punaḥpunaḥ || 30 ||
tasyā bhoṣaṇādena pūritā ca nabhaḥsthalī ||
pratiśabdo mahānāsīcchubhe bhuvanratrayam || 31 ||
celuḥ samudrāścatvāro vasudhā ca cacāla ha ||
jayaśabdastato devairaśkārir mahiṣādite || 32 ||
tato'mbikāṃ parāṃ śaktiṃ mahālakṣmīsvarūpiṇīm ||
tuṣṭuvuḥ surāssarve bhaktigadgadayā girā || 33 ||
lokaṃ sankhubhamālokvya devatāparipanthinaḥ ||
sambaddhasainikāste ca saṃtatthastyuruḍātughaḥ || 34 ||
mahiṣo'pi ca taṃśabdamabhyaghāvaḍuśānvitaḥ ||
sa dadṛśe tato devīṃ vyāptalokatrayāṃ rucā || 35 ||
etasminnantare tatra mahiṣāsurāpālitāḥ ||
samājaġmurme mahāvīrāḥ koṭiśo hṛtahetayaḥ || 36 ||
cikhuraś ca mārodaymo karāloddatavāṣkalāḥ ||
tāmro'śyatyogavīryāṃśca biḍāloṣṇabaka eva ca || 37 ||
durghairo duḥkhakheva cinītrabhya mahāhṛduḥ ||
ete cānye ca bahvaḥ śūrā yuddhiviśāradāḥ || 38 ||
yuṃdhu buḥ samare devyā saha śastrāstrāparagāḥ ||
ityaṃ kālo vyatīyāya yudhyato rbhīṣaṇa stantayoḥ || 39 ||
ārivaṃgaiḥkṛkiṣṭā nānāśastrāstrāśayaḥ ||
mahāmāyāprabhaṇeṇa viphalā abhavan kṣaṇāt || 40 ||
tato jagāna sā devī cikhuraprāmukhā narīḥ ||
tugaṇāṃgadyā bāṇaiḥ śūlaśaktiparaśvabhaiḥ || 41 ||
evaṃ svīyeṣu sainyeṣu hateṣu mahiṣāsuraḥ ||
devīniḥśvasasaṃbhūtānbhāvayāmāsa tāṃgaṇān || 42 ||
atāḍayatkhuḥraiḥ kāṃścit kāṃści cchādadrayeṇa ca ||
lāṃgūlena ca tuṇḍena bhinnāṃ naṃ mahuṃbhūbuḥ || 43 ||
ithaṃ devīgaṇānhatvābhyaghāvatsāsurādhipaḥ ||
siṃhaṃ māryitun devyāstatoső kupitāśabhavat || 44 ||
kopātsopi mahāvīryaḥ khurkuṭitabhṛtalaḥ ||
śṛṃgābhyāṃ śailamurutpādbya cikṣepa praṇādaṃ ca || 45 ||
vegena viṣvaṃ bhramatā prakṣiptā guravo'dṛdhyaḥ ||
ākāśato mahīmadhye nipetustṛṇapasattam || 46 ||
śṛṃgabhinnāḥ payovāhāḥ khaṇḍaṃsaṇḍ amayāsiduḥ ||
lāṃgūlenāhataś cāṃdhirbhiṣṣvaghūḍelmaspadantam || 47 ||
evaṃ kuddhaṃ samālokvya mahiṣāsuramambikā ||
vidoghe tadghopaṃ devanāmamabhayaṃkarī || 48 ||
tataḥ pāśaṃ samutthāpya kṣiptvā tasyopariśvarī ||
babandhaca mahiṣaṃ so'pi rūpantaty ājanmahiṣam || 49 ||
tataḥ siṃho babhūvāśu māyāvī tacchirobikā ||
yāvadbhinataṃ tāvatsa khaḍgapāṇibabhūva ha || 50 ||
sacarmāsthikaram taṃ ca devī bāṇairatāḍayat ||
tato gajabhūtvā siṃhaṃ ciccheda śuṇḍayā || 51 ||
tatotsya ca karaṃ devī cakate svamahāsinā ||
aghanāraṃ ca punā rūpaṃ svakīyaṃ tena rakṣasā || 52 ||
tadaiva kṣobhayāmāsa

