trailokyaṃ sacarācaraṃ ||
tataḥ krudhā mahāmāyā caṇḍikā mānavikramā || 56 ||
papau punaḥ punaḥ pānaṃ jahāsodhāntalocanā ||
jagajjabāhuḥ sopi balabīryamadoddhataḥ || 57 ||
tasyā upāri cikṣepa śailānnutpātya so'suraḥ ||
sā ca bāṇāvalīghātaiścūrṇayāmāsa satvarām || 58 ||
vāruṇīmadaṃ sañjātamukharagāssakulendriyā ||
provāca parameśānī meghagambhīrayā girā || 59 || ||
devyuvāca ||
re mūḍha re hataprajña vṛthā kiṃ kuruṣe haṭham ||
na madareṣurāḥ ke pi sthāsnavjo jagatītraye || 60 ||

||
ṛṣiruvāca ||
pavamābhāṣya koditā devī sarvakalāmayī ||
padākamyāsuraṃ kaṇṭhe śūlenogreṇa sābhinat || 57 ||
tatastaccaraṇāgrāntasya svakīyamukhāttataḥ ||
ardheniskānta evāsīddevyā vīryeṇa saṃvṛtaḥ || 58 ||
ardheniskānta evāso bhuśyamāno mahāghamaḥ ||
mahāsinā śiro bhettvā nyapāti dharaṇītale || 60 ||
hāhāśabdaṃ samuccārya vāṅmukhāstadruṇāstataḥ ||
palāyanta raṇādritāstadihitā vādīnaḥ || 61 ||
tuṣṭuvuśca tadā devīmindraādyāḥ sakalāḥ surāḥ ||
gandharśo gītamubbera nṛtutanentaṃkījanāḥ || 62 ||
evante kathitā rājin mahālakṣmyāḥ samudbhavaḥ ||
sarasvatyāsthatpatti śṛṇu suisthena cetasā || 63 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe paṃcamyāṃ umāsaṃhitāyāṃ mahiṣāsuravadhopaṃkhyāne mahālakṣmyavatāravarṇanaṃ nāma ṣaṭcatvāriṃśo'dhyāyaḥ || 46 ||

||
ṛṣiruvāca ||
āsīcchuṃbhāsuro daityo niśuṃbhaśca pratāpavān ||
trailokyamojasākāntaṃ ārūḍhyāṃ sacarācaraṃ || 1 ||
tābhyāṃ prapīḍitā devā himavantaṃ samāyayuḥ ||
jananīṃ sarvasūtānāṃ kāmadātrīṃ vavandire || 2 ||
devā ūcuḥ ||
jaya durge maheśāni jayatmīyajananipriye ||
trailokyarāṇakāriṇye śivāyai te namonmaḥ || 3 ||
namo śuktipradāyinyai parāmbāyai namonmaḥ ||
namaḥ samastasaṃsārotpattisthityantakāriṇe || 4 ||
kālikakārupassaṃpanne namastārākṛte namaḥ ||
chidrāmastāsvarūpāyai śrīvidyāyai namostu te || 5 ||
bhuvanīśa namastubhyaṃ namaste bhairavākṛte ||
namostu bagalāmukhye ghūmāvatyai namonmaḥ || 6 ||
namaśśūrsunadryai mātṛṇyai te namonmaḥ ||
ajitāyai namastubhyaṃ vijayāyai namonmaḥ || 7 ||
jayāyai maṃgalāyai te vilāsinyai namonmaḥ ||
droṃśrīrūpe namastubhyaṃ namoghōrākṛtestu te || 8 ||
namo'parājitākāre nityākāre namonmaḥ ||
śaraṇāgatapālinyai rudrāṇyai te namonmaḥ || 9 ||
namo vedāntavedyāyai namaste paramātmane ||
anantakoṭibrahmaṇḍanāyikāyai namonmaḥ || 10 ||
iti devaiḥ stutā gaurī prasannā varadā śivā ||
provāca tridasānsarvānyuṣmābhiḥ stūyatetra kā || 11 ||
tato gaurītanoreṃkā prādurāsītkumārikā ||
sovāca miṣatāṃ teṣāṃ śivaśaṃkaṃ parādravat || 12 ||
stotraṃ me kriyate mātaḥ samastaiḥ svargavāsibhiḥ ||
niśuṃbhaśuṃbhadaityābhyāṃ prabalābhyāṃ prapīḍitaiḥ || 13 ||
śarīrakoṣādyatasyā nirgatā tena kauśikī ||
nāmnā

--- Page 101 ---
सा गीयते साक्षाच्छुम्भासुरनिवहिणी || १४ ||
सैवोग्रतारिका प्रोक्ता महोग्रतारिकापि च ||
प्रादुर्भूता यतः सा वै मातंगीत्युच्यते शुचि || १५ ||
बभाषे निर्विक्लान्देवान्युयं तिष्ठत निर्भयाः ||
कार्यं वः साधयिष्यामि स्वतन्त्राहं विनाश्रयम् || १६ ||
इत्युक्ता सा तदा देवी तरसान्तिहिताभवत् ||
चण्डखण्डौ तु तान्देवीमद्राष्टां सेवकौ तयोः || १७ ||
दृष्ट्वा मनोहरं तस्या रूपं नेत्रसुखावहम् ||
पेततुस्तो घरामध्ये नष्टसंज्ञौ विमोहितौ || १८ ||
गत्वा व्याजहृतुः सवै राज्ञे वृत्तान्तमादितः ||
दृष्ट्वा काचिन्मयापूर्वा नारी राजन्मनोरमा || १९ ||
हिमवाच्छिखरे रम्ये संस्थिता सिंहवाहिनी ||
समन्तादेवकन्याभिः सेविता बद्धपाणिभिः || २० ||
कुरुते पादसंवाहं काचित्संस्कुरुते कंचान् ||
पाणिसंवाहनं काचित्काचिद्भ्रूनेत्राञ्जनं न्यधात् || २१ ||
काचिद् गृहीत्वा हस्तेनादर्शं दर्शयते मुखम् ||
नागवल्लीं ददात्येका लवंगेलादिसंयुताम् || २२ ||
पतदभ्रं करे कृत्वा स्थिता काचित्सखी पुरः ||
भूषयत्यस्यिलांगानि काचिद्भूषाम्बरादिभिः || २३ ||
कदलीस्तंभजंघोरुः कीरनासाऽहिदोलता ||
रणन्मञ्जीरचरणा रम्यमेखलया युता || २४ ||
लसत्कस्तूरिकामोदसुकाहारचलस्तनी ||
ग्रैवेयंकलसद्रीवा ललन्तीदाममण्डिता || २५ ||
अर्द्धचन्द्रधरा देवी मणिकुण्डलधारिणी ||
रम्यवेणिनिविशालाक्षी लोचनत्रयभूषिता || २६ ||
साक्षरा मालिंकोपेता पाणिराजितकंकणा ||
स्वणौर्मिकांगुलिर्भ्राजत्पारिहार्यलसत्करा || २७ ||
शुभवस्त्रावृता गौरी पद्मासनविराजिता ||
काश्मीरिबिन्दुतिलका चन्द्रालंकृतमस्तका || २८ ||
तिडिद्धुतिमहामूल्याम्बरचोलोन्नमत्कुचा ||
भुजैरष्टाभिरचुंगेर्घार्यन्ती वराणुघात् || २९ ||
तांदृशी नासुरी नागी न गन्धवीं न दानवी ||
विद्यते त्रिषु लोकेषु यादृशी सा मनोरमा || ३० ||
तस्मात्संभोगयोग्यत्वं तस्यास्त्वच्च्येव शोभते ||
नारीरत्नं यतः सा वै पुरत्नं च भवान्प्रभो || ३१ ||
इत्युक्तं चण्डमुण्डाभ्यां निशम्य स महासुरः ||
दूतं सुग्रीवनामानं प्रेषयामास तां प्रति || ३२ ||
गच्छ दूत तुषाराद्रों तत्रास्ते कापि सुन्दरी ||
सानितव्या प्रयत्नेन कथयित्वा वचो मम् || ३३ ||
इति विज्ञापितस्तेन सुग्रीवो दानवोत्तमः ||
गत्वा हिमाचलं प्राह जगदम्बां महेश्वरीम् || ३४ ||
दूत उवाच

देवि शुम्भासुरो दैत्यो निशुम्भस्तस्य चानुजः ||
विख्यातौ त्रिषु लोकेषु महाबलपराक्रमः || ३५ ||
चारोहं प्रेषितस्तेन संविधिन्ते समागमम् ||
स यज्ञैः सुरेशानि तत्समाकर्णयातुना || ३६ ||
इन्द्रादीन्समरे जित्वा तेषां रत्नान्यपाहरम् ||
देवभागं स्वयं भुंसे यागे दत्तं सुरादिभिः || ३७ ||
क्षीरतनं त्वामहं मन्ये सर्वरत्नोपरि स्थितम् ||
सा त्वं ममानुजं मां वा भजन्तात्कामजे रसैः || ३८ ||
इति दूतोक्तमाकर्ण्य वचनं शुम्भभाषितम् ||
जगाद सा महामाया भूतेशप्राणवल्लभा || ३९ ||
देव्युवाच

सत्यं वदसि भो दूत नानृतं किंचिदुच्यते ||
परन्त्वेका कृता पूर्वं प्रतिज्ञा तान्निबोध मे || ४० ||
यो मे दर्पं विध्नुते यो मां

--- Page 102 ---
jayati saṃgare ||
utsahe tamahaṃ kartu patiṃ nānayimiti śruvaṃ || 41 ||
sa tvaṃ kathaya śumbhāya niśumbhāya vaco mama ||
yathā śuktaṃ bhavdetra vidaghātu tathāśra saḥ || 42 ||
itthaṃ devīvacaḥ śrutvā śumbhīvoḥ nāma dānavaḥ ||
rājñe vijñāpayāmāsa gatvā tatra savistaram || 43 ||
atha dūtokta mākṛṇye śumbho bhairavaśāsanaḥ ||
dhūmrākṣaṃ prāha sakodhḥ senānāṃ balinām varam || 44 ||
he dhūmrākṣa tuṣārādreḥ varttate kāpi sundarī ||
tāmānatya dūtaṃ gatvā yathā yāsyati sātra vai || 45 ||
tasyā ānanaye bhītinaṃ kāryāṃśaśurasattam ||
yuddhaṃ kaiścit prayatnaena yadi sā yoddhum icchati || 46 ||
evaṃ vijñāpito daityo dhūmralocanasakaḥ ||
gatvā himācalaṃ prāha śuvanaiśiśumārśajām || 47 ||
maṭuṃmāmāntakaṃ gaccha nocetvaṃ vātayāṃyadṛśam ||
ṣaṣṭhā śasmurāṇāṃ sahitaḥ sahasrāṇāṃ nitānvini || 48 ||
devyuvāca ||
daityarāṭ preṣito vīra haṃsi cennaṃ karomi te ||
parantu sādhyaṃ gamanaṃ manye saṃgrāma mantrā || 49 ||
ityuktas tāmānavacavāhanova dhūmralocanaḥ ||
huṃkārocāraṇenaiva tandadāha maheśvarī || 50 ||
tataḥ prabhṛti sā devī dhūmāvatyu cyate śuvi ||
ārādhitā svabhaktānāṃ ṣaṭvagīnikīrtinī || 51 ||
dhūmrākṣe nihate devyā vāhananātikopiṇā ||
cinvāntastadṛṇāsstraiḥspalāyantāvroṣitāḥ || || 52 ||
itthaṃ devyā hataṃ daityaṃ śrutvā śumbhaḥ pratāpavān ||
cakāra bahulaṃ kopaṃ sandaśeṣṭapuṭadḥrayaḥ || 53 ||
caṇḍaṃ muṇḍaṃ raktabījaṃ preṣyatkamatosrāc ||
teti cājñāpitā daityā yatyeṇāṃbikā sthitā || 54 ||
siṃhārūḍhāṃ bhagavatīṃ maṇimādibhirāśritām ||
bhāsyanntīṃ diśo bhāsā dṛṣṭocudrānavārṣebhāḥ || || 55 ||
he devi tarasā śūlaṃ yāhi śumbhaniśumbhayoḥ ||
anyathā cātiyāsyāmaḥ sagaṇāstvāṃ savāhanām || 56 ||
vṛṇīṣva taṃ patiṃ vāme lokapāladibhiḥ stutam ||
prapatsy ase mahānandaṃ devānāmapi durlabham || 57 ||
ityuktamākalayāṃbvā smayitvā parameśvarī ||
udājahāra sā devī su nṛtaṃ rasavadracaḥ || || 58 ||
devyuvāca ||
adrītīyo maheśānaḥ parabrahma sadāśivaḥ ||
yattactvamavidu vedā viṣṇvādīnāṃ ca kā kathā || 59 ||
tasyāiṃ prakṛtiḥ sūkṣmā kathā manye pitambhṛṇe ||
siṃhī kāmāturā naiva jambūkaṃ vṛṇute kiñcit || 60 ||
kareṇu gārdabham naiva dīpinī śaśakaṃ na vā ||
mṛṣā vadat bho daitya mṛtyurbyā lā niyantritāḥ || 61 ||
yuyaṃ prayāt pātālaṃ yuddhyaḥvaṃ śaktiristha cetuh ||
iti kodhakāraṃ vākyaṃ śrutvocuṣte parasparaṃ || 62 ||
abalāṃ manasi jñātvā na hanymo bhavato vayam ||
atho sthiraihi pañcāśye yadṛcchāṃ mānase asita cet || 63 ||
teṣāmevaṃ vivadatāṃ kalahaḥ samavartata ||
tasyā bhavabhūpāḥ smere bāṇā ubhayādirvalayośatāḥ || 64 ||
evantaiḥ samaraṃ kṛtvā līlayā parameśvarī ||
jaghāna caṇḍamuṇḍābhyāṃ raktabījaṃ mahāvaruḥ smareḥ || 65 ||
dveṣabuddhiṃ vidhāyāpi vidśāḥ tantyoāsyamī ||
antesrāpanparaṃ lokaṃ yaścokāṃ yānti tajjñānāḥ || 66 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe surame || 66 ||
--- Page 103 ---
पञ्चम्याउमासंहितायां घूम्रलोचनचण्डमुण्डरक्तबीजवधो नाम सप्तचत्वारिंशोऽध्यायः || ४७ ||
राजोवाच

घूम्राक्षं चण्डमुण्डं च रक्तबीजासुर- न्तथा ||
भगवन्ब्रहतन्देव्या श्रुत्वा शुम्भः सुरादनः || १ ||
किमकाषीत्ततो ब्रह्मन्तन्मे ब्रूहि साम्प्रतम् |
शुश्रूषे जगद्योनेश्चरितं पापनाशनम् ||२||
ऋषिरुवाच

इतानिमान्दैत्यवरान्महासुरो निशम्य राजन्महनीयविक्रमः |
अजिज्ञपत्स्वीयगणान्दुरासदान्रणाभिमुखेऽचरणजातसंमदान् || ३ ||
बलान्वितास्संमिलिता ममाज्ञया जयाशया कालकवशसंभवाः |
सकालकेयासुरमौर्य्यैदैहेदास्तथा परेष्याशु प्रयाणयन्तु ते || ४ ||
निशुंभमुभौ दितिजान्विदेश्य तात्राधिरूढौ निर्यान्बभूवतुः |
बलान्यनुखर्षेलिनोस्तयोऽघंराद्विनाशवन्तः शलभा इवोत्थिताः || ५ ||
प्रवाद्यामास मृदंगमर्दलं संमेरिकाडिण्डमझझंरानकम् |
रणस्थले संजह्षू रंगिप्रिया असुमिप्रयाः संगतः परायुः || ६ ||
भटाश्वते युद्धपटाबृतास्तदा रणस्थलीं मापुरपापविग्रहाः |
गृहीतशस्त्रास्त्रचया जिगीषया परस्परं विग्रहयन्त उल्बणम् || ७ ||
गजाधिरूढास्तुरगाधिरोहिणो रथाधिरूढाश्च तथापरेऽसुराः |
अलक्षयन्तः स्वपराज्ञनान्सुदाऽसुरेशसंगे समरेऽभिरेभिरे || ८ ||
ध्वनिः शतग्नीजनितो घुड्घुड्धुभूव तेन विदशाः समेजिताः |
महान्च कारः समपद्यताम्बरे विलोक्यते नो रथमण्डलं रवेः || ९ ||
पदातयो निर्वेवङ्गुहीं कोटिशः प्रभूतमाना विजयाभिलाषिणः |
रथाश्वगा वारणगाऽथापरेऽसुरा निरीयुः कति कोटिशो मुदा || १० ||
अशुक्रशैला इव मत्तवारणाः अतानिषुश्रीत्कृतिशब्दमाहवे |
क्रमेलकाश्चापि गलद्रुलघ्विन् वितन्वते क्षुद्रमहीघरोपमाः || ११ ||
हयाश्च द्रेषन्त उदग्रभूमिजा विशालकण्ठाभरणा गतेर्विदः |
पदानि दन्तावलमूर्धिन विभ्रतः शुडिडिच्यरे व्योमपथा यथाऽवयः || १२ ||
समीक्ष्य शत्रोर्बलमित्यमापतत्चकार सज्यं घनुराम्बिका तदा |
ननाद घण्टां रिपुसाद्दायिनीं जगजे सिंहोऽपि सटां विध्वनयन् || १३ ||
ततो निशुंभस्तुहिनाचलस्थितां विलोक्य रम्याभरणायुषां शिवाम् |
गिरं बभाषे रसनिर्भरां परां विला सिनीभावविचक्षणो यथा || १४ ||
भवादृशीनां रमणीयविग्रहे दुनोति कीणे खलुमालतीदलम् |
कथं कराला हवमातनोष्यये महेश तेनैव मनोज्ञवर्षमेणा || १५ ||
इतीरयित्वा वचनं महासुरो बभूव मौनी तथुवाच चण्डिका |
वृथा किमाथासुर मूढ संगरं कुरुष्व नागालयमन्यथा व्रज || १६ ||
ततोतिरुष्टः समरे महारथश्चकार बाणाविलवृष्टिमदुताम् |
घनाघनाः संवृषुषंयथोद्कं रणस्थले प्राशुडिवागता तदा || १७ ||
शरैश्शितैश्शूलपरश्वघातुयैः संभिन्दुपालैः परिघैश्शरासनैः |
शुशुण्डिकाप्राससुरप्रसङ्गैर्महासिभिः संयुयुधे मदोद्धतैः || १८ ||
विभ्रमुस्तत्समरे महागजा विभ्रत्कुंभा असिताद्रिसन्निभाः |
चलद्दलाकाघवलावकेतवो विसेतवः शुंभिनशुंभकेतवः || १९ ||
--- Page 104 ---
vibhinnadehā ditijā jhaṣopamā vikaṃvarā vājigaṇā bhayaṃkarāḥ ||
parasavaḥ kālikayā kṛtā raṇe mṛgāriṇā cāśiṃvatāpareṣurāḥ || 20 ||
viṣṭuṣuvū rktavāstadantare siñcayāstatra viṣupluṣuve haitaiḥ ||
kacā bhaṭānāṃ jalanīlikopamastaduṭṭarīyaṃ sitaphenasaṃnibham || 21 ||
turaṃgasādī turaṃgābhirodhi paṃ gajasthitānabhyapataṃgajāruḥ ||
rathī ratheśaṃ khalu pitṛraṃdhibhigānsamprātidvandvikaliṃhānabhṛt || 22 ||
tato niśuṃmo hṛdaye vyacintyatkaralakā loyaṣṭupāgatos'ḍhunā ||
bhavedridro'pi mahāghano mahāghano daridro viparītakālataḥ || 23 ||
jaḍo bhavetspītatmitaṃhāmitajaṃḍo nṛśaṃso bahuman tuṃ stutaḥ ||
parājayaṃ yānti raṇe mahābalā jayanti saṃgrāmabhuṣe ca durbalāḥ || 24 ||
jayo'jayo vā parameśvarecchayā bhavannayāyasat eva dehinām ||
na kālamuñcañca śaśāka jīvituṃ maheśvaraḥ pañcajanī ramāpitaḥ || 25 ||
upetyā saṃgrāmamukhaṃ palāyanaṃ na sādhu vīrā hṛdye'śrumanvate ||
parantu yuddhe kathamebhyā jayo vināśitaṃ me sakalaṃ balaṃ yathā || 26 ||
iyaṃ hi nunaṃ surkarme sādhituṃ samāgatā daityabalaṃ ca bādhatume ||
purāṇabhūtiḥ prakṛtiḥ parā śivā na laukikīyaṃ vinatā kadāpi vā || 27 ||
vagho'pi nārīvihitoyaśaskaraḥ pragīyate yuddhrasaṃ liliṣubhiḥ ||
tathāpyaktvā samaraṃ kathaṃ mukhe pradarśayāmo'surārājasaṃnighau || 28 ||
vicārayitveḥ mahārathī rathaṃ mahāntaraṃ adhyāsya niyantṛcoditam ||
yayau drutaṃ yatra maheśvarāgṇanā surāṅganāprārthitayo'vanodramā || 29 ||
avocaddenāṃ sa maheśa kiṃ bhavedebhirhaiṃteniñjīvibhirhetaiḥ ||
tavāsti kāṃkṣā yadi yodhum āvayostadā raṇaḥ syāddruta yudhasatpate || 30 ||
uvāca kālīṃ pratikausiśakī tadā samīkṣyatāmeṣa durāgmo'nayoḥ ||
karoti kālo vipadāgame matiṃ vibhinnvṛttiḥ sadaḥ pravattakaḥ || 31 ||
tato niśuṃbho'bhijagāna caṇḍikāṃ śaireḥ sahasraiḥ tathaiva kālikām ||
vibheda vāṇānasurápracoditan sahasrakhaṇḍaṃ svaśarotkaraiḥ śivā || 32 ||
tataḥ sautayā kṛpāṇabhujyevaṃlaṃ sa carmaṃ kaṃṭhīravamṛghanyentāḍayat ||
vibheda taṃ cāpi mahāsinā ambikā yathā kuṭhoreṇa taruṃ tacchidaḥ || 33 ||
sa bhinnakhaḍgo nijakāna mārgaṇaṃ parā mibhikāvaṣkiḥ so'pi cicchide ||
punarbhiśūlaṃ hṛdaye'śikipattadyaṃ yadāṇayan muṣṭinipātanena sā || 34 ||
gadāṃ samādāya punarmehārtho'bhyahāvadambāṃ maraṇonmukho'suraḥ ||
acūrṇayatāmapi śūladhārayā punarbhiśūlaṃ vidadāra so'nyayā || 35 ||
tato'mbikā bheṃ bhujaṃgamopamaiḥ suradviṣāṃ śoṇitacūṣaṇocitaiḥ ||
niśubham ātmīyaśilīmukhaiḥ śatenihatya bhūmīmanayaddviṣoḥkṣitaiḥ || 36 ||
nipātito'smānabalo'suráprabhuḥ kanī

--- Page 105 ---
yasi śrātari roṣapūritaḥ ||
rathasthito bāhubhirardhabhiḥ vṛto jagāma yatra pramadā maheśituḥ || 37 ||
avādayacchāṅkhvamirandamaṃ tadā ghaṭusvanaṃ cāpi cakāra duḥsaham ||
nanāda siṃho'pi saṭāṃ vidhūnayan babhūva nādatrayenādita nabhaḥ || 38 ||
tattoṣṭahāsaṃ jagmikākarodbhitaraṭhusrena surāryokhilāḥ ||
jaye ti śabdaṃ jagadus tadā śurā yadāmbikāvāca raṇe sthiro bhava || 39 ||
sa daityarājo mahatiṃ jvalicchalvāṃ kṣumoca śaktiṃ nihata ca solkayā ||
bibheda śūmbhapraditāñccharāñ chivā śivairitan so'pi sahasradhā śarān || 40 ||
triśūlaghaṭiṣya jaghāna caṇḍikā mahāśūraṃ taṃ sa papāta bhūchitaḥ ||
vibhinna pakṣo hariṇā yathā nagaḥ prakaṃpataṃ dyāṃ vasudhāṃ sa vārigham || 41 ||
tato mṛṣitvā triśakhodvavāṃ vyasthāṃ vidhāya bāhunatṛutaṃ yathāvalaḥ ||
sa kālikāṃ siṃhayutāṃ maheśvarīṃ jaghāna cakrairamarākṣaṃ yaikairaiḥ || 42 ||
tadṛṣṭacakrāṇi vibhidya līlayā triśūlagmuhuryaṃ jaghāna śāśurasya ||
śivājagat pāvana pāṇipa ḍujādu pātan nṛtyu paramaṃ padaṃ gataḥ || 43 ||
hate tasmin mahāvīrye niśumbe bhīmavikrame ||
śumbe ca sakalā daityā vividhuvilasmajin || 44 ||
bhakṣitā apare kālīsiṃhādyairamarādhipaiḥ ||
palāyitās tathānye ca daśadiśu bhayākulāḥ || 45 ||
bahuṣu bhaṅgervāhinyassaritaḥ svacchapathsaḥ ||
vaḍu vāntāḥ sukhaspṛśo nirmalatvaṃ yatyo nabhaḥ || 46 ||
punaryo gaḥ samāreme devairbrahmārṣibhis tathā ||
suvina śvābhavan sarve mahendādyā divaukasaḥ || 47 ||
pavitraṃ paramaṃ puṇyasumāyāścaritaṃ prabho ||
daityarājavaghopaetaṃ śraddhayā yaḥ samabhyaset || 48 ||
sa śukehākhilān bhogān bhuvidairapi durlabhān ||
paranmālatyaṃ gacchen mahāmāyāprasādataḥ || 49 ||
ṛṣaya ūcuḥ ||
evandevi saṣṭutvam śumbhāsuranibaddhinī ||
proktā sarasvatī sākṣādu māṃśāvibhevā nṛpa || 50 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāsumāsaṃhitāyāṃ niśumbhaśumbhavagho pākhyāne sarasvatīprādurbhāvavarṇanaṃ nāmāṣṭacatvāriṃśod adhyāyaḥ || 48 ||
munaya ūcuḥ ||
umāyā bhuvanešānyas suta sarvārthavittama ||
avatāraṃ samācakṣva yato jātā sarasvatī || 1 ||
yā gīyate parabrahmamūlaprakṛtirīśvarī ||
nirākārāpi sākārā nityānandamayī satī || 2 ||
sūta uvāca ||
tāpasāḥ śṛṇuta premṇā caritaṃ paramaṃ mahat ||
yasya vijñānamātreṇa naro yāti parāṃ gatiṃ || 3 ||
devadānavayorduddha mekadāsīt parasparasya ||
mahāmāyāpra bhavenāsmarāṇāṃ vijayo'bhavat || 4 ||
tato'vilatā amarāssvaprśaṃsāṃ vitenire ||
vayaṃ dhanyā vayaṃ dhanyāḥ kiṃ kariṣyanti no'śūrāḥ || 5 ||
ye prabhāvaṃ samālokya asmākaṃ paramaduḥ

--- Page 106 ---
saham ||
bhītā nāgālayaṃ yātā yātayātīti vādinaḥ || 6 ||
aho balamaho tejo daityavaṃśakṣayaṃkaram ||
aho bhāgyaṃ sumanasāmevaṃ sarveṣābhyavaṇāyam || 7 ||
tata āvirabhūttejaskūṭarūpantadeva hi ||
adṛṣṭapūvaṃ tadañjā vismitā abhavan surāḥ || 8 ||
kimidaṃ kimidaṃ ceti ruddhkaṇṭhāssamabhūvan ||
ajānantaḥ paraṃ śyāmānubhāvaṃ mānabhañjanam || 9 ||
tata ājñāpayedavān devānāmadhinayakaḥ ||
yāta yūyaṃ parīkṣadhvaṃ yāthātatthyena kiñciti || 10 ||
surendrapreroto vāyurmahāsaḥ sanniddhiṃ gataḥ ||
kastvam bhoriti sambhokṣyāvocedenaṃ ca tanmahaḥ || 11 ||
iti pṛṣṭastadiā vāyurmahāsātigarīyasā ||
vāyurasmi jagatprāṇassābhimāno'bravīddṛḍham || 12 ||
jaṅgamājaṅgamaṃ sarvaṃmotprottimadaṃ jagat ||
madhyeva nikṣiṃlāpāre cālayāmyakhilaṃ jagat || 13 ||
tadovāca mahātejāḥ śakoasi yadī cālane ||
dhṛtametacchūnaṃ vāyo cālayasva nijecchhayā || 14 ||
tataḥ sarvapratnenākarodbalaṃ sadā gatiḥ ||
na cacāla yadā sthānāttadāsau lajjito'bhavat || 15 ||
tūṣṇīṃ bhūtvā tato vāyurjagāmendrā sabhāṃ prati ||
kathayāmāsa tad vṛttaṃ svakīyābhiravān vitam || 16 ||
sarveśatvaṃ vayaṃ sarve mṛṣāvātmani manyamahe ||
na pārayāmahe kiñcidvighātuṃ kṣudravastuvapi || 17 ||
tataśca preṣayāmāsa marutvānsca kalānsurān ||
na śekuste yadā jñātuṃ tadendrāḥ svayamabhyagāt || 18 ||
maghavantamathāyāntaṃ dṛṣṭvā tejotiduḥsaham ||
babhūvāntidṛḍhaṃ sadyo vismito bhūca vāsavaḥ || 19 ||
cāritramīdṛśaṃ yasya tamevasaraṇaṃ śraye ||
iti saṃcintayāmāsa sahasrākṣaḥ punaḥpunaḥ || 20 ||
pratismannantare tatra niyojokaru nātavuḥ ||
teṣāmanu ahaṃ kattuṃ idam garvam śivāgnā || 21 ||
caitraśuklananavamyāṃ tu madhyāhrasthe divākare ||
prādurāsīdumā devī saccidānandarūpiṇī || 22 ||
mahāmadhye virājantī bhāsayantī diśo rucā ||
bodhayantī surānsarvān brahmaivāhamiti sphūṭam || 23 ||
caturbhirdevatī hasteṣvaṃ pāśāṃkuśābhayāt ||
śutiabhissevitā ramyā navatyauvanagivantā || 24 ||
raktāmbaraparīghānā raktamāsyānulepanā ||
koṭikaṃdarpasaṃkāśā candrakoṭisamaprabhā || 25 ||
vyājahāra mahāmāyā sarvāntarbhimrūpiṇī ||
sākṣiṇī sarvabhūtānāṃ parabrahmastvarorūpiṇī || 26 ||
umovāca |
na brahmā na surāritvena purāratidrīśvaraḥ ||
madagre garvitaṃ kiñcitkalā kathānyastupavaṇāt || 27 ||
paraṃ brahma paraṃ jyotiḥ praṇavatvandarūpiṇī ||
ahamevāsmi sakalaṃ madanyo nāsti kaścana || 28 ||
nirākārāpi sākārā sarvatantvasvarūpiṇī ||
apratakṣyaguṇā nityā kāryakāraṇharūpiṇī || 29 ||
kadācidṛtyitākārā kadācitpuruṣākṛtiḥ ||
kadācidubhayākārā sarvākārahameśvarī || 30 ||
virañciḥ sṛṣṭikatāheṃ jagatpātāhamaṃcyutaḥ ||
rudraḥ saṃhārakatāheṃ sarvaivāścatrimohinī || 31 ||
kālikā kamalāvāṇī kṣubhāssvā hi śakrayaḥ ||
madaṃśādeva saṃjātāstathemāḥskalāḥ kalāḥ || 32 ||
matprabhāvāṃ jitāssarve yuṣmābhirditi

--- Page 107 ---
nandanāḥ ||
tāmvijñāya sā yūyaṃ vṛthā lodeśamāninaḥ || 33 ||
yathā dārumayī yoṣā naitaytyaindrajālikaḥ ||
tathaiva sarvabhūtāni naitasmābhyahamīśvarī || 34 ||
maccayāddhāti pavanaḥ sarve dahati havyavuk ||
lokapālāḥ prakurvanti svastvakaṃ mānyānaratasya || 35 ||
kadāciddevavarṇīnāṃ kadācichiditajanmanā śu ||
karomi vijayaṃ samyaksvataṃtra nijālīlayā || 36 ||
avināśi paraṃ dhāma māyālītaṃ parātparam ||
śrutayo varṇyante yattadupantu mameva hi || 37 ||
saguṇaṃ nirguṇaṃ ceti madrūpaṃ dvividhaṃ sataḥ ||
māyāśablitatam caikaṃ dvitīyaṃ tadanāśritam || 38 ||
evaṃ vijñāya sā devāstūṣṇīm sve gatā vihāya ca ||
bhajata praṇatopetāḥ prakṛtiṃ māṃ sanātanīm || 39 ||
iti devyā vacaḥ śrutvā karuṇāgabhītaṃ surāḥ ||
tuṣṭuvuḥ parameśānīṃ śaktiṃsanatakandharāḥ || 40 ||
kṣamasva jagadīśāni prasīda parameśvari ||
maivam bhūyātkadācicno gavāṃ mātargyāṃ kuru || 41 ||
tataḥ prahṛtite devā hitā gavai samāhitāḥ ||
umāmāradhayāmāsuryathāpūrvaṃ yathāvidhi || 42 ||
iti vaḥ kathito viṣṇa umāmāhātmabheno yayā ||
yasya śravaṇamātreṇa paraṃ padmamśnute || 43 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyāsumāsaṃhitāyāṃ umāmāhātmovvarṇanaṃ nāmaikonapañcāśattamo'dhyāyaḥ || 49 ||
hṛnaya ūcuḥ ||
śrotukāmā vayaṃ sarve dugdhācāritamanvakham ||
aparaṃ ca mahāprājña tattvaṃ varṇaya noddutam || 1 ||
śṛṇvatāntavanukulābhojātakathā nānā sughopmāḥ ||
na tṛpyati mano'smākaṃ suta sarvārthevittam || 2 || ||
sūta uvāca ||
durgamaḥ prathito nāmnā rurpūtro mahābalaḥ ||
brāhmaṇo varadānena cataso'labhat śrutīḥ || 3 ||
devājeyabalaṃ cāpi saṃprāpya jagatītale ||
karoti sma bahutrāpātindīve devāśakimpaре || 4 ||
sarvo naṣṭeṣu vedeṣu kriyā naṣṭā babhūvaha ||
brāhmaṇāśca durācārā babhuñuḥ sasurāstadā || 5 ||
na dānaṃ na tapo'dhyukam na yāgo havanaṃ na hi ||
anāvṛṣṭistato jātā pṛthivyāṃ śatavārṣikī || 6 ||
hāhākāro mahāsanīṣu lokeṣu duḥkhitāḥ ||
ambāvaṃśa janāssarve kṣutpipāsyā pīḍitā bhuśa || 7 ||
saritaḥ sāgarāścaiva vāpīkūpasarāṃsiśca ||
nirjalā abhavansarve saṃśuṣkā vṛkṣavīrudhāḥ || 8 ||
tato hṛṣṭā mahāduḥkhaṃ prajānāṃ dīnacetasām ||
viśvāśaśaraṇaṃ yātā yogamāyāṃ maheśvarīm || 9 ||
devā ūcuḥ ||
rakṣa rakṣa mahāmāye svakīyāssakalāḥ prajāḥ ||
kopaṃ saṃhara tṛṇantvaṃ lokā naśyanti cānyathā || 10 ||
yathā śumbho hato daityyo niśumbhaśca mahābalaḥ ||
ghrāṇakṣaṇḍamuṇḍau ca raktavījo mahābalaḥ || 11 ||
sa madhuḥ kaiṭabho daityyo mahiṣāsura eva ca ||
tathaivāsmaṃ kṛpāsindhau dīnabandho jahi drutam || 12 ||
aparādho bhavateva bālakānāṃ pade pade ||
sahate ko jano loke kevalaṃ mātaraṃ vinā || 13 ||
yadā yadābhavduḥkhaṃ devānāṃ brahmaṇāṃ tathā ||
tadā tadāvatīryāśu kuruṣe sukhino janān || 14 ||
iti vikṣitaṃ teṣāṃ samākarṇya kṛpāmayī ||
anantākṣamayaṃ rūpaṃ darśayāmāsa

--- Page 108 ---
sāmpratam || 15 ||
dhanurbāṇau tathā padmaṃ nānāmūlaphalāni ca ||
caturbhirdaṃṣṭhati hastaiḥ prasannamukhapaṅkajā || 16 ||
tato dṛṣṭvā prajāstanāḥ karuṇāpūritekṣaṇā |
ruroda nava ghaṇṭāni nava rātriṣsamākulā || 17 ||
mocayāmāsa diṣṭibhyo vārigharāḥ sahasraśaḥ ||
tābhiḥ pratipitā lokā auṣadhyaḥ sakalā api || 18 ||
agāghatoyāssārito babhūvuḥ sāgarā api ||
ruruhugharaṇīpṛṣṭhe śākamūlaphalāni ca || 19 ||
vittatāra karasthāni sumanobhyaḥ phalāni ca ||
gobhyastṛṇāni ramyāṇi tathānyebhyo yathārhataḥ || 20 ||
santuṣṭā abhavansarve sadevadvijamantuṣāḥ ||
tato jagāda sā devī kimanvatkarvāṇi vaḥ || 21 ||
samṛtyocuḥtadā devā bhavatyā toṣitā janāḥ ||
vedāndehiḥ kṛpāṃ kṛtvā durgameṇa samāhṛtān || 22 ||
tathāstiviti prabhāṣyāha yātayāt nijālayam ||
vitariṣyāmi vo vedānācaraṇaiva kālataḥ || 23 ||
tataḥ pramuditā devāssvam svam dhāma samāyayuḥ ||
supraṇamya jagdhoniṃ phuṭhendīvaralocanaṃ || 24 ||
tataḥ kolāhalo jāto diviṃ bhuvanatarikṣake ||
tacchutvā rauravḥ sadyo nyaruṇatsarvataḥ purīm || 25 ||
tataste jāmitham cakaṃ vidhāya paritaḥ śivā ||
rakṣaṇārtham devatānāṃ svayam tasmāddhigantā || 26 ||
tataḥ samambhavacchudraṃ devyā daityasya cobhayoḥ ||
vavṛṣuḥ samare bāṇāgniśatānke ḍūṭacchidaḥ || 27 ||
etasminantare tasyāḥ śarīrādravyamūrtayaḥ ||
kālī tārā cchinnnamastā śrīvidyā bhuvanešvarī || 28 ||
bhairavī bagalā ghūṣā śrīmahātripurasundarī ||
mātaṅgī ca mahāvidyā nirgītā daśa sāyudhāḥ || 29 ||
asaṃkhyātāstato jātā mātaro divyamūrtayaḥ ||
candralekābhagharāssvośruvāṃ vidyutsaṃprabhāḥ || 30 ||
tato mātṛgaṇeśuddhaṃ prāvartata bhayaṃkaram ||
rauravīyam itantāmibhardalamakaśauriṇiśatam || 31 ||
jaghāna sā tadā daityam durgaṃ śūladhārayā ||
papāta dharaṇīpṛṣṭhe khātamūladrumo yathā || 32 ||
itthaṃ hatvā tadā daityam durgamāsuranaṃmakam ||
ādāya caturo vedāndadau devebhya īśvarī || 33 ||
devā ūcuḥ || ||
asmadartham tvayā rūpamananttākṣimayam ghṛtam ||
munayaḥ kīrtayiṣyanti śatākṣīntvāmato'mbike || 34 ||
ātmadehasaṃbhūtaiḥ śākailonkābhṛtā yataḥ ||
śākaṃbharīti vikhyātantatte nāma bhaviṣyati || 35 ||
durgamākhyo mahādaityo hato yasmātataḥ śive ||
durgā bhagavatī bhadrāṃ vyāhariṣyanti mānavāḥ || 36 ||
yoganidrē namastubhyam namaste'stu mahābale ||
namo jñānaprade tubhyam viśvamātre namo namaḥ || 37 ||
tattvamasyādivākyaināṃ bodhyate parameśvarī ||
anantakoṭibrahmaṇḍanāyikāyai namo namaḥ || 38 ||
vāṅmanaskāyaduṣpāpāṃ suryacandragnilocanāṃ ||
stotum na śaknumo mātastvatpramābhāvābhugha vayam || 39 ||
māhāśānamarāndṛṣṭā kaḥ kuryādīdṛśīndayām ||
varjayitvā śureśānīṃ śatākṣīṃ mātaraṃ vinā || 40 ||
trilokī nābhiṣūyet bādhābhiśca nirantaram ||
evaṃ kāryestavayyā yatno'smākaṃ vairināśanam || 41 ||
devyuvāca || ||
vatsāndṛṣṭā

--- Page 109 ---
yathā gāvo vyagrā dhāvanti satvaram ||
tathāiva bhavato dṛṣṭā dhāvāmi vyākulā satī || 42 ||
mama yuṣmānapaśyantyāḥ paśyantyā bālakāniva ||
api prāṇānprayacchantyas tāḥ kṣaṇam eko yugāyate || 43 ||
kāpi cintā na kartavyā yuṣmābhirbhaktiśālinibhiḥ ||
bhavatīṃ mayi tiṣṭhantyāṃ saṃcarantyāṃ nijapadaḥ || 44 ||
yathā pūrvam itā daityā haniṣyāmi tathāsurān ||
saṃśayo nātra kartavyaḥ satyaṃ satyaṃ bravīmyaham || 45 ||
yadā śumbho niśumbhaśca parau daityau bhaviṣyataḥ ||
tadāhaṃ nandabhāryāyāṃ yaśodāyāṃ yaśomayī || 46 ||
yoginaṃ rūpamāsthāya jamiṣye gopagokule ||
haniṣyāmi paśtrau tanmān vyāhariṣyanti nandajām || 47 ||
āmāraṃ rūpamāsthāya vadhiṣyāmyaruṇaṃ yataḥ ||
āmareṇa iti ca māṃ loke kīrtayiṣyanti mānavāḥ || 48 ||
kṛtvā bhīmaṃ punaḥ rūpaṃ rakṣāṃsyatasyāmyaham yadā ||
bhīmā devīti vikhyātaṃ tanme nāma bhaviṣyati || 49 ||
yadāyadāḍurothaiva bādhā bhuvi bhaviṣyati ||
tadā tadāvatīyohaṃ śaṃkariṣyāmysaṃśayam || 50 ||
yā śāntākṣī smṛtā devī sā eva śākambharī matā ||
sā eva prakīrtitā durgā vyaktirekaiva triṣvapi || 51 ||
na śāntākṣīsamā kācicchadyācchrubhuvi devatā ||
dṛṣṭā rudraprajāstas tā yā navāhaṃ maheśvarī || 52 ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe paścamyāmumāsaṃhitāyāṃ śatākṣīyavatāravarṇanaṃ nāma pañcāśattamo'dhyāyaḥ || 50 ||
munaya ūcuḥ |
||
vyāsaśiṣya mahābhāga sūta paurāṇikottama ||
aparaṃ śrotumicchāmaḥ kramapaṃkhyānmīśituḥ || 1 ||
umāyā jagadbhāyāḥ kriyāyogamuttamam ||
proktaṃ sanatkumāreṇa vyāsāya ca mahātmane || 2 ||
sūta uvāca |
||
dhanya yuṃ mahātmāno devībhaktadḍhavratāḥ ||
parāśakteḥ paraṃ śubhaṃ rahasyaṃ śṛṇutādarat || 3 ||
vyāsa uvāca |
||
sanatkumāra sarvajña brahmaputra mahāmate ||
umāyāḥ śrotumicchāmi kriyāyogaṃ mahādbhutam || 4 ||
kīdṛkca lakṣaṇaṃ tasya kiṃ kurute ca phalaṃ bhavet ||
priyaṃ yacca parāmbhāyāstadaśeṣaṃ vadасва me || 5 ||
sanatkumāra uvāca |
||
dvepāyana yadatattvaṃ rahasyaṃ paripṛcchasi ||
tacchṛṇuṣva mahābuddhe sarvaṃ me varṇayiṣyataḥ || 6 ||
jñānayogaḥ kriyāyogo bhaktiyogastathāiva ca ||
trayaḥ mārgāḥ samākhyātāḥ śrīmātṛbhuktimuktipraddāḥ || 7 ||
jñānayogastu saṃyogaścittasya evātmanā tu yaḥ ||
yastu bāhyārthesaṃyogaḥ kriyāyoga sa ucyate || 8 ||
bhaktiyogo mato devyā ātmanaścaikyabhāvanam ||
trayāṇāmapi yogānāṃ kriyāyogasya ucyate || 9 ||
karmaṇā jāyate bhaktiḥ bhaktyā jñānaṃ prajāyate ||
jñānātprajāyate muktiriti śāstreṣu niścayaḥ || 10 ||
pradhānaṃ kāraṇaṃ yogo viṣṇukteṣu niśattam ||
kriyāyogastu yogasya paramandhyeyasādhanam || 11 ||
māyantu prakṛtiṃ vidyānmāyāvī brahma śāśvatam ||
abhītraṃ tadbudhyaitvā

---

¹ janā iti śeṣaḥ |
--- Page 110 ---
mucyate bhavabandhanāt || 12 ||
yastu devyālayaṃ kuryātpāṣāṇadāravantathā ||
mṛṇmayaṃ vātha kāleya tasya puṇyaphalaṃ śṛṇu ||
aharnyahāni yogena yajato yanmahāphalam || 13 ||
prāpnoti tatphalandevyā yaḥ kārayati mandiram ||
sahasrakulamāgāmi vyatītaṃ ca sahasrakam ||
sa tārayati dharmātmā śrīmāturghaṃ kārayan || 14 ||
koṭijanmakṛtaṃ pāpaṃ svarupaṃ vā yadi vā bahu ||
śrīmāturmandirarambhakṣaṇādeva praṇaśyati || 15 ||
nadīṣu ca yathā gaṅgā śoṇaḥ sarvanadeṣu ca ||
kṣamāyāṃ ca yathā pṛthvī gāmbhīryeṃ ca yathodadhiḥ || 16 ||
brāhmaṇāṃ ca samastānāṃ yathā sūryyo viśiṣyate ||
tathā sarveṣu deveṣu śrīpārambhā viśiṣyate || 17 ||
sarvandeveṣu sā mukhyā yastasyāḥ kāryedgṛham ||
pratiṣṭhāṃ samavāpnoti sa ca janmani janmani || 18 ||
vārāṇasyāṃ kurukṣetre prayāge puṣkare tathā ||
gaṅgāsamudratīre ca naimiṣeṣamarakaṇṭake || 19 ||
śrīparvate mahāpuṇye gokarṇe jñānapāvane ||
mathurāyāmayodhyāyāṃ dvāravātyāṃ tathaiva ca || 20 ||
ityādiputānyadeśeṣu yatra kutra sthaleṣvapi vā ||
kārayanmāturāvāsaṃ mukto bhavati bandhānāt || 21 ||
iṣṭakānāṃ tu vinyāso yāvadvarṣāṇi tiṣṭhati ||
tāvadvarṣasahasrāṇi māṇḍīpe mahīyate || 22 ||
pratimāḥ kārayedyastu sarvalaṣaṇalaśitāḥ ||
sa umāyāḥ paraṃ lokaṃ nirjayo vrajati dhruvam || 23 ||
devīśrutīṃ pratiṣṭhāpya śubhatīrthamahātārake ||
kṛtakṛtyo bhavenmartyaḥ yogamāyāprasādataḥ || 24 ||
ye bhaviṣyanti yeṣṭītā ākalpatpuruṣāḥ kule ||
tāṃstāṃstārayate devyā mūrtiṃ saṃsthāpya śobhanām || 25 ||
trilokīsthāpanātpuṇyaṃ yadrbhavenmunipuṅgava ||
tatkoṭiguṇitaṃ puṇyaṃ śrīdevīsthāpanādrbhavet || 26 ||
madhye devīṃ sthāpayitvā paścāyatanadevatāḥ ||
caturdiśeṣu sthāpayedyastasya puṇyaṃ na gaṇyate || 27 ||
viṣṇonāmāṃ koṭijapādbbhaṇe candrasūryayoḥ ||
yatphalaṃ labhyate tasmācchatakoṭiguṇottaram || 28 ||
śivanāmno japādeva tasmātkoṭiguṇottaram ||
śrīdevīnāmajapātu tataḥ koṭiguṇottaram || 29 ||
devyāḥ prāsādakaraṇātpuṇyantau samavāpyate ||
sthāpitāyena sā devī jaganmātā trayīmayī || 30 ||
na tasya durlabhaṃ kiñcicchrīmātuḥ karuṇāvaśāt ||
vardhante putrapautrādyā naśyantyakhilakalamaḥ || 31 ||
manasā ye cikīrṣanti mūrtisthāpanasutamam ||
teṣyumāṃyāḥ paraṃ lokaṃ prayānti durniduralbhaṃam || 32 ||
kriyamāṇantu yaḥ prekṣya cetasā dhanucintayat ||
kāriṣyāmyadhaṃ yāhīṃ saṃpanme saṃbhaviṣyati || 33 ||
evantasya kulaṃ sadyo yāti svarge na saṃśayaḥ ||
mahāmāyāprabhāveṇa durlabhaṃ kiṃ jagattarye || 34 ||
śrīpārambhāṃ jagadyoniṃ kevalaṃ ye samāśritāḥ ||
te manuṣyā na manteṣyassāṣādevīgaṇāśca te || 35 ||
ye vrajantaḥ svapantaśca tiṣṭhanto vāpyahrniśam ||
umeti dviakṣaraṃ nāma bruvate te śivagaṇāḥ || 36 ||
nitye naimittike

--- Page 111 ---
devīṃ ye yajanti parāṃ śivām ||
puṣpaiḥ dhūpaiḥ tathā dīpaiḥ te prayāsyanti umālayam || 37 ||
ye devīmaṇḍapaṃ nityaṃ gomayena smṛdāya vā ||
upalimpanti mārjanti te prayāsyanti umālayam || 38 ||
ye devyā mandiraṃ ramyaṃ nimāpitam uttamam ||
tatkuLīnāñjanānmātā jhāśiṣaḥ saṃprayacchati || || 39 ||
madīyāḥ śatavaṛṣiṇo jīvantu premabhāgjjanāḥ ||
nāpadāmyanānītthaṃ śrīmātā vaktyahinīśam || 40 ||
yena mūrtiṃ mahādevyā umāyāḥ kāritā śubhā ||
narāśutantatkulajaṃ maṇiḍīpe mahīyate || 41 ||
sthāpayitvā mahāmāyāmūrtiṃ samyakpūjya ca ||
yaṃ yaṃ prārthayate kāmaṃ tantaṃ prāpnoti sādhakaḥ || 42 ||
yaḥ snāpayati śrīmātuḥ sthāpitāṃ mūrtiṃ uttamām ||
ghṛtena madhuanāktena tatphalaṃ gaṇayetu kaḥ || 43 ||
candanāgurukaṃkumāṃsīṣṭustaṃ divyuṃ jalaiḥ ||
ekavarṇagavāṃ kṣīreḥ snāpayetparamemśvarīm || 44 ||
ghūpenāṣṭādaśāṅgena dadyādāhūtiṃ uttamām ||
nīrājanaṃ careddinyāsasājyakaṃdhūpravartibhiḥ || || 45 ||
kṛṣṇāṣṭamyāṃ navamyāṃ vāmāyāṃ vā pañcadikītthaḥ ||
pūjayejjagatāṃ dhātrīṃ gandhaṃ puṣpaiḥ viśeṣataḥ || 46 ||
saṃpaṭhannī sūktaṃ śrīsūktamatha vā paṭhan ||
devī sūktamatha vāpi mūlamantramathāpi vā || 47 ||
viṣṇukāntāṃ ca tulasīṃ varjayitvā akhilaṃ sumam ||
devīprītikaraṃ jñeyaṃ kamalanttu viśeṣataḥ || 48 ||
arpayetsvagaṇapuṣpaṃ yo devyai rājatameva vā ||
sa yāti paramaṃ dhāma siddhakoṭibhirañvitam || 49 ||
pūjanānte sadā kārye dāsereṇaḥ kṣamāpaṇam ||
prasīdaṃ parameśāni jagadānandadāyini || 50 ||
iti vākyaiḥ stuvanmantrī devībhaktiparāyaṇaḥ ||
dhyāyetkaṇṭhīrvāḍhāṃ varadābhayapāṇikām || 51 ||
itthaṃ dhyātvā maheśānīṃ bhaktābhīṣṭaphalapradām ||
nānāphalāni pakvāni naiveddye prakalpayet || 52 ||
naiveddyaṃ bhakṣayedyastu śaṃśuśakteḥ parātmanaḥ ||
sa nirddhyākhilaṃ pāpaṃ nirmalo mānavvo bhavet || 53 ||
caitraśuklatṛtīyāyāṃ yo bhavānīvrataṃ caret ||
bhavabandhaniniḥśuktaḥ prāpnuyātparamapadam || 54 ||
asyāmeva tṛtīyāyāṃ kuyāndolotsavaṃ budhaḥ ||
pūjayejjagatāṃ mātrīśmāṃ śaṃkarasaṃyutām || 55 ||
kusumaiḥ kuṃkumaiḥ śreṣṭhaiḥ kaṣṭurāgurucandinaiḥ ||
dhūpaiḥ dīpaiḥ sanaiveddyaiḥ kṣamagaṃdhairparairapi || 56 ||
āndolayettato devīṃ mahāmāyāṃ maheśvarīm ||
śrīgaurīṃ śivasaṃyuktāṃ sarvakalyāṇakāriṇīm || 57 ||
pratyabdaṃ kurute yoṣyāṃ vrataṃ āndolanaṃ tathā ||
niyamena śivā tasmai sarvamiṣṭaṃ prayacchati || 58 ||
mādhvasya site pakṣe tṛtīyā yāṃ śākṣyābhigā ||
tasyāṃ yo jagadambāyā vrataṃ kuryādatinirddhutaḥ || 59 ||
mahlikāmālatīcampājapabandhūkapañkajaiḥ ||
kusumaiḥ pūjayet devīṃ śaṃkareṇa samanvitām || 60 ||
koṭijjanmakṛtaṃ pāpaṃ manovākkāyasambhavam ||
nirddhūya caturo vargānkṣayāniha soāśnute || 61 ||
jyeṣṭhaśuklatṛtīyāyāṃ vrataṃ kṛtvā maheśvarīm ||
yoāśnīyetparamapritāyā tasyāsāddhyaṃ na kiñcana || 62 ||
āṣāḍhaśuklapañcamyadvitīyāyāṃ ryotsavam ||
devyāḥ priyatamaṃ kuryāt

--- Page 112 ---
thāvittātusārataḥ || 63 ||
rathaṃ pṛthvīṃ vijānīyādrathaṅge candrabhāskarau ||
vedānśvānnvijānīyātsārathaṃ pañcasaṃbhavam || 64 ||
nānāmaṇigaṇākīrṇaṃ puṣpamālāvirājitam ||
evaṃ rathaṃ kalpayitvā tasminnsaṃsthāpayecchivām || 65 ||
lokasaṃrakṣaṇārthāya lokaṃ draṣṭuṃ parāmbikā ||
rathāmadhye saṃsthitetibhāvayennmitamānaraḥ || 66 ||
rathe pracalite mandan jayaśabdamuddīrayet ||
pāhi devi janānasmānprapannāndīnavatsale || 67 ||
iti vākyaistatuṣyecca nānāvāditranisvanaīḥ ||
sīmānte tu rathaṃ nītvā tatra saṃpūjayedṛthā || 68 ||
nānāstotraistatastutvapy ānayet tāṃ svaveśmani ||
praṇipātaśataṃ kṛtvā prārthayejja gadambikām || 69 ||
evaṃ yaḥ kurute vidvānpūjāvrataṃthotsavam ||
iha sukhākhilānbhogānsonte devīpadaṃ vrajet || 70 ||
śuklāyantu tṛtīyāyāmevaṃ śrāvaṇabhādrayoḥ ||
yo vrataṃ kurute'mbāyāḥ pūjanaṃ ca yathāvidhi || 71 ||
modate putrapautrādyairdhannādyairiha santataṃ ||
so'nte gacchedumāloke sarvalokopariṣṭhitam || 72 ||
āśvine śukle pakṣe navarātravrataṃ caret ||
yatkurute saṃkalāḥ kāmānsiddhacantyeva na saṃśayaḥ || 73 ||
navarātravratasya asya prabhāvaṃ vaktumiśvaraḥ ||
caturāsyo na pañcāsyo na ṣaḍāsyo nako'paraḥ || 74 ||
navarātravrataṃ kṛtvā bhūpālo viratātmajaḥ ||
hataṃ rājyaṃ nijaṃ lebhe surathā munisattamāḥ || 75 ||
dhruvasiṃhakṣuto dhīmānayodhyādhipatirnṛpaḥ ||
sudaśano hataṃ rājyaṃ prāpadantyapra bhāvataḥ || 76 ||
vratarajimīmam kṛtvā samārādhya maheśvarīm ||
saṃsārabandhānānnmuktaḥ samādhiṣṭhānikā bhabhūt || 77 ||
tṛtīyāyāṃ ca pañcamyāṃ saptamyāmaṣṭamītithau ||
navamyāṃ vā caturdaśyāṃ yo devīṃ pūjayedvraraḥ || 78 ||
āśvinasya site pakṣe vrataṃ kṛtvā vidhānataḥ ||
tasya sarvemanobbīṣṭaṃ pūrayatyaniśaṃ śivā || 79 ||
yaḥ kārttikasya mārgasya pauṣasya tapasastathā ||
tapasyasya site pakṣe tṛtīyāyāṃ vrataṃ caret || 80 ||
lohitaiḥ karavīrādyaiḥ puṣpairdhūpairsugandhitaiḥ ||
pūjayennmaṅgalāndevīṃ sa sarvaṃ maṅgalaṃ labhet || 81 ||
saubhāgyāya sadā śrībhiḥ kāvyametanmahāvratam ||
vidhyāghnaśrutāpyarthaṃ vigheyyaṃ puruṣairapi || 82 ||
umāmaheśvarādīnnr̥ vrataanyanyāni yānyapi ||
devīpriyāṇi kāryāṇi svabhaktayaivaṃ mumukṣubhiḥ || 83 ||
saṃhiteyaṃ mahāpuṇyā śivabhaktivivardhinī ||
nānākhyānanasamāyuktā muktibhuktipradā śivā || 84 ||
ya enāṃ śṛṇuyādṛttayā śrāvayedvā samāhitaḥ ||
paṭhedvā pāṭhayedvāpi sa yāti paramāṃ gatim || 85 ||
yasya gehe sthitā ceyaṃ likhitā lalitākṣaraiḥ ||
saṃpūjitā ca vidhivatsarvānkāmānsa āpnuyāt || 86 ||
bhūtapretapiśācādidduṣṭebhyo na bhayaṃ kvacit ||
putrapautrādisampattilbhansatyeva na saṃśayaḥ || 87 ||
tasmādiyaṃ mahāpuṇyā raśyomāsaṃhitā sadā ||
śrotavyā paṭhitavyā ca śivabhaktimabhīpsubhiḥ || 88 || ||
iti śrīśivamahāpurāṇe pañcamyumāsaṃhitāyāṃ kriyāyoginirūpaṇaṃ nāmaikāpañcāśatamo'dhyāyaḥ || 51 || ||
samāpteyaṃ pañcamyumāsaṃhitā ||
